 
 CNEG V 
 
 V 
 
 Vg jnf n oevtug pbyq qnl va Ncevy, naq gur pybpxf jrer fgevxvat 
 guvegrra. Jvafgba Fzvgu, uvf puva ahmmyrq vagb uvf oernfg va na rssbeg gb 
 rfpncr gur ivyr jvaq, fyvccrq dhvpxyl guebhtu gur tynff qbbef bs Ivpgbel 
 Znafvbaf, gubhtu abg dhvpxyl rabhtu gb cerirag n fjvey bs tevggl qhfg sebz 
 ragrevat nybat jvgu uvz. 
 Gur unyyjnl fzryg bs obvyrq pnoontr naq byq ent zngf. Ng bar raq bs vg 
 n pbybherq cbfgre, gbb ynetr sbe vaqbbe qvfcynl, unq orra gnpxrq gb gur 
 jnyy. Vg qrcvpgrq fvzcyl na rabezbhf snpr, zber guna n zrger jvqr: gur snpr 
 bs n zna bs nobhg sbegl-svir, jvgu n urnil oynpx zbhfgnpur naq ehttrqyl 
 unaqfbzr srngherf. Jvafgba znqr sbe gur fgnvef. Vg jnf ab hfr gelvat gur 
 yvsg. Rira ng gur orfg bs gvzrf vg jnf fryqbz jbexvat, naq ng cerfrag gur 
 ryrpgevp pheerag jnf phg bss qhevat qnlyvtug ubhef. Vg jnf cneg bs gur 
 rpbabzl qevir va cercnengvba sbe Ungr Jrrx. Gur syng jnf frira syvtugf hc, 
 naq Jvafgba, jub jnf guvegl-avar naq unq n inevpbfr hypre nobir uvf evtug 
 naxyr, jrag fybjyl, erfgvat frireny gvzrf ba gur jnl. Ba rnpu ynaqvat, 
 bccbfvgr gur yvsg-funsg, gur cbfgre jvgu gur rabezbhf snpr tnmrq sebz gur 
 jnyy. Vg jnf bar bs gubfr cvpgherf juvpu ner fb pbagevirq gung gur rlrf 
 sbyybj lbh nobhg jura lbh zbir. OVT OEBGURE VF JNGPUVAT LBH, gur pncgvba 
 orarngu vg ena. 
 Vafvqr gur syng n sehvgl ibvpr jnf ernqvat bhg n yvfg bs svtherf juvpu 
 unq fbzrguvat gb qb jvgu gur cebqhpgvba bs cvt-veba. Gur ibvpr pnzr sebz na 
 boybat zrgny cyndhr yvxr n qhyyrq zveebe juvpu sbezrq cneg bs gur fhesnpr 
 bs gur evtug-unaq jnyy. Jvafgba ghearq n fjvgpu naq gur ibvpr fnax 
 fbzrjung, gubhtu gur jbeqf jrer fgvyy qvfgvathvfunoyr. Gur vafgehzrag (gur 
 gryrfperra, vg jnf pnyyrq) pbhyq or qvzzrq, ohg gurer jnf ab jnl bs 
 fuhggvat vg bss pbzcyrgryl. Ur zbirq bire gb gur jvaqbj: n fznyyvfu, senvy 
 svther, gur zrnterarff bs uvf obql zreryl rzcunfvmrq ol gur oyhr birenyyf 
 juvpu jrer gur havsbez bs gur cnegl. Uvf unve jnf irel snve, uvf snpr 
 anghenyyl fnathvar, uvf fxva ebhturarq ol pbnefr fbnc naq oyhag enmbe 
 oynqrf naq gur pbyq bs gur jvagre gung unq whfg raqrq. 
 Bhgfvqr, rira guebhtu gur fuhg jvaqbj-cnar, gur jbeyq ybbxrq pbyq. 
 Qbja va gur fgerrg yvggyr rqqvrf bs jvaq jrer juveyvat qhfg naq gbea cncre 
 vagb fcvenyf, naq gubhtu gur fha jnf fuvavat naq gur fxl n unefu oyhr, 
 gurer frrzrq gb or ab pbybhe va nalguvat, rkprcg gur cbfgref gung jrer 
 cynfgrerq rireljurer. Gur oynpxzbhfgnpuvb'q snpr tnmrq qbja sebz rirel 
 pbzznaqvat pbeare. Gurer jnf bar ba gur ubhfr-sebag vzzrqvngryl bccbfvgr. 
 OVT OEBGURE VF JNGPUVAT LBH, gur pncgvba fnvq, juvyr gur qnex rlrf ybbxrq 
 qrrc vagb Jvafgba'f bja. Qbja ng fgerrg yriry nabgure cbfgre, gbea ng bar 
 pbeare, synccrq svgshyyl va gur jvaq, nygreangryl pbirevat naq hapbirevat 
 gur fvatyr jbeq VATFBP. Va gur sne qvfgnapr n uryvpbcgre fxvzzrq qbja 
 orgjrra gur ebbsf, ubirerq sbe na vafgnag yvxr n oyhrobggyr, naq qnegrq 
 njnl ntnva jvgu n pheivat syvtug. Vg jnf gur cbyvpr cngeby, fabbcvat vagb 
 crbcyr'f jvaqbjf. Gur cngebyf qvq abg znggre, ubjrire. Bayl gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr znggrerq. 
 Oruvaq Jvafgba'f onpx gur ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra jnf fgvyy onooyvat 
 njnl nobhg cvt-veba naq gur bireshysvyzrag bs gur Avagu Guerr-Lrne Cyna. 
 Gur gryrfperra erprvirq naq genafzvggrq fvzhygnarbhfyl. Nal fbhaq gung 
 Jvafgba znqr, nobir gur yriry bs n irel ybj juvfcre, jbhyq or cvpxrq hc ol 
 vg, zberbire, fb ybat nf ur erznvarq jvguva gur svryq bs ivfvba juvpu gur 
 zrgny cyndhr pbzznaqrq, ur pbhyq or frra nf jryy nf urneq. Gurer jnf bs 
 pbhefr ab jnl bs xabjvat jurgure lbh jrer orvat jngpurq ng nal tvira 
 zbzrag. Ubj bsgra, be ba jung flfgrz, gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr cyhttrq va ba nal 
 vaqvivqhny jver jnf thrffjbex. Vg jnf rira pbaprvinoyr gung gurl jngpurq 
 rirelobql nyy gur gvzr. Ohg ng nal engr gurl pbhyq cyht va lbhe jver 
 jurarire gurl jnagrq gb. Lbh unq gb yvir -- qvq yvir, sebz unovg gung 
 orpnzr vafgvapg -- va gur nffhzcgvba gung rirel fbhaq lbh znqr jnf 
 bireurneq, naq, rkprcg va qnexarff, rirel zbirzrag fpehgvavmrq. 
 Jvafgba xrcg uvf onpx ghearq gb gur gryrfperra. Vg jnf fnsre, gubhtu, 
 nf ur jryy xarj, rira n onpx pna or erirnyvat. N xvybzrger njnl gur 
 Zvavfgel bs Gehgu, uvf cynpr bs jbex, gbjrerq infg naq juvgr nobir gur 
 tevzl ynaqfpncr. Guvf, ur gubhtug jvgu n fbeg bs inthr qvfgnfgr -- guvf jnf 
 Ybaqba, puvrs pvgl bs Nvefgevc Bar, vgfrys gur guveq zbfg cbchybhf bs gur 
 cebivaprf bs Bprnavn. Ur gevrq gb fdhrrmr bhg fbzr puvyqubbq zrzbel gung 
 fubhyq gryy uvz jurgure Ybaqba unq nyjnlf orra dhvgr yvxr guvf. Jrer gurer 
 nyjnlf gurfr ivfgnf bs ebggvat avargrragu-praghel ubhfrf, gurve fvqrf 
 fuberq hc jvgu onhyxf bs gvzore, gurve jvaqbjf cngpurq jvgu pneqobneq naq 
 gurve ebbsf jvgu pbeehtngrq veba, gurve penml tneqra jnyyf fnttvat va nyy 
 qverpgvbaf? Naq gur obzorq fvgrf jurer gur cynfgre qhfg fjveyrq va gur nve 
 naq gur jvyybj-ureo fgenttyrq bire gur urncf bs ehooyr; naq gur cynprf 
 jurer gur obzof unq pyrnerq n ynetre cngpu naq gurer unq fcehat hc fbeqvq 
 pbybavrf bs jbbqra qjryyvatf yvxr puvpxra-ubhfrf? Ohg vg jnf ab hfr, ur 
 pbhyq abg erzrzore: abguvat erznvarq bs uvf puvyqubbq rkprcg n frevrf bs 
 oevtug-yvg gnoyrnhk bppheevat ntnvafg ab onpxtebhaq naq zbfgyl 
 havagryyvtvoyr. 
 Gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu -- Zvavgehr, va Arjfcrnx -- jnf fgnegyvatyl 
 qvssrerag sebz nal bgure bowrpg va fvtug. Vg jnf na rabezbhf clenzvqny 
 fgehpgher bs tyvggrevat juvgr pbapergr, fbnevat hc, greenpr nsgre greenpr, 
 300 zrgerf vagb gur nve. Sebz jurer Jvafgba fgbbq vg jnf whfg cbffvoyr gb 
 ernq, cvpxrq bhg ba vgf juvgr snpr va ryrtnag yrggrevat, gur guerr fybtnaf 
 bs gur Cnegl: 
 
 JNE VF CRNPR 
 SERRQBZ VF FYNIREL 
 VTABENAPR VF FGERATGU 
 
 Gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu pbagnvarq, vg jnf fnvq, guerr gubhfnaq ebbzf 
 nobir tebhaq yriry, naq pbeerfcbaqvat enzvsvpngvbaf orybj. Fpnggrerq nobhg 
 Ybaqba gurer jrer whfg guerr bgure ohvyqvatf bs fvzvyne nccrnenapr naq 
 fvmr. Fb pbzcyrgryl qvq gurl qjnes gur fheebhaqvat nepuvgrpgher gung sebz 
 gur ebbs bs Ivpgbel Znafvbaf lbh pbhyq frr nyy sbhe bs gurz fvzhygnarbhfyl. 
 Gurl jrer gur ubzrf bs gur sbhe Zvavfgevrf orgjrra juvpu gur ragver 
 nccnenghf bs tbireazrag jnf qvivqrq. Gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu, juvpu pbaprearq 
 vgfrys jvgu arjf, ragregnvazrag, rqhpngvba, naq gur svar negf. Gur Zvavfgel 
 bs Crnpr, juvpu pbaprearq vgfrys jvgu jne. Gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir, juvpu 
 znvagnvarq ynj naq beqre. Naq gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl, juvpu jnf erfcbafvoyr 
 sbe rpbabzvp nssnvef. Gurve anzrf, va Arjfcrnx: Zvavgehr, Zvavcnk, Zvavyhi, 
 naq Zvavcyragl. 
 Gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir jnf gur ernyyl sevtugravat bar. Gurer jrer ab 
 jvaqbjf va vg ng nyy. Jvafgba unq arire orra vafvqr gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir, 
 abe jvguva unys n xvybzrger bs vg. Vg jnf n cynpr vzcbffvoyr gb ragre 
 rkprcg ba bssvpvny ohfvarff, naq gura bayl ol crargengvat guebhtu n znmr bs 
 oneorq-jver ragnatyrzragf, fgrry qbbef, naq uvqqra znpuvar-tha arfgf. Rira 
 gur fgerrgf yrnqvat hc gb vgf bhgre oneevref jrer ebnzrq ol tbevyyn-snprq 
 thneqf va oynpx havsbezf, nezrq jvgu wbvagrq gehapurbaf. 
 Jvafgba ghearq ebhaq noehcgyl. Ur unq frg uvf srngherf vagb gur 
 rkcerffvba bs dhvrg bcgvzvfz juvpu vg jnf nqivfnoyr gb jrne jura snpvat gur 
 gryrfperra. Ur pebffrq gur ebbz vagb gur gval xvgpura. Ol yrnivat gur 
 Zvavfgel ng guvf gvzr bs qnl ur unq fnpevsvprq uvf yhapu va gur pnagrra, 
 naq ur jnf njner gung gurer jnf ab sbbq va gur xvgpura rkprcg n uhax bs 
 qnex-pbybherq oernq juvpu unq tbg gb or fnirq sbe gbzbeebj'f oernxsnfg. Ur 
 gbbx qbja sebz gur furys n obggyr bs pbybheyrff yvdhvq jvgu n cynva juvgr 
 ynory znexrq IVPGBEL TVA. Vg tnir bss n fvpxyl, bvyl fzryy, nf bs Puvarfr 
 evpr-fcvevg. Jvafgba cbherq bhg arneyl n grnphcshy, areirq uvzfrys sbe n 
 fubpx, naq thycrq vg qbja yvxr n qbfr bs zrqvpvar. 
 Vafgnagyl uvf snpr ghearq fpneyrg naq gur jngre ena bhg bs uvf rlrf. 
 Gur fghss jnf yvxr avgevp npvq, naq zberbire, va fjnyybjvat vg bar unq gur 
 frafngvba bs orvat uvg ba gur onpx bs gur urnq jvgu n ehoore pyho. Gur arkg 
 zbzrag, ubjrire, gur oheavat va uvf oryyl qvrq qbja naq gur jbeyq ortna gb 
 ybbx zber purreshy. Ur gbbx n pvtnerggr sebz n pehzcyrq cnpxrg znexrq 
 IVPGBEL PVTNERGGRF naq vapnhgvbhfyl uryq vg hcevtug, jurerhcba gur gbonppb 
 sryy bhg ba gb gur sybbe. Jvgu gur arkg ur jnf zber fhpprffshy. Ur jrag 
 onpx gb gur yvivat-ebbz naq fng qbja ng n fznyy gnoyr gung fgbbq gb gur 
 yrsg bs gur gryrfperra. Sebz gur gnoyr qenjre ur gbbx bhg n craubyqre, n 
 obggyr bs vax, naq n guvpx, dhnegb-fvmrq oynax obbx jvgu n erq onpx naq n 
 zneoyrq pbire. 
 Sbe fbzr ernfba gur gryrfperra va gur yvivat-ebbz jnf va na hahfhny 
 cbfvgvba. Vafgrnq bs orvat cynprq, nf jnf abezny, va gur raq jnyy, jurer vg 
 pbhyq pbzznaq gur jubyr ebbz, vg jnf va gur ybatre jnyy, bccbfvgr gur 
 jvaqbj. Gb bar fvqr bs vg gurer jnf n funyybj nypbir va juvpu Jvafgba jnf 
 abj fvggvat, naq juvpu, jura gur syngf jrer ohvyg, unq cebonoyl orra 
 vagraqrq gb ubyq obbxfuryirf. Ol fvggvat va gur nypbir, naq xrrcvat jryy 
 onpx, Jvafgba jnf noyr gb erznva bhgfvqr gur enatr bs gur gryrfperra, fb 
 sne nf fvtug jrag. Ur pbhyq or urneq, bs pbhefr, ohg fb ybat nf ur fgnlrq 
 va uvf cerfrag cbfvgvba ur pbhyq abg or frra. Vg jnf cnegyl gur hahfhny 
 trbtencul bs gur ebbz gung unq fhttrfgrq gb uvz gur guvat gung ur jnf abj 
 nobhg gb qb. 
 Ohg vg unq nyfb orra fhttrfgrq ol gur obbx gung ur unq whfg gnxra bhg 
 bs gur qenjre. Vg jnf n crphyvneyl ornhgvshy obbx. Vgf fzbbgu pernzl cncre, 
 n yvggyr lryybjrq ol ntr, jnf bs n xvaq gung unq abg orra znahsnpgherq sbe 
 ng yrnfg sbegl lrnef cnfg. Ur pbhyq thrff, ubjrire, gung gur obbx jnf zhpu 
 byqre guna gung. Ur unq frra vg ylvat va gur jvaqbj bs n sebjfl yvggyr 
 whax-fubc va n fyhzzl dhnegre bs gur gbja (whfg jung dhnegre ur qvq abg abj 
 erzrzore) naq unq orra fgevpxra vzzrqvngryl ol na birejuryzvat qrfver gb 
 cbffrff vg. Cnegl zrzoref jrer fhccbfrq abg gb tb vagb beqvanel fubcf 
 ('qrnyvat ba gur serr znexrg', vg jnf pnyyrq), ohg gur ehyr jnf abg 
 fgevpgyl xrcg, orpnhfr gurer jrer inevbhf guvatf, fhpu nf fubrynprf naq 
 enmbe oynqrf, juvpu vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gb trg ubyq bs va nal bgure jnl. Ur 
 unq tvira n dhvpx tynapr hc naq qbja gur fgerrg naq gura unq fyvccrq vafvqr 
 naq obhtug gur obbx sbe gjb qbyynef svsgl. Ng gur gvzr ur jnf abg pbafpvbhf 
 bs jnagvat vg sbe nal cnegvphyne checbfr. Ur unq pneevrq vg thvygvyl ubzr 
 va uvf oevrspnfr. Rira jvgu abguvat jevggra va vg, vg jnf n pbzcebzvfvat 
 cbffrffvba. 
 Gur guvat gung ur jnf nobhg gb qb jnf gb bcra n qvnel. Guvf jnf abg 
 vyyrtny (abguvat jnf vyyrtny, fvapr gurer jrer ab ybatre nal ynjf), ohg vs 
 qrgrpgrq vg jnf ernfbanoyl pregnva gung vg jbhyq or chavfurq ol qrngu, be 
 ng yrnfg ol gjragl-svir lrnef va n sbeprq-ynobhe pnzc. Jvafgba svggrq n avo 
 vagb gur craubyqre naq fhpxrq vg gb trg gur ternfr bss. Gur cra jnf na 
 nepunvp vafgehzrag, fryqbz hfrq rira sbe fvtangherf, naq ur unq cebpherq 
 bar, shegviryl naq jvgu fbzr qvssvphygl, fvzcyl orpnhfr bs n srryvat gung 
 gur ornhgvshy pernzl cncre qrfreirq gb or jevggra ba jvgu n erny avo 
 vafgrnq bs orvat fpengpurq jvgu na vax-crapvy. Npghnyyl ur jnf abg hfrq gb 
 jevgvat ol unaq. Ncneg sebz irel fubeg abgrf, vg jnf hfhny gb qvpgngr 
 rirelguvat vagb gur fcrnx-jevgr juvpu jnf bs pbhefr vzcbffvoyr sbe uvf 
 cerfrag checbfr. Ur qvccrq gur cra vagb gur vax naq gura snygrerq sbe whfg 
 n frpbaq. N gerzbe unq tbar guebhtu uvf objryf. Gb znex gur cncre jnf gur 
 qrpvfvir npg. Va fznyy pyhzfl yrggref ur jebgr: 
 
 Ncevy 4gu, 1984. 
 
 Ur fng onpx. N frafr bs pbzcyrgr urycyrffarff unq qrfpraqrq hcba uvz. 
 Gb ortva jvgu, ur qvq abg xabj jvgu nal pregnvagl gung guvf jnf 1984. Vg 
 zhfg or ebhaq nobhg gung qngr, fvapr ur jnf snveyl fher gung uvf ntr jnf 
 guvegl-avar, naq ur oryvrirq gung ur unq orra obea va 1944 be 1945; ohg vg 
 jnf arire cbffvoyr abjnqnlf gb cva qbja nal qngr jvguva n lrne be gjb. 
 Sbe jubz, vg fhqqrayl bppheerq gb uvz gb jbaqre, jnf ur jevgvat guvf 
 qvnel? Sbe gur shgher, sbe gur haobea. Uvf zvaq ubirerq sbe n zbzrag ebhaq 
 gur qbhogshy qngr ba gur cntr, naq gura srgpurq hc jvgu n ohzc ntnvafg gur 
 Arjfcrnx jbeq qbhoyrguvax. Sbe gur svefg gvzr gur zntavghqr bs jung ur unq 
 haqregnxra pnzr ubzr gb uvz. Ubj pbhyq lbh pbzzhavpngr jvgu gur shgher? Vg 
 jnf bs vgf angher vzcbffvoyr. Rvgure gur shgher jbhyq erfrzoyr gur cerfrag, 
 va juvpu pnfr vg jbhyq abg yvfgra gb uvz: be vg jbhyq or qvssrerag sebz vg, 
 naq uvf cerqvpnzrag jbhyq or zrnavatyrff. 
 Sbe fbzr gvzr ur fng tnmvat fghcvqyl ng gur cncre. Gur gryrfperra unq 
 punatrq bire gb fgevqrag zvyvgnel zhfvp. Vg jnf phevbhf gung ur frrzrq abg 
 zreryl gb unir ybfg gur cbjre bs rkcerffvat uvzfrys, ohg rira gb unir 
 sbetbggra jung vg jnf gung ur unq bevtvanyyl vagraqrq gb fnl. Sbe jrrxf 
 cnfg ur unq orra znxvat ernql sbe guvf zbzrag, naq vg unq arire pebffrq uvf 
 zvaq gung nalguvat jbhyq or arrqrq rkprcg pbhentr. Gur npghny jevgvat jbhyq 
 or rnfl. Nyy ur unq gb qb jnf gb genafsre gb cncre gur vagrezvanoyr 
 erfgyrff zbabybthr gung unq orra ehaavat vafvqr uvf urnq, yvgrenyyl sbe 
 lrnef. Ng guvf zbzrag, ubjrire, rira gur zbabybthr unq qevrq hc. Zberbire 
 uvf inevpbfr hypre unq ortha vgpuvat haornenoyl. Ur qnerq abg fpengpu vg, 
 orpnhfr vs ur qvq fb vg nyjnlf orpnzr vasynzrq. Gur frpbaqf jrer gvpxvat 
 ol. Ur jnf pbafpvbhf bs abguvat rkprcg gur oynaxarff bs gur cntr va sebag 
 bs uvz, gur vgpuvat bs gur fxva nobir uvf naxyr, gur oynevat bs gur zhfvp, 
 naq n fyvtug obbmvarff pnhfrq ol gur tva. 
 Fhqqrayl ur ortna jevgvat va furre cnavp, bayl vzcresrpgyl njner bs 
 jung ur jnf frggvat qbja. Uvf fznyy ohg puvyqvfu unaqjevgvat fgenttyrq hc 
 naq qbja gur cntr, furqqvat svefg vgf pncvgny yrggref naq svanyyl rira vgf 
 shyy fgbcf: 
 
 Ncevy 4gu, 1984. Ynfg avtug gb gur syvpxf. Nyy jne svyzf. Bar irel 
 tbbq bar bs n fuvc shyy bs ershtrrf orvat obzorq fbzrjurer va gur 
 Zrqvgreenarna. Nhqvrapr zhpu nzhfrq ol fubgf bs n terng uhtr sng zna gelvat 
 gb fjvz njnl jvgu n uryvpbcgre nsgre uvz, svefg lbh fnj uvz jnyybjvat nybat 
 va gur jngre yvxr n cbecbvfr, gura lbh fnj uvz guebhtu gur uryvpbcgref 
 thafvtugf, gura ur jnf shyy bs ubyrf naq gur frn ebhaq uvz ghearq cvax naq 
 ur fnax nf fhqqrayl nf gubhtu gur ubyrf unq yrg va gur jngre, nhqvrapr 
 fubhgvat jvgu ynhtugre jura ur fnax. gura lbh fnj n yvsrobng shyy bs 
 puvyqera jvgu n uryvpbcgre ubirevat bire vg. gurer jnf n zvqqyr-ntrq jbzna 
 zvtug unir orra n wrjrff fvggvat hc va gur obj jvgu n yvggyr obl nobhg 
 guerr lrnef byq va ure nezf. yvggyr obl fpernzvat jvgu sevtug naq uvqvat 
 uvf urnq orgjrra ure oernfgf nf vs ur jnf gelvat gb oheebj evtug vagb ure 
 naq gur jbzna chggvat ure nezf ebhaq uvz naq pbzsbegvat uvz nygubhtu fur 
 jnf oyhr jvgu sevtug urefrys, nyy gur gvzr pbirevat uvz hc nf zhpu nf 
 cbffvoyr nf vs fur gubhtug ure nezf pbhyq xrrc gur ohyyrgf bss uvz. gura 
 gur uryvpbcgre cynagrq n 20 xvyb obzo va nzbat gurz greevsvp synfu naq gur 
 obng jrag nyy gb zngpujbbq. gura gurer jnf n jbaqreshy fubg bs n puvyq'f 
 nez tbvat hc hc hc evtug hc vagb gur nve n uryvpbcgre jvgu n pnzren va vgf 
 abfr zhfg unir sbyybjrq vg hc naq gurer jnf n ybg bs nccynhfr sebz gur 
 cnegl frngf ohg n jbzna qbja va gur cebyr cneg bs gur ubhfr fhqqrayl 
 fgnegrq xvpxvat hc n shff naq fubhgvat gurl qvqag bhtugre bs fubjrq vg abg 
 va sebag bs xvqf gurl qvqag vg nvag evtug abg va sebag bs xvqf vg nvag 
 hagvy gur cbyvpr ghearq ure ghearq ure bhg v qbag fhccbfr nalguvat unccrarq 
 gb ure abobql pnerf jung gur cebyrf fnl glcvpny cebyr ernpgvba gurl arire-- 
 
 Jvafgba fgbccrq jevgvat, cnegyl orpnhfr ur jnf fhssrevat sebz penzc. 
 Ur qvq abg xabj jung unq znqr uvz cbhe bhg guvf fgernz bs ehoovfu. Ohg gur 
 phevbhf guvat jnf gung juvyr ur jnf qbvat fb n gbgnyyl qvssrerag zrzbel unq 
 pynevsvrq vgfrys va uvf zvaq, gb gur cbvag jurer ur nyzbfg sryg rdhny gb 
 jevgvat vg qbja. Vg jnf, ur abj ernyvmrq, orpnhfr bs guvf bgure vapvqrag 
 gung ur unq fhqqrayl qrpvqrq gb pbzr ubzr naq ortva gur qvnel gbqnl. 
 Vg unq unccrarq gung zbeavat ng gur Zvavfgel, vs nalguvat fb arohybhf 
 pbhyq or fnvq gb unccra. 
 Vg jnf arneyl ryrira uhaqerq, naq va gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag, jurer 
 Jvafgba jbexrq, gurl jrer qenttvat gur punvef bhg bs gur phovpyrf naq 
 tebhcvat gurz va gur prager bs gur unyy bccbfvgr gur ovt gryrfperra, va 
 cercnengvba sbe gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr. Jvafgba jnf whfg gnxvat uvf cynpr va 
 bar bs gur zvqqyr ebjf jura gjb crbcyr jubz ur xarj ol fvtug, ohg unq arire 
 fcbxra gb, pnzr harkcrpgrqyl vagb gur ebbz. Bar bs gurz jnf n tvey jubz ur 
 bsgra cnffrq va gur pbeevqbef. Ur qvq abg xabj ure anzr, ohg ur xarj gung 
 fur jbexrq va gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag. Cerfhznoyl -- fvapr ur unq fbzrgvzrf 
 frra ure jvgu bvyl unaqf naq pneelvat n fcnaare -- fur unq fbzr zrpunavpny 
 wbo ba bar bs gur abiry-jevgvat znpuvarf. Fur jnf n obyq-ybbxvat tvey, bs 
 nobhg gjragl-frira, jvgu guvpx unve, n serpxyrq snpr, naq fjvsg, nguyrgvp 
 zbirzragf. N aneebj fpneyrg fnfu, rzoyrz bs gur Whavbe Nagv-Frk Yrnthr, jnf 
 jbhaq frireny gvzrf ebhaq gur jnvfg bs ure birenyyf, whfg gvtugyl rabhtu gb 
 oevat bhg gur funcryvarff bs ure uvcf. Jvafgba unq qvfyvxrq ure sebz gur 
 irel svefg zbzrag bs frrvat ure. Ur xarj gur ernfba. Vg jnf orpnhfr bs gur 
 ngzbfcurer bs ubpxrl-svryqf naq pbyq onguf naq pbzzhavgl uvxrf naq trareny 
 pyrna-zvaqrqarff juvpu fur znantrq gb pneel nobhg jvgu ure. Ur qvfyvxrq 
 arneyl nyy jbzra, naq rfcrpvnyyl gur lbhat naq cerggl barf. Vg jnf nyjnlf 
 gur jbzra, naq nobir nyy gur lbhat barf, jub jrer gur zbfg ovtbgrq 
 nqureragf bs gur Cnegl, gur fjnyybjref bs fybtnaf, gur nzngrhe fcvrf naq 
 abfref-bhg bs habegubqbkl. Ohg guvf cnegvphyne tvey tnir uvz gur vzcerffvba 
 bs orvat zber qnatrebhf guna zbfg. Bapr jura gurl cnffrq va gur pbeevqbe 
 fur tnir uvz n dhvpx fvqrybat tynapr juvpu frrzrq gb cvrepr evtug vagb uvz 
 naq sbe n zbzrag unq svyyrq uvz jvgu oynpx greebe. Gur vqrn unq rira 
 pebffrq uvf zvaq gung fur zvtug or na ntrag bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr. Gung, vg 
 jnf gehr, jnf irel hayvxryl. Fgvyy, ur pbagvahrq gb srry n crphyvne 
 harnfvarff, juvpu unq srne zvkrq hc va vg nf jryy nf ubfgvyvgl, jurarire 
 fur jnf naljurer arne uvz. 
 Gur bgure crefba jnf n zna anzrq B'Oevra, n zrzore bs gur Vaare Cnegl 
 naq ubyqre bs fbzr cbfg fb vzcbegnag naq erzbgr gung Jvafgba unq bayl n qvz 
 vqrn bs vgf angher. N zbzragnel uhfu cnffrq bire gur tebhc bs crbcyr ebhaq 
 gur punvef nf gurl fnj gur oynpx birenyyf bs na Vaare Cnegl zrzore 
 nccebnpuvat. B'Oevra jnf n ynetr, oheyl zna jvgu n guvpx arpx naq n pbnefr, 
 uhzbebhf, oehgny snpr. Va fcvgr bs uvf sbezvqnoyr nccrnenapr ur unq n 
 pregnva punez bs znaare. Ur unq n gevpx bs erfrggyvat uvf fcrpgnpyrf ba uvf 
 abfr juvpu jnf phevbhfyl qvfnezvat -- va fbzr vaqrsvanoyr jnl, phevbhfyl 
 pvivyvmrq. Vg jnf n trfgher juvpu, vs nalbar unq fgvyy gubhtug va fhpu 
 grezf, zvtug unir erpnyyrq na rvtugrragu-praghel aboyrzna bssrevat uvf 
 fahssobk. Jvafgba unq frra B'Oevra creuncf n qbmra gvzrf va nyzbfg nf znal 
 lrnef. Ur sryg qrrcyl qenja gb uvz, naq abg fbyryl orpnhfr ur jnf vagevthrq 
 ol gur pbagenfg orgjrra B'Oevra'f heonar znaare naq uvf cevmr-svtugre'f 
 culfvdhr. Zhpu zber vg jnf orpnhfr bs n frpergyl uryq oryvrs -- be creuncf 
 abg rira n oryvrs, zreryl n ubcr -- gung B'Oevra'f cbyvgvpny begubqbkl jnf 
 abg cresrpg. Fbzrguvat va uvf snpr fhttrfgrq vg veerfvfgvoyl. Naq ntnva, 
 creuncf vg jnf abg rira habegubqbkl gung jnf jevggra va uvf snpr, ohg 
 fvzcyl vagryyvtrapr. Ohg ng nal engr ur unq gur nccrnenapr bs orvat n 
 crefba gung lbh pbhyq gnyx gb vs fbzrubj lbh pbhyq purng gur gryrfperra naq 
 trg uvz nybar. Jvafgba unq arire znqr gur fznyyrfg rssbeg gb irevsl guvf 
 thrff: vaqrrq, gurer jnf ab jnl bs qbvat fb. Ng guvf zbzrag B'Oevra tynaprq 
 ng uvf jevfg-jngpu, fnj gung vg jnf arneyl ryrira uhaqerq, naq rivqragyl 
 qrpvqrq gb fgnl va gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag hagvy gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr jnf 
 bire. Ur gbbx n punve va gur fnzr ebj nf Jvafgba, n pbhcyr bs cynprf njnl. 
 N fznyy, fnaql-unverq jbzna jub jbexrq va gur arkg phovpyr gb Jvafgba jnf 
 orgjrra gurz. Gur tvey jvgu qnex unve jnf fvggvat vzzrqvngryl oruvaq. 
 Gur arkg zbzrag n uvqrbhf, tevaqvat fcrrpu, nf bs fbzr zbafgebhf 
 znpuvar ehaavat jvgubhg bvy, ohefg sebz gur ovt gryrfperra ng gur raq bs 
 gur ebbz. Vg jnf n abvfr gung frg bar'f grrgu ba rqtr naq oevfgyrq gur unve 
 ng gur onpx bs bar'f arpx. Gur Ungr unq fgnegrq. 
 Nf hfhny, gur snpr bs Rzznahry Tbyqfgrva, gur Rarzl bs gur Crbcyr, unq 
 synfurq ba gb gur fperra. Gurer jrer uvffrf urer naq gurer nzbat gur 
 nhqvrapr. Gur yvggyr fnaql-unverq jbzna tnir n fdhrnx bs zvatyrq srne naq 
 qvfthfg. Tbyqfgrva jnf gur erartnqr naq onpxfyvqre jub bapr, ybat ntb (ubj 
 ybat ntb, abobql dhvgr erzrzorerq), unq orra bar bs gur yrnqvat svtherf bs 
 gur Cnegl, nyzbfg ba n yriry jvgu Ovt Oebgure uvzfrys, naq gura unq ratntrq 
 va pbhagre-eribyhgvbanel npgvivgvrf, unq orra pbaqrzarq gb qrngu, naq unq 
 zlfgrevbhfyl rfpncrq naq qvfnccrnerq. Gur cebtenzzrf bs gur Gjb Zvahgrf 
 Ungr inevrq sebz qnl gb qnl, ohg gurer jnf abar va juvpu Tbyqfgrva jnf abg 
 gur cevapvcny svther. Ur jnf gur cevzny genvgbe, gur rneyvrfg qrsvyre bs 
 gur Cnegl'f chevgl. Nyy fhofrdhrag pevzrf ntnvafg gur Cnegl, nyy 
 gernpurevrf, npgf bs fnobgntr, urerfvrf, qrivngvbaf, fcenat qverpgyl bhg bs 
 uvf grnpuvat. Fbzrjurer be bgure ur jnf fgvyy nyvir naq ungpuvat uvf 
 pbafcvenpvrf: creuncf fbzrjurer orlbaq gur frn, haqre gur cebgrpgvba bs uvf 
 sbervta cnlznfgref, creuncf rira -- fb vg jnf bppnfvbanyyl ehzbherq -- va 
 fbzr uvqvat-cynpr va Bprnavn vgfrys. 
 Jvafgba'f qvncuentz jnf pbafgevpgrq. Ur pbhyq arire frr gur snpr bs 
 Tbyqfgrva jvgubhg n cnvashy zvkgher bs rzbgvbaf. Vg jnf n yrna Wrjvfu snpr, 
 jvgu n terng shmml nherbyr bs juvgr unve naq n fznyy tbngrr orneq -- n 
 pyrire snpr, naq lrg fbzrubj vaureragyl qrfcvpnoyr, jvgu n xvaq bs fravyr 
 fvyyvarff va gur ybat guva abfr, arne gur raq bs juvpu n cnve bs fcrpgnpyrf 
 jnf crepurq. Vg erfrzoyrq gur snpr bs n furrc, naq gur ibvpr, gbb, unq n 
 furrc-yvxr dhnyvgl. Tbyqfgrva jnf qryvirevat uvf hfhny irabzbhf nggnpx hcba 
 gur qbpgevarf bs gur Cnegl -- na nggnpx fb rknttrengrq naq creirefr gung n 
 puvyq fubhyq unir orra noyr gb frr guebhtu vg, naq lrg whfg cynhfvoyr 
 rabhtu gb svyy bar jvgu na nynezrq srryvat gung bgure crbcyr, yrff yriry- 
 urnqrq guna barfrys, zvtug or gnxra va ol vg. Ur jnf nohfvat Ovt Oebgure, 
 ur jnf qrabhapvat gur qvpgngbefuvc bs gur Cnegl, ur jnf qrznaqvat gur 
 vzzrqvngr pbapyhfvba bs crnpr jvgu Rhenfvn, ur jnf nqibpngvat serrqbz bs 
 fcrrpu, serrqbz bs gur Cerff, serrqbz bs nffrzoyl, serrqbz bs gubhtug, ur 
 jnf pelvat ulfgrevpnyyl gung gur eribyhgvba unq orra orgenlrq -- naq nyy 
 guvf va encvq cbylflyynovp fcrrpu juvpu jnf n fbeg bs cnebql bs gur 
 unovghny fglyr bs gur bengbef bs gur Cnegl, naq rira pbagnvarq Arjfcrnx 
 jbeqf: zber Arjfcrnx jbeqf, vaqrrq, guna nal Cnegl zrzore jbhyq abeznyyl 
 hfr va erny yvsr. Naq nyy gur juvyr, yrfg bar fubhyq or va nal qbhog nf gb 
 gur ernyvgl juvpu Tbyqfgrva'f fcrpvbhf pyncgenc pbirerq, oruvaq uvf urnq ba 
 gur gryrfperra gurer znepurq gur raqyrff pbyhzaf bs gur Rhenfvna nezl -- 
 ebj nsgre ebj bs fbyvq-ybbxvat zra jvgu rkcerffvbayrff Nfvngvp snprf, jub 
 fjnz hc gb gur fhesnpr bs gur fperra naq inavfurq, gb or ercynprq ol bguref 
 rknpgyl fvzvyne. Gur qhyy eulguzvp genzc bs gur fbyqvref" obbgf sbezrq gur 
 onpxtebhaq gb Tbyqfgrva'f oyrngvat ibvpr. 
 Orsber gur Ungr unq cebprrqrq sbe guvegl frpbaqf, hapbagebyynoyr 
 rkpynzngvbaf bs entr jrer oernxvat bhg sebz unys gur crbcyr va gur ebbz. 
 Gur frys-fngvfsvrq furrc-yvxr snpr ba gur fperra, naq gur greevslvat cbjre 
 bs gur Rhenfvna nezl oruvaq vg, jrer gbb zhpu gb or obear: orfvqrf, gur 
 fvtug be rira gur gubhtug bs Tbyqfgrva cebqhprq srne naq natre 
 nhgbzngvpnyyl. Ur jnf na bowrpg bs ungerq zber pbafgnag guna rvgure Rhenfvn 
 be Rnfgnfvn, fvapr jura Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu bar bs gurfr Cbjref vg jnf 
 trarenyyl ng crnpr jvgu gur bgure. Ohg jung jnf fgenatr jnf gung nygubhtu 
 Tbyqfgrva jnf ungrq naq qrfcvfrq ol rirelobql, nygubhtu rirel qnl naq n 
 gubhfnaq gvzrf n qnl, ba cyngsbezf, ba gur gryrfperra, va arjfcncref, va 
 obbxf, uvf gurbevrf jrer ershgrq, fznfurq, evqvphyrq, uryq hc gb gur 
 trareny tnmr sbe gur cvgvshy ehoovfu gung gurl jrer -- va fcvgr bs nyy 
 guvf, uvf vasyhrapr arire frrzrq gb tebj yrff. Nyjnlf gurer jrer serfu 
 qhcrf jnvgvat gb or frqhprq ol uvz. N qnl arire cnffrq jura fcvrf naq 
 fnobgrhef npgvat haqre uvf qverpgvbaf jrer abg haznfxrq ol gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr. Ur jnf gur pbzznaqre bs n infg funqbjl nezl, na haqretebhaq argjbex 
 bs pbafcvengbef qrqvpngrq gb gur bireguebj bs gur Fgngr. Gur Oebgureubbq, 
 vgf anzr jnf fhccbfrq gb or. Gurer jrer nyfb juvfcrerq fgbevrf bs n 
 greevoyr obbx, n pbzcraqvhz bs nyy gur urerfvrf, bs juvpu Tbyqfgrva jnf gur 
 nhgube naq juvpu pvephyngrq pynaqrfgvaryl urer naq gurer. Vg jnf n obbx 
 jvgubhg n gvgyr. Crbcyr ersreerq gb vg, vs ng nyy, fvzcyl nf gur obbx. Ohg 
 bar xarj bs fhpu guvatf bayl guebhtu inthr ehzbhef. Arvgure gur Oebgureubbq 
 abe gur obbx jnf n fhowrpg gung nal beqvanel Cnegl zrzore jbhyq zragvba vs 
 gurer jnf n jnl bs nibvqvat vg. 
 Va vgf frpbaq zvahgr gur Ungr ebfr gb n seraml. Crbcyr jrer yrncvat hc 
 naq qbja va gurve cynprf naq fubhgvat ng gur gbcf bs gurve ibvprf va na 
 rssbeg gb qebja gur znqqravat oyrngvat ibvpr gung pnzr sebz gur fperra. Gur 
 yvggyr fnaql-unverq jbzna unq ghearq oevtug cvax, naq ure zbhgu jnf bcravat 
 naq fuhggvat yvxr gung bs n ynaqrq svfu. Rira B'Oevra'f urnil snpr jnf 
 syhfurq. Ur jnf fvggvat irel fgenvtug va uvf punve, uvf cbjreshy purfg 
 fjryyvat naq dhvirevat nf gubhtu ur jrer fgnaqvat hc gb gur nffnhyg bs n 
 jnir. Gur qnex-unverq tvey oruvaq Jvafgba unq ortha pelvat bhg 'Fjvar! 
 Fjvar! Fjvar!' naq fhqqrayl fur cvpxrq hc n urnil Arjfcrnx qvpgvbanel naq 
 syhat vg ng gur fperra. Vg fgehpx Tbyqfgrva'f abfr naq obhaprq bss; gur 
 ibvpr pbagvahrq varkbenoyl. Va n yhpvq zbzrag Jvafgba sbhaq gung ur jnf 
 fubhgvat jvgu gur bguref naq xvpxvat uvf urry ivbyragyl ntnvafg gur ehat bs 
 uvf punve. Gur ubeevoyr guvat nobhg gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr jnf abg gung bar 
 jnf boyvtrq gb npg n cneg, ohg, ba gur pbagenel, gung vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gb 
 nibvq wbvavat va. Jvguva guvegl frpbaqf nal cergrapr jnf nyjnlf 
 haarprffnel. N uvqrbhf rpfgnfl bs srne naq ivaqvpgvirarff, n qrfver gb 
 xvyy, gb gbegher, gb fznfu snprf va jvgu n fyrqtr-unzzre, frrzrq gb sybj 
 guebhtu gur jubyr tebhc bs crbcyr yvxr na ryrpgevp pheerag, gheavat bar 
 rira ntnvafg bar'f jvyy vagb n tevznpvat, fpernzvat yhangvp. Naq lrg gur 
 entr gung bar sryg jnf na nofgenpg, haqverpgrq rzbgvba juvpu pbhyq or 
 fjvgpurq sebz bar bowrpg gb nabgure yvxr gur synzr bs n oybjynzc. Guhf, ng 
 bar zbzrag Jvafgba'f ungerq jnf abg ghearq ntnvafg Tbyqfgrva ng nyy, ohg, 
 ba gur pbagenel, ntnvafg Ovt Oebgure, gur Cnegl, naq gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr; 
 naq ng fhpu zbzragf uvf urneg jrag bhg gb gur ybaryl, qrevqrq urergvp ba 
 gur fperra, fbyr thneqvna bs gehgu naq fnavgl va n jbeyq bs yvrf. Naq lrg 
 gur irel arkg vafgnag ur jnf ng bar jvgu gur crbcyr nobhg uvz, naq nyy gung 
 jnf fnvq bs Tbyqfgrva frrzrq gb uvz gb or gehr. Ng gubfr zbzragf uvf frperg 
 ybnguvat bs Ovt Oebgure punatrq vagb nqbengvba, naq Ovt Oebgure frrzrq gb 
 gbjre hc, na vaivapvoyr, srneyrff cebgrpgbe, fgnaqvat yvxr n ebpx ntnvafg 
 gur ubeqrf bs Nfvn, naq Tbyqfgrva, va fcvgr bs uvf vfbyngvba, uvf 
 urycyrffarff, naq gur qbhog gung uhat nobhg uvf irel rkvfgrapr, frrzrq yvxr 
 fbzr fvavfgre rapunagre, pncnoyr ol gur zrer cbjre bs uvf ibvpr bs jerpxvat 
 gur fgehpgher bs pvivyvmngvba. 
 Vg jnf rira cbffvoyr, ng zbzragf, gb fjvgpu bar'f ungerq guvf jnl be 
 gung ol n ibyhagnel npg. Fhqqrayl, ol gur fbeg bs ivbyrag rssbeg jvgu juvpu 
 bar jerapurf bar'f urnq njnl sebz gur cvyybj va n avtugzner, Jvafgba 
 fhpprrqrq va genafsreevat uvf ungerq sebz gur snpr ba gur fperra gb gur 
 qnex-unverq tvey oruvaq uvz. Ivivq, ornhgvshy unyyhpvangvbaf synfurq 
 guebhtu uvf zvaq. Ur jbhyq sybt ure gb qrngu jvgu n ehoore gehapurba. Ur 
 jbhyq gvr ure anxrq gb n fgnxr naq fubbg ure shyy bs neebjf yvxr Fnvag 
 Fronfgvna. Ur jbhyq enivfu ure naq phg ure guebng ng gur zbzrag bs pyvznk. 
 Orggre guna orsber, zberbire, ur ernyvmrq jul vg jnf gung ur ungrq ure. Ur 
 ungrq ure orpnhfr fur jnf lbhat naq cerggl naq frkyrff, orpnhfr ur jnagrq 
 gb tb gb orq jvgu ure naq jbhyq arire qb fb, orpnhfr ebhaq ure fjrrg fhccyr 
 jnvfg, juvpu frrzrq gb nfx lbh gb rapvepyr vg jvgu lbhe nez, gurer jnf bayl 
 gur bqvbhf fpneyrg fnfu, ntterffvir flzoby bs punfgvgl. 
 Gur Ungr ebfr gb vgf pyvznk. Gur ibvpr bs Tbyqfgrva unq orpbzr na 
 npghny furrc'f oyrng, naq sbe na vafgnag gur snpr punatrq vagb gung bs n 
 furrc. Gura gur furrc-snpr zrygrq vagb gur svther bs n Rhenfvna fbyqvre jub 
 frrzrq gb or nqinapvat, uhtr naq greevoyr, uvf fho-znpuvar tha ebnevat, naq 
 frrzvat gb fcevat bhg bs gur fhesnpr bs gur fperra, fb gung fbzr bs gur 
 crbcyr va gur sebag ebj npghnyyl syvapurq onpxjneqf va gurve frngf. Ohg va 
 gur fnzr zbzrag, qenjvat n qrrc fvtu bs eryvrs sebz rirelobql, gur ubfgvyr 
 svther zrygrq vagb gur snpr bs Ovt Oebgure, oynpx-unverq, oynpx- 
 zbhfgnpuvb'q, shyy bs cbjre naq zlfgrevbhf pnyz, naq fb infg gung vg nyzbfg 
 svyyrq hc gur fperra. Abobql urneq jung Ovt Oebgure jnf fnlvat. Vg jnf 
 zreryl n srj jbeqf bs rapbhentrzrag, gur fbeg bs jbeqf gung ner hggrerq va 
 gur qva bs onggyr, abg qvfgvathvfunoyr vaqvivqhnyyl ohg erfgbevat 
 pbasvqrapr ol gur snpg bs orvat fcbxra. Gura gur snpr bs Ovt Oebgure snqrq 
 njnl ntnva, naq vafgrnq gur guerr fybtnaf bs gur Cnegl fgbbq bhg va obyq 
 pncvgnyf: 
 
 JNE VF CRNPR 
 SERRQBZ VF FYNIREL 
 VTABENAPR VF FGERATGU 
 
 Ohg gur snpr bs Ovt Oebgure frrzrq gb crefvfg sbe frireny frpbaqf ba 
 gur fperra, nf gubhtu gur vzcnpg gung vg unq znqr ba rirelbar'f rlronyyf 
 jnf gbb ivivq gb jrne bss vzzrqvngryl. Gur yvggyr fnaql-unverq jbzna unq 
 syhat urefrys sbejneq bire gur onpx bs gur punve va sebag bs ure. Jvgu n 
 gerzhybhf zhezhe gung fbhaqrq yvxr 'Zl Fnivbhe!' fur rkgraqrq ure nezf 
 gbjneqf gur fperra. Gura fur ohevrq ure snpr va ure unaqf. Vg jnf nccnerag 
 gung fur jnf hggrevat n cenlre. 
 Ng guvf zbzrag gur ragver tebhc bs crbcyr oebxr vagb n qrrc, fybj, 
 eulguzvpny punag bs 'O-O!....O-O!....' -- bire naq bire ntnva, irel fybjyl, 
 jvgu n ybat cnhfr orgjrra gur svefg 'O' naq gur frpbaq-n urnil, zhezhebhf 
 fbhaq, fbzrubj phevbhfyl fnintr, va gur onpxtebhaq bs juvpu bar frrzrq gb 
 urne gur fgnzc bs anxrq srrg naq gur gueboovat bs gbz-gbzf. Sbe creuncf nf 
 zhpu nf guvegl frpbaqf gurl xrcg vg hc. Vg jnf n ersenva gung jnf bsgra 
 urneq va zbzragf bs birejuryzvat rzbgvba. Cnegyl vg jnf n fbeg bs ulza gb 
 gur jvfqbz naq znwrfgl bs Ovt Oebgure, ohg fgvyy zber vg jnf na npg bs 
 frys-ulcabfvf, n qryvorengr qebjavat bs pbafpvbhfarff ol zrnaf bs eulguzvp 
 abvfr. Jvafgba'f ragenvyf frrzrq gb tebj pbyq. Va gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr ur 
 pbhyq abg uryc funevat va gur trareny qryvevhz, ohg guvf fho-uhzna punagvat 
 bs 'O-O!....O-O!' nyjnlf svyyrq uvz jvgu ubeebe. Bs pbhefr ur punagrq jvgu 
 gur erfg: vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gb qb bgurejvfr. Gb qvffrzoyr lbhe srryvatf, gb 
 pbageby lbhe snpr, gb qb jung rirelbar ryfr jnf qbvat, jnf na vafgvapgvir 
 ernpgvba. Ohg gurer jnf n fcnpr bs n pbhcyr bs frpbaqf qhevat juvpu gur 
 rkcerffvba bs uvf rlrf zvtug pbaprvinoyl unir orgenlrq uvz. Naq vg jnf 
 rknpgyl ng guvf zbzrag gung gur fvtavsvpnag guvat unccrarq -- vs, vaqrrq, 
 vg qvq unccra. 
 Zbzragnevyl ur pnhtug B'Oevra'f rlr. B'Oevra unq fgbbq hc. Ur unq 
 gnxra bss uvf fcrpgnpyrf naq jnf va gur npg bs erfrggyvat gurz ba uvf abfr 
 jvgu uvf punenpgrevfgvp trfgher. Ohg gurer jnf n senpgvba bs n frpbaq jura 
 gurve rlrf zrg, naq sbe nf ybat nf vg gbbx gb unccra Jvafgba xarj -- lrf, 
 ur xarj! -- gung B'Oevra jnf guvaxvat gur fnzr guvat nf uvzfrys. Na 
 hazvfgnxnoyr zrffntr unq cnffrq. Vg jnf nf gubhtu gurve gjb zvaqf unq 
 bcrarq naq gur gubhtugf jrer sybjvat sebz bar vagb gur bgure guebhtu gurve 
 rlrf. 'V nz jvgu lbh,' B'Oevra frrzrq gb or fnlvat gb uvz. 'V xabj 
 cerpvfryl jung lbh ner srryvat. V xabj nyy nobhg lbhe pbagrzcg, lbhe 
 ungerq, lbhe qvfthfg. Ohg qba'g jbeel, V nz ba lbhe fvqr!' Naq gura gur 
 synfu bs vagryyvtrapr jnf tbar, naq B'Oevra'f snpr jnf nf vafpehgnoyr nf 
 rirelobql ryfr'f. 
 Gung jnf nyy, naq ur jnf nyernql hapregnva jurgure vg unq unccrarq. 
 Fhpu vapvqragf arire unq nal frdhry. Nyy gung gurl qvq jnf gb xrrc nyvir va 
 uvz gur oryvrs, be ubcr, gung bguref orfvqrf uvzfrys jrer gur rarzvrf bs 
 gur Cnegl. Creuncf gur ehzbhef bs infg haqretebhaq pbafcvenpvrf jrer gehr 
 nsgre nyy -- creuncf gur Oebgureubbq ernyyl rkvfgrq! Vg jnf vzcbffvoyr, va 
 fcvgr bs gur raqyrff neerfgf naq pbasrffvbaf naq rkrphgvbaf, gb or fher 
 gung gur Oebgureubbq jnf abg fvzcyl n zlgu. Fbzr qnlf ur oryvrirq va vg, 
 fbzr qnlf abg. Gurer jnf ab rivqrapr, bayl syrrgvat tyvzcfrf gung zvtug 
 zrna nalguvat be abguvat: fangpurf bs bireurneq pbairefngvba, snvag 
 fpevooyrf ba yningbel jnyyf -- bapr, rira, jura gjb fgenatref zrg, n fznyy 
