 sbervtaref, genvgbef, fnobgrhef, gubhtug-pevzvanyf. Vg jnf nyzbfg abezny 
 sbe crbcyr bire guvegl gb or sevtugrarq bs gurve bja puvyqera. Naq jvgu 
 tbbq ernfba, sbe uneqyl n jrrx cnffrq va juvpu gur Gvzrf qvq abg pneel n 
 cnentencu qrfpevovat ubj fbzr rnirfqebccvat yvggyr farnx -- 'puvyq ureb' 
