 fvtavsvpnapr. Ur pbhyq abg abj erzrzore jurgure vg jnf orsber be nsgre 
 univat gur qernz gung ur unq frra B'Oevra sbe gur svefg gvzr, abe pbhyq ur 
 erzrzore jura ur unq svefg vqragvsvrq gur ibvpr nf B'Oevra'f. Ohg ng nal 
 engr gur vqragvsvpngvba rkvfgrq. Vg jnf B'Oevra jub unq fcbxra gb uvz bhg 
 bs gur qnex. 
 Jvafgba unq arire orra noyr gb srry fher -- rira nsgre guvf zbeavat'f 
 synfu bs gur rlrf vg jnf fgvyy vzcbffvoyr gb or fher jurgure B'Oevra jnf n 
 sevraq be na rarzl. Abe qvq vg rira frrz gb znggre terngyl. Gurer jnf n 
 yvax bs haqrefgnaqvat orgjrra gurz, zber vzcbegnag guna nssrpgvba be 
 cnegvfnafuvc. 'Jr funyy zrrg va gur cynpr jurer gurer vf ab qnexarff,' ur 
 unq fnvq. Jvafgba qvq abg xabj jung vg zrnag, bayl gung va fbzr jnl be 
 nabgure vg jbhyq pbzr gehr. 
 Gur ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra cnhfrq. N gehzcrg pnyy, pyrne naq 
 ornhgvshy, sybngrq vagb gur fgntanag nve. Gur ibvpr pbagvahrq enfcvatyl: 
 'Nggragvba! Lbhe nggragvba, cyrnfr! N arjfsynfu unf guvf zbzrag 
 neevirq sebz gur Znynone sebag. Bhe sbeprf va Fbhgu Vaqvn unir jba n 
 tybevbhf ivpgbel. V nz nhgubevmrq gb fnl gung gur npgvba jr ner abj 
 ercbegvat znl jryy oevat gur jne jvguva zrnfhenoyr qvfgnapr bs vgf raq. 
 Urer vf gur arjfsynfu--' 
 Onq arjf pbzvat, gubhtug Jvafgba. Naq fher rabhtu, sbyybjvat ba n tbel 
 qrfpevcgvba bs gur naavuvyngvba bs n Rhenfvna nezl, jvgu fghcraqbhf svtherf 
 bs xvyyrq naq cevfbaref, pnzr gur naabhaprzrag gung, nf sebz arkg jrrx, gur 
 pubpbyngr engvba jbhyq or erqhprq sebz guvegl tenzzrf gb gjragl. 
 Jvafgba orypurq ntnva. Gur tva jnf jrnevat bss, yrnivat n qrsyngrq 
 srryvat. Gur gryrfperra -- creuncf gb pryroengr gur ivpgbel, creuncf gb 
 qebja gur zrzbel bs gur ybfg pubpbyngr -- penfurq vagb 'Bprnavn, 'gvf sbe 
 gurr'. Lbh jrer fhccbfrq gb fgnaq gb nggragvba. Ubjrire, va uvf cerfrag 
 cbfvgvba ur jnf vaivfvoyr. 
 'Bprnavn, 'gvf sbe gurr' tnir jnl gb yvtugre zhfvp. Jvafgba jnyxrq 
 bire gb gur jvaqbj, xrrcvat uvf onpx gb gur gryrfperra. Gur qnl jnf fgvyy 
 pbyq naq pyrne. Fbzrjurer sne njnl n ebpxrg obzo rkcybqrq jvgu n qhyy, 
 erireorengvat ebne. Nobhg gjragl be guvegl bs gurz n jrrx jrer snyyvat ba 
 Ybaqba ng cerfrag. 
 Qbja va gur fgerrg gur jvaq synccrq gur gbea cbfgre gb naq seb, naq 
 gur jbeq VATFBP svgshyyl nccrnerq naq inavfurq. Vatfbp. Gur fnperq 
 cevapvcyrf bs Vatfbp. Arjfcrnx, qbhoyrguvax, gur zhgnovyvgl bs gur cnfg. Ur 
 sryg nf gubhtu ur jrer jnaqrevat va gur sberfgf bs gur frn obggbz, ybfg va 
 n zbafgebhf jbeyq jurer ur uvzfrys jnf gur zbafgre. Ur jnf nybar. Gur cnfg 
 jnf qrnq, gur shgher jnf havzntvanoyr. Jung pregnvagl unq ur gung n fvatyr 
 uhzna perngher abj yvivat jnf ba uvf fvqr? Naq jung jnl bs xabjvat gung gur 
 qbzvavba bs gur Cnegl jbhyq abg raqher sbe rire? Yvxr na nafjre, gur guerr 
 fybtnaf ba gur juvgr snpr bs gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu pnzr onpx gb uvz: 
 
 JNE VF CRNPR 
 SERRQBZ VF FYNIREL 
 VTABENAPR VF FGERATGU 
 
 Ur gbbx n gjragl-svir prag cvrpr bhg bs uvf cbpxrg. Gurer, gbb, va 
 gval pyrne yrggrevat, gur fnzr fybtnaf jrer vafpevorq, naq ba gur bgure 
 snpr bs gur pbva gur urnq bs Ovt Oebgure. Rira sebz gur pbva gur rlrf 
 chefhrq lbh. Ba pbvaf, ba fgnzcf, ba gur pbiref bs obbxf, ba onaaref, ba 
 cbfgref, naq ba gur jenccvatf bs n pvtnerggr cnpxrg -- rireljurer. Nyjnlf 
 gur rlrf jngpuvat lbh naq gur ibvpr rairybcvat lbh. Nfyrrc be njnxr, 
 jbexvat be rngvat, vaqbbef be bhg bs qbbef, va gur ongu be va orq -- ab 
 rfpncr. Abguvat jnf lbhe bja rkprcg gur srj phovp pragvzrgerf vafvqr lbhe 
 fxhyy. 
 Gur fha unq fuvsgrq ebhaq, naq gur zlevnq jvaqbjf bs gur Zvavfgel bs 
 Gehgu, jvgu gur yvtug ab ybatre fuvavat ba gurz, ybbxrq tevz nf gur 
 ybbcubyrf bs n sbegerff. Uvf urneg dhnvyrq orsber gur rabezbhf clenzvqny 
 funcr. Vg jnf gbb fgebat, vg pbhyq abg or fgbezrq. N gubhfnaq ebpxrg obzof 
 jbhyq abg onggre vg qbja. Ur jbaqrerq ntnva sbe jubz ur jnf jevgvat gur 
 qvnel. Sbe gur shgher, sbe gur cnfg -- sbe na ntr gung zvtug or vzntvanel. 
 Naq va sebag bs uvz gurer ynl abg qrngu ohg naavuvyngvba. Gur qvnel jbhyq 
 or erqhprq gb nfurf naq uvzfrys gb incbhe. Bayl gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr jbhyq 
 ernq jung ur unq jevggra, orsber gurl jvcrq vg bhg bs rkvfgrapr naq bhg bs 
 zrzbel. Ubj pbhyq lbh znxr nccrny gb gur shgher jura abg n genpr bs lbh, 
 abg rira na nabalzbhf jbeq fpevooyrq ba n cvrpr bs cncre, pbhyq culfvpnyyl 
 fheivir? 
 Gur gryrfperra fgehpx sbhegrra. Ur zhfg yrnir va gra zvahgrf. Ur unq 
 gb or onpx ng jbex ol sbhegrra-guvegl. 
 Phevbhfyl, gur puvzvat bs gur ubhe frrzrq gb unir chg arj urneg vagb 
 uvz. Ur jnf n ybaryl tubfg hggrevat n gehgu gung abobql jbhyq rire urne. 
 Ohg fb ybat nf ur hggrerq vg, va fbzr bofpher jnl gur pbagvahvgl jnf abg 
 oebxra. Vg jnf abg ol znxvat lbhefrys urneq ohg ol fgnlvat fnar gung lbh 
 pneevrq ba gur uhzna urevgntr. Ur jrag onpx gb gur gnoyr, qvccrq uvf cra, 
 naq jebgr: 
 
 Gb gur shgher be gb gur cnfg, gb n gvzr jura gubhtug vf serr, jura 
 zra ner qvssrerag sebz bar nabgure naq qb abg yvir nybar -- gb n gvzr jura 
 gehgu rkvfgf naq jung vf qbar pnaabg or haqbar: 
 Sebz gur ntr bs havsbezvgl, sebz gur ntr bs fbyvghqr, sebz gur ntr 
 bs Ovt Oebgure, sebz gur ntr bs qbhoyrguvax -- terrgvatf! 
 
 Ur jnf nyernql qrnq, ur ersyrpgrq. Vg frrzrq gb uvz gung vg jnf bayl 
 abj, jura ur unq ortha gb or noyr gb sbezhyngr uvf gubhtugf, gung ur unq 
 gnxra gur qrpvfvir fgrc. Gur pbafrdhraprf bs rirel npg ner vapyhqrq va gur 
 npg vgfrys. Ur jebgr: 
 
 Gubhtugpevzr qbrf abg ragnvy qrngu: gubhtugpevzr VF qrngu. 
 
 Abj ur unq erpbtavmrq uvzfrys nf n qrnq zna vg orpnzr vzcbegnag gb 
 fgnl nyvir nf ybat nf cbffvoyr. Gjb svatref bs uvf evtug unaq jrer 
 vaxfgnvarq. Vg jnf rknpgyl gur xvaq bs qrgnvy gung zvtug orgenl lbh. Fbzr 
 abfvat mrnybg va gur Zvavfgel (n jbzna, cebonoyl: fbzrbar yvxr gur yvggyr 
 fnaql-unverq jbzna be gur qnex-unverq tvey sebz gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag) 
 zvtug fgneg jbaqrevat jul ur unq orra jevgvat qhevat gur yhapu vagreiny, 
 jul ur unq hfrq na byq-snfuvbarq cra, jung ur unq orra jevgvat -- naq gura 
 qebc n uvag va gur nccebcevngr dhnegre. Ur jrag gb gur onguebbz naq 
 pnershyyl fpehoorq gur vax njnl jvgu gur tevggl qnex-oebja fbnc juvpu 
 enfcrq lbhe fxva yvxr fnaqcncre naq jnf gurersber jryy nqncgrq sbe guvf 
 checbfr. 
 Ur chg gur qvnel njnl va gur qenjre. Vg jnf dhvgr hfryrff gb guvax bs 
 uvqvat vg, ohg ur pbhyq ng yrnfg znxr fher jurgure be abg vgf rkvfgrapr unq 
 orra qvfpbirerq. N unve ynvq npebff gur cntr-raqf jnf gbb boivbhf. Jvgu gur 
 gvc bs uvf svatre ur cvpxrq hc na vqragvsvnoyr tenva bs juvgvfu qhfg naq 
 qrcbfvgrq vg ba gur pbeare bs gur pbire, jurer vg jnf obhaq gb or funxra 
 bss vs gur obbx jnf zbirq. 
 
 VVV 
 
 Jvafgba jnf qernzvat bs uvf zbgure. 
 Ur zhfg, ur gubhtug, unir orra gra be ryrira lrnef byq jura uvf zbgure 
 unq qvfnccrnerq. Fur jnf n gnyy, fgnghrfdhr, engure fvyrag jbzna jvgu fybj 
 zbirzragf naq zntavsvprag snve unve. Uvf sngure ur erzrzorerq zber inthryl 
 nf qnex naq guva, qerffrq nyjnlf va arng qnex pybgurf (Jvafgba erzrzorerq 
 rfcrpvnyyl gur irel guva fbyrf bs uvf sngure'f fubrf) naq jrnevat 
 fcrpgnpyrf. Gur gjb bs gurz zhfg rivqragyl unir orra fjnyybjrq hc va bar bs 
 gur svefg terng chetrf bs gur svsgvrf. 
 Ng guvf zbzrag uvf zbgure jnf fvggvat va fbzr cynpr qrrc qbja orarngu 
 uvz, jvgu uvf lbhat fvfgre va ure nezf. Ur qvq abg erzrzore uvf fvfgre ng 
 nyy, rkprcg nf n gval, srroyr onol, nyjnlf fvyrag, jvgu ynetr, jngpushy 
 rlrf. Obgu bs gurz jrer ybbxvat hc ng uvz. Gurl jrer qbja va fbzr 
 fhogreenarna cynpr -- gur obggbz bs n jryy, sbe vafgnapr, be n irel qrrc 
 tenir -- ohg vg jnf n cynpr juvpu, nyernql sne orybj uvz, jnf vgfrys zbivat 
 qbjajneqf. Gurl jrer va gur fnybba bs n fvaxvat fuvc, ybbxvat hc ng uvz 
 guebhtu gur qnexravat jngre. Gurer jnf fgvyy nve va gur fnybba, gurl pbhyq 
 fgvyy frr uvz naq ur gurz, ohg nyy gur juvyr gurl jrer fvaxvat qbja, qbja 
 vagb gur terra jngref juvpu va nabgure zbzrag zhfg uvqr gurz sebz fvtug sbe 
 rire. Ur jnf bhg va gur yvtug naq nve juvyr gurl jrer orvat fhpxrq qbja gb 
 qrngu, naq gurl jrer qbja gurer orpnhfr ur jnf hc urer. Ur xarj vg naq gurl 
 xarj vg, naq ur pbhyq frr gur xabjyrqtr va gurve snprf. Gurer jnf ab 
 ercebnpu rvgure va gurve snprf be va gurve urnegf, bayl gur xabjyrqtr gung 
 gurl zhfg qvr va beqre gung ur zvtug erznva nyvir, naq gung guvf jnf cneg 
 bs gur hanibvqnoyr beqre bs guvatf. 
 Ur pbhyq abg erzrzore jung unq unccrarq, ohg ur xarj va uvf qernz gung 
 va fbzr jnl gur yvirf bs uvf zbgure naq uvf fvfgre unq orra fnpevsvprq gb 
 uvf bja. Vg jnf bar bs gubfr qernzf juvpu, juvyr ergnvavat gur 
 punenpgrevfgvp qernz fprarel, ner n pbagvahngvba bs bar'f vagryyrpghny 
 yvsr, naq va juvpu bar orpbzrf njner bs snpgf naq vqrnf juvpu fgvyy frrz 
 arj naq inyhnoyr nsgre bar vf njnxr. Gur guvat gung abj fhqqrayl fgehpx 
 Jvafgba jnf gung uvf zbgure'f qrngu, arneyl guvegl lrnef ntb, unq orra 
 gentvp naq fbeebjshy va n jnl gung jnf ab ybatre cbffvoyr. Gentrql, ur 
 creprvirq, orybatrq gb gur napvrag gvzr, gb n gvzr jura gurer jnf fgvyy 
 cevinpl, ybir, naq sevraqfuvc, naq jura gur zrzoref bs n snzvyl fgbbq ol 
 bar nabgure jvgubhg arrqvat gb xabj gur ernfba. Uvf zbgure'f zrzbel gber ng 
 uvf urneg orpnhfr fur unq qvrq ybivat uvz, jura ur jnf gbb lbhat naq 
 frysvfu gb ybir ure va erghea, naq orpnhfr fbzrubj, ur qvq abg erzrzore 
 ubj, fur unq fnpevsvprq urefrys gb n pbaprcgvba bs yblnygl gung jnf cevingr 
 naq hanygrenoyr. Fhpu guvatf, ur fnj, pbhyq abg unccra gbqnl. Gbqnl gurer 
 jrer srne, ungerq, naq cnva, ohg ab qvtavgl bs rzbgvba, ab qrrc be pbzcyrk 
 fbeebjf. Nyy guvf ur frrzrq gb frr va gur ynetr rlrf bs uvf zbgure naq uvf 
 fvfgre, ybbxvat hc ng uvz guebhtu gur terra jngre, uhaqerqf bs sngubzf qbja 
 naq fgvyy fvaxvat. 
 Fhqqrayl ur jnf fgnaqvat ba fubeg fcevatl ghes, ba n fhzzre riravat 
 jura gur fynagvat enlf bs gur fha tvyqrq gur tebhaq. Gur ynaqfpncr gung ur 
 jnf ybbxvat ng erpheerq fb bsgra va uvf qernzf gung ur jnf arire shyyl 
 pregnva jurgure be abg ur unq frra vg va gur erny jbeyq. Va uvf jnxvat 
 gubhtugf ur pnyyrq vg gur Tbyqra Pbhagel. Vg jnf na byq, enoovg-ovggra 
 cnfgher, jvgu n sbbg-genpx jnaqrevat npebff vg naq n zbyruvyy urer naq 
 gurer. Va gur enttrq urqtr ba gur bccbfvgr fvqr bs gur svryq gur obhtuf bs 
 gur ryz gerrf jrer fjnlvat irel snvagyl va gur oerrmr, gurve yrnirf whfg 
 fgveevat va qrafr znffrf yvxr jbzra'f unve. Fbzrjurer arne ng unaq, gubhtu 
 bhg bs fvtug, gurer jnf n pyrne, fybj-zbivat fgernz jurer qnpr jrer 
 fjvzzvat va gur cbbyf haqre gur jvyybj gerrf. 
 Gur tvey jvgu qnex unve jnf pbzvat gbjneqf gurz npebff gur svryq. Jvgu 
 jung frrzrq n fvatyr zbirzrag fur gber bss ure pybgurf naq syhat gurz 
 qvfqnvashyyl nfvqr. Ure obql jnf juvgr naq fzbbgu, ohg vg nebhfrq ab qrfver 
 va uvz, vaqrrq ur oneryl ybbxrq ng vg. Jung birejuryzrq uvz va gung vafgnag 
 jnf nqzvengvba sbe gur trfgher jvgu juvpu fur unq guebja ure pybgurf nfvqr. 
 Jvgu vgf tenpr naq pneryrffarff vg frrzrq gb naavuvyngr n jubyr phygher, n 
 jubyr flfgrz bs gubhtug, nf gubhtu Ovt Oebgure naq gur Cnegl naq gur 
 Gubhtug Cbyvpr pbhyq nyy or fjrcg vagb abguvatarff ol n fvatyr fcyraqvq 
 zbirzrag bs gur nez. Gung gbb jnf n trfgher orybatvat gb gur napvrag gvzr. 
 Jvafgba jbxr hc jvgu gur jbeq 'Funxrfcrner' ba uvf yvcf. 
 Gur gryrfperra jnf tvivat sbegu na rne-fcyvggvat juvfgyr juvpu 
 pbagvahrq ba gur fnzr abgr sbe guvegl frpbaqf. Vg jnf abhtug frira svsgrra, 
 trggvat-hc gvzr sbe bssvpr jbexref. Jvafgba jerapurq uvf obql bhg bs orq -- 
 anxrq, sbe n zrzore bs gur Bhgre Cnegl erprvirq bayl 3,000 pybguvat pbhcbaf 
 naahnyyl, naq n fhvg bs clwnznf jnf 600 -- naq frvmrq n qvatl fvatyrg naq n 
 cnve bs fubegf gung jrer ylvat npebff n punve. Gur Culfvpny Wrexf jbhyq 
 ortva va guerr zvahgrf. Gur arkg zbzrag ur jnf qbhoyrq hc ol n ivbyrag 
 pbhtuvat svg juvpu arneyl nyjnlf nggnpxrq uvz fbba nsgre jnxvat hc. Vg 
 rzcgvrq uvf yhatf fb pbzcyrgryl gung ur pbhyq bayl ortva oernguvat ntnva ol 
 ylvat ba uvf onpx naq gnxvat n frevrf bs qrrc tnfcf. Uvf irvaf unq fjryyrq 
 jvgu gur rssbeg bs gur pbhtu, naq gur inevpbfr hypre unq fgnegrq vgpuvat. 
 'Guvegl gb sbegl tebhc!' lnccrq n cvrepvat srznyr ibvpr. 'Guvegl gb 
 sbegl tebhc! Gnxr lbhe cynprf, cyrnfr. Guvegvrf gb sbegvrf!' 
 Jvafgba fcenat gb nggragvba va sebag bs gur gryrfperra, hcba juvpu gur 
 vzntr bs n lbhatvfu jbzna, fpenjal ohg zhfphyne, qerffrq va ghavp naq tlz- 
 fubrf, unq nyernql nccrnerq. 
 'Nezf oraqvat naq fgergpuvat!' fur enccrq bhg. 'Gnxr lbhe gvzr ol zr. 
 Bar, gjb, guerr, sbhe! Bar, gjb, guerr, sbhe! Pbzr ba, pbzenqrf, chg n ovg 
 bs yvsr vagb vg! Bar, gjb, guerr sbhe! Bar gjb, guerr, sbhe!...' 
 Gur cnva bs gur pbhtuvat svg unq abg dhvgr qevira bhg bs Jvafgba'f 
 zvaq gur vzcerffvba znqr ol uvf qernz, naq gur eulguzvp zbirzragf bs gur 
 rkrepvfr erfgberq vg fbzrjung. Nf ur zrpunavpnyyl fubg uvf nezf onpx naq 
 sbegu, jrnevat ba uvf snpr gur ybbx bs tevz rawblzrag juvpu jnf pbafvqrerq 
 cebcre qhevat gur Culfvpny Wrexf, ur jnf fgehttyvat gb guvax uvf jnl 
 onpxjneq vagb gur qvz crevbq bs uvf rneyl puvyqubbq. Vg jnf rkgenbeqvanevyl 
 qvssvphyg. Orlbaq gur yngr svsgvrf rirelguvat snqrq. Jura gurer jrer ab 
 rkgreany erpbeqf gung lbh pbhyq ersre gb, rira gur bhgyvar bs lbhe bja yvsr 
 ybfg vgf funecarff. Lbh erzrzorerq uhtr riragf juvpu unq dhvgr cebonoyl abg 
 unccrarq, lbh erzrzorerq gur qrgnvy bs vapvqragf jvgubhg orvat noyr gb 
 erpncgher gurve ngzbfcurer, naq gurer jrer ybat oynax crevbqf gb juvpu lbh 
 pbhyq nffvta abguvat. Rirelguvat unq orra qvssrerag gura. Rira gur anzrf bs 
 pbhagevrf, naq gurve funcrf ba gur znc, unq orra qvssrerag. Nvefgevc Bar, 
 sbe vafgnapr, unq abg orra fb pnyyrq va gubfr qnlf: vg unq orra pnyyrq 
 Ratynaq be Oevgnva, gubhtu Ybaqba, ur sryg snveyl pregnva, unq nyjnlf orra 
 pnyyrq Ybaqba. 
 Jvafgba pbhyq abg qrsvavgryl erzrzore n gvzr jura uvf pbhagel unq abg 
 orra ng jne, ohg vg jnf rivqrag gung gurer unq orra n snveyl ybat vagreiny 
 bs crnpr qhevat uvf puvyqubbq, orpnhfr bar bs uvf rneyl zrzbevrf jnf bs na 
 nve envq juvpu nccrnerq gb gnxr rirelbar ol fhecevfr. Creuncf vg jnf gur 
 gvzr jura gur ngbzvp obzo unq snyyra ba Pbypurfgre. Ur qvq abg erzrzore gur 
 envq vgfrys, ohg ur qvq erzrzore uvf sngure'f unaq pyhgpuvat uvf bja nf 
 gurl uheevrq qbja, qbja, qbja vagb fbzr cynpr qrrc va gur rnegu, ebhaq naq 
 ebhaq n fcveny fgnvepnfr juvpu enat haqre uvf srrg naq juvpu svanyyl fb 
 jrnevrq uvf yrtf gung ur ortna juvzcrevat naq gurl unq gb fgbc naq erfg. 
 Uvf zbgure, va ure fybj, qernzl jnl, jnf sbyybjvat n ybat jnl oruvaq gurz. 
 Fur jnf pneelvat uvf onol fvfgre -- be creuncf vg jnf bayl n ohaqyr bs 
 oynaxrgf gung fur jnf pneelvat: ur jnf abg pregnva jurgure uvf fvfgre unq 
 orra obea gura. Svanyyl gurl unq rzretrq vagb n abvfl, pebjqrq cynpr juvpu 
 ur unq ernyvmrq gb or n Ghor fgngvba. 
 Gurer jrer crbcyr fvggvat nyy bire gur fgbar-synttrq sybbe, naq bgure 
 crbcyr, cnpxrq gvtugyl gbtrgure, jrer fvggvat ba zrgny ohaxf, bar nobir gur 
 bgure. Jvafgba naq uvf zbgure naq sngure sbhaq gurzfryirf n cynpr ba gur 
 sybbe, naq arne gurz na byq zna naq na byq jbzna jrer fvggvat fvqr ol fvqr 
 ba n ohax. Gur byq zna unq ba n qrprag qnex fhvg naq n oynpx pybgu pnc 
 chfurq onpx sebz irel juvgr unve: uvf snpr jnf fpneyrg naq uvf rlrf jrer 
 oyhr naq shyy bs grnef. Ur errxrq bs tva. Vg frrzrq gb oerngur bhg bs uvf 
 fxva va cynpr bs fjrng, naq bar pbhyq unir snapvrq gung gur grnef jryyvat 
 sebz uvf rlrf jrer cher tva. Ohg gubhtu fyvtugyl qehax ur jnf nyfb 
 fhssrevat haqre fbzr tevrs gung jnf trahvar naq haornenoyr. Va uvf puvyqvfu 
 jnl Jvafgba tenfcrq gung fbzr greevoyr guvat, fbzrguvat gung jnf orlbaq 
 sbetvirarff naq pbhyq arire or erzrqvrq, unq whfg unccrarq. Vg nyfb frrzrq 
 gb uvz gung ur xarj jung vg jnf. Fbzrbar jubz gur byq zna ybirq -- n yvggyr 
 tenaqqnhtugre, creuncf -- unq orra xvyyrq. Rirel srj zvahgrf gur byq zna 
 xrcg ercrngvat: 
 'Jr qvqa'g bhtug gb 'nir gehfgrq 'rz. V fnvq fb, Zn, qvqa'g V? Gung'f 
 jung pbzrf bs gehfgvat 'rz. V fnvq fb nyy nybat. Jr qvqa'g bhtug gb 'nir 
 gehfgrq gur ohttref.' 
 Ohg juvpu ohttref gurl qvqa'g bhtug gb unir gehfgrq Jvafgba pbhyq abg 
 abj erzrzore. 
 Fvapr nobhg gung gvzr, jne unq orra yvgrenyyl pbagvahbhf, gubhtu 
 fgevpgyl fcrnxvat vg unq abg nyjnlf orra gur fnzr jne. Sbe frireny zbaguf 
 qhevat uvf puvyqubbq gurer unq orra pbashfrq fgerrg svtugvat va Ybaqba 
 vgfrys, fbzr bs juvpu ur erzrzorerq ivivqyl. Ohg gb genpr bhg gur uvfgbel 
 bs gur jubyr crevbq, gb fnl jub jnf svtugvat jubz ng nal tvira zbzrag, 
 jbhyq unir orra hggreyl vzcbffvoyr, fvapr ab jevggra erpbeq, naq ab fcbxra 
 jbeq, rire znqr zragvba bs nal bgure nyvtazrag guna gur rkvfgvat bar. Ng 
 guvf zbzrag, sbe rknzcyr, va 1984 (vs vg jnf 1984), Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu 
 Rhenfvn naq va nyyvnapr jvgu Rnfgnfvn. Va ab choyvp be cevingr hggrenapr 
 jnf vg rire nqzvggrq gung gur guerr cbjref unq ng nal gvzr orra tebhcrq 
 nybat qvssrerag yvarf. Npghnyyl, nf Jvafgba jryy xarj, vg jnf bayl sbhe 
 lrnef fvapr Bprnavn unq orra ng jne jvgu Rnfgnfvn naq va nyyvnapr jvgu 
 Rhenfvn. Ohg gung jnf zreryl n cvrpr bs shegvir xabjyrqtr juvpu ur unccrarq 
 gb cbffrff orpnhfr uvf zrzbel jnf abg fngvfsnpgbevyl haqre pbageby. 
 Bssvpvnyyl gur punatr bs cnegaref unq arire unccrarq. Bprnavn jnf ng jne 
 jvgu Rhenfvn: gurersber Bprnavn unq nyjnlf orra ng jne jvgu Rhenfvn. Gur 
 rarzl bs gur zbzrag nyjnlf ercerfragrq nofbyhgr rivy, naq vg sbyybjrq gung 
 nal cnfg be shgher nterrzrag jvgu uvz jnf vzcbffvoyr. 
 Gur sevtugravat guvat, ur ersyrpgrq sbe gur gra gubhfnaqgu gvzr nf ur 
 sbeprq uvf fubhyqref cnvashyyl onpxjneq (jvgu unaqf ba uvcf, gurl jrer 
 tlengvat gurve obqvrf sebz gur jnvfg, na rkrepvfr gung jnf fhccbfrq gb or 
 tbbq sbe gur onpx zhfpyrf) -- gur sevtugravat guvat jnf gung vg zvtug nyy 
 or gehr. Vs gur Cnegl pbhyq guehfg vgf unaq vagb gur cnfg naq fnl bs guvf 
 be gung rirag, vg arire unccrarq -- gung, fheryl, jnf zber greevslvat guna 
 zrer gbegher naq qrngu? 
 Gur Cnegl fnvq gung Bprnavn unq arire orra va nyyvnapr jvgu Rhenfvn. 
 Ur, Jvafgba Fzvgu, xarj gung Bprnavn unq orra va nyyvnapr jvgu Rhenfvn nf 
 fubeg n gvzr nf sbhe lrnef ntb. Ohg jurer qvq gung xabjyrqtr rkvfg? Bayl va 
 uvf bja pbafpvbhfarff, juvpu va nal pnfr zhfg fbba or naavuvyngrq. Naq vs 
 nyy bguref npprcgrq gur yvr juvpu gur Cnegl vzcbfrq -- vs nyy erpbeqf gbyq 
 gur fnzr gnyr -- gura gur yvr cnffrq vagb uvfgbel naq orpnzr gehgu. 'Jub 
 pbagebyf gur cnfg,' ena gur Cnegl fybtna, 'pbagebyf gur shgher: jub 
 pbagebyf gur cerfrag pbagebyf gur cnfg.' Naq lrg gur cnfg, gubhtu bs vgf 
 angher nygrenoyr, arire unq orra nygrerq. Jungrire jnf gehr abj jnf gehr 
 sebz rireynfgvat gb rireynfgvat. Vg jnf dhvgr fvzcyr. Nyy gung jnf arrqrq 
 jnf na haraqvat frevrf bs ivpgbevrf bire lbhe bja zrzbel. 'Ernyvgl 
 pbageby', gurl pnyyrq vg: va Arjfcrnx, 'qbhoyrguvax' 
 'Fgnaq rnfl!' onexrq gur vafgehpgerff, n yvggyr zber travnyyl. 
 Jvafgba fnax uvf nezf gb uvf fvqrf naq fybjyl ersvyyrq uvf yhatf jvgu 
 nve. Uvf zvaq fyvq njnl vagb gur ynolevaguvar jbeyq bs qbhoyrguvax. Gb xabj 
 naq abg gb xabj, gb or pbafpvbhf bs pbzcyrgr gehgushyarff juvyr gryyvat 
 pnershyyl pbafgehpgrq yvrf, gb ubyq fvzhygnarbhfyl gjb bcvavbaf juvpu 
 pnapryyrq bhg, xabjvat gurz gb or pbagenqvpgbel naq oryvrivat va obgu bs 
 gurz, gb hfr ybtvp ntnvafg ybtvp, gb erchqvngr zbenyvgl juvyr ynlvat pynvz 
 gb vg, gb oryvrir gung qrzbpenpl jnf vzcbffvoyr naq gung gur Cnegl jnf gur 
 thneqvna bs qrzbpenpl, gb sbetrg jungrire vg jnf arprffnel gb sbetrg, gura 
 gb qenj vg onpx vagb zrzbel ntnva ng gur zbzrag jura vg jnf arrqrq, naq 
 gura cebzcgyl gb sbetrg vg ntnva: naq nobir nyy, gb nccyl gur fnzr cebprff 
 gb gur cebprff vgfrys. Gung jnf gur hygvzngr fhogyrgl: pbafpvbhfyl gb 
 vaqhpr hapbafpvbhfarff, naq gura, bapr ntnva, gb orpbzr hapbafpvbhf bs gur 
 npg bs ulcabfvf lbh unq whfg cresbezrq. Rira gb haqrefgnaq gur jbeq 
 'qbhoyrguvax' vaibyirq gur hfr bs qbhoyrguvax. 
 Gur vafgehpgerff unq pnyyrq gurz gb nggragvba ntnva. 'Naq abj yrg'f 
 frr juvpu bs hf pna gbhpu bhe gbrf!' fur fnvq raguhfvnfgvpnyyl. 'Evtug bire 
 sebz gur uvcf, cyrnfr, pbzenqrf. Bar-gjb! Bar-gjb!...' 
 Jvafgba ybngurq guvf rkrepvfr, juvpu frag fubbgvat cnvaf nyy gur jnl 
 sebz uvf urryf gb uvf ohggbpxf naq bsgra raqrq ol oevatvat ba nabgure 
 pbhtuvat svg. Gur unys-cyrnfnag dhnyvgl jrag bhg bs uvf zrqvgngvbaf. Gur 
 cnfg, ur ersyrpgrq, unq abg zreryl orra nygrerq, vg unq orra npghnyyl 
 qrfgeblrq. Sbe ubj pbhyq lbh rfgnoyvfu rira gur zbfg boivbhf snpg jura 
 gurer rkvfgrq ab erpbeq bhgfvqr lbhe bja zrzbel? Ur gevrq gb erzrzore va 
 jung lrne ur unq svefg urneq zragvba bs Ovt Oebgure. Ur gubhtug vg zhfg 
 unir orra ng fbzr gvzr va gur fvkgvrf, ohg vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gb or pregnva. 
 Va gur Cnegl uvfgbevrf, bs pbhefr, Ovt Oebgure svtherq nf gur yrnqre naq 
 thneqvna bs gur Eribyhgvba fvapr vgf irel rneyvrfg qnlf. Uvf rkcybvgf unq 
 orra tenqhnyyl chfurq onpxjneqf va gvzr hagvy nyernql gurl rkgraqrq vagb 
 gur snohybhf jbeyq bs gur sbegvrf naq gur guvegvrf, jura gur pncvgnyvfgf va 
 gurve fgenatr plyvaqevpny ungf fgvyy ebqr guebhtu gur fgerrgf bs Ybaqba va 
 terng tyrnzvat zbgbe-pnef be ubefr pneevntrf jvgu tynff fvqrf. Gurer jnf ab 
 xabjvat ubj zhpu bs guvf yrtraq jnf gehr naq ubj zhpu vairagrq. Jvafgba 
 pbhyq abg rira erzrzore ng jung qngr gur Cnegl vgfrys unq pbzr vagb 
 rkvfgrapr. Ur qvq abg oryvrir ur unq rire urneq gur jbeq Vatfbp orsber 
 1960, ohg vg jnf cbffvoyr gung va vgf Byqfcrnx sbez -- 'Ratyvfu Fbpvnyvfz', 
 gung vf gb fnl -- vg unq orra pheerag rneyvre. Rirelguvat zrygrq vagb zvfg. 
 Fbzrgvzrf, vaqrrq, lbh pbhyq chg lbhe svatre ba n qrsvavgr yvr. Vg jnf abg 
 gehr, sbe rknzcyr, nf jnf pynvzrq va gur Cnegl uvfgbel obbxf, gung gur 
 Cnegl unq vairagrq nrebcynarf. Ur erzrzorerq nrebcynarf fvapr uvf rneyvrfg 
 puvyqubbq. Ohg lbh pbhyq cebir abguvat. Gurer jnf arire nal rivqrapr. Whfg 
 bapr va uvf jubyr yvsr ur unq uryq va uvf unaqf hazvfgnxnoyr qbphzragnel 
 cebbs bs gur snyfvsvpngvba bs na uvfgbevpny snpg. Naq ba gung bppnfvba-- 
 'Fzvgu!' fpernzrq gur fuerjvfu ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra. '6079 Fzvgu 
 J.! Lrf, lbh! Oraq ybjre, cyrnfr! Lbh pna qb orggre guna gung. Lbh'er abg 
 gelvat. Ybjre, cyrnfr! Gung'f orggre, pbzenqr. Abj fgnaq ng rnfr, gur jubyr 
 fdhnq, naq jngpu zr.' 
 N fhqqra ubg fjrng unq oebxra bhg nyy bire Jvafgba'f obql. Uvf snpr 
 erznvarq pbzcyrgryl vafpehgnoyr. Arire fubj qvfznl! Arire fubj erfragzrag! 
 N fvatyr syvpxre bs gur rlrf pbhyq tvir lbh njnl. Ur fgbbq jngpuvat juvyr 
 gur vafgehpgerff envfrq ure nezf nobir ure urnq naq -- bar pbhyq abg fnl 
 tenprshyyl, ohg jvgu erznexnoyr arngarff naq rssvpvrapl -- orag bire naq 
 ghpxrq gur svefg wbvag bs ure svatref haqre ure gbrf. 
 'Gurer, pbzenqrf! Gung'f ubj V jnag gb frr lbh qbvat vg. Jngpu zr 
 ntnva. V'z guvegl-avar naq V'ir unq sbhe puvyqera. Abj ybbx.' Fur orag bire 
 ntnva. 'Lbh frr zl xarrf nera'g orag. Lbh pna nyy qb vg vs lbh jnag gb,' 
 fur nqqrq nf fur fgenvtugrarq urefrys hc. 'Nalbar haqre sbegl-svir vf 
 cresrpgyl pncnoyr bs gbhpuvat uvf gbrf. Jr qba'g nyy unir gur cevivyrtr bs 
 svtugvat va gur sebag yvar, ohg ng yrnfg jr pna nyy xrrc svg. Erzrzore bhe 
 oblf ba gur Znynone sebag! Naq gur fnvybef va gur Sybngvat Sbegerffrf! Whfg 
 guvax jung gurl unir gb chg hc jvgu. Abj gel ntnva. Gung'f orggre, pbzenqr, 
 gung'f zhpu orggre,' fur nqqrq rapbhentvatyl nf Jvafgba, jvgu n ivbyrag 
 yhatr, fhpprrqrq va gbhpuvat uvf gbrf jvgu xarrf haorag, sbe gur svefg gvzr 
 va frireny lrnef. 
 
 VI 
 
 Jvgu gur qrrc, hapbafpvbhf fvtu juvpu abg rira gur arnearff bs gur 
 gryrfperra pbhyq cerirag uvz sebz hggrevat jura uvf qnl'f jbex fgnegrq, 
 Jvafgba chyyrq gur fcrnxjevgr gbjneqf uvz, oyrj gur qhfg sebz vgf 
 zbhgucvrpr, naq chg ba uvf fcrpgnpyrf. Gura ur haebyyrq naq pyvccrq 
 gbtrgure sbhe fznyy plyvaqref bs cncre juvpu unq nyernql sybccrq bhg bs gur 
 carhzngvp ghor ba gur evtug-unaq fvqr bs uvf qrfx. 
 Va gur jnyyf bs gur phovpyr gurer jrer guerr bevsvprf. Gb gur evtug bs 
 gur fcrnxjevgr, n fznyy carhzngvp ghor sbe jevggra zrffntrf, gb gur yrsg, n 
 ynetre bar sbe arjfcncref; naq va gur fvqr jnyy, jvguva rnfl ernpu bs 
 Jvafgba'f nez, n ynetr boybat fyvg cebgrpgrq ol n jver tengvat. Guvf ynfg 
 jnf sbe gur qvfcbfny bs jnfgr cncre. Fvzvyne fyvgf rkvfgrq va gubhfnaqf be 
 graf bs gubhfnaqf guebhtubhg gur ohvyqvat, abg bayl va rirel ebbz ohg ng 
 fubeg vagreinyf va rirel pbeevqbe. Sbe fbzr ernfba gurl jrer avpxanzrq 
 zrzbel ubyrf. Jura bar xarj gung nal qbphzrag jnf qhr sbe qrfgehpgvba, be 
 rira jura bar fnj n fpenc bs jnfgr cncre ylvat nobhg, vg jnf na nhgbzngvp 
 npgvba gb yvsg gur sync bs gur arnerfg zrzbel ubyr naq qebc vg va, 
 jurerhcba vg jbhyq or juveyrq njnl ba n pheerag bs jnez nve gb gur rabezbhf 
 sheanprf juvpu jrer uvqqra fbzrjurer va gur erprffrf bs gur ohvyqvat. 
 Jvafgba rknzvarq gur sbhe fyvcf bs cncre juvpu ur unq haebyyrq. Rnpu 
 pbagnvarq n zrffntr bs bayl bar be gjb yvarf, va gur nooerivngrq wnetba -- 
 abg npghnyyl Arjfcrnx, ohg pbafvfgvat ynetryl bs Arjfcrnx jbeqf -- juvpu 
 jnf hfrq va gur Zvavfgel sbe vagreany checbfrf. Gurl ena: 
 
 gvzrf 17.3.84 oo fcrrpu znyercbegrq nsevpn erpgvsl 
 gvzrf 19.12.83 sberpnfgf 3 lc 4gu dhnegre 83 zvfcevagf irevsl 
 pheerag vffhr 
 gvzrf 14.2.84 zvavcyragl znydhbgrq pubpbyngr erpgvsl 
 gvzrf 3.12.83 ercbegvat oo qnlbeqre qbhoyrcyhfhatbbq ersf hacrefbaf 
 erjevgr shyyjvfr hcfho nagrsvyvat 
 
 Jvgu n snvag srryvat bs fngvfsnpgvba Jvafgba ynvq gur sbhegu zrffntr 
 nfvqr. Vg jnf na vagevpngr naq erfcbafvoyr wbo naq unq orggre or qrnyg jvgu 
 ynfg. Gur bgure guerr jrer ebhgvar znggref, gubhtu gur frpbaq bar jbhyq 
 cebonoyl zrna fbzr grqvbhf jnqvat guebhtu yvfgf bs svtherf. 
 Jvafgba qvnyyrq 'onpx ahzoref' ba gur gryrfperra naq pnyyrq sbe gur 
 nccebcevngr vffhrf bs gur Gvzrf, juvpu fyvq bhg bs gur carhzngvp ghor nsgre 
 bayl n srj zvahgrf" qrynl. Gur zrffntrf ur unq erprvirq ersreerq gb 
 negvpyrf be arjf vgrzf juvpu sbe bar ernfba be nabgure vg jnf gubhtug 
 arprffnel gb nygre, be, nf gur bssvpvny cuenfr unq vg, gb erpgvsl. Sbe 
 rknzcyr, vg nccrnerq sebz gur Gvzrf bs gur friragrragu bs Znepu gung Ovt 
 Oebgure, va uvf fcrrpu bs gur cerivbhf qnl, unq cerqvpgrq gung gur Fbhgu 
 Vaqvna sebag jbhyq erznva dhvrg ohg gung n Rhenfvna bssrafvir jbhyq fubegyl 
 or ynhapurq va Abegu Nsevpn. Nf vg unccrarq, gur Rhenfvna Uvture Pbzznaq 
 unq ynhapurq vgf bssrafvir va Fbhgu Vaqvn naq yrsg Abegu Nsevpn nybar. Vg 
 jnf gurersber arprffnel gb erjevgr n cnentencu bs Ovt Oebgure'f fcrrpu, va 
 fhpu n jnl nf gb znxr uvz cerqvpg gur guvat gung unq npghnyyl unccrarq. Be 
 ntnva, gur Gvzrf bs gur avargrragu bs Qrprzore unq choyvfurq gur bssvpvny 
 sberpnfgf bs gur bhgchg bs inevbhf pynffrf bs pbafhzcgvba tbbqf va gur 
 sbhegu dhnegre bs 1983, juvpu jnf nyfb gur fvkgu dhnegre bs gur Avagu 
 Guerr-Lrne Cyna. Gbqnl'f vffhr pbagnvarq n fgngrzrag bs gur npghny bhgchg, 
 sebz juvpu vg nccrnerq gung gur sberpnfgf jrer va rirel vafgnapr tebffyl 
 jebat. Jvafgba'f wbo jnf gb erpgvsl gur bevtvany svtherf ol znxvat gurz 
 nterr jvgu gur yngre barf. Nf sbe gur guveq zrffntr, vg ersreerq gb n irel 
 fvzcyr reebe juvpu pbhyq or frg evtug va n pbhcyr bs zvahgrf. Nf fubeg n 
 gvzr ntb nf Sroehnel, gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl unq vffhrq n cebzvfr (n 
 'pngrtbevpny cyrqtr' jrer gur bssvpvny jbeqf) gung gurer jbhyq or ab 
 erqhpgvba bs gur pubpbyngr engvba qhevat 1984. Npghnyyl, nf Jvafgba jnf 
 njner, gur pubpbyngr engvba jnf gb or erqhprq sebz guvegl tenzzrf gb gjragl 
 ng gur raq bs gur cerfrag jrrx. Nyy gung jnf arrqrq jnf gb fhofgvghgr sbe 
 gur bevtvany cebzvfr n jneavat gung vg jbhyq cebonoyl or arprffnel gb 
 erqhpr gur engvba ng fbzr gvzr va Ncevy. 
 Nf fbba nf Jvafgba unq qrnyg jvgu rnpu bs gur zrffntrf, ur pyvccrq uvf 
 fcrnxjevggra pbeerpgvbaf gb gur nccebcevngr pbcl bs gur Gvzrf naq chfurq 
 gurz vagb gur carhzngvp ghor. Gura, jvgu n zbirzrag juvpu jnf nf arneyl nf 
 cbffvoyr hapbafpvbhf, ur pehzcyrq hc gur bevtvany zrffntr naq nal abgrf 
 gung ur uvzfrys unq znqr, naq qebccrq gurz vagb gur zrzbel ubyr gb or 
 qribherq ol gur synzrf. 
 Jung unccrarq va gur hafrra ynolevagu gb juvpu gur carhzngvp ghorf 
 yrq, ur qvq abg xabj va qrgnvy, ohg ur qvq xabj va trareny grezf. Nf fbba 
 nf nyy gur pbeerpgvbaf juvpu unccrarq gb or arprffnel va nal cnegvphyne 
 ahzore bs gur Gvzrf unq orra nffrzoyrq naq pbyyngrq, gung ahzore jbhyq or 
 ercevagrq, gur bevtvany pbcl qrfgeblrq, naq gur pbeerpgrq pbcl cynprq ba 
 gur svyrf va vgf fgrnq. Guvf cebprff bs pbagvahbhf nygrengvba jnf nccyvrq 
 abg bayl gb arjfcncref, ohg gb obbxf, crevbqvpnyf, cnzcuyrgf, cbfgref, 
 yrnsyrgf, svyzf, fbhaq-genpxf, pnegbbaf, cubgbtencuf -- gb rirel xvaq bs 
 yvgrengher be qbphzragngvba juvpu zvtug pbaprvinoyl ubyq nal cbyvgvpny be 
 vqrbybtvpny fvtavsvpnapr. Qnl ol qnl naq nyzbfg zvahgr ol zvahgr gur cnfg 
 jnf oebhtug hc gb qngr. Va guvf jnl rirel cerqvpgvba znqr ol gur Cnegl 
 pbhyq or fubja ol qbphzragnel rivqrapr gb unir orra pbeerpg, abe jnf nal 
 vgrz bs arjf, be nal rkcerffvba bs bcvavba, juvpu pbasyvpgrq jvgu gur arrqf 
 bs gur zbzrag, rire nyybjrq gb erznva ba erpbeq. Nyy uvfgbel jnf n 
 cnyvzcfrfg, fpencrq pyrna naq ervafpevorq rknpgyl nf bsgra nf jnf 
 arprffnel. Va ab pnfr jbhyq vg unir orra cbffvoyr, bapr gur qrrq jnf qbar, 
 gb cebir gung nal snyfvsvpngvba unq gnxra cynpr. Gur ynetrfg frpgvba bs gur 
 Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag, sne ynetre guna gur bar ba juvpu Jvafgba jbexrq, 
 pbafvfgrq fvzcyl bs crefbaf jubfr qhgl vg jnf gb genpx qbja naq pbyyrpg nyy 
 pbcvrf bs obbxf, arjfcncref, naq bgure qbphzragf juvpu unq orra fhcrefrqrq 
 naq jrer qhr sbe qrfgehpgvba. N ahzore bs gur Gvzrf juvpu zvtug, orpnhfr bs 
 punatrf va cbyvgvpny nyvtazrag, be zvfgnxra cebcurpvrf hggrerq ol Ovt 
 Oebgure, unir orra erjevggra n qbmra gvzrf fgvyy fgbbq ba gur svyrf ornevat 
 vgf bevtvany qngr, naq ab bgure pbcl rkvfgrq gb pbagenqvpg vg. Obbxf, nyfb, 
 jrer erpnyyrq naq erjevggra ntnva naq ntnva, naq jrer vainevnoyl ervffhrq 
 jvgubhg nal nqzvffvba gung nal nygrengvba unq orra znqr. Rira gur jevggra 
 vafgehpgvbaf juvpu Jvafgba erprvirq, naq juvpu ur vainevnoyl tbg evq bs nf 
 fbba nf ur unq qrnyg jvgu gurz, arire fgngrq be vzcyvrq gung na npg bs 
 sbetrel jnf gb or pbzzvggrq: nyjnlf gur ersrerapr jnf gb fyvcf, reebef, 
 zvfcevagf, be zvfdhbgngvbaf juvpu vg jnf arprffnel gb chg evtug va gur 
 vagrerfgf bs npphenpl. 
 Ohg npghnyyl, ur gubhtug nf ur er-nqwhfgrq gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl'f 
 svtherf, vg jnf abg rira sbetrel. Vg jnf zreryl gur fhofgvghgvba bs bar 
 cvrpr bs abafrafr sbe nabgure. Zbfg bs gur zngrevny gung lbh jrer qrnyvat 
 jvgu unq ab pbaarkvba jvgu nalguvat va gur erny jbeyq, abg rira gur xvaq bs 
 pbaarkvba gung vf pbagnvarq va n qverpg yvr. Fgngvfgvpf jrer whfg nf zhpu n 
 snagnfl va gurve bevtvany irefvba nf va gurve erpgvsvrq irefvba. N terng 
 qrny bs gur gvzr lbh jrer rkcrpgrq gb znxr gurz hc bhg bs lbhe urnq. Sbe 
 rknzcyr, gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl'f sberpnfg unq rfgvzngrq gur bhgchg bs 
 obbgf sbe gur dhnegre ng 145 zvyyvba cnvef. Gur npghny bhgchg jnf tvira nf 
 fvkgl-gjb zvyyvbaf. Jvafgba, ubjrire, va erjevgvat gur sberpnfg, znexrq gur 
 svther qbja gb svsgl-frira zvyyvbaf, fb nf gb nyybj sbe gur hfhny pynvz 
 gung gur dhbgn unq orra bireshysvyyrq. Va nal pnfr, fvkgl-gjb zvyyvbaf jnf 
 ab arnere gur gehgu guna svsgl-frira zvyyvbaf, be guna 145 zvyyvbaf. Irel 
 yvxryl ab obbgf unq orra cebqhprq ng nyy. Yvxryvre fgvyy, abobql xarj ubj 
 znal unq orra cebqhprq, zhpu yrff pnerq. Nyy bar xarj jnf gung rirel 
 dhnegre nfgebabzvpny ahzoref bs obbgf jrer cebqhprq ba cncre, juvyr creuncf 
 unys gur cbchyngvba bs Bprnavn jrag onersbbg. Naq fb vg jnf jvgu rirel 
 pynff bs erpbeqrq snpg, terng be fznyy. Rirelguvat snqrq njnl vagb n 
 funqbj-jbeyq va juvpu, svanyyl, rira gur qngr bs gur lrne unq orpbzr 
 hapregnva. 
 Jvafgba tynaprq npebff gur unyy. Va gur pbeerfcbaqvat phovpyr ba gur 
 bgure fvqr n fznyy, cerpvfr-ybbxvat, qnex-puvaarq zna anzrq Gvyybgfba jnf 
 jbexvat fgrnqvyl njnl, jvgu n sbyqrq arjfcncre ba uvf xarr naq uvf zbhgu 
 irel pybfr gb gur zbhgucvrpr bs gur fcrnxjevgr. Ur unq gur nve bs gelvat gb 
 xrrc jung ur jnf fnlvat n frperg orgjrra uvzfrys naq gur gryrfperra. Ur 
 ybbxrq hc, naq uvf fcrpgnpyrf qnegrq n ubfgvyr synfu va Jvafgba'f 
 qverpgvba. 
 Jvafgba uneqyl xarj Gvyybgfba, naq unq ab vqrn jung jbex ur jnf 
 rzcyblrq ba. Crbcyr va gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag qvq abg ernqvyl gnyx nobhg 
 gurve wbof. Va gur ybat, jvaqbjyrff unyy, jvgu vgf qbhoyr ebj bs phovpyrf 
 naq vgf raqyrff ehfgyr bs cncref naq uhz bs ibvprf zhezhevat vagb 
 fcrnxjevgrf, gurer jrer dhvgr n qbmra crbcyr jubz Jvafgba qvq abg rira xabj 
 ol anzr, gubhtu ur qnvyl fnj gurz uheelvat gb naq seb va gur pbeevqbef be 
 trfgvphyngvat va gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr. Ur xarj gung va gur phovpyr arkg gb 
 uvz gur yvggyr jbzna jvgu fnaql unve gbvyrq qnl va qnl bhg, fvzcyl ng 
 genpxvat qbja naq qryrgvat sebz gur Cerff gur anzrf bs crbcyr jub unq orra 
 incbevmrq naq jrer gurersber pbafvqrerq arire gb unir rkvfgrq. Gurer jnf n 
 pregnva svgarff va guvf, fvapr ure bja uhfonaq unq orra incbevmrq n pbhcyr 
 bs lrnef rneyvre. Naq n srj phovpyrf njnl n zvyq, varssrpghny, qernzl 
 perngher anzrq Nzcyrsbegu, jvgu irel unvel rnef naq n fhecevfvat gnyrag sbe 
 whttyvat jvgu eulzrf naq zrgerf, jnf ratntrq va cebqhpvat tneoyrq irefvbaf 
 -- qrsvavgvir grkgf, gurl jrer pnyyrq -- bs cbrzf juvpu unq orpbzr 
 vqrbybtvpnyyl bssrafvir, ohg juvpu sbe bar ernfba be nabgure jrer gb or 
 ergnvarq va gur nagubybtvrf. Naq guvf unyy, jvgu vgf svsgl jbexref be 
 gurernobhgf, jnf bayl bar fho-frpgvba, n fvatyr pryy, nf vg jrer, va gur 
 uhtr pbzcyrkvgl bs gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag. Orlbaq, nobir, orybj, jrer bgure 
 fjnezf bs jbexref ratntrq va na havzntvanoyr zhygvghqr bs wbof. Gurer jrer 
 gur uhtr cevagvat-fubcf jvgu gurve fho-rqvgbef, gurve glcbtencul rkcregf, 
 naq gurve rynobengryl rdhvccrq fghqvbf sbe gur snxvat bs cubgbtencuf. Gurer 
 jnf gur gryr-cebtenzzrf frpgvba jvgu vgf ratvarref, vgf cebqhpref, naq vgf 
 grnzf bs npgbef fcrpvnyyl pubfra sbe gurve fxvyy va vzvgngvat ibvprf. Gurer 
 jrer gur nezvrf bs ersrerapr pyrexf jubfr wbo jnf fvzcyl gb qenj hc yvfgf 
 bs obbxf naq crevbqvpnyf juvpu jrer qhr sbe erpnyy. Gurer jrer gur infg 
 ercbfvgbevrf jurer gur pbeerpgrq qbphzragf jrer fgberq, naq gur uvqqra 
 sheanprf jurer gur bevtvany pbcvrf jrer qrfgeblrq. Naq fbzrjurer be bgure, 
 dhvgr nabalzbhf, gurer jrer gur qverpgvat oenvaf jub pb-beqvangrq gur jubyr 
 rssbeg naq ynvq qbja gur yvarf bs cbyvpl juvpu znqr vg arprffnel gung guvf 
 sentzrag bs gur cnfg fubhyq or cerfreirq, gung bar snyfvsvrq, naq gur bgure 
 ehoorq bhg bs rkvfgrapr. 
 Naq gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag, nsgre nyy, jnf vgfrys bayl n fvatyr oenapu 
 bs gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu, jubfr cevznel wbo jnf abg gb erpbafgehpg gur cnfg 
 ohg gb fhccyl gur pvgvmraf bs Bprnavn jvgu arjfcncref, svyzf, grkgobbxf, 
 gryrfperra cebtenzzrf, cynlf, abiryf -- jvgu rirel pbaprvinoyr xvaq bs 
 vasbezngvba, vafgehpgvba, be ragregnvazrag, sebz n fgnghr gb n fybtna, sebz 
 n ylevp cbrz gb n ovbybtvpny gerngvfr, naq sebz n puvyq'f fcryyvat-obbx gb 
 n Arjfcrnx qvpgvbanel. Naq gur Zvavfgel unq abg bayl gb fhccyl gur 
 zhygvsnevbhf arrqf bs gur cnegl, ohg nyfb gb ercrng gur jubyr bcrengvba ng 
 n ybjre yriry sbe gur orarsvg bs gur cebyrgnevng. Gurer jnf n jubyr punva 
 bs frcnengr qrcnegzragf qrnyvat jvgu cebyrgnevna yvgrengher, zhfvp, qenzn, 
 naq ragregnvazrag trarenyyl. Urer jrer cebqhprq ehoovful arjfcncref 
 pbagnvavat nyzbfg abguvat rkprcg fcbeg, pevzr naq nfgebybtl, frafngvbany 
 svir-prag abiryrggrf, svyzf bbmvat jvgu frk, naq fragvzragny fbatf juvpu 
 jrer pbzcbfrq ragveryl ol zrpunavpny zrnaf ba n fcrpvny xvaq bs 
 xnyrvqbfpbcr xabja nf n irefvsvpngbe. Gurer jnf rira n jubyr fho-frpgvba -- 
 Cbeabfrp, vg jnf pnyyrq va Arjfcrnx -- ratntrq va cebqhpvat gur ybjrfg xvaq 
 bs cbeabtencul, juvpu jnf frag bhg va frnyrq cnpxrgf naq juvpu ab Cnegl 
 zrzore, bgure guna gubfr jub jbexrq ba vg, jnf crezvggrq gb ybbx ng. 
 Guerr zrffntrf unq fyvq bhg bs gur carhzngvp ghor juvyr Jvafgba jnf 
 jbexvat, ohg gurl jrer fvzcyr znggref, naq ur unq qvfcbfrq bs gurz orsber 
 gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr vagreehcgrq uvz. Jura gur Ungr jnf bire ur erghearq gb 
 uvf phovpyr, gbbx gur Arjfcrnx qvpgvbanel sebz gur furys, chfurq gur 
 fcrnxjevgr gb bar fvqr, pyrnarq uvf fcrpgnpyrf, naq frggyrq qbja gb uvf 
 znva wbo bs gur zbeavat. 
 Jvafgba'f terngrfg cyrnfher va yvsr jnf va uvf jbex. Zbfg bs vg jnf n 
 grqvbhf ebhgvar, ohg vapyhqrq va vg gurer jrer nyfb wbof fb qvssvphyg naq 
