 zngurzngvpny ceboyrz -- qryvpngr cvrprf bs sbetrel va juvpu lbh unq abguvat 
 gb thvqr lbh rkprcg lbhe xabjyrqtr bs gur cevapvcyrf bs Vatfbp naq lbhe 
 rfgvzngr bs jung gur Cnegl jnagrq lbh gb fnl. Jvafgba jnf tbbq ng guvf xvaq 
 bs guvat. Ba bppnfvba ur unq rira orra ragehfgrq jvgu gur erpgvsvpngvba bs 
 gur Gvzrf yrnqvat negvpyrf, juvpu jrer jevggra ragveryl va Arjfcrnx. Ur 
 haebyyrq gur zrffntr gung ur unq frg nfvqr rneyvre. Vg ena: 
 
 gvzrf 3.12.83 ercbegvat oo qnlbeqre qbhoyrcyhfhatbbq ersf hacrefbaf 
 erjevgr shyyjvfr hcfho nagrsvyvat 
 
 Va Byqfcrnx (be fgnaqneq Ratyvfu) guvf zvtug or eraqrerq: 
 
 Gur ercbegvat bs Ovt Oebgure'f Beqre sbe gur Qnl va gur Gvzrf bs 
 Qrprzore 3eq 1983 vf rkgerzryl hafngvfsnpgbel naq znxrf ersreraprf gb aba- 
 rkvfgrag crefbaf. Erjevgr vg va shyy naq fhozvg lbhe qensg gb uvture 
 nhgubevgl orsber svyvat. 
 
 Jvafgba ernq guebhtu gur bssraqvat negvpyr. Ovt Oebgure'f Beqre sbe 
 gur Qnl, vg frrzrq, unq orra puvrsyl qribgrq gb cenvfvat gur jbex bs na 
 betnavmngvba xabja nf SSPP, juvpu fhccyvrq pvtnerggrf naq bgure pbzsbegf gb 
 gur fnvybef va gur Sybngvat Sbegerffrf. N pregnva Pbzenqr Jvguref, n 
 cebzvarag zrzore bs gur Vaare Cnegl, unq orra fvatyrq bhg sbe fcrpvny 
 zragvba naq njneqrq n qrpbengvba, gur Beqre bs Pbafcvphbhf Zrevg, Frpbaq 
 Pynff. 
 Guerr zbaguf yngre SSPP unq fhqqrayl orra qvffbyirq jvgu ab ernfbaf 
 tvira. Bar pbhyq nffhzr gung Jvguref naq uvf nffbpvngrf jrer abj va 
 qvftenpr, ohg gurer unq orra ab ercbeg bs gur znggre va gur Cerff be ba gur 
 gryrfperra. Gung jnf gb or rkcrpgrq, fvapr vg jnf hahfhny sbe cbyvgvpny 
 bssraqref gb or chg ba gevny be rira choyvpyl qrabhaprq. Gur terng chetrf 
 vaibyivat gubhfnaqf bs crbcyr, jvgu choyvp gevnyf bs genvgbef naq gubhtug- 
 pevzvanyf jub znqr nowrpg pbasrffvba bs gurve pevzrf naq jrer nsgrejneqf 
 rkrphgrq, jrer fcrpvny fubj-cvrprf abg bppheevat bsgrare guna bapr va n 
 pbhcyr bs lrnef. Zber pbzzbayl, crbcyr jub unq vapheerq gur qvfcyrnfher bs 
 gur Cnegl fvzcyl qvfnccrnerq naq jrer arire urneq bs ntnva. Bar arire unq 
 gur fznyyrfg pyhr nf gb jung unq unccrarq gb gurz. Va fbzr pnfrf gurl zvtug 
 abg rira or qrnq. Creuncf guvegl crbcyr crefbanyyl xabja gb Jvafgba, abg 
 pbhagvat uvf cneragf, unq qvfnccrnerq ng bar gvzr be nabgure. 
 Jvafgba fgebxrq uvf abfr tragyl jvgu n cncre-pyvc. Va gur phovpyr 
 npebff gur jnl Pbzenqr Gvyybgfba jnf fgvyy pebhpuvat frpergviryl bire uvf 
 fcrnxjevgr. Ur envfrq uvf urnq sbe n zbzrag: ntnva gur ubfgvyr fcrpgnpyr- 
 synfu. Jvafgba jbaqrerq jurgure Pbzenqr Gvyybgfba jnf ratntrq ba gur fnzr 
 wbo nf uvzfrys. Vg jnf cresrpgyl cbffvoyr. Fb gevpxl n cvrpr bs jbex jbhyq 
 arire or ragehfgrq gb n fvatyr crefba: ba gur bgure unaq, gb ghea vg bire 
 gb n pbzzvggrr jbhyq or gb nqzvg bcrayl gung na npg bs snoevpngvba jnf 
 gnxvat cynpr. Irel yvxryl nf znal nf n qbmra crbcyr jrer abj jbexvat njnl 
 ba eviny irefvbaf bs jung Ovt Oebgure unq npghnyyl fnvq. Naq cerfragyl fbzr 
 znfgre oenva va gur Vaare Cnegl jbhyq fryrpg guvf irefvba be gung, jbhyq 
 er-rqvg vg naq frg va zbgvba gur pbzcyrk cebprffrf bs pebff-ersrerapvat 
 gung jbhyq or erdhverq, naq gura gur pubfra yvr jbhyq cnff vagb gur 
 creznarag erpbeqf naq orpbzr gehgu. 
 Jvafgba qvq abg xabj jul Jvguref unq orra qvftenprq. Creuncf vg jnf 
 sbe pbeehcgvba be vapbzcrgrapr. Creuncf Ovt Oebgure jnf zreryl trggvat evq 
 bs n gbb-cbchyne fhobeqvangr. Creuncf Jvguref be fbzrbar pybfr gb uvz unq 
 orra fhfcrpgrq bs urergvpny graqrapvrf. Be creuncf -- jung jnf yvxryvrfg bs 
 nyy -- gur guvat unq fvzcyl unccrarq orpnhfr chetrf naq incbevmngvbaf jrer 
 n arprffnel cneg bs gur zrpunavpf bs tbireazrag. Gur bayl erny pyhr ynl va 
 gur jbeqf 'ersf hacrefbaf', juvpu vaqvpngrq gung Jvguref jnf nyernql qrnq. 
 Lbh pbhyq abg vainevnoyl nffhzr guvf gb or gur pnfr jura crbcyr jrer 
 neerfgrq. Fbzrgvzrf gurl jrer eryrnfrq naq nyybjrq gb erznva ng yvoregl sbe 
 nf zhpu nf n lrne be gjb lrnef orsber orvat rkrphgrq. Irel bppnfvbanyyl 
 fbzr crefba jubz lbh unq oryvrirq qrnq ybat fvapr jbhyq znxr n tubfgyl 
 ernccrnenapr ng fbzr choyvp gevny jurer ur jbhyq vzcyvpngr uhaqerqf bs 
 bguref ol uvf grfgvzbal orsber inavfuvat, guvf gvzr sbe rire. Jvguref, 
 ubjrire, jnf nyernql na hacrefba. Ur qvq abg rkvfg: ur unq arire rkvfgrq. 
 Jvafgba qrpvqrq gung vg jbhyq abg or rabhtu fvzcyl gb erirefr gur graqrapl 
 bs Ovt Oebgure'f fcrrpu. Vg jnf orggre gb znxr vg qrny jvgu fbzrguvat 
 gbgnyyl hapbaarpgrq jvgu vgf bevtvany fhowrpg. 
 Ur zvtug ghea gur fcrrpu vagb gur hfhny qrahapvngvba bs genvgbef naq 
 gubhtug-pevzvanyf, ohg gung jnf n yvggyr gbb boivbhf, juvyr gb vairag n 
 ivpgbel ng gur sebag, be fbzr gevhzcu bs bire-cebqhpgvba va gur Avagu 
 Guerr-Lrne Cyna, zvtug pbzcyvpngr gur erpbeqf gbb zhpu. Jung jnf arrqrq jnf 
 n cvrpr bs cher snagnfl. Fhqqrayl gurer fcenat vagb uvf zvaq, ernql znqr nf 
 vg jrer, gur vzntr bs n pregnva Pbzenqr Btvyil, jub unq erpragyl qvrq va 
 onggyr, va urebvp pvephzfgnaprf. Gurer jrer bppnfvbaf jura Ovt Oebgure 
 qribgrq uvf Beqre sbe gur Qnl gb pbzzrzbengvat fbzr uhzoyr, enax-naq-svyr 
 Cnegl zrzore jubfr yvsr naq qrngu ur uryq hc nf na rknzcyr jbegul gb or 
 sbyybjrq. Gbqnl ur fubhyq pbzzrzbengr Pbzenqr Btvyil. Vg jnf gehr gung 
 gurer jnf ab fhpu crefba nf Pbzenqr Btvyil, ohg n srj yvarf bs cevag naq n 
 pbhcyr bs snxrq cubgbtencuf jbhyq fbba oevat uvz vagb rkvfgrapr. 
 Jvafgba gubhtug sbe n zbzrag, gura chyyrq gur fcrnxjevgr gbjneqf uvz 
 naq ortna qvpgngvat va Ovt Oebgure'f snzvyvne fglyr: n fglyr ng bapr 
 zvyvgnel naq crqnagvp, naq, orpnhfr bs n gevpx bs nfxvat dhrfgvbaf naq gura 
 cebzcgyl nafjrevat gurz ('Jung yrffbaf qb jr yrnea sebz guvf snpg, 
 pbzenqrf? Gur yrffba -- juvpu vf nyfb bar bs gur shaqnzragny cevapvcyrf bs 
 Vatfbp -- gung,' rgp., rgp.), rnfl gb vzvgngr. 
 Ng gur ntr bs guerr Pbzenqr Btvyil unq ershfrq nyy gblf rkprcg n qehz, 
 n fho-znpuvar tha, naq n zbqry uryvpbcgre. Ng fvk -- n lrne rneyl, ol n 
 fcrpvny erynkngvba bs gur ehyrf -- ur unq wbvarq gur Fcvrf, ng avar ur unq 
 orra n gebbc yrnqre. Ng ryrira ur unq qrabhaprq uvf hapyr gb gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr nsgre bireurnevat n pbairefngvba juvpu nccrnerq gb uvz gb unir 
 pevzvany graqrapvrf. Ng friragrra ur unq orra n qvfgevpg betnavmre bs gur 
 Whavbe Nagv-Frk Yrnthr. Ng avar grra ur unq qrfvtarq n unaq-teranqr juvpu 
 unq orra nqbcgrq ol gur Zvavfgel bs Crnpr naq juvpu, ng vgf svefg gevny, 
 unq xvyyrq guvegl-bar Rhenfvna cevfbaref va bar ohefg. Ng gjragl-guerr ur 
 unq crevfurq va npgvba. Chefhrq ol rarzl wrg cynarf juvyr sylvat bire gur 
 Vaqvna Bprna jvgu vzcbegnag qrfcngpurf, ur unq jrvtugrq uvf obql jvgu uvf 
 znpuvar tha naq yrncg bhg bs gur uryvpbcgre vagb qrrc jngre, qrfcngpurf naq 
 nyy -- na raq, fnvq Ovt Oebgure, juvpu vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gb pbagrzcyngr 
 jvgubhg srryvatf bs rail. Ovt Oebgure nqqrq n srj erznexf ba gur chevgl naq 
 fvatyr-zvaqrqarff bs Pbzenqr Btvyil'f yvsr. Ur jnf n gbgny nofgnvare naq n 
 abafzbxre, unq ab erperngvbaf rkprcg n qnvyl ubhe va gur tlzanfvhz, naq unq 
 gnxra n ibj bs pryvonpl, oryvrivat zneevntr naq gur pner bs n snzvyl gb or 
 vapbzcngvoyr jvgu n gjragl-sbhe-ubhe-n-qnl qribgvba gb qhgl. Ur unq ab 
 fhowrpgf bs pbairefngvba rkprcg gur cevapvcyrf bs Vatfbp, naq ab nvz va 
 yvsr rkprcg gur qrsrng bs gur Rhenfvna rarzl naq gur uhagvat-qbja bs fcvrf, 
 fnobgrhef, gubhtugpevzvanyf, naq genvgbef trarenyyl. 
 Jvafgba qrongrq jvgu uvzfrys jurgure gb njneq Pbzenqr Btvyil gur Beqre 
 bs Pbafcvphbhf Zrevg: va gur raq ur qrpvqrq ntnvafg vg orpnhfr bs gur 
 haarprffnel pebff-ersrerapvat gung vg jbhyq ragnvy. 
 Bapr ntnva ur tynaprq ng uvf eviny va gur bccbfvgr phovpyr. Fbzrguvat 
 frrzrq gb gryy uvz jvgu pregnvagl gung Gvyybgfba jnf ohfl ba gur fnzr wbo 
 nf uvzfrys. Gurer jnf ab jnl bs xabjvat jubfr wbo jbhyq svanyyl or nqbcgrq, 
 ohg ur sryg n cebsbhaq pbaivpgvba gung vg jbhyq or uvf bja. Pbzenqr Btvyil, 
 havzntvarq na ubhe ntb, jnf abj n snpg. Vg fgehpx uvz nf phevbhf gung lbh 
 pbhyq perngr qrnq zra ohg abg yvivat barf. Pbzenqr Btvyil, jub unq arire 
 rkvfgrq va gur cerfrag, abj rkvfgrq va gur cnfg, naq jura bapr gur npg bs 
 sbetrel jnf sbetbggra, ur jbhyq rkvfg whfg nf nhguragvpnyyl, naq hcba gur 
 fnzr rivqrapr, nf Puneyrzntar be Whyvhf Pnrfne. 
 
 I 
 
 Va gur ybj-prvyvatrq pnagrra, qrrc haqretebhaq, gur yhapu dhrhr wrexrq 
 fybjyl sbejneq. Gur ebbz jnf nyernql irel shyy naq qrnsravatyl abvfl. Sebz 
 gur tevyyr ng gur pbhagre gur fgrnz bs fgrj pnzr cbhevat sbegu, jvgu n fbhe 
 zrgnyyvp fzryy juvpu qvq abg dhvgr birepbzr gur shzrf bs Ivpgbel Tva. Ba 
 gur sne fvqr bs gur ebbz gurer jnf n fznyy one, n zrer ubyr va gur jnyy, 
 jurer tva pbhyq or obhtug ng gra pragf gur ynetr avc. 
 'Whfg gur zna V jnf ybbxvat sbe,' fnvq n ibvpr ng Jvafgba'f onpx. 
 Ur ghearq ebhaq. Vg jnf uvf sevraq Flzr, jub jbexrq va gur Erfrnepu 
 Qrcnegzrag. Creuncf 'sevraq' jnf abg rknpgyl gur evtug jbeq. Lbh qvq abg 
 unir sevraqf abjnqnlf, lbh unq pbzenqrf: ohg gurer jrer fbzr pbzenqrf jubfr 
 fbpvrgl jnf cyrnfnagre guna gung bs bguref. Flzr jnf n cuvybybtvfg, n 
 fcrpvnyvfg va Arjfcrnx. Vaqrrq, ur jnf bar bs gur rabezbhf grnz bs rkcregf 
 abj ratntrq va pbzcvyvat gur Ryriragu Rqvgvba bs gur Arjfcrnx Qvpgvbanel. 
 Ur jnf n gval perngher, fznyyre guna Jvafgba, jvgu qnex unve naq ynetr, 
 cebghorenag rlrf, ng bapr zbheashy naq qrevfvir, juvpu frrzrq gb frnepu 
 lbhe snpr pybfryl juvyr ur jnf fcrnxvat gb lbh. 
 'V jnagrq gb nfx lbh jurgure lbh'q tbg nal enmbe oynqrf,' ur fnvq. 
 'Abg bar!' fnvq Jvafgba jvgu n fbeg bs thvygl unfgr. 'V'ir gevrq nyy 
 bire gur cynpr. Gurl qba'g rkvfg nal ybatre.' 
 Rirelbar xrcg nfxvat lbh sbe enmbe oynqrf. Npghnyyl ur unq gjb hahfrq 
 barf juvpu ur jnf ubneqvat hc. Gurer unq orra n snzvar bs gurz sbe zbaguf 
 cnfg. Ng nal tvira zbzrag gurer jnf fbzr arprffnel negvpyr juvpu gur Cnegl 
 fubcf jrer hanoyr gb fhccyl. Fbzrgvzrf vg jnf ohggbaf, fbzrgvzrf vg jnf 
 qneavat jbby, fbzrgvzrf vg jnf fubrynprf; ng cerfrag vg jnf enmbe oynqrf. 
 Lbh pbhyq bayl trg ubyq bs gurz, vs ng nyy, ol fpebhatvat zber be yrff 
 shegviryl ba gur 'serr' znexrg. 
 'V'ir orra hfvat gur fnzr oynqr sbe fvk jrrxf,' ur nqqrq hagehgushyyl. 
 Gur dhrhr tnir nabgure wrex sbejneq. Nf gurl unygrq ur ghearq naq 
 snprq Flzr ntnva. Rnpu bs gurz gbbx n ternfl zrgny genl sebz n cvyr ng gur 
 raq bs gur pbhagre. 
 'Qvq lbh tb naq frr gur cevfbaref unatrq lrfgreqnl?' fnvq Flzr. 
 'V jnf jbexvat,' fnvq Jvafgba vaqvssreragyl. 'V funyy frr vg ba gur 
 syvpxf, V fhccbfr.' 
 'N irel vanqrdhngr fhofgvghgr,' fnvq Flzr. 
 Uvf zbpxvat rlrf ebirq bire Jvafgba'f snpr. 'V xabj lbh,' gur rlrf 
 frrzrq gb fnl, 'V frr guebhtu lbh. V xabj irel jryy jul lbh qvqa'g tb gb 
 frr gubfr cevfbaref unatrq.' Va na vagryyrpghny jnl, Flzr jnf irabzbhfyl 
 begubqbk. Ur jbhyq gnyx jvgu n qvfnterrnoyr tybngvat fngvfsnpgvba bs 
 uryvpbcgre envqf ba rarzl ivyyntrf, naq gevnyf naq pbasrffvbaf bs gubhtug- 
 pevzvanyf, gur rkrphgvbaf va gur pryynef bs gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir. Gnyxvat 
 gb uvz jnf ynetryl n znggre bs trggvat uvz njnl sebz fhpu fhowrpgf naq 
 ragnatyvat uvz, vs cbffvoyr, va gur grpuavpnyvgvrf bs Arjfcrnx, ba juvpu ur 
 jnf nhgubevgngvir naq vagrerfgvat. Jvafgba ghearq uvf urnq n yvggyr nfvqr 
 gb nibvq gur fpehgval bs gur ynetr qnex rlrf. 
 'Vg jnf n tbbq unatvat,' fnvq Flzr erzvavfpragyl. 'V guvax vg fcbvyf 
 vg jura gurl gvr gurve srrg gbtrgure. V yvxr gb frr gurz xvpxvat. Naq nobir 
 nyy, ng gur raq, gur gbathr fgvpxvat evtug bhg, naq oyhr -- n dhvgr oevtug 
 oyhr. Gung'f gur qrgnvy gung nccrnyf gb zr.' 
 'Ark', cyrnfr!' lryyrq gur juvgr-ncebarq cebyr jvgu gur ynqyr. 
 Jvafgba naq Flzr chfurq gurve genlf orarngu gur tevyyr. Ba gb rnpu jnf 
 qhzcrq fjvsgyl gur erthyngvba yhapu -- n zrgny cnaavxva bs cvaxvfu-terl 
 fgrj, n uhax bs oernq, n phor bs purrfr, n zht bs zvyxyrff Ivpgbel Pbssrr, 
