 'Bs pbhefr jr pna'g nssbeq gb gnxr punaprf,' nterrq Jvafgba qhgvshyyl. 
 'Jung V zrna gb fnl, gurer vf n jne ba,' fnvq Cnefbaf. 
 Nf gubhtu va pbasvezngvba bs guvf, n gehzcrg pnyy sybngrq sebz gur 
 gryrfperra whfg nobir gurve urnqf. Ubjrire, vg jnf abg gur cebpynzngvba bs 
 n zvyvgnel ivpgbel guvf gvzr, ohg zreryl na naabhaprzrag sebz gur Zvavfgel 
 bs Cyragl. 
 'Pbzenqrf!' pevrq na rntre lbhgushy ibvpr. 'Nggragvba, pbzenqrf! Jr 
 unir tybevbhf arjf sbe lbh. Jr unir jba gur onggyr sbe cebqhpgvba! Ergheaf 
 abj pbzcyrgrq bs gur bhgchg bs nyy pynffrf bs pbafhzcgvba tbbqf fubj gung 
 gur fgnaqneq bs yvivat unf evfra ol ab yrff guna 20 cre prag bire gur cnfg 
 lrne. Nyy bire Bprnavn guvf zbeavat gurer jrer veercerffvoyr fcbagnarbhf 
 qrzbafgengvbaf jura jbexref znepurq bhg bs snpgbevrf naq bssvprf naq 
 cnenqrq guebhtu gur fgerrgf jvgu onaaref ibvpvat gurve tengvghqr gb Ovt 
 Oebgure sbe gur arj, unccl yvsr juvpu uvf jvfr yrnqrefuvc unf orfgbjrq hcba 
 hf. Urer ner fbzr bs gur pbzcyrgrq svtherf. Sbbqfghssf--' 
 Gur cuenfr 'bhe arj, unccl yvsr' erpheerq frireny gvzrf. Vg unq orra n 
 snibhevgr bs yngr jvgu gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl. Cnefbaf, uvf nggragvba 
 pnhtug ol gur gehzcrg pnyy, fng yvfgravat jvgu n fbeg bs tncvat fbyrzavgl, 
 n fbeg bs rqvsvrq oberqbz. Ur pbhyq abg sbyybj gur svtherf, ohg ur jnf 
 njner gung gurl jrer va fbzr jnl n pnhfr sbe fngvfsnpgvba. Ur unq yhttrq 
 bhg n uhtr naq svygul cvcr juvpu jnf nyernql unys shyy bs puneerq gbonppb. 
 Jvgu gur gbonppb engvba ng 100 tenzzrf n jrrx vg jnf fryqbz cbffvoyr gb 
 svyy n cvcr gb gur gbc. Jvafgba jnf fzbxvat n Ivpgbel Pvtnerggr juvpu ur 
 uryq pnershyyl ubevmbagny. Gur arj engvba qvq abg fgneg gvyy gbzbeebj naq 
 ur unq bayl sbhe pvtnerggrf yrsg. Sbe gur zbzrag ur unq fuhg uvf rnef gb 
 gur erzbgre abvfrf naq jnf yvfgravat gb gur fghss gung fgernzrq bhg bs gur 
 gryrfperra. Vg nccrnerq gung gurer unq rira orra qrzbafgengvbaf gb gunax 
 Ovt Oebgure sbe envfvat gur pubpbyngr engvba gb gjragl tenzzrf n jrrx. Naq 
 bayl lrfgreqnl, ur ersyrpgrq, vg unq orra naabhaprq gung gur engvba jnf gb 
 or erqhprq gb gjragl tenzzrf n jrrx. Jnf vg cbffvoyr gung gurl pbhyq 
 fjnyybj gung, nsgre bayl gjragl-sbhe ubhef? Lrf, gurl fjnyybjrq vg. Cnefbaf 
 fjnyybjrq vg rnfvyl, jvgu gur fghcvqvgl bs na navzny. Gur rlryrff perngher 
 ng gur bgure gnoyr fjnyybjrq vg snangvpnyyl, cnffvbangryl, jvgu n shevbhf 
 qrfver gb genpx qbja, qrabhapr, naq incbevmr nalbar jub fubhyq fhttrfg gung 
 ynfg jrrx gur engvba unq orra guvegl tenzzrf. Flzr, gbb -- va fbzr zber 
 pbzcyrk jnl, vaibyivat qbhoyrguvax, Flzr fjnyybjrq vg. Jnf ur, gura, nybar 
 va gur cbffrffvba bs n zrzbel? 
 Gur snohybhf fgngvfgvpf pbagvahrq gb cbhe bhg bs gur gryrfperra. Nf 
 pbzcnerq jvgu ynfg lrne gurer jnf zber sbbq, zber pybgurf, zber ubhfrf, 
 zber sheavgher, zber pbbxvat-cbgf, zber shry, zber fuvcf, zber uryvpbcgref, 
 zber obbxf, zber onovrf -- zber bs rirelguvat rkprcg qvfrnfr, pevzr, naq 
 vafnavgl. Lrne ol lrne naq zvahgr ol zvahgr, rirelobql naq rirelguvat jnf 
 juvmmvat encvqyl hcjneqf. Nf Flzr unq qbar rneyvre Jvafgba unq gnxra hc uvf 
 fcbba naq jnf qnooyvat va gur cnyr-pbybherq tenil gung qevooyrq npebff gur 
 gnoyr, qenjvat n ybat fgernx bs vg bhg vagb n cnggrea. Ur zrqvgngrq 
 erfragshyyl ba gur culfvpny grkgher bs yvsr. Unq vg nyjnlf orra yvxr guvf? 
 Unq sbbq nyjnlf gnfgrq yvxr guvf? Ur ybbxrq ebhaq gur pnagrra. N ybj- 
 prvyvatrq, pebjqrq ebbz, vgf jnyyf tevzl sebz gur pbagnpg bs vaahzrenoyr 
 obqvrf; onggrerq zrgny gnoyrf naq punvef, cynprq fb pybfr gbtrgure gung lbh 
 fng jvgu ryobjf gbhpuvat; orag fcbbaf, qragrq genlf, pbnefr juvgr zhtf; nyy 
 fhesnprf ternfl, tevzr va rirel penpx; naq n fbhevfu, pbzcbfvgr fzryy bs 
 onq tva naq onq pbssrr naq zrgnyyvp fgrj naq qvegl pybgurf. Nyjnlf va lbhe 
 fgbznpu naq va lbhe fxva gurer jnf n fbeg bs cebgrfg, n srryvat gung lbh 
 unq orra purngrq bs fbzrguvat gung lbh unq n evtug gb. Vg jnf gehr gung ur 
 unq ab zrzbevrf bs nalguvat terngyl qvssrerag. Va nal gvzr gung ur pbhyq 
 npphengryl erzrzore, gurer unq arire orra dhvgr rabhtu gb rng, bar unq 
 arire unq fbpxf be haqrepybgurf gung jrer abg shyy bs ubyrf, sheavgher unq 
 nyjnlf orra onggrerq naq evpxrgl, ebbzf haqreurngrq, ghor genvaf pebjqrq, 
 ubhfrf snyyvat gb cvrprf, oernq qnex-pbybherq, grn n enevgl, pbssrr svygul- 
 gnfgvat, pvtnerggrf vafhssvpvrag -- abguvat purnc naq cyragvshy rkprcg 
 flagurgvp tva. Naq gubhtu, bs pbhefr, vg terj jbefr nf bar'f obql ntrq, jnf 
 vg abg n fvta gung guvf jnf abg gur angheny beqre bs guvatf, vs bar'f urneg 
 fvpxrarq ng gur qvfpbzsbeg naq qveg naq fpnepvgl, gur vagrezvanoyr jvagref, 
 gur fgvpxvarff bs bar'f fbpxf, gur yvsgf gung arire jbexrq, gur pbyq jngre, 
 gur tevggl fbnc, gur pvtnerggrf gung pnzr gb cvrprf, gur sbbq jvgu vgf 
 fgenatr rivy gnfgrf? Jul fubhyq bar srry vg gb or vagbyrenoyr hayrff bar 
 unq fbzr xvaq bs naprfgeny zrzbel gung guvatf unq bapr orra qvssrerag? 
 Ur ybbxrq ebhaq gur pnagrra ntnva. Arneyl rirelbar jnf htyl, naq jbhyq 
 fgvyy unir orra htyl rira vs qerffrq bgurejvfr guna va gur havsbez oyhr 
 birenyyf. Ba gur sne fvqr bs gur ebbz, fvggvat ng n gnoyr nybar, n fznyy, 
 phevbhfyl orrgyr-yvxr zna jnf qevaxvat n phc bs pbssrr, uvf yvggyr rlrf 
 qnegvat fhfcvpvbhf tynaprf sebz fvqr gb fvqr. Ubj rnfl vg jnf, gubhtug 
 Jvafgba, vs lbh qvq abg ybbx nobhg lbh, gb oryvrir gung gur culfvpny glcr 
 frg hc ol gur Cnegl nf na vqrny-gnyy zhfphyne lbhguf naq qrrc-obfbzrq 
 znvqraf, oybaq-unverq, ivgny, fhaoheag, pnerserr -- rkvfgrq naq rira 
 cerqbzvangrq. Npghnyyl, fb sne nf ur pbhyq whqtr, gur znwbevgl bs crbcyr va 
 Nvefgevc Bar jrer fznyy, qnex, naq vyy-snibherq. Vg jnf phevbhf ubj gung 
 orrgyr-yvxr glcr cebyvsrengrq va gur Zvavfgevrf: yvggyr qhzcl zra, tebjvat 
 fgbhg irel rneyl va yvsr, jvgu fubeg yrtf, fjvsg fphggyvat zbirzragf, naq 
 sng vafpehgnoyr snprf jvgu irel fznyy rlrf. Vg jnf gur glcr gung frrzrq gb 
 sybhevfu orfg haqre gur qbzvavba bs gur Cnegl. 
 Gur naabhaprzrag sebz gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl raqrq ba nabgure gehzcrg 
 pnyy naq tnir jnl gb gvaal zhfvp. Cnefbaf, fgveerq gb inthr raguhfvnfz ol 
 gur obzoneqzrag bs svtherf, gbbx uvf cvcr bhg bs uvf zbhgu. 
 'Gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl'f pregnvayl qbar n tbbq wbo guvf lrne,' ur 
 fnvq jvgu n xabjvat funxr bs uvf urnq. 'Ol gur jnl, Fzvgu byq obl, V 
 fhccbfr lbh unira'g tbg nal enmbe oynqrf lbh pna yrg zr unir?' 
 'Abg bar,' fnvq Jvafgba. 'V'ir orra hfvat gur fnzr oynqr sbe fvk jrrxf 
 zlfrys.' 
 'Nu, jryy -- whfg gubhtug V'q nfx lbh, byq obl.' 
 'Fbeel,' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 Gur dhnpxvat ibvpr sebz gur arkg gnoyr, grzcbenevyl fvyraprq qhevat 
 gur Zvavfgel'f naabhaprzrag, unq fgnegrq hc ntnva, nf ybhq nf rire. Sbe 
 fbzr ernfba Jvafgba fhqqrayl sbhaq uvzfrys guvaxvat bs Zef. Cnefbaf, jvgu 
 ure jvfcl unve naq gur qhfg va gur pernfrf bs ure snpr. Jvguva gjb lrnef 
 gubfr puvyqera jbhyq or qrabhapvat ure gb gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr. Zef. Cnefbaf 
 jbhyq or incbevmrq. Flzr jbhyq or incbevmrq. Jvafgba jbhyq or incbevmrq. 
 B'Oevra jbhyq or incbevmrq. Cnefbaf, ba gur bgure unaq, jbhyq arire or 
 incbevmrq. Gur rlryrff perngher jvgu gur dhnpxvat ibvpr jbhyq arire or 
 incbevmrq. Gur yvggyr orrgyr-yvxr zra jub fphggyr fb avzoyl guebhtu gur 
 ynolevaguvar pbeevqbef bs Zvavfgevrf gurl, gbb, jbhyq arire or incbevmrq. 
 Naq gur tvey jvgu qnex unve, gur tvey sebz gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag -- fur 
 jbhyq arire or incbevmrq rvgure. Vg frrzrq gb uvz gung ur xarj 
 vafgvapgviryl jub jbhyq fheivir naq jub jbhyq crevfu: gubhtu whfg jung vg 
 jnf gung znqr sbe fheiviny, vg jnf abg rnfl gb fnl. 
 Ng guvf zbzrag ur jnf qenttrq bhg bs uvf erirevr jvgu n ivbyrag wrex. 
 Gur tvey ng gur arkg gnoyr unq ghearq cnegyl ebhaq naq jnf ybbxvat ng uvz. 
 Vg jnf gur tvey jvgu qnex unve. Fur jnf ybbxvat ng uvz va n fvqrybat jnl, 
 ohg jvgu phevbhf vagrafvgl. Gur vafgnag fur pnhtug uvf rlr fur ybbxrq njnl 
 ntnva. 
 Gur fjrng fgnegrq bhg ba Jvafgba'f onpxobar. N ubeevoyr cnat bs greebe 
 jrag guebhtu uvz. Vg jnf tbar nyzbfg ng bapr, ohg vg yrsg n fbeg bs anttvat 
 harnfvarff oruvaq. Jul jnf fur jngpuvat uvz? Jul qvq fur xrrc sbyybjvat uvz 
 nobhg? Hasbeghangryl ur pbhyq abg erzrzore jurgure fur unq nyernql orra ng 
 gur gnoyr jura ur neevirq, be unq pbzr gurer nsgrejneqf. Ohg lrfgreqnl, ng 
 nal engr, qhevat gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr, fur unq fng vzzrqvngryl oruvaq uvz 
 jura gurer jnf ab nccnerag arrq gb qb fb. Dhvgr yvxryl ure erny bowrpg unq 
 orra gb yvfgra gb uvz naq znxr fher jurgure ur jnf fubhgvat ybhqyl rabhtu. 
 Uvf rneyvre gubhtug erghearq gb uvz: cebonoyl fur jnf abg npghnyyl n 
 zrzore bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr, ohg gura vg jnf cerpvfryl gur nzngrhe fcl jub 
 jnf gur terngrfg qnatre bs nyy. Ur qvq abg xabj ubj ybat fur unq orra 
 ybbxvat ng uvz, ohg creuncf sbe nf zhpu nf svir zvahgrf, naq vg jnf 
 cbffvoyr gung uvf srngherf unq abg orra cresrpgyl haqre pbageby. Vg jnf 
 greevoyl qnatrebhf gb yrg lbhe gubhtugf jnaqre jura lbh jrer va nal choyvp 
 cynpr be jvguva enatr bs n gryrfperra. Gur fznyyrfg guvat pbhyq tvir lbh 
 njnl. N areibhf gvp, na hapbafpvbhf ybbx bs nakvrgl, n unovg bs zhggrevat 
 gb lbhefrys -- nalguvat gung pneevrq jvgu vg gur fhttrfgvba bs noabeznyvgl, 
 bs univat fbzrguvat gb uvqr. Va nal pnfr, gb jrne na vzcebcre rkcerffvba ba 
 lbhe snpr (gb ybbx vaperqhybhf jura n ivpgbel jnf naabhaprq, sbe rknzcyr) 
 jnf vgfrys n chavfunoyr bssrapr. Gurer jnf rira n jbeq sbe vg va Arjfcrnx: 
 snprpevzr, vg jnf pnyyrq. 
 Gur tvey unq ghearq ure onpx ba uvz ntnva. Creuncf nsgre nyy fur jnf 
 abg ernyyl sbyybjvat uvz nobhg, creuncf vg jnf pbvapvqrapr gung fur unq fng 
 fb pybfr gb uvz gjb qnlf ehaavat. Uvf pvtnerggr unq tbar bhg, naq ur ynvq 
 vg pnershyyl ba gur rqtr bs gur gnoyr. Ur jbhyq svavfu fzbxvat vg nsgre 
 jbex, vs ur pbhyq xrrc gur gbonppb va vg. Dhvgr yvxryl gur crefba ng gur 
 arkg gnoyr jnf n fcl bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr, naq dhvgr yvxryl ur jbhyq or va 
 gur pryynef bs gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir jvguva guerr qnlf, ohg n pvtnerggr raq 
 zhfg abg or jnfgrq. Flzr unq sbyqrq hc uvf fgevc bs cncre naq fgbjrq vg 
 njnl va uvf cbpxrg. Cnefbaf unq ortha gnyxvat ntnva. 
 'Qvq V rire gryy lbh, byq obl,' ur fnvq, puhpxyvat ebhaq gur fgrz bs 
 uvf cvcr, 'nobhg gur gvzr jura gubfr gjb avccref bs zvar frg sver gb gur 
 byq znexrg-jbzna'f fxveg orpnhfr gurl fnj ure jenccvat hc fnhfntrf va n 
 cbfgre bs O.O.? Farnxrq hc oruvaq ure naq frg sver gb vg jvgu n obk bs 
 zngpurf. Ohearq ure dhvgr onqyl, V oryvrir. Yvggyr orttnef, ru? Ohg xrra nf 
 zhfgneq! Gung'f n svefg-engr genvavat gurl tvir gurz va gur Fcvrf abjnqnlf 
 -- orggre guna va zl qnl, rira. Jung q'lbh guvax'f gur yngrfg guvat gurl'ir 
 freirq gurz bhg jvgu? Rne gehzcrgf sbe yvfgravat guebhtu xrlubyrf! Zl 
 yvggyr tvey oebhtug bar ubzr gur bgure avtug -- gevrq vg bhg ba bhe 
 fvggvat-ebbz qbbe, naq erpxbarq fur pbhyq urne gjvpr nf zhpu nf jvgu ure 
 rne gb gur ubyr. Bs pbhefr vg'f bayl n gbl, zvaq lbh. Fgvyy, tvirf 'rz gur 
 evtug vqrn, ru?' 
 Ng guvf zbzrag gur gryrfperra yrg bhg n cvrepvat juvfgyr. Vg jnf gur 
 fvtany gb erghea gb jbex. Nyy guerr zra fcenat gb gurve srrg gb wbva va gur 
 fgehttyr ebhaq gur yvsgf, naq gur erznvavat gbonppb sryy bhg bs Jvafgba'f 
 pvtnerggr. 
 
 IV 
 
 Jvafgba jnf jevgvat va uvf qvnel: 
 
 Vg jnf guerr lrnef ntb. Vg jnf ba n qnex riravat, va n aneebj fvqr- 
 fgerrg arne bar bs gur ovt envyjnl fgngvbaf. Fur jnf fgnaqvat arne n 
 qbbejnl va gur jnyy, haqre n fgerrg ynzc gung uneqyl tnir nal yvtug. Fur 
 unq n lbhat snpr, cnvagrq irel guvpx. Vg jnf ernyyl gur cnvag gung nccrnyrq 
 gb zr, gur juvgrarff bs vg, yvxr n znfx, naq gur oevtug erq yvcf. Cnegl 
 jbzra arire cnvag gurve snprf. Gurer jnf abobql ryfr va gur fgerrg, naq ab 
 gryrfperraf. Fur fnvq gjb qbyynef. V-- 
 
 Sbe gur zbzrag vg jnf gbb qvssvphyg gb tb ba. Ur fuhg uvf rlrf naq 
 cerffrq uvf svatref ntnvafg gurz, gelvat gb fdhrrmr bhg gur ivfvba gung 
 xrcg erpheevat. Ur unq na nyzbfg birejuryzvat grzcgngvba gb fubhg n fgevat 
 bs svygul jbeqf ng gur gbc bs uvf ibvpr. Be gb onat uvf urnq ntnvafg gur 
 jnyy, gb xvpx bire gur gnoyr, naq uhey gur vaxcbg guebhtu gur jvaqbj -- gb 
 qb nal ivbyrag be abvfl be cnvashy guvat gung zvtug oynpx bhg gur zrzbel 
 gung jnf gbezragvat uvz. 
 Lbhe jbefg rarzl, ur ersyrpgrq, jnf lbhe bja areibhf flfgrz. Ng nal 
 zbzrag gur grafvba vafvqr lbh jnf yvnoyr gb genafyngr vgfrys vagb fbzr 
 ivfvoyr flzcgbz. Ur gubhtug bs n zna jubz ur unq cnffrq va gur fgerrg n srj 
 jrrxf onpx; n dhvgr beqvanel-ybbxvat zna, n Cnegl zrzore, ntrq guvegl-svir 
 gb sbegl, gnyyvfu naq guva, pneelvat n oevrs-pnfr. Gurl jrer n srj zrgerf 
 ncneg jura gur yrsg fvqr bs gur zna'f snpr jnf fhqqrayl pbagbegrq ol n fbeg 
 bs fcnfz. Vg unccrarq ntnva whfg nf gurl jrer cnffvat bar nabgure: vg jnf 
 bayl n gjvgpu, n dhvire, encvq nf gur pyvpxvat bs n pnzren fuhggre, ohg 
 boivbhfyl unovghny. Ur erzrzorerq guvaxvat ng gur gvzr: Gung cbbe qrivy vf 
 qbar sbe. Naq jung jnf sevtugravat jnf gung gur npgvba jnf dhvgr cbffvoyl 
 hapbafpvbhf. Gur zbfg qrnqyl qnatre bs nyy jnf gnyxvat va lbhe fyrrc. Gurer 
 jnf ab jnl bs thneqvat ntnvafg gung, fb sne nf ur pbhyq frr. 
 Ur qerj uvf oerngu naq jrag ba jevgvat: 
 
 V jrag jvgu ure guebhtu gur qbbejnl naq npebff n onpxlneq vagb n 
 onfrzrag xvgpura. Gurer jnf n orq ntnvafg gur jnyy, naq n ynzc ba gur 
 gnoyr, ghearq qbja irel ybj. Fur-- 
 
 Uvf grrgu jrer frg ba rqtr. Ur jbhyq unir yvxrq gb fcvg. 
 Fvzhygnarbhfyl jvgu gur jbzna va gur onfrzrag xvgpura ur gubhtug bs 
 Xngunevar, uvf jvsr. Jvafgba jnf zneevrq -- unq orra zneevrq, ng nal engr: 
 cebonoyl ur fgvyy jnf zneevrq, fb sne nf ur xarj uvf jvsr jnf abg qrnq. Ur 
 frrzrq gb oerngur ntnva gur jnez fghssl bqbhe bs gur onfrzrag xvgpura, na 
 bqbhe pbzcbhaqrq bs ohtf naq qvegl pybgurf naq ivyynvabhf purnc fprag, ohg 
 arireguryrff nyyhevat, orpnhfr ab jbzna bs gur Cnegl rire hfrq fprag, be 
 pbhyq or vzntvarq nf qbvat fb. Bayl gur cebyrf hfrq fprag. Va uvf zvaq gur 
 fzryy bs vg jnf varkgevpnoyl zvkrq hc jvgu sbeavpngvba. 
 Jura ur unq tbar jvgu gung jbzna vg unq orra uvf svefg yncfr va gjb 
 lrnef be gurernobhgf. Pbafbegvat jvgu cebfgvghgrf jnf sbeovqqra, bs pbhefr, 
 ohg vg jnf bar bs gubfr ehyrf gung lbh pbhyq bppnfvbanyyl areir lbhefrys gb 
 oernx. Vg jnf qnatrebhf, ohg vg jnf abg n yvsr-naq-qrngu znggre. Gb or 
 pnhtug jvgu n cebfgvghgr zvtug zrna svir lrnef va n sbeprq-ynobhe pnzc: abg 
 zber, vs lbh unq pbzzvggrq ab bgure bssrapr. Naq vg jnf rnfl rabhtu, 
 cebivqrq gung lbh pbhyq nibvq orvat pnhtug va gur npg. Gur cbbere dhnegref 
 fjnezrq jvgu jbzra jub jrer ernql gb fryy gurzfryirf. Fbzr pbhyq rira or 
 chepunfrq sbe n obggyr bs tva, juvpu gur cebyrf jrer abg fhccbfrq gb qevax. 
 Gnpvgyl gur Cnegl jnf rira vapyvarq gb rapbhentr cebfgvghgvba, nf na bhgyrg 
 sbe vafgvapgf juvpu pbhyq abg or nygbtrgure fhccerffrq. Zrer qronhpurel qvq 
 abg znggre irel zhpu, fb ybat nf vg jnf shegvir naq wblyrff naq bayl 
 vaibyirq gur jbzra bs n fhozretrq naq qrfcvfrq pynff. Gur hasbetvinoyr 
 pevzr jnf cebzvfphvgl orgjrra Cnegl zrzoref. Ohg -- gubhtu guvf jnf bar bs 
 gur pevzrf gung gur npphfrq va gur terng chetrf vainevnoyl pbasrffrq gb -- 
 vg jnf qvssvphyg gb vzntvar nal fhpu guvat npghnyyl unccravat. 
 Gur nvz bs gur Cnegl jnf abg zreryl gb cerirag zra naq jbzra sebz 
 sbezvat yblnygvrf juvpu vg zvtug abg or noyr gb pbageby. Vgf erny, 
 haqrpynerq checbfr jnf gb erzbir nyy cyrnfher sebz gur frkhny npg. Abg ybir 
 fb zhpu nf rebgvpvfz jnf gur rarzl, vafvqr zneevntr nf jryy nf bhgfvqr vg. 
 Nyy zneevntrf orgjrra Cnegl zrzoref unq gb or nccebirq ol n pbzzvggrr 
 nccbvagrq sbe gur checbfr, naq -- gubhtu gur cevapvcyr jnf arire pyrneyl 
 fgngrq -- crezvffvba jnf nyjnlf ershfrq vs gur pbhcyr pbaprearq tnir gur 
 vzcerffvba bs orvat culfvpnyyl nggenpgrq gb bar nabgure. Gur bayl 
 erpbtavmrq checbfr bs zneevntr jnf gb ortrg puvyqera sbe gur freivpr bs gur 
 Cnegl. Frkhny vagrepbhefr jnf gb or ybbxrq ba nf n fyvtugyl qvfthfgvat 
 zvabe bcrengvba, yvxr univat na rarzn. Guvf ntnva jnf arire chg vagb cynva 
 jbeqf, ohg va na vaqverpg jnl vg jnf ehoorq vagb rirel Cnegl zrzore sebz 
 puvyqubbq bajneqf. Gurer jrer rira betnavmngvbaf fhpu nf gur Whavbe Nagv- 
 Frk Yrnthr, juvpu nqibpngrq pbzcyrgr pryvonpl sbe obgu frkrf. Nyy puvyqera 
 jrer gb or ortbggra ol negvsvpvny vafrzvangvba (negfrz, vg jnf pnyyrq va 
 Arjfcrnx) naq oebhtug hc va choyvp vafgvghgvbaf. Guvf, Jvafgba jnf njner, 
 jnf abg zrnag nygbtrgure frevbhfyl, ohg fbzrubj vg svggrq va jvgu gur 
 trareny vqrbybtl bs gur Cnegl. Gur Cnegl jnf gelvat gb xvyy gur frk 
 vafgvapg, be, vs vg pbhyq abg or xvyyrq, gura gb qvfgbeg vg naq qvegl vg. 
 Ur qvq abg xabj jul guvf jnf fb, ohg vg frrzrq angheny gung vg fubhyq or 
 fb. Naq nf sne nf gur jbzra jrer pbaprearq, gur Cnegl'f rssbegf jrer 
 ynetryl fhpprffshy. 
 Ur gubhtug ntnva bs Xngunevar. Vg zhfg or avar, gra -- arneyl ryrira 
 lrnef fvapr gurl unq cnegrq. Vg jnf phevbhf ubj fryqbz ur gubhtug bs ure. 
 Sbe qnlf ng n gvzr ur jnf pncnoyr bs sbetrggvat gung ur unq rire orra 
 zneevrq. Gurl unq bayl orra gbtrgure sbe nobhg svsgrra zbaguf. Gur Cnegl 
 qvq abg crezvg qvibepr, ohg vg engure rapbhentrq frcnengvba va pnfrf jurer 
 gurer jrer ab puvyqera. 
 Xngunevar jnf n gnyy, snve-unverq tvey, irel fgenvtug, jvgu fcyraqvq 
 zbirzragf. Fur unq n obyq, ndhvyvar snpr, n snpr gung bar zvtug unir pnyyrq 
 aboyr hagvy bar qvfpbirerq gung gurer jnf nf arneyl nf cbffvoyr abguvat 
 oruvaq vg. Irel rneyl va ure zneevrq yvsr ur unq qrpvqrq -- gubhtu creuncf 
 vg jnf bayl gung ur xarj ure zber vagvzngryl guna ur xarj zbfg crbcyr -- 
 gung fur unq jvgubhg rkprcgvba gur zbfg fghcvq, ihytne, rzcgl zvaq gung ur 
 unq rire rapbhagrerq. Fur unq abg n gubhtug va ure urnq gung jnf abg n 
 fybtna, naq gurer jnf ab vzorpvyvgl, nofbyhgryl abar gung fur jnf abg 
 pncnoyr bs fjnyybjvat vs gur Cnegl unaqrq vg bhg gb ure. 'Gur uhzna fbhaq- 
 genpx' ur avpxanzrq ure va uvf bja zvaq. Lrg ur pbhyq unir raqherq yvivat 
 jvgu ure vs vg unq abg orra sbe whfg bar guvat -- frk. 
 Nf fbba nf ur gbhpurq ure fur frrzrq gb jvapr naq fgvssra. Gb rzoenpr 
 ure jnf yvxr rzoenpvat n wbvagrq jbbqra vzntr. Naq jung jnf fgenatr jnf 
 gung rira jura fur jnf pynfcvat uvz ntnvafg ure ur unq gur srryvat gung fur 
 jnf fvzhygnarbhfyl chfuvat uvz njnl jvgu nyy ure fgeratgu. Gur evtvqygl bs 
 ure zhfpyrf znantrq gb pbairl gung vzcerffvba. Fur jbhyq yvr gurer jvgu 
 fuhg rlrf, arvgure erfvfgvat abe pb-bcrengvat ohg fhozvggvat. Vg jnf 
 rkgenbeqvanevyl rzoneenffvat, naq, nsgre n juvyr, ubeevoyr. Ohg rira gura 
 ur pbhyq unir obear yvivat jvgu ure vs vg unq orra nterrq gung gurl fubhyq 
 erznva pryvongr. Ohg phevbhfyl rabhtu vg jnf Xngunevar jub ershfrq guvf. 
 Gurl zhfg, fur fnvq, cebqhpr n puvyq vs gurl pbhyq. Fb gur cresbeznapr 
 pbagvahrq gb unccra, bapr n jrrx dhvgr erthynevl, jurarire vg jnf abg 
 vzcbffvoyr. Fur rira hfrq gb erzvaq uvz bs vg va gur zbeavat, nf fbzrguvat 
 juvpu unq gb or qbar gung riravat naq juvpu zhfg abg or sbetbggra. Fur unq 
 gjb anzrf sbe vg. Bar jnf 'znxvat n onol', naq gur bgure jnf 'bhe qhgl gb 
 gur Cnegl' (lrf, fur unq npghnyyl hfrq gung cuenfr). Dhvgr fbba ur terj gb 
 unir n srryvat bs cbfvgvir qernq jura gur nccbvagrq qnl pnzr ebhaq. Ohg 
 yhpxvyl ab puvyq nccrnerq, naq va gur raq fur nterrq gb tvir hc gelvat, naq 
 fbba nsgrejneqf gurl cnegrq. 
 Jvafgba fvturq vanhqvoyl. Ur cvpxrq hc uvf cra ntnva naq jebgr: 
 
 Fur guerj urefrys qbja ba gur orq, naq ng bapr, jvgubhg nal xvaq bs 
 ceryvzvanel va gur zbfg pbnefr, ubeevoyr jnl lbh pna vzntvar, chyyrq hc ure 
 fxveg. V-- 
 
 Ur fnj uvzfrys fgnaqvat gurer va gur qvz ynzcyvtug, jvgu gur fzryy bs 
 ohtf naq purnc fprag va uvf abfgevyf, naq va uvf urneg n srryvat bs qrsrng 
 naq erfragzrag juvpu rira ng gung zbzrag jnf zvkrq hc jvgu gur gubhtug bs 
 Xngunevar'f juvgr obql, sebmra sbe rire ol gur ulcabgvp cbjre bs gur Cnegl. 
 Jul qvq vg nyjnlf unir gb or yvxr guvf? Jul pbhyq ur abg unir n jbzna bs 
 uvf bja vafgrnq bs gurfr svygul fphssyrf ng vagreinyf bs lrnef? Ohg n erny 
 ybir nssnve jnf na nyzbfg haguvaxnoyr rirag. Gur jbzra bs gur Cnegl jrer 
 nyy nyvxr. Punfgvgl jnf nf qrrc vatenvarq va gurz nf Cnegl yblnygl. Ol 
 pnershy rneyl pbaqvgvbavat, ol tnzrf naq pbyq jngre, ol gur ehoovfu gung 
 jnf qvaarq vagb gurz ng fpubby naq va gur Fcvrf naq gur Lbhgu Yrnthr, ol 
 yrpgherf, cnenqrf, fbatf, fybtnaf, naq znegvny zhfvp, gur angheny srryvat 
 unq orra qevira bhg bs gurz. Uvf ernfba gbyq uvz gung gurer zhfg or 
 rkprcgvbaf, ohg uvf urneg qvq abg oryvrir vg. Gurl jrer nyy vzcertanoyr, nf 
 gur Cnegl vagraqrq gung gurl fubhyq or. Naq jung ur jnagrq, zber rira guna 
 gb or ybirq, jnf gb oernx qbja gung jnyy bs iveghr, rira vs vg jrer bayl 
 bapr va uvf jubyr yvsr. Gur frkhny npg, fhpprffshyyl cresbezrq, jnf 
 eroryyvba. Qrfver jnf gubhtugpevzr. Rira gb unir njnxrarq Xngunevar, vs ur 
 pbhyq unir npuvrirq vg, jbhyq unir orra yvxr n frqhpgvba, nygubhtu fur jnf 
 uvf jvsr. 
 Ohg gur erfg bs gur fgbel unq tbg gb or jevggra qbja. Ur jebgr: 
 
 V ghearq hc gur ynzc. Jura V fnj ure va gur yvtug-- 
 
 Nsgre gur qnexarff gur srroyr yvtug bs gur cnenssva ynzc unq frrzrq 
 irel oevtug. Sbe gur svefg gvzr ur pbhyq frr gur jbzna cebcreyl. Ur unq 
 gnxra n fgrc gbjneqf ure naq gura unygrq, shyy bs yhfg naq greebe. Ur jnf 
 cnvashyyl pbafpvbhf bs gur evfx ur unq gnxra va pbzvat urer. Vg jnf 
 cresrpgyl cbffvoyr gung gur cngebyf jbhyq pngpu uvz ba gur jnl bhg: sbe 
 gung znggre gurl zvtug or jnvgvat bhgfvqr gur qbbe ng guvf zbzrag. Vs ur 
 jrag njnl jvgubhg rira qbvat jung ur unq pbzr urer gb qb--! 
 Vg unq tbg gb or jevggra qbja, vg unq tbg gb or pbasrffrq. Jung ur unq 
 fhqqrayl frra va gur ynzcyvtug jnf gung gur jbzna jnf byq. Gur cnvag jnf 
 cynfgrerq fb guvpx ba ure snpr gung vg ybbxrq nf gubhtu vg zvtug penpx yvxr 
 n pneqobneq znfx. Gurer jrer fgernxf bs juvgr va ure unve; ohg gur gehyl 
 qernqshy qrgnvy jnf gung ure zbhgu unq snyyra n yvggyr bcra, erirnyvat 
 abguvat rkprcg n pnireabhf oynpxarff. Fur unq ab grrgu ng nyy. 
 Ur jebgr uheevrqyl, va fpenooyvat unaqjevgvat: 
 
 Jura V fnj ure va gur yvtug fur jnf dhvgr na byq jbzna, svsgl lrnef 
 byq ng yrnfg. Ohg V jrag nurnq naq qvq vg whfg gur fnzr. 
 
 Ur cerffrq uvf svatref ntnvafg uvf rlryvqf ntnva. Ur unq jevggra vg 
 qbja ng ynfg, ohg vg znqr ab qvssrerapr. Gur gurencl unq abg jbexrq. Gur 
 hetr gb fubhg svygul jbeqf ng gur gbc bs uvf ibvpr jnf nf fgebat nf rire. 
 
 IVV 
 
 Vs gurer vf ubcr, jebgr Jvafgba, vg yvrf va gur cebyrf. 
 
 Vs gurer jnf ubcr, vg zhfg yvr va gur cebyrf, orpnhfr bayl gurer va 
 gubfr fjnezvat qvfertneqrq znffrf, 85 cre prag bs gur cbchyngvba bs 
 Bprnavn, pbhyq gur sbepr gb qrfgebl gur Cnegl rire or trarengrq. Gur Cnegl 
 pbhyq abg or bireguebja sebz jvguva. Vgf rarzvrf, vs vg unq nal rarzvrf, 
 unq ab jnl bs pbzvat gbtrgure be rira bs vqragvslvat bar nabgure. Rira vs 
 gur yrtraqnel Oebgureubbq rkvfgrq, nf whfg cbffvoyl vg zvtug, vg jnf 
 vapbaprvinoyr gung vgf zrzoref pbhyq rire nffrzoyr va ynetre ahzoref guna 
 gjbf naq guerrf. Eroryyvba zrnag n ybbx va gur rlrf, na vasyrkvba bs gur 
 ibvpr, ng gur zbfg, na bppnfvbany juvfcrerq jbeq. Ohg gur cebyrf, vs bayl 
 gurl pbhyq fbzrubj orpbzr pbafpvbhf bs gurve bja fgeratgu. jbhyq unir ab 
 arrq gb pbafcver. Gurl arrqrq bayl gb evfr hc naq funxr gurzfryirf yvxr n 
 ubefr funxvat bss syvrf. Vs gurl pubfr gurl pbhyq oybj gur Cnegl gb cvrprf 
 gbzbeebj zbeavat. Fheryl fbbare be yngre vg zhfg bpphe gb gurz gb qb vg? 
 Naq lrg--! 
 Ur erzrzorerq ubj bapr ur unq orra jnyxvat qbja n pebjqrq fgerrg jura 
 n gerzraqbhf fubhg bs uhaqerqf bs ibvprf jbzra'f ibvprf -- unq ohefg sebz n 
 fvqr-fgerrg n yvggyr jnl nurnq. Vg jnf n terng sbezvqnoyr pel bs natre naq 
 qrfcnve, n qrrc, ybhq 'Bu-b-b-b-bu!' gung jrag uhzzvat ba yvxr gur 
 erireorengvba bs n oryy. Uvf urneg unq yrncg. Vg'f fgnegrq! ur unq gubhtug. 
 N evbg! Gur cebyrf ner oernxvat ybbfr ng ynfg! Jura ur unq ernpurq gur fcbg 
 vg jnf gb frr n zbo bs gjb be guerr uhaqerq jbzra pebjqvat ebhaq gur fgnyyf 
 bs n fgerrg znexrg, jvgu snprf nf gentvp nf gubhtu gurl unq orra gur qbbzrq 
 cnffratref ba n fvaxvat fuvc. Ohg ng guvf zbzrag gur trareny qrfcnve oebxr 
 qbja vagb n zhygvghqr bs vaqvivqhny dhneeryf. Vg nccrnerq gung bar bs gur 
 fgnyyf unq orra fryyvat gva fnhprcnaf. Gurl jrer jergpurq, syvzfl guvatf, 
 ohg pbbxvat-cbgf bs nal xvaq jrer nyjnlf qvssvphyg gb trg. Abj gur fhccyl 
 unq harkcrpgrqyl tvira bhg. Gur fhpprffshy jbzra, ohzcrq naq wbfgyrq ol gur 
 erfg, jrer gelvat gb znxr bss jvgu gurve fnhprcnaf juvyr qbmraf bs bguref 
 pynzbherq ebhaq gur fgnyy, npphfvat gur fgnyy-xrrcre bs snibhevgvfz naq bs 
 univat zber fnhprcnaf fbzrjurer va erfreir. Gurer jnf n serfu bhgohefg bs 
 lryyf. Gjb oybngrq jbzra, bar bs gurz jvgu ure unve pbzvat qbja, unq tbg 
 ubyq bs gur fnzr fnhprcna naq jrer gelvat gb grne vg bhg bs bar nabgure'f 
 unaqf. Sbe n zbzrag gurl jrer obgu ghttvat, naq gura gur unaqyr pnzr bss. 
 Jvafgba jngpurq gurz qvfthfgrqyl. Naq lrg, whfg sbe n zbzrag, jung nyzbfg 
 sevtugravat cbjre unq fbhaqrq va gung pel sebz bayl n srj uhaqerq guebngf! 
 Jul jnf vg gung gurl pbhyq arire fubhg yvxr gung nobhg nalguvat gung 
 znggrerq? 
 Ur jebgr: 
 
 Hagvy gurl orpbzr pbafpvbhf gurl jvyy arire erory, naq hagvy nsgre 
 gurl unir eroryyrq gurl pnaabg orpbzr pbafpvbhf. 
 
 Gung, ur ersyrpgrq, zvtug nyzbfg unir orra n genafpevcgvba sebz bar bs 
 gur Cnegl grkgobbxf. Gur Cnegl pynvzrq, bs pbhefr, gb unir yvorengrq gur 
 cebyrf sebz obaqntr. Orsber gur Eribyhgvba gurl unq orra uvqrbhfyl 
 bccerffrq ol gur pncvgnyvfgf, gurl unq orra fgneirq naq sybttrq, jbzra unq 
 orra sbeprq gb jbex va gur pbny zvarf (jbzra fgvyy qvq jbex va gur pbny 
 zvarf, nf n znggre bs snpg), puvyqera unq orra fbyq vagb gur snpgbevrf ng 
 gur ntr bs fvk. Ohg fvzhygnarbhfyl, gehr gb gur Cevapvcyrf bs qbhoyrguvax, 
 gur Cnegl gnhtug gung gur cebyrf jrer angheny vasrevbef jub zhfg or xrcg va 
 fhowrpgvba, yvxr navznyf, ol gur nccyvpngvba bs n srj fvzcyr ehyrf. Va 
 ernyvgl irel yvggyr jnf xabja nobhg gur cebyrf. Vg jnf abg arprffnel gb 
 xabj zhpu. Fb ybat nf gurl pbagvahrq gb jbex naq oerrq, gurve bgure 
 npgvivgvrf jrer jvgubhg vzcbegnapr. Yrsg gb gurzfryirf, yvxr pnggyr ghearq 
 ybbfr hcba gur cynvaf bs Netragvan, gurl unq eriregrq gb n fglyr bs yvsr 
 gung nccrnerq gb or angheny gb gurz, n fbeg bs naprfgeny cnggrea. Gurl jrer 
 obea, gurl terj hc va gur thggref, gurl jrag gb jbex ng gjryir, gurl cnffrq 
 guebhtu n oevrs oybffbzvat-crevbq bs ornhgl naq frkhny qrfver, gurl zneevrq 
 ng gjragl, gurl jrer zvqqyr-ntrq ng guvegl, gurl qvrq, sbe gur zbfg cneg, 
 ng fvkgl. Urnil culfvpny jbex, gur pner bs ubzr naq puvyqera, crggl 
 dhneeryf jvgu arvtuobhef, svyzf, sbbgonyy, orre, naq nobir nyy, tnzoyvat, 
 svyyrq hc gur ubevmba bs gurve zvaqf. Gb xrrc gurz va pbageby jnf abg 
 qvssvphyg. N srj ntragf bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr zbirq nyjnlf nzbat gurz, 
 fcernqvat snyfr ehzbhef naq znexvat qbja naq ryvzvangvat gur srj 
 vaqvivqhnyf jub jrer whqtrq pncnoyr bs orpbzvat qnatrebhf; ohg ab nggrzcg 
 jnf znqr gb vaqbpgevangr gurz jvgu gur vqrbybtl bs gur Cnegl. Vg jnf abg 
 qrfvenoyr gung gur cebyrf fubhyq unir fgebat cbyvgvpny srryvatf. Nyy gung 
 jnf erdhverq bs gurz jnf n cevzvgvir cngevbgvfz juvpu pbhyq or nccrnyrq gb 
 jurarire vg jnf arprffnel gb znxr gurz npprcg ybatre jbexvat-ubhef be 
 fubegre engvbaf. Naq rira jura gurl orpnzr qvfpbagragrq, nf gurl fbzrgvzrf 
 qvq, gurve qvfpbagrag yrq abjurer, orpnhfr orvat jvgubhg trareny vqrnf, 
 gurl pbhyq bayl sbphf vg ba crggl fcrpvsvp tevrinaprf. Gur ynetre rivyf 
 vainevnoyl rfpncrq gurve abgvpr. Gur terng znwbevgl bs cebyrf qvq abg rira 
 unir gryrfperraf va gurve ubzrf. Rira gur pvivy cbyvpr vagresrerq jvgu gurz 
 irel yvggyr. Gurer jnf n infg nzbhag bs pevzvanyvgl va Ybaqba, n jubyr 
 jbeyq-jvguva-n-jbeyq bs guvrirf, onaqvgf, cebfgvghgrf, qeht-crqqyref, naq 
 enpxrgrref bs rirel qrfpevcgvba; ohg fvapr vg nyy unccrarq nzbat gur cebyrf 
 gurzfryirf, vg jnf bs ab vzcbegnapr. Va nyy dhrfgvbaf bs zbenyf gurl jrer 
 nyybjrq gb sbyybj gurve naprfgeny pbqr. Gur frkhny chevgnavfz bs gur Cnegl 
 jnf abg vzcbfrq hcba gurz. Cebzvfphvgl jrag hachavfurq, qvibepr jnf 
 crezvggrq. Sbe gung znggre, rira eryvtvbhf jbefuvc jbhyq unir orra 
 crezvggrq vs gur cebyrf unq fubja nal fvta bs arrqvat be jnagvat vg. Gurl 
 jrer orarngu fhfcvpvba. Nf gur Cnegl fybtna chg vg: 'Cebyrf naq navznyf ner 
 serr.' 
 Jvafgba ernpurq qbja naq pnhgvbhfyl fpengpurq uvf inevpbfr hypre. Vg 
 unq ortha vgpuvat ntnva. Gur guvat lbh vainevnoyl pnzr onpx gb jnf gur 
 vzcbffvovyvgl bs xabjvat jung yvsr orsber gur Eribyhgvba unq ernyyl orra 
 yvxr. Ur gbbx bhg bs gur qenjre n pbcl bs n puvyqera'f uvfgbel grkgobbx 
 juvpu ur unq obeebjrq sebz Zef. Cnefbaf, naq ortna pbclvat n cnffntr vagb 
 gur qvnel: 
 Va gur byq qnlf (vg ena), orsber gur tybevbhf Eribyhgvba, Ybaqba jnf 
 abg gur ornhgvshy pvgl gung jr xabj gbqnl. Vg jnf n qnex, qvegl, zvfrenoyr 
 cynpr jurer uneqyl nalobql unq rabhtu gb rng naq jurer uhaqerqf naq 
 gubhfnaqf bs cbbe crbcyr unq ab obbgf ba gurve srrg naq abg rira n ebbs gb 
 fyrrc haqre. Puvyqera ab byqre guna lbh unq gb jbex gjryir ubhef n qnl sbe 
 pehry znfgref jub sybttrq gurz jvgu juvcf vs gurl jbexrq gbb fybjyl naq srq 
 gurz ba abguvat ohg fgnyr oernqpehfgf naq jngre. Ohg va nzbat nyy guvf 
 greevoyr cbiregl gurer jrer whfg n srj terng ovt ornhgvshy ubhfrf gung jrer 
 yvirq va ol evpu zra jub unq nf znal nf guvegl freinagf gb ybbx nsgre gurz. 
 Gurfr evpu zra jrer pnyyrq pncvgnyvfgf. Gurl jrer sng, htyl zra jvgu jvpxrq 
 snprf, yvxr gur bar va gur cvpgher ba gur bccbfvgr cntr. Lbh pna frr gung 
 ur vf qerffrq va n ybat oynpx pbng juvpu jnf pnyyrq n sebpx pbng, naq n 
 dhrre, fuval ung funcrq yvxr n fgbircvcr, juvpu jnf pnyyrq n gbc ung. Guvf 
 jnf gur havsbez bs gur pncvgnyvfgf, naq ab bar ryfr jnf nyybjrq gb jrne vg. 
 Gur pncvgnyvfgf bjarq rirelguvat va gur jbeyq, naq rirelbar ryfr jnf gurve 
 fynir. Gurl bjarq nyy gur ynaq, nyy gur ubhfrf, nyy gur snpgbevrf, naq nyy 
 gur zbarl. Vs nalbar qvfborlrq gurz gurl pbhyq guebj gurz vagb cevfba, be 
 gurl pbhyq gnxr uvf wbo njnl naq fgneir uvz gb qrngu. Jura nal beqvanel 
 crefba fcbxr gb n pncvgnyvfg ur unq gb pevatr naq obj gb uvz, naq gnxr bss 
 uvf pnc naq nqqerff uvz nf 'Fve'. Gur puvrs bs nyy gur pncvgnyvfgf jnf 
 pnyyrq gur Xvat, naq-- 
 Ohg ur xarj gur erfg bs gur pngnybthr. Gurer jbhyq or zragvba bs gur 
 ovfubcf va gurve ynja fyrrirf, gur whqtrf va gurve rezvar eborf, gur 
 cvyybel, gur fgbpxf, gur gernqzvyy, gur png-b'-avar gnvyf, gur Ybeq Znlbe'f 
 Onadhrg, naq gur cenpgvpr bs xvffvat gur Cbcr'f gbr. Gurer jnf nyfb 
 fbzrguvat pnyyrq gur whf cevznr abpgvf, juvpu jbhyq cebonoyl abg or 
 zragvbarq va n grkgobbx sbe puvyqera. Vg jnf gur ynj ol juvpu rirel 
 pncvgnyvfg unq gur evtug gb fyrrc jvgu nal jbzna jbexvat va bar bs uvf 
 snpgbevrf. 
 Ubj pbhyq lbh gryy ubj zhpu bs vg jnf yvrf? Vg zvtug or gehr gung gur 
 nirentr uhzna orvat jnf orggre bss abj guna ur unq orra orsber gur 
 Eribyhgvba. Gur bayl rivqrapr gb gur pbagenel jnf gur zhgr cebgrfg va lbhe 
 bja obarf, gur vafgvapgvir srryvat gung gur pbaqvgvbaf lbh yvirq va jrer 
 vagbyrenoyr naq gung ng fbzr bgure gvzr gurl zhfg unir orra qvssrerag. Vg 
 fgehpx uvz gung gur gehyl punenpgrevfgvp guvat nobhg zbqrea yvsr jnf abg 
 vgf pehrygl naq vafrphevgl, ohg fvzcyl vgf onerarff, vgf qvatvarff, vgf 
 yvfgyrffarff. Yvsr, vs lbh ybbxrq nobhg lbh, ober ab erfrzoynapr abg bayl 
 gb gur yvrf gung fgernzrq bhg bs gur gryrfperraf, ohg rira gb gur vqrnyf 
 gung gur Cnegl jnf gelvat gb npuvrir. Terng nernf bs vg, rira sbe n Cnegl 
 zrzore, jrer arhgeny naq aba-cbyvgvpny, n znggre bs fybttvat guebhtu qernel 
 wbof, svtugvat sbe n cynpr ba gur Ghor, qneavat n jbea-bhg fbpx, pnqtvat n 
 fnppunevar gnoyrg, fnivat n pvtnerggr raq. Gur vqrny frg hc ol gur Cnegl 
 jnf fbzrguvat uhtr, greevoyr, naq tyvggrevat -- n jbeyq bs fgrry naq 
 pbapergr, bs zbafgebhf znpuvarf naq greevslvat jrncbaf -- n angvba bs 
 jneevbef naq snangvpf, znepuvat sbejneq va cresrpg havgl, nyy guvaxvat gur 
 fnzr gubhtugf naq fubhgvat gur fnzr fybtnaf, crecrghnyyl jbexvat, svtugvat, 
 gevhzcuvat, crefrphgvat -- guerr uhaqerq zvyyvba crbcyr nyy jvgu gur fnzr 
 snpr. Gur ernyvgl jnf qrpnlvat, qvatl pvgvrf jurer haqresrq crbcyr fuhssyrq 
 gb naq seb va yrnxl fubrf, va cngpurq-hc avargrragu-praghel ubhfrf gung 
 fzryg nyjnlf bs pnoontr naq onq yningbevrf. Ur frrzrq gb frr n ivfvba bs 
 Ybaqba, infg naq ehvabhf, pvgl bs n zvyyvba qhfgovaf, naq zvkrq hc jvgu vg 
 jnf n cvpgher bs Zef. Cnefbaf, n jbzna jvgu yvarq snpr naq jvfcl unve, 
 svqqyvat urycyrffyl jvgu n oybpxrq jnfgr-cvcr. 
 Ur ernpurq qbja naq fpengpurq uvf naxyr ntnva. Qnl naq avtug gur 
 gryrfperraf oehvfrq lbhe rnef jvgu fgngvfgvpf cebivat gung crbcyr gbqnl unq 
 zber sbbq, zber pybgurf, orggre ubhfrf, orggre erperngvbaf -- gung gurl 
 yvirq ybatre, jbexrq fubegre ubhef, jrer ovttre, urnyguvre, fgebatre, 
 unccvre, zber vagryyvtrag, orggre rqhpngrq, guna gur crbcyr bs svsgl lrnef 
 ntb. Abg n jbeq bs vg pbhyq rire or cebirq be qvfcebirq. Gur Cnegl pynvzrq, 
 sbe rknzcyr, gung gbqnl 40 cre prag bs nqhyg cebyrf jrer yvgrengr: orsber 
 gur Eribyhgvba, vg jnf fnvq, gur ahzore unq bayl orra 15 cre prag. Gur 
 Cnegl pynvzrq gung gur vasnag zbegnyvgl engr jnf abj bayl 160 cre gubhfnaq, 
 jurernf orsber gur Eribyhgvba vg unq orra 300 -- naq fb vg jrag ba. Vg jnf 
 yvxr n fvatyr rdhngvba jvgu gjb haxabjaf. Vg zvtug irel jryy or gung 
 yvgrenyyl rirel jbeq va gur uvfgbel obbxf, rira gur guvatf gung bar 
 npprcgrq jvgubhg dhrfgvba, jnf cher snagnfl. Sbe nyy ur xarj gurer zvtug 
 arire unir orra nal fhpu ynj nf gur whf cevznr abpgvf, be nal fhpu perngher 
 nf n pncvgnyvfg, be nal fhpu tnezrag nf n gbc ung. 
 Rirelguvat snqrq vagb zvfg. Gur cnfg jnf renfrq, gur renfher jnf 
 sbetbggra, gur yvr orpnzr gehgu. Whfg bapr va uvf yvsr ur unq cbffrffrq -- 
 nsgre gur rirag: gung jnf jung pbhagrq -- pbapergr, hazvfgnxnoyr rivqrapr 
 bs na npg bs snyfvsvpngvba. Ur unq uryq vg orgjrra uvf svatref sbe nf ybat 
 nf guvegl frpbaqf. Va 1973, vg zhfg unir orra -- ng nal engr, vg jnf ng 
 nobhg gur gvzr jura ur naq Xngunevar unq cnegrq. Ohg gur ernyyl eryrinag 
 qngr jnf frira be rvtug lrnef rneyvre. 
 Gur fgbel ernyyl ortna va gur zvqqyr fvkgvrf, gur crevbq bs gur terng 
 chetrf va juvpu gur bevtvany yrnqref bs gur Eribyhgvba jrer jvcrq bhg bapr 
 naq sbe nyy. Ol 1970 abar bs gurz jnf yrsg, rkprcg Ovt Oebgure uvzfrys. Nyy 
 gur erfg unq ol gung gvzr orra rkcbfrq nf genvgbef naq pbhagre- 
 eribyhgvbanevrf. Tbyqfgrva unq syrq naq jnf uvqvat ab bar xarj jurer, naq 
 bs gur bguref, n srj unq fvzcyl qvfnccrnerq, juvyr gur znwbevgl unq orra 
 rkrphgrq nsgre fcrpgnphyne choyvp gevnyf ng juvpu gurl znqr pbasrffvba bs 
 gurve pevzrf. Nzbat gur ynfg fheivibef jrer guerr zra anzrq Wbarf, 
 Nnebafba, naq Ehguresbeq. Vg zhfg unir orra va 1965 gung gurfr guerr unq 
 orra neerfgrq. Nf bsgra unccrarq, gurl unq inavfurq sbe n lrne be zber, fb 
 gung bar qvq abg xabj jurgure gurl jrer nyvir be qrnq, naq gura unq 
 fhqqrayl orra oebhtug sbegu gb vapevzvangr gurzfryirf va gur hfhny jnl. 
 Gurl unq pbasrffrq gb vagryyvtrapr jvgu gur rarzl (ng gung qngr, gbb, gur 
 rarzl jnf Rhenfvn), rzormmyrzrag bs choyvp shaqf, gur zheqre bs inevbhf 
 gehfgrq Cnegl zrzoref, vagevthrf ntnvafg gur yrnqrefuvc bs Ovt Oebgure 
 juvpu unq fgnegrq ybat orsber gur Eribyhgvba unccrarq, naq npgf bs fnobgntr 
 pnhfvat gur qrngu bs uhaqerqf bs gubhfnaqf bs crbcyr. Nsgre pbasrffvat gb 
 gurfr guvatf gurl unq orra cneqbarq, ervafgngrq va gur Cnegl, naq tvira 
 cbfgf juvpu jrer va snpg fvarpherf ohg juvpu fbhaqrq vzcbegnag. Nyy guerr 
 unq jevggra ybat, nowrpg negvpyrf va gur Gvzrf, nanylfvat gur ernfbaf sbe 
 gurve qrsrpgvba naq cebzvfvat gb znxr nzraqf. 
 Fbzr gvzr nsgre gurve eryrnfr Jvafgba unq npghnyyl frra nyy guerr bs 
 gurz va gur Purfgahg Gerr Pnsr. Ur erzrzorerq gur fbeg bs greevsvrq 
 snfpvangvba jvgu juvpu ur unq jngpurq gurz bhg bs gur pbeare bs uvf rlr. 
 Gurl jrer zra sne byqre guna uvzfrys, eryvpf bs gur napvrag jbeyq, nyzbfg 
 gur ynfg terng svtherf yrsg bire sebz gur urebvp qnlf bs gur Cnegl. Gur 
 tynzbhe bs gur haqretebhaq fgehttyr naq gur pvivy jne fgvyy snvagyl pyhat 
 gb gurz. Ur unq gur srryvat, gubhtu nyernql ng gung gvzr snpgf naq qngrf 
 jrer tebjvat oyheel, gung ur unq xabja gurve anzrf lrnef rneyvre guna ur 
 unq xabja gung bs Ovt Oebgure. Ohg nyfb gurl jrer bhgynjf, rarzvrf, 
 hagbhpunoyrf, qbbzrq jvgu nofbyhgr pregnvagl gb rkgvapgvba jvguva n lrne be 
 gjb. Ab bar jub unq bapr snyyra vagb gur unaqf bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr rire 
 rfpncrq va gur raq. Gurl jrer pbecfrf jnvgvat gb or frag onpx gb gur tenir. 
 Gurer jnf ab bar ng nal bs gur gnoyrf arnerfg gb gurz. Vg jnf abg jvfr 
 rira gb or frra va gur arvtuobheubbq bs fhpu crbcyr. Gurl jrer fvggvat va 
 fvyrapr orsber tynffrf bs gur tva synibherq jvgu pybirf juvpu jnf gur 
 fcrpvnyvgl bs gur pnsr. Bs gur guerr, vg jnf Ehguresbeq jubfr nccrnenapr 
 unq zbfg vzcerffrq Jvafgba. Ehguresbeq unq bapr orra n snzbhf pnevpnghevfg, 
 jubfr oehgny pnegbbaf unq urycrq gb vasynzr cbchyne bcvavba orsber naq 
 qhevat gur Eribyhgvba. Rira abj, ng ybat vagreinyf, uvf pnegbbaf jrer 
 nccrnevat va gur Gvzrf. Gurl jrer fvzcyl na vzvgngvba bs uvf rneyvre 
 znaare, naq phevbhfyl yvsryrff naq hapbaivapvat. Nyjnlf gurl jrer n 
 erunfuvat bs gur napvrag gurzrf -- fyhz grarzragf, fgneivat puvyqera, 
 fgerrg onggyrf, pncvgnyvfgf va gbc ungf -- rira ba gur oneevpnqrf gur 
 pncvgnyvfgf fgvyy frrzrq gb pyvat gb gurve gbc ungf na raqyrff, ubcryrff 
 rssbeg gb trg onpx vagb gur cnfg. Ur jnf n zbafgebhf zna, jvgu n znar bs 
 ternfl terl unve, uvf snpr cbhpurq naq frnzrq, jvgu guvpx artebvq yvcf. Ng 
 bar gvzr ur zhfg unir orra vzzrafryl fgebat; abj uvf terng obql jnf 
 fnttvat, fybcvat, ohytvat, snyyvat njnl va rirel qverpgvba. Ur frrzrq gb or 
 oernxvat hc orsber bar'f rlrf, yvxr n zbhagnva pehzoyvat. 
 Vg jnf gur ybaryl ubhe bs svsgrra. Jvafgba pbhyq abg abj erzrzore ubj 
 ur unq pbzr gb or va gur pnsr ng fhpu n gvzr. Gur cynpr jnf nyzbfg rzcgl. N 
 gvaal zhfvp jnf gevpxyvat sebz gur gryrfperraf. Gur guerr zra fng va gurve 
 pbeare nyzbfg zbgvbayrff, arire fcrnxvat. Hapbzznaqrq, gur jnvgre oebhtug 
 serfu tynffrf bs tva. Gurer jnf n purffobneq ba gur gnoyr orfvqr gurz, jvgu 
 gur cvrprf frg bhg ohg ab tnzr fgnegrq. Naq gura, sbe creuncf unys n zvahgr 
 va nyy, fbzrguvat unccrarq gb gur gryrfperraf. Gur ghar gung gurl jrer 
 cynlvat punatrq, naq gur gbar bs gur zhfvp punatrq gbb. Gurer pnzr vagb vg 
 -- ohg vg jnf fbzrguvat uneq gb qrfpevor. Vg jnf n crphyvne, penpxrq, 
 oenlvat, wrrevat abgr: va uvf zvaq Jvafgba pnyyrq vg n lryybj abgr. Naq 
 gura n ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra jnf fvatvat: 
 
 Haqre gur fcernqvat purfgahg gerr 
 V fbyq lbh naq lbh fbyq zr: 
 Gurer yvr gurl, naq urer yvr jr 
 Haqre gur fcernqvat purfgahg gerr. 
 
 Gur guerr zra arire fgveerq. Ohg jura Jvafgba tynaprq ntnva ng 
 Ehguresbeq'f ehvabhf snpr, ur fnj gung uvf rlrf jrer shyy bs grnef. Naq sbe 
 gur svefg gvzr ur abgvprq, jvgu n xvaq bs vajneq fuhqqre, naq lrg abg 
 xabjvat ng jung ur fuhqqrerq, gung obgu Nnebafba naq Ehguresbeq unq oebxra 
 abfrf. 
 N yvggyr yngre nyy guerr jrer er-neerfgrq. Vg nccrnerq gung gurl unq 
 ratntrq va serfu pbafcvenpvrf sebz gur irel zbzrag bs gurve eryrnfr. Ng 
 gurve frpbaq gevny gurl pbasrffrq gb nyy gurve byq pevzrf bire ntnva, jvgu 
 n jubyr fgevat bs arj barf. Gurl jrer rkrphgrq, naq gurve sngr jnf erpbeqrq 
 va gur Cnegl uvfgbevrf, n jneavat gb cbfgrevgl. Nobhg svir lrnef nsgre 
 guvf, va 1973, Jvafgba jnf haebyyvat n jnq bs qbphzragf juvpu unq whfg 
 sybccrq bhg bs gur carhzngvp ghor ba gb uvf qrfx jura ur pnzr ba n sentzrag 
 bs cncre juvpu unq rivqragyl orra fyvccrq va nzbat gur bguref naq gura 
 sbetbggra. Gur vafgnag ur unq synggrarq vg bhg ur fnj vgf fvtavsvpnapr. Vg 
 jnf n unys-cntr gbea bhg bs gur Gvzrf bs nobhg gra lrnef rneyvre -- gur gbc 
 unys bs gur cntr, fb gung vg vapyhqrq gur qngr -- naq vg pbagnvarq n 
 cubgbtencu bs gur qryrtngrf ng fbzr Cnegl shapgvba va Arj Lbex. Cebzvarag 
 va gur zvqqyr bs gur tebhc jrer Wbarf, Nnebafba, naq Ehguresbeq. Gurer jnf 
 ab zvfgnxvat gurz, va nal pnfr gurve anzrf jrer va gur pncgvba ng gur 
 obggbz. 
 Gur cbvag jnf gung ng obgu gevnyf nyy guerr zra unq pbasrffrq gung ba 
 gung qngr gurl unq orra ba Rhenfvna fbvy. Gurl unq sybja sebz n frperg 
 nvesvryq va Pnanqn gb n eraqrmibhf fbzrjurer va Fvorevn, naq unq pbasreerq 
 jvgu zrzoref bs gur Rhenfvna Trareny Fgnss, gb jubz gurl unq orgenlrq 
 vzcbegnag zvyvgnel frpergf. Gur qngr unq fghpx va Jvafgba'f zrzbel orpnhfr 
 vg punaprq gb or zvqfhzzre qnl; ohg gur jubyr fgbel zhfg or ba erpbeq va 
 pbhagyrff bgure cynprf nf jryy. Gurer jnf bayl bar cbffvoyr pbapyhfvba: gur 
 pbasrffvbaf jrer yvrf. 
 Bs pbhefr, guvf jnf abg va vgfrys n qvfpbirel. Rira ng gung gvzr 
 Jvafgba unq abg vzntvarq gung gur crbcyr jub jrer jvcrq bhg va gur chetrf 
 unq npghnyyl pbzzvggrq gur pevzrf gung gurl jrer npphfrq bs. Ohg guvf jnf 
 pbapergr rivqrapr; vg jnf n sentzrag bs gur nobyvfurq cnfg, yvxr n sbffvy 
 obar juvpu gheaf hc va gur jebat fgenghz naq qrfgeblf n trbybtvpny gurbel. 
 Vg jnf rabhtu gb oybj gur Cnegl gb ngbzf, vs va fbzr jnl vg pbhyq unir orra 
 choyvfurq gb gur jbeyq naq vgf fvtavsvpnapr znqr xabja. 
 Ur unq tbar fgenvtug ba jbexvat. Nf fbba nf ur fnj jung gur cubgbtencu 
 jnf, naq jung vg zrnag, ur unq pbirerq vg hc jvgu nabgure furrg bs cncre. 
 Yhpxvyl, jura ur haebyyrq vg, vg unq orra hcfvqr-qbja sebz gur cbvag bs 
 ivrj bs gur gryrfperra. 
 Ur gbbx uvf fpevooyvat cnq ba uvf xarr naq chfurq onpx uvf punve fb nf 
 gb trg nf sne njnl sebz gur gryrfperra nf cbffvoyr. Gb xrrc lbhe snpr 
 rkcerffvbayrff jnf abg qvssvphyg, naq rira lbhe oernguvat pbhyq or 
 pbagebyyrq, jvgu na rssbeg: ohg lbh pbhyq abg pbageby gur orngvat bs lbhe 
 urneg, naq gur gryrfperra jnf dhvgr qryvpngr rabhtu gb cvpx vg hc. Ur yrg 
 jung ur whqtrq gb or gra zvahgrf tb ol, gbezragrq nyy gur juvyr ol gur srne 
 gung fbzr nppvqrag -- n fhqqra qenhtug oybjvat npebff uvf qrfx, sbe 
 vafgnapr -- jbhyq orgenl uvz. Gura, jvgubhg hapbirevat vg ntnva, ur qebccrq 
 gur cubgbtencu vagb gur zrzbel ubyr, nybat jvgu fbzr bgure jnfgr cncref. 
 Jvguva nabgure zvahgr, creuncf, vg jbhyq unir pehzoyrq vagb nfurf. 
 Gung jnf gra -- ryrira lrnef ntb. Gbqnl, cebonoyl, ur jbhyq unir xrcg 
 gung cubgbtencu. Vg jnf phevbhf gung gur snpg bs univat uryq vg va uvf 
 svatref frrzrq gb uvz gb znxr n qvssrerapr rira abj, jura gur cubgbtencu 
 vgfrys, nf jryy nf gur rirag vg erpbeqrq, jnf bayl zrzbel. Jnf gur Cnegl'f 
 ubyq hcba gur cnfg yrff fgebat, ur jbaqrerq, orpnhfr n cvrpr bs rivqrapr 
 juvpu rkvfgrq ab ybatre unq bapr rkvfgrq? 
 Ohg gbqnl, fhccbfvat gung vg pbhyq or fbzrubj erfheerpgrq sebz vgf 
 nfurf, gur cubgbtencu zvtug abg rira or rivqrapr. Nyernql, ng gur gvzr jura 
 ur znqr uvf qvfpbirel, Bprnavn jnf ab ybatre ng jne jvgu Rhenfvn, naq vg 
 zhfg unir orra gb gur ntragf bs Rnfgnfvn gung gur guerr qrnq zra unq 
 orgenlrq gurve pbhagel. Fvapr gura gurer unq orra bgure punatrf -- gjb, 
 guerr, ur pbhyq abg erzrzore ubj znal. Irel yvxryl gur pbasrffvbaf unq orra 
 erjevggra naq erjevggra hagvy gur bevtvany snpgf naq qngrf ab ybatre unq 
 gur fznyyrfg fvtavsvpnapr. Gur cnfg abg bayl punatrq, ohg punatrq 
 pbagvahbhfyl. Jung zbfg nssyvpgrq uvz jvgu gur frafr bs avtugzner jnf gung 
 ur unq arire pyrneyl haqrefgbbq jul gur uhtr vzcbfgher jnf haqregnxra. Gur 
 vzzrqvngr nqinagntrf bs snyfvslvat gur cnfg jrer boivbhf, ohg gur hygvzngr 
 zbgvir jnf zlfgrevbhf. Ur gbbx hc uvf cra ntnva naq jebgr: 
 
 V haqrefgnaq UBJ: V qb abg haqrefgnaq JUL. 
 
 Ur jbaqrerq, nf ur unq znal gvzrf jbaqrerq orsber, jurgure ur uvzfrys 
 jnf n yhangvp. Creuncf n yhangvp jnf fvzcyl n zvabevgl bs bar. Ng bar gvzr 
 vg unq orra n fvta bs znqarff gb oryvrir gung gur rnegu tbrf ebhaq gur fha; 
 gbqnl, gb oryvrir gung gur cnfg vf vanygrenoyr. Ur zvtug or nybar va 
 ubyqvat gung oryvrs, naq vs nybar, gura n yhangvp. Ohg gur gubhtug bs orvat 
 n yhangvp qvq abg terngyl gebhoyr uvz: gur ubeebe jnf gung ur zvtug nyfb or 
 jebat. 
 Ur cvpxrq hc gur puvyqera'f uvfgbel obbx naq ybbxrq ng gur cbegenvg bs 
 Ovt Oebgure juvpu sbezrq vgf sebagvfcvrpr. Gur ulcabgvp rlrf tnmrq vagb uvf 
 bja. Vg jnf nf gubhtu fbzr uhtr sbepr jrer cerffvat qbja hcba lbh -- 
 fbzrguvat gung crargengrq vafvqr lbhe fxhyy, onggrevat ntnvafg lbhe oenva, 
 sevtugravat lbh bhg bs lbhe oryvrsf, crefhnqvat lbh, nyzbfg, gb qral gur 
 rivqrapr bs lbhe frafrf. Va gur raq gur Cnegl jbhyq naabhapr gung gjb naq 
 gjb znqr svir, naq lbh jbhyq unir gb oryvrir vg. Vg jnf varivgnoyr gung 
 gurl fubhyq znxr gung pynvz fbbare be yngre: gur ybtvp bs gurve cbfvgvba 
 qrznaqrq vg. Abg zreryl gur inyvqvgl bs rkcrevrapr, ohg gur irel rkvfgrapr 
 bs rkgreany ernyvgl, jnf gnpvgyl qravrq ol gurve cuvybfbcul. Gur urerfl bs 
 urerfvrf jnf pbzzba frafr. Naq jung jnf greevslvat jnf abg gung gurl jbhyq 
 xvyy lbh sbe guvaxvat bgurejvfr, ohg gung gurl zvtug or evtug. Sbe, nsgre 
 nyy, ubj qb jr xabj gung gjb naq gjb znxr sbhe? Be gung gur sbepr bs 
 tenivgl jbexf? Be gung gur cnfg vf hapunatrnoyr? Vs obgu gur cnfg naq gur 
 rkgreany jbeyq rkvfg bayl va gur zvaq, naq vs gur zvaq vgfrys vf 
 pbagebyynoyr jung gura? 
 Ohg ab! Uvf pbhentr frrzrq fhqqrayl gb fgvssra bs vgf bja nppbeq. Gur 
 snpr bs B'Oevra, abg pnyyrq hc ol nal boivbhf nffbpvngvba, unq sybngrq vagb 
 uvf zvaq. Ur xarj, jvgu zber pregnvagl guna orsber, gung B'Oevra jnf ba uvf 
 fvqr. Ur jnf jevgvat gur qvnel sbe B'Oevra -- gb B'Oevra: vg jnf yvxr na 
 vagrezvanoyr yrggre juvpu ab bar jbhyq rire ernq, ohg juvpu jnf nqqerffrq 
 gb n cnegvphyne crefba naq gbbx vgf pbybhe sebz gung snpg. 
 Gur Cnegl gbyq lbh gb erwrpg gur rivqrapr bs lbhe rlrf naq rnef. Vg 
 jnf gurve svany, zbfg rffragvny pbzznaq. Uvf urneg fnax nf ur gubhtug bs 
 gur rabezbhf cbjre neenlrq ntnvafg uvz, gur rnfr jvgu juvpu nal Cnegl 
 vagryyrpghny jbhyq bireguebj uvz va qrongr, gur fhogyr nethzragf juvpu ur 
 jbhyq abg or noyr gb haqrefgnaq, zhpu yrff nafjre. Naq lrg ur jnf va gur 
 evtug! Gurl jrer jebat naq ur jnf evtug. Gur boivbhf, gur fvyyl, naq gur 
 gehr unq tbg gb or qrsraqrq. Gehvfzf ner gehr, ubyq ba gb gung! Gur fbyvq 
 jbeyq rkvfgf, vgf ynjf qb abg punatr. Fgbarf ner uneq, jngre vf jrg, 
 bowrpgf hafhccbegrq snyy gbjneqf gur rnegu'f prager. Jvgu gur srryvat gung 
 ur jnf fcrnxvat gb B'Oevra, naq nyfb gung ur jnf frggvat sbegu na vzcbegnag 
 nkvbz, ur jebgr: 
 
 Serrqbz vf gur serrqbz gb fnl gung gjb cyhf gjb znxr sbhe. Vs gung 
 vf tenagrq, nyy ryfr sbyybjf. 
 
 IVVV 
 
 Sebz fbzrjurer ng gur obggbz bs n cnffntr gur fzryy bs ebnfgvat pbssrr 
 -- erny pbssrr, abg Ivpgbel Pbssrr -- pnzr sybngvat bhg vagb gur fgerrg. 
 Jvafgba cnhfrq vaibyhagnevyl. Sbe creuncf gjb frpbaqf ur jnf onpx va gur 
 unys-sbetbggra jbeyq bs uvf puvyqubbq. Gura n qbbe onatrq, frrzvat gb phg 
 bss gur fzryy nf noehcgyl nf gubhtu vg unq orra n fbhaq. 
 Ur unq jnyxrq frireny xvybzrgerf bire cnirzragf, naq uvf inevpbfr 
 hypre jnf gueboovat. Guvf jnf gur frpbaq gvzr va guerr jrrxf gung ur unq 
 zvffrq na riravat ng gur Pbzzhavgl Prager: n enfu npg, fvapr lbh pbhyq or 
 pregnva gung gur ahzore bs lbhe nggraqnaprf ng gur Prager jnf pnershyyl 
 purpxrq. Va cevapvcyr n Cnegl zrzore unq ab fcner gvzr, naq jnf arire nybar 
 rkprcg va orq. Vg jnf nffhzrq gung jura ur jnf abg jbexvat, rngvat, be 
 fyrrcvat ur jbhyq or gnxvat cneg va fbzr xvaq bs pbzzhany erperngvba: gb qb 
 nalguvat gung fhttrfgrq n gnfgr sbe fbyvghqr, rira gb tb sbe n jnyx ol 
 lbhefrys, jnf nyjnlf fyvtugyl qnatrebhf. Gurer jnf n jbeq sbe vg va 
 Arjfcrnx: bjayvsr, vg jnf pnyyrq, zrnavat vaqvivqhnyvfz naq rppragevpvgl. 
 Ohg guvf riravat nf ur pnzr bhg bs gur Zvavfgel gur onyzvarff bs gur Ncevy 
 nve unq grzcgrq uvz. Gur fxl jnf n jnezre oyhr guna ur unq frra vg gung 
 lrne, naq fhqqrayl gur ybat, abvfl riravat ng gur Prager, gur obevat, 
 rkunhfgvat tnzrf, gur yrpgherf, gur pernxvat pnznenqrevr bvyrq ol tva, unq 
 frrzrq vagbyrenoyr. Ba vzchyfr ur unq ghearq njnl sebz gur ohf-fgbc naq 
 jnaqrerq bss vagb gur ynolevagu bs Ybaqba, svefg fbhgu, gura rnfg, gura 
 abegu ntnva, ybfvat uvzfrys nzbat haxabja fgerrgf naq uneqyl obgurevat va 
 juvpu qverpgvba ur jnf tbvat. 
 'Vs gurer vf ubcr,' ur unq jevggra va gur qvnel, 'vg yvrf va gur 
 cebyrf.' Gur jbeqf xrcg pbzvat onpx gb uvz, fgngrzrag bs n zlfgvpny gehgu 
 naq n cnycnoyr nofheqvgl. Ur jnf fbzrjurer va gur inthr, oebja-pbybherq 
 fyhzf gb gur abegu naq rnfg bs jung unq bapr orra Fnvag Cnapenf Fgngvba. Ur 
 jnf jnyxvat hc n pbooyrq fgerrg bs yvggyr gjb-fgberl ubhfrf jvgu onggrerq 
 qbbejnlf juvpu tnir fgenvtug ba gur cnirzrag naq juvpu jrer fbzrubj 
 phevbhfyl fhttrfgvir bs engubyrf. Gurer jrer chqqyrf bs svygul jngre urer 
 naq gurer nzbat gur pbooyrf. Va naq bhg bs gur qnex qbbejnlf, naq qbja 
 aneebj nyyrl-jnlf gung oenapurq bss ba rvgure fvqr, crbcyr fjnezrq va 
 nfgbavfuvat ahzoref -- tveyf va shyy oybbz, jvgu pehqryl yvcfgvpxrq zbhguf, 
 naq lbhguf jub punfrq gur tveyf, naq fjbyyra jnqqyvat jbzra jub fubjrq lbh 
 jung gur tveyf jbhyq or yvxr va gra lrnef" gvzr, naq byq orag perngherf 
 fuhssyvat nybat ba fcynlrq srrg, naq enttrq onersbbgrq puvyqera jub cynlrq 
 va gur chqqyrf naq gura fpnggrerq ng natel lryyf sebz gurve zbguref. 
 Creuncf n dhnegre bs gur jvaqbjf va gur fgerrg jrer oebxra naq obneqrq hc. 
 Zbfg bs gur crbcyr cnvq ab nggragvba gb Jvafgba; n srj rlrq uvz jvgu n fbeg 
 bs thneqrq phevbfvgl. Gjb zbafgebhf jbzra jvgu oevpx-erq sbernezf sbyqrq 
 npebff gurye ncebaf jrer gnyxvat bhgfvqr n qbbejnl. Jvafgba pnhtug fpencf 
 bs pbairefngvba nf ur nccebnpurq. 
 '"Lrf," V fnlf gb 're, "gung'f nyy irel jryy," V fnlf. "Ohg vs lbh'q 
 bs orra va zl cynpr lbh'q bs qbar gur fnzr nf jung V qbar. Vg'f rnfl gb 
 pevgvpvmr," V fnlf, "ohg lbh nva'g tbg gur fnzr ceboyrzf nf jung V tbg."' 
 'Nu,' fnvq gur bgure, 'gung'f wrfg vg. Gung'f wrfg jurer vg vf.' 
 Gur fgevqrag ibvprf fgbccrq noehcgyl. Gur jbzra fghqvrq uvz va ubfgvyr 
 fvyrapr nf ur jrag cnfg. Ohg vg jnf abg ubfgvyvgl, rknpgyl; zreryl n xvaq 
