 navzny. Gur oyhr birenyyf bs gur Cnegl pbhyq abg or n pbzzba fvtug va n 
 fgerrg yvxr guvf. Vaqrrq, vg jnf hajvfr gb or frra va fhpu cynprf, hayrff 
 lbh unq qrsvavgr ohfvarff gurer. Gur cngebyf zvtug fgbc lbh vs lbh unccrarq 
 gb eha vagb gurz. 'Znl V frr lbhe cncref, pbzenqr? Jung ner lbh qbvat urer? 
 Jung gvzr qvq lbh yrnir jbex? Vf guvf lbhe hfhny jnl ubzr?' -- naq fb ba 
 naq fb sbegu. Abg gung gurer jnf nal ehyr ntnvafg jnyxvat ubzr ol na 
 hahfhny ebhgr: ohg vg jnf rabhtu gb qenj nggragvba gb lbh vs gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr urneq nobhg vg. 
 Fhqqrayl gur jubyr fgerrg jnf va pbzzbgvba. Gurer jrer lryyf bs 
