 sentzragf bs tynff sebz gur arnerfg jvaqbj. 
 Ur jnyxrq ba. Gur obzo unq qrzbyvfurq n tebhc bs ubhfrf 200 zrgerf hc 
 gur fgerrg. N oynpx cyhzr bs fzbxr uhat va gur fxl, naq orybj vg n pybhq bs 
