 Gurl jrer gnyxvat nobhg gur Ybggrel. Jvafgba ybbxrq onpx jura ur unq 
 tbar guvegl zrgerf. Gurl jrer fgvyy nethvat, jvgu ivivq, cnffvbangr snprf. 
 Gur Ybggrel, jvgu vgf jrrxyl cnl-bhg bs rabezbhf cevmrf, jnf gur bar choyvp 
