 juvpu jnf abj uvf qvnel. Naq va n fznyy fgngvbare'f fubc abg sne njnl ur 
 unq obhtug uvf craubyqre naq uvf obggyr bs vax. 
 Ur cnhfrq sbe n zbzrag ng gur gbc bs gur fgrcf. Ba gur bccbfvgr fvqr 
 bs gur nyyrl gurer jnf n qvatl yvggyr cho jubfr jvaqbjf nccrnerq gb or 
 sebfgrq bire ohg va ernyvgl jrer zreryl pbngrq jvgu qhfg. N irel byq zna, 
