 jvcrq bhg va gur terng chetrf bs gur svsgvrf naq fvkgvrf, naq gur srj jub 
 fheivirq unq ybat ntb orra greevsvrq vagb pbzcyrgr vagryyrpghny fheeraqre. 
 Vs gurer jnf nal bar fgvyy nyvir jub pbhyq tvir lbh n gehgushy nppbhag bs 
 pbaqvgvbaf va gur rneyl cneg bs gur praghel, vg pbhyq bayl or n cebyr. 
 Fhqqrayl gur cnffntr sebz gur uvfgbel obbx gung ur unq pbcvrq vagb uvf 
 qvnel pnzr onpx vagb Jvafgba'f zvaq, naq n yhangvp vzchyfr gbbx ubyq bs 
