 zna naq dhrfgvba uvz. Ur jbhyq fnl gb uvz: 'Gryy zr nobhg lbhe yvsr jura 
 lbh jrer n obl. Jung jnf vg yvxr va gubfr qnlf? Jrer guvatf orggre guna 
 gurl ner abj, be jrer gurl jbefr?' 
