 jvgu gur gvcf bs uvf svatref ba gur pbhagre. 
 'Nex ng 'vz! Pnyyf 'vffrys n onezna naq qba'g xabj jung n cvag vf! 
 Jul, n cvag'f gur 'nys bs n dhneg, naq gurer'f sbhe dhnegf gb gur tnyyba. 
 'Nir gb grnpu lbh gur N, O, P arkg.' 
