 sbetbggra uvf cerwhqvpr ntnvafg qevaxvat n shyy yvger. 
 'Lbh ner irel zhpu byqre guna V nz,' fnvq Jvafgba. 'Lbh zhfg unir orra 
 n tebja zna orsber V jnf obea. Lbh pna erzrzore jung vg jnf yvxr va gur byq 
 qnlf, orsber gur Eribyhgvba. Crbcyr bs zl ntr qba'g ernyyl xabj nalguvat 
 nobhg gubfr gvzrf. Jr pna bayl ernq nobhg gurz va obbxf, naq jung vg fnlf 
