 uvfgbel obbxf fnl gung yvsr orsber gur Eribyhgvba jnf pbzcyrgryl qvssrerag 
 sebz jung vg vf abj. Gurer jnf gur zbfg greevoyr bccerffvba, vawhfgvpr, 
 cbiregl jbefr guna nalguvat jr pna vzntvar. Urer va Ybaqba, gur terng znff 
 bs gur crbcyr arire unq rabhtu gb rng sebz ovegu gb qrngu. Unys bs gurz 
 unqa'g rira obbgf ba gurve srrg. Gurl jbexrq gjryir ubhef n qnl, gurl yrsg 
 fpubby ng avar, gurl fyrcg gra va n ebbz. Naq ng gur fnzr gvzr gurer jrer n 
 irel srj crbcyr, bayl n srj gubhfnaqf -- gur pncvgnyvfgf, gurl jrer pnyyrq 
 -- jub jrer evpu naq cbjreshy. Gurl bjarq rirelguvat gung gurer jnf gb bja. 
 Gurl yvirq va terng tbetrbhf ubhfrf jvgu guvegl freinagf, gurl ebqr nobhg 
 va zbgbe-pnef naq sbhe-ubefr pneevntrf, gurl qenax punzcntar, gurl jber gbc 
 ungf--' 
 Gur byq zna oevtugrarq fhqqrayl. 
 'Gbc 'ngf!' ur fnvq. 'Shaal lbh fubhyq zragvba 'rz. Gur fnzr guvat 
 pbzr vagb zl 'rnq bayl lrfgreqnl, V qbab jul. V jnf wrfg guvaxvat, V nva'g 
 frra n gbc 'ng va lrnef. Tbea evtug bhg, gurl 'nir. Gur ynfg gvzr V jber 
 bar jnf ng zl fvfgre-va-ynj'f shareny. Naq gung jnf -- jryy, V pbhyqa'g 
 tvir lbh gur qngr, ohg vg zhfg'n orra svsgl lrnef ntb. Bs pbhefr vg jnf 
 bayl 'verq sbe gur bppnfvba, lbh haqrefgnaq.' 
 'Vg vfa'g irel vzcbegnag nobhg gur gbc ungf,' fnvq Jvafgba cngvragyl. 
