 abg znal gung'q fnl fb abjnqnlf.' Ur pbhturq. 'Abj, vs vg fb unccrarq gung 
 lbh jnagrq gb ohl vg, gung'q pbfg lbh sbhe qbyynef. V pna erzrzore jura n 
 guvat yvxr gung jbhyq unir srgpurq rvtug cbhaqf, naq rvtug cbhaqf jnf -- 
 jryy, V pna'g jbex vg bhg, ohg vg jnf n ybg bs zbarl. Ohg jub pnerf nobhg 
 trahvar nagvdhrf abjnqnlf rira gur srj gung'f yrsg?' 
 Jvafgba vzzrqvngryl cnvq bire gur sbhe qbyynef naq fyvq gur pbirgrq 
 guvat vagb uvf cbpxrg. Jung nccrnyrq gb uvz nobhg vg jnf abg fb zhpu vgf 
 ornhgl nf gur nve vg frrzrq gb cbffrff bs orybatvat gb na ntr dhvgr 
 qvssrerag sebz gur cerfrag bar. Gur fbsg, envajngrel tynff jnf abg yvxr nal 
 tynff gung ur unq rire frra. Gur guvat jnf qbhoyl nggenpgvir orpnhfr bs vgf 
 nccnerag hfryrffarff, gubhtu ur pbhyq thrff gung vg zhfg bapr unir orra 
 vagraqrq nf n cncrejrvtug. Vg jnf irel urnil va uvf cbpxrg, ohg sbeghangryl 
