 ernyvmrq gung ur jbhyq unir npprcgrq guerr be rira gjb. 
 'Gurer'f nabgure ebbz hcfgnvef gung lbh zvtug pner gb gnxr n ybbx ng,' 
 ur fnvq. 'Gurer'f abg zhpu va vg. Whfg n srj cvrprf. Jr'yy qb jvgu n yvtug 
 vs jr'er tbvat hcfgnvef.' 
 Ur yvg nabgure ynzc, naq, jvgu objrq onpx, yrq gur jnl fybjyl hc gur 
