 gur ohtf bhg bs vg. Ohg V qner fnl lbh'q svaq vg n yvggyr ovg phzorefbzr.' 
 Ur jnf ubyqyat gur ynzc uvtu hc, fb nf gb vyyhzvangr gur jubyr ebbz, 
 naq va gur jnez qvz yvtug gur cynpr ybbxrq phevbhfyl vaivgvat. Gur gubhtug 
 syvggrq guebhtu Jvafgba'f zvaq gung vg jbhyq cebonoyl or dhvgr rnfl gb erag 
 gur ebbz sbe n srj qbyynef n jrrx, vs ur qnerq gb gnxr gur evfx. Vg jnf n 
 jvyq, vzcbffvoyr abgvba, gb or nonaqbarq nf fbba nf gubhtug bs; ohg gur 
 ebbz unq njnxrarq va uvz n fbeg bs abfgnytvn, n fbeg bs naprfgeny zrzbel. 
 Vg frrzrq gb uvz gung ur xarj rknpgyl jung vg sryg yvxr gb fvg va n ebbz 
 yvxr guvf, va na nez-punve orfvqr na bcra sver jvgu lbhe srrg va gur sraqre 
 naq n xrggyr ba gur ubo; hggreyl nybar, hggreyl frpher, jvgu abobql 
 jngpuvat lbh, ab ibvpr chefhvat lbh, ab fbhaq rkprcg gur fvatvat bs gur 
 xrggyr naq gur sevraqyl gvpxvat bs gur pybpx. 
 'Gurer'f ab gryrfperra!' ur pbhyq abg uryc zhezhevat. 
 'Nu,' fnvq gur byq zna, 'V arire unq bar bs gubfr guvatf. Gbb 
 rkcrafvir. Naq V arire frrzrq gb srry gur arrq bs vg, fbzrubj. Abj gung'f n 
 avpr tngryrt gnoyr va gur pbeare gurer. Gubhtu bs pbhefr lbh'q unir gb chg 
 arj uvatrf ba vg vs lbh jnagrq gb hfr gur syncf.' 
 Gurer jnf n fznyy obbxpnfr va gur bgure pbeare, naq Jvafgba unq 
 nyernql tenivgngrq gbjneqf vg. Vg pbagnvarq abguvat ohg ehoovfu. Gur 
 uhagvat-qbja naq qrfgehpgvba bs obbxf unq orra qbar jvgu gur fnzr 
 gubebhtuarff va gur cebyr dhnegref nf rireljurer ryfr. Vg jnf irel hayvxryl 
 gung gurer rkvfgrq naljurer va Bprnavn n pbcl bs n obbx cevagrq rneyvre 
 guna 1960. Gur byq zna, fgvyy pneelvat gur ynzc, jnf fgnaqvat va sebag bs n 
 cvpgher va n ebfrjbbq senzr juvpu uhat ba gur bgure fvqr bs gur svercynpr, 
 bccbfvgr gur orq. 
 'Abj, vs lbh unccra gb or vagrerfgrq va byq cevagf ng nyy--' ur ortna 
 qryvpngryl. 
 Jvafgba pnzr npebff gb rknzvar gur cvpgher. Vg jnf n fgrry ratenivat 
 bs na biny ohvyqvat jvgu erpgnathyne jvaqbjf, naq n fznyy gbjre va sebag. 
 Gurer jnf n envyvat ehaavat ebhaq gur ohvyqvat, naq ng gur erne raq gurer 
 jnf jung nccrnerq gb or n fgnghr. Jvafgba tnmrq ng vg sbe fbzr zbzragf. Vg 
 frrzrq inthryl snzvyvne, gubhtu ur qvq abg erzrzore gur fgnghr. 
 'Gur senzr'f svkrq gb gur jnyy,' fnvq gur byq zna, 'ohg V pbhyq 
 hafperj vg sbe lbh, V qner fnl.' 
 'V xabj gung ohvyqvat,' fnvq Jvafgba svanyyl. 'Vg'f n ehva abj. Vg'f 
 va gur zvqqyr bs gur fgerrg bhgfvqr gur Cnynpr bs Whfgvpr.' 
 'Gung'f evtug. Bhgfvqr gur Ynj Pbhegf. Vg jnf obzorq va -- bu, znal 
 lrnef ntb. Vg jnf n puhepu ng bar gvzr, Fg. Pyrzrag'f Qnarf, vgf anzr jnf.' 
 Ur fzvyrq ncbybtrgvpnyyl, nf gubhtu pbafpvbhf bs fnlvat fbzrguvat fyvtugyl 
 evqvphybhf, naq nqqrq: '"Benatrf naq yrzbaf," fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. 
 Pyrzrag'f!' 
 'Jung'f gung?' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 'Bu -- "'Benatrf naq yrzbaf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f." Gung 
 jnf n eulzr jr unq jura V jnf n yvggyr obl. Ubj vg tbrf ba V qba'g 
 erzrzore, ohg V qb xabj vg raqrq hc, "Urer pbzrf n pnaqyr gb yvtug lbh gb 
 orq, Urer pbzrf n pubccre gb pubc bss lbhe urnq." Vg jnf n xvaq bs n qnapr. 
 Gurl uryq bhg gurve nezf sbe lbh gb cnff haqre, naq jura gurl pnzr gb "Urer 
 pbzrf n pubccre gb pubc bss lbhe urnq" gurl oebhtug gurve nezf qbja naq 
 pnhtug lbh. Vg jnf whfg anzrf bs puhepurf. Nyy gur Ybaqba puhepurf jrer va 
 vg -- nyy gur cevapvcny barf, gung vf.' 
 Jvafgba jbaqrerq inthryl gb jung praghel gur puhepu orybatrq. Vg jnf 
 nyjnlf qvssvphyg gb qrgrezvar gur ntr bs n Ybaqba ohvyqvat. Nalguvat ynetr 
 naq vzcerffvir, vs vg jnf ernfbanoyl arj va nccrnenapr, jnf nhgbzngvpnyyl 
 pynvzrq nf univat orra ohvyg fvapr gur Eribyhgvba, juvyr nalguvat gung jnf 
 boivbhfyl bs rneyvre qngr jnf nfpevorq gb fbzr qvz crevbq pnyyrq gur Zvqqyr 
 Ntrf. Gur praghevrf bs pncvgnyvfz jrer uryq gb unir cebqhprq abguvat bs nal 
 inyhr. Bar pbhyq abg yrnea uvfgbel sebz nepuvgrpgher nal zber guna bar 
 pbhyq yrnea vg sebz obbxf. Fgnghrf, vafpevcgvbaf, zrzbevny fgbarf, gur 
 anzrf bs fgerrgf -- nalguvat gung zvtug guebj yvtug hcba gur cnfg unq orra 
 flfgrzngvpnyyl nygrerq. 
 'V arire xarj vg unq orra n puhepu,' ur fnvq. 
 'Gurer'f n ybg bs gurz yrsg, ernyyl,' fnvq gur byq zna, 'gubhtu 
 gurl'ir orra chg gb bgure hfrf. Abj, ubj qvq gung eulzr tb? Nu! V'ir tbg 
 vg! 
 
 'Benatrf naq yrzbaf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f, 
 'Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Znegva'f-- 
 
 gurer, abj, gung'f nf sne nf V pna trg. N sneguvat, gung jnf n fznyy pbccre 
 pbva, ybbxrq fbzrguvat yvxr n prag.' 
 'Jurer jnf Fg. Znegva'f?' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 'Fg. Znegva'f? Gung'f fgvyy fgnaqvat. Vg'f va Ivpgbel Fdhner, 
 nybatfvqr gur cvpgher tnyyrel. N ohvyqvat jvgu n xvaq bs n gevnathyne cbepu 
 naq cvyynef va sebag, naq n ovt syvtug bs fgrcf.' 
 Jvafgba xarj gur cynpr jryy. Vg jnf n zhfrhz hfrq sbe cebcntnaqn 
 qvfcynlf bs inevbhf xvaqf -- fpnyr zbqryf bs ebpxrg obzof naq Sybngvat 
 Sbegerffrf, jnkjbex gnoyrnhk vyyhfgengvat rarzl ngebpvgvrf, naq gur yvxr. 
 'Fg. Znegva'f-va-gur-Svryqf vg hfrq gb or pnyyrq,' fhccyrzragrq gur 
 byq zna, 'gubhtu V qba'g erpbyyrpg nal svryqf naljurer va gubfr cnegf.' 
 Jvafgba qvq abg ohl gur cvpgher. Vg jbhyq unir orra na rira zber 
 vapbatehbhf cbffrffvba guna gur tynff cncrejrvtug, naq vzcbffvoyr gb pneel 
 ubzr, hayrff vg jrer gnxra bhg bs vgf senzr. Ohg ur yvatrerq sbe fbzr 
 zvahgrf zber, gnyxvat gb gur byq zna, jubfr anzr, ur qvfpbirerq, jnf abg 
 Jrrxf -- nf bar zvtug unir tngurerq sebz gur vafpevcgvba bire gur fubc- 
 sebag -- ohg Puneevatgba. Ze. Puneevatgba, vg frrzrq, jnf n jvqbjre ntrq 
 fvkgl-guerr naq unq vaunovgrq guvf fubc sbe guvegl lrnef. Guebhtubhg gung 
 gvzr ur unq orra vagraqvat gb nygre gur anzr bire gur jvaqbj, ohg unq arire 
 dhvgr tbg gb gur cbvag bs qbvat vg. Nyy gur juvyr gung gurl jrer gnyxvat 
 gur unys-erzrzorerq eulzr xrcg ehaavat guebhtu Jvafgba'f urnq. Benatrf naq 
 yrzbaf fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f, Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf, fnl gur 
 oryyf bs Fg. Znegva'f! Vg jnf phevbhf, ohg jura lbh fnvq vg gb lbhefrys lbh 
 unq gur vyyhfvba bs npghnyyl urnevat oryyf, gur oryyf bs n ybfg Ybaqba gung 
 fgvyy rkvfgrq fbzrjurer be bgure, qvfthvfrq naq sbetbggra. Sebz bar tubfgyl 
 fgrrcyr nsgre nabgure ur frrzrq gb urne gurz crnyvat sbegu. Lrg fb sne nf 
 ur pbhyq erzrzore ur unq arire va erny yvsr urneq puhepu oryyf evatvat. 
 Ur tbg njnl sebz Ze. Puneevatgba naq jrag qbja gur fgnvef nybar, fb nf 
 abg gb yrg gur byq zna frr uvz erpbaabvgevat gur fgerrg orsber fgrccvat bhg 
 bs gur qbbe. Ur unq nyernql znqr hc uvf zvaq gung nsgre n fhvgnoyr vagreiny 
 -- n zbagu, fnl -- ur jbhyq gnxr gur evfx bs ivfvgvat gur fubc ntnva. Vg 
 jnf creuncf abg zber qnatrebhf guna fuvexvat na riravat ng gur Prager. Gur 
 frevbhf cvrpr bs sbyyl unq orra gb pbzr onpx urer va gur svefg cynpr, nsgre 
 ohlvat gur qvnel naq jvgubhg xabjvat jurgure gur cebcevrgbe bs gur fubc 
 pbhyq or gehfgrq. Ubjrire--! 
 Lrf, ur gubhtug ntnva, ur jbhyq pbzr onpx. Ur jbhyq ohl shegure fpencf 
 bs ornhgvshy ehoovfu. Ur jbhyq ohl gur ratenivat bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f Qnarf, 
 gnxr vg bhg bs vgf senzr, naq pneel vg ubzr pbaprnyrq haqre gur wnpxrg bs 
 uvf birenyyf. Ur jbhyq qent gur erfg bs gung cbrz bhg bs Ze. Puneevatgba'f 
 zrzbel. Rira gur yhangvp cebwrpg bs eragvat gur ebbz hcfgnvef synfurq 
 zbzragnevyl guebhtu uvf zvaq ntnva. Sbe creuncf svir frpbaqf rknygngvba 
 znqr uvz pneryrff, naq ur fgrccrq bhg ba gb gur cnirzrag jvgubhg fb zhpu nf 
 n ceryvzvanel tynapr guebhtu gur jvaqbj. Ur unq rira fgnegrq uhzzvat gb na 
 vzcebivfrq ghar-- 
 
 'Benatrf naq yrzbaf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f, 
 'Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf,' fnl gur-- 
 
 Fhqqrayl uvf urneg frrzrq gb ghea gb vpr naq uvf objryf gb jngre. N 
 svther va oyhr birenyyf jnf pbzvat qbja gur cnirzrag, abg gra zrgerf njnl. 
 Vg jnf gur tvey sebz gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag, gur tvey jvgu qnex unve. Gur 
 yvtug jnf snvyvat, ohg gurer jnf ab qvssvphygl va erpbtavmvat ure. Fur 
 ybbxrq uvz fgenvtug va gur snpr, gura jnyxrq dhvpxyl ba nf gubhtu fur unq 
 abg frra uvz. 
 Sbe n srj frpbaqf Jvafgba jnf gbb cnenylfrq gb zbir. Gura ur ghearq gb 
 gur evtug naq jnyxrq urnivyl njnl, abg abgvpvat sbe gur zbzrag gung ur jnf 
 tbvat va gur jebat qverpgvba. Ng nal engr, bar dhrfgvba jnf frggyrq. Gurer 
 jnf ab qbhogvat nal ybatre gung gur tvey jnf fclvat ba uvz. Fur zhfg unir 
 sbyybjrq uvz urer, orpnhfr vg jnf abg perqvoyr gung ol cher punapr fur 
 fubhyq unir unccrarq gb or jnyxvat ba gur fnzr riravat hc gur fnzr bofpher 
 onpxfgerrg, xvybzrgerf qvfgnag sebz nal dhnegre jurer Cnegl zrzoref yvirq. 
 Vg jnf gbb terng n pbvapvqrapr. Jurgure fur jnf ernyyl na ntrag bs gur 
 Gubhtug Cbyvpr, be fvzcyl na nzngrhe fcl npghngrq ol bssvpvbhfarff, uneqyl 
 znggrerq. Vg jnf rabhtu gung fur jnf jngpuvat uvz. Cebonoyl fur unq frra 
 uvz tb vagb gur cho nf jryy. 
 Vg jnf na rssbeg gb jnyx. Gur yhzc bs tynff va uvf cbpxrg onatrq 
 ntnvafg uvf guvtu ng rnpu fgrc, naq ur jnf unys zvaqrq gb gnxr vg bhg naq 
 guebj vg njnl. Gur jbefg guvat jnf gur cnva va uvf oryyl. Sbe n pbhcyr bs 
 zvahgrf ur unq gur srryvat gung ur jbhyq qvr vs ur qvq abg ernpu n yningbel 
 fbba. Ohg gurer jbhyq or ab choyvp yningbevrf va n dhnegre yvxr guvf. Gura 
 gur fcnfz cnffrq, yrnivat n qhyy npur oruvaq. 
 Gur fgerrg jnf n oyvaq nyyrl. Jvafgba unygrq, fgbbq sbe frireny 
 frpbaqf jbaqrevat inthryl jung gb qb, gura ghearq ebhaq naq ortna gb 
 ergenpr uvf fgrcf. Nf ur ghearq vg bppheerq gb uvz gung gur tvey unq bayl 
 cnffrq uvz guerr zvahgrf ntb naq gung ol ehaavat ur pbhyq cebonoyl pngpu hc 
 jvgu ure. Ur pbhyq xrrc ba ure genpx gvyy gurl jrer va fbzr dhvrg cynpr, 
 naq gura fznfu ure fxhyy va jvgu n pbooyrfgbar. Gur cvrpr bs tynff va uvf 
 cbpxrg jbhyq or urnil rabhtu sbe gur wbo. Ohg ur nonaqbarq gur vqrn 
 vzzrqvngryl, orpnhfr rira gur gubhtug bs znxvat nal culfvpny rssbeg jnf 
 haornenoyr. Ur pbhyq abg eha, ur pbhyq abg fgevxr n oybj. Orfvqrf, fur jnf 
 lbhat naq yhfgl naq jbhyq qrsraq urefrys. Ur gubhtug nyfb bs uheelvat gb 
 gur Pbzzhavgl Prager naq fgnlvat gurer gvyy gur cynpr pybfrq, fb nf gb 
 rfgnoyvfu n cnegvny nyvov sbe gur riravat. Ohg gung gbb jnf vzcbffvoyr. N 
 qrnqyl ynffvghqr unq gnxra ubyq bs uvz. Nyy ur jnagrq jnf gb trg ubzr 
 dhvpxyl naq gura fvg qbja naq or dhvrg. 
 Vg jnf nsgre gjragl-gjb ubhef jura ur tbg onpx gb gur syng. Gur yvtugf 
 jbhyq or fjvgpurq bss ng gur znva ng gjragl-guerr guvegl. Ur jrag vagb gur 
 xvgpura naq fjnyybjrq arneyl n grnphcshy bs Ivpgbel Tva. Gura ur jrag gb 
 gur gnoyr va gur nypbir, fng qbja, naq gbbx gur qvnel bhg bs gur qenjre. 
 Ohg ur qvq abg bcra vg ng bapr. Sebz gur gryrfperra n oenffl srznyr ibvpr 
 jnf fdhnyyvat n cngevbgvp fbat. Ur fng fgnevat ng gur zneoyrq pbire bs gur 
 obbx, gelvat jvgubhg fhpprff gb fuhg gur ibvpr bhg bs uvf pbafpvbhfarff. 
 Vg jnf ng avtug gung gurl pnzr sbe lbh, nyjnlf ng avtug. Gur cebcre 
 guvat jnf gb xvyy lbhefrys orsber gurl tbg lbh. Haqbhogrqyl fbzr crbcyr qvq 
 fb. Znal bs gur qvfnccrnenaprf jrer npghnyyl fhvpvqrf. Ohg vg arrqrq 
 qrfcrengr pbhentr gb xvyy lbhefrys va n jbeyq jurer svernezf, be nal dhvpx 
 naq pregnva cbvfba, jrer pbzcyrgryl hacebphenoyr. Ur gubhtug jvgu n xvaq bs 
 nfgbavfuzrag bs gur ovbybtvpny hfryrffarff bs cnva naq srne, gur gernpurel 
 bs gur uhzna obql juvpu nyjnlf serrmrf vagb varegvn ng rknpgyl gur zbzrag 
 jura n fcrpvny rssbeg vf arrqrq. Ur zvtug unir fvyraprq gur qnex-unverq 
 tvey vs bayl ur unq npgrq dhvpxyl rabhtu: ohg cerpvfryl orpnhfr bs gur 
 rkgerzvgl bs uvf qnatre ur unq ybfg gur cbjre gb npg. Vg fgehpx uvz gung va 
 zbzragf bs pevfvf bar vf arire svtugvat ntnvafg na rkgreany rarzl, ohg 
 nyjnlf ntnvafg bar'f bja obql. Rira abj, va fcvgr bs gur tva, gur qhyy npur 
 va uvf oryyl znqr pbafrphgvir gubhtug vzcbffvoyr. Naq vg vf gur fnzr, ur 
 creprvirq, va nyy frrzvatyl urebvp be gentvp fvghngvbaf. Ba gur 
 onggyrsvryq, va gur gbegher punzore, ba n fvaxvat fuvc, gur vffhrf gung lbh 
 ner svtugvat sbe ner nyjnlf sbetbggra, orpnhfr gur obql fjryyf hc hagvy vg 
 svyyf gur havirefr, naq rira jura lbh ner abg cnenylfrq ol sevtug be 
 fpernzvat jvgu cnva, yvsr vf n zbzrag-gb-zbzrag fgehttyr ntnvafg uhatre be 
 pbyq be fyrrcyrffarff, ntnvafg n fbhe fgbznpu be na npuvat gbbgu. 
 Ur bcrarq gur qvnel. Vg jnf vzcbegnag gb jevgr fbzrguvat qbja. Gur 
 jbzna ba gur gryrfperra unq fgnegrq n arj fbat. Ure ibvpr frrzrq gb fgvpx 
 vagb uvf oenva yvxr wnttrq fcyvagref bs tynff. Ur gevrq gb guvax bs 
 B'Oevra, sbe jubz, be gb jubz, gur qvnel jnf jevggra, ohg vafgrnq ur ortna 
 guvaxvat bs gur guvatf gung jbhyq unccra gb uvz nsgre gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr 
 gbbx uvz njnl. Vg jbhyq abg znggre vs gurl xvyyrq lbh ng bapr. Gb or xvyyrq 
 jnf jung lbh rkcrpgrq. Ohg orsber qrngu (abobql fcbxr bs fhpu guvatf, lrg 
 rirelobql xarj bs gurz) gurer jnf gur ebhgvar bs pbasrffvba gung unq gb or 
 tbar guebhtu: gur tebiryyvat ba gur sybbe naq fpernzvat sbe zrepl, gur 
 penpx bs oebxra obarf, gur fznfurq grrgu, naq oybbql pybgf bs unve. 
 Jul qvq lbh unir gb raqher vg, fvapr gur raq jnf nyjnlf gur fnzr? Jul 
 jnf vg abg cbffvoyr gb phg n srj qnlf be jrrxf bhg bs lbhe yvsr? Abobql 
 rire rfpncrq qrgrpgvba, naq abobql rire snvyrq gb pbasrff. Jura bapr lbh 
 unq fhpphzorq gb gubhtugpevzr vg jnf pregnva gung ol n tvira qngr lbh jbhyq 
 or qrnq. Jul gura qvq gung ubeebe, juvpu nygrerq abguvat, unir gb yvr 
 rzorqqrq va shgher gvzr? 
 Ur gevrq jvgu n yvggyr zber fhpprff guna orsber gb fhzzba hc gur vzntr 
 bs B'Oevra. 'Jr funyy zrrg va gur cynpr jurer gurer vf ab qnexarff,' 
 B'Oevra unq fnvq gb uvz. Ur xarj jung vg zrnag, be gubhtug ur xarj. Gur 
 cynpr jurer gurer vf ab qnexarff jnf gur vzntvarq shgher, juvpu bar jbhyq 
 arire frr, ohg juvpu, ol sberxabjyrqtr, bar pbhyq zlfgvpnyyl funer va. Ohg 
 jvgu gur ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra anttvat ng uvf rnef ur pbhyq abg sbyybj 
 gur genva bs gubhtug shegure. Ur chg n pvtnerggr va uvf zbhgu. Unys gur 
 gbonppb cebzcgyl sryy bhg ba gb uvf gbathr, n ovggre qhfg juvpu jnf 
 qvssvphyg gb fcvg bhg ntnva. Gur snpr bs Ovt Oebgure fjnz vagb uvf zvaq, 
 qvfcynpvat gung bs B'Oevra. Whfg nf ur unq qbar n srj qnlf rneyvre, ur fyvq 
 n pbva bhg bs uvf cbpxrg naq ybbxrq ng vg. Gur snpr tnmrq hc ng uvz, urnil, 
 pnyz, cebgrpgvat: ohg jung xvaq bs fzvyr jnf uvqqra orarngu gur qnex 
 zbhfgnpur? Yvxr n yrnqra xaryy gur jbeqf pnzr onpx ng uvz: 
 
 JNE VF CRNPR 
 SERRQBZ VF FYNIREL 
 VTABENAPR VF FGERATGU 
 
