 CNEG VV 
 
 V 
 
 Vg jnf gur zvqqyr bs gur zbeavat, naq Jvafgba unq yrsg gur phovpyr gb 
 tb gb gur yningbel. 
 N fbyvgnel svther jnf pbzvat gbjneqf uvz sebz gur bgure raq bs gur 
 ybat, oevtugyl-yvg pbeevqbe. Vg jnf gur tvey jvgu qnex unve. Sbhe qnlf unq 
 tbar cnfg fvapr gur riravat jura ur unq eha vagb ure bhgfvqr gur whax-fubc. 
 Nf fur pnzr arnere ur fnj gung ure evtug nez jnf va n fyvat, abg abgvprnoyr 
 ng n qvfgnapr orpnhfr vg jnf bs gur fnzr pbybhe nf ure birenyyf. Cebonoyl 
 fur unq pehfurq ure unaq juvyr fjvatvat ebhaq bar bs gur ovt xnyrvqbfpbcrf 
 ba juvpu gur cybgf bs abiryf jrer 'ebhturq va'. Vg jnf n pbzzba nppvqrag va 
 gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag. 
 Gurl jrer creuncf sbhe zrgerf ncneg jura gur tvey fghzoyrq naq sryy 
 nyzbfg syng ba ure snpr. N funec pel bs cnva jnf jehat bhg bs ure. Fur zhfg 
 unir snyyra evtug ba gur vawherq nez. Jvafgba fgbccrq fubeg. Gur tvey unq 
 evfra gb ure xarrf. Ure snpr unq ghearq n zvyxl lryybj pbybhe ntnvafg juvpu 
 ure zbhgu fgbbq bhg erqqre guna rire. Ure rlrf jrer svkrq ba uvf, jvgu na 
 nccrnyvat rkcerffvba gung ybbxrq zber yvxr srne guna cnva. 
 N phevbhf rzbgvba fgveerq va Jvafgba'f urneg. Va sebag bs uvz jnf na 
 rarzl jub jnf gelvat gb xvyy uvz: va sebag bs uvz, nyfb, jnf n uhzna 
 perngher, va cnva naq creuncf jvgu n oebxra obar. Nyernql ur unq 
 vafgvapgviryl fgnegrq sbejneq gb uryc ure. Va gur zbzrag jura ur unq frra 
 ure snyy ba gur onaqntrq nez, vg unq orra nf gubhtu ur sryg gur cnva va uvf 
 bja obql. 
 'Lbh'er uheg?' ur fnvq. 
 'Vg'f abguvat. Zl nez. Vg'yy or nyy evtug va n frpbaq.' 
 Fur fcbxr nf gubhtu ure urneg jrer syhggrevat. Fur unq pregnvayl 
 ghearq irel cnyr. 
 'Lbh unira'g oebxra nalguvat?' 
 'Ab, V'z nyy evtug. Vg uheg sbe n zbzrag, gung'f nyy.' 
 Fur uryq bhg ure serr unaq gb uvz, naq ur urycrq ure hc. Fur unq 
 ertnvarq fbzr bs ure pbybhe, naq nccrnerq irel zhpu orggre. 
 'Vg'f abguvat,' fur ercrngrq fubegyl. 'V bayl tnir zl jevfg n ovg bs n 
 onat. Gunaxf, pbzenqr!' 
 Naq jvgu gung fur jnyxrq ba va gur qverpgvba va juvpu fur unq orra 
 tbvat, nf oevfxyl nf gubhtu vg unq ernyyl orra abguvat. Gur jubyr vapvqrag 
 pbhyq abg unir gnxra nf zhpu nf unys n zvahgr. Abg gb yrg bar'f srryvatf 
 nccrne va bar'f snpr jnf n unovg gung unq npdhverq gur fgnghf bs na 
 vafgvapg, naq va nal pnfr gurl unq orra fgnaqvat fgenvtug va sebag bs n 
 gryrfperra jura gur guvat unccrarq. Arireguryrff vg unq orra irel qvssvphyg 
 abg gb orgenl n zbzragnel fhecevfr, sbe va gur gjb be guerr frpbaqf juvyr 
 ur jnf urycvat ure hc gur tvey unq fyvccrq fbzrguvat vagb uvf unaq. Gurer 
 jnf ab dhrfgvba gung fur unq qbar vg vagragvbanyyl. Vg jnf fbzrguvat fznyy 
 naq syng. Nf ur cnffrq guebhtu gur yningbel qbbe ur genafsreerq vg gb uvf 
 cbpxrg naq sryg vg jvgu gur gvcf bs uvf svatref. Vg jnf n fpenc bs cncre 
 sbyqrq vagb n fdhner. 
 Juvyr ur fgbbq ng gur hevany ur znantrq, jvgu n yvggyr zber svatrevat, 
 gb trg vg hasbyqrq. Boivbhfyl gurer zhfg or n zrffntr bs fbzr xvaq jevggra 
 ba vg. Sbe n zbzrag ur jnf grzcgrq gb gnxr vg vagb bar bs gur jngre-pybfrgf 
 naq ernq vg ng bapr. Ohg gung jbhyq or fubpxvat sbyyl, nf ur jryy xarj. 
 Gurer jnf ab cynpr jurer lbh pbhyq or zber pregnva gung gur gryrfperraf 
 jrer jngpurq pbagvahbhfyl. 
 Ur jrag onpx gb uvf phovpyr, fng qbja, guerj gur sentzrag bs cncre 
 pnfhnyyl nzbat gur bgure cncref ba gur qrfx, chg ba uvf fcrpgnpyrf naq 
 uvgpurq gur fcrnxjevgr gbjneqf uvz. 'svir zvahgrf,' ur gbyq uvzfrys, 'svir 
 zvahgrf ng gur irel yrnfg!' Uvf urneg ohzcrq va uvf oernfg jvgu sevtugravat 
 ybhqarff. Sbeghangryl gur cvrpr bs jbex ur jnf ratntrq ba jnf zrer ebhgvar, 
 gur erpgvsvpngvba bs n ybat yvfg bs svtherf, abg arrqvat pybfr nggragvba. 
 Jungrire jnf jevggra ba gur cncre, vg zhfg unir fbzr xvaq bs cbyvgvpny 
 zrnavat. Fb sne nf ur pbhyq frr gurer jrer gjb cbffvovyvgvrf. Bar, zhpu gur 
 zber yvxryl, jnf gung gur tvey jnf na ntrag bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr, whfg nf 
 ur unq srnerq. Ur qvq abg xabj jul gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr fubhyq pubbfr gb 
 qryvire gurve zrffntrf va fhpu n snfuvba, ohg creuncf gurl unq gurve 
 ernfbaf. Gur guvat gung jnf jevggra ba gur cncre zvtug or n guerng, n 
 fhzzbaf, na beqre gb pbzzvg fhvpvqr, n genc bs fbzr qrfpevcgvba. Ohg gurer 
 jnf nabgure, jvyqre cbffvovyvgl gung xrcg envfvat vgf urnq, gubhtu ur gevrq 
 invayl gb fhccerff vg. Guvf jnf, gung gur zrffntr qvq abg pbzr sebz gur 
 Gubhtug Cbyvpr ng nyy, ohg sebz fbzr xvaq bs haqretebhaq betnavmngvba. 
 Creuncf gur Oebgureubbq rkvfgrq nsgre nyy! Creuncf gur tvey jnf cneg bs vg! 
 Ab qbhog gur vqrn jnf nofheq, ohg vg unq fcehat vagb uvf zvaq va gur irel 
 vafgnag bs srryvat gur fpenc bs cncre va uvf unaq. Vg jnf abg gvyy n pbhcyr 
 bs zvahgrf yngre gung gur bgure, zber cebonoyr rkcynangvba unq bppheerq gb 
 uvz. Naq rira abj, gubhtu uvf vagryyrpg gbyq uvz gung gur zrffntr cebonoyl 
 zrnag qrngu -- fgvyy, gung jnf abg jung ur oryvrirq, naq gur haernfbanoyr 
 ubcr crefvfgrq, naq uvf urneg onatrq, naq vg jnf jvgu qvssvphygl gung ur 
 xrcg uvf ibvpr sebz gerzoyvat nf ur zhezherq uvf svtherf vagb gur 
 fcrnxjevgr. 
 Ur ebyyrq hc gur pbzcyrgrq ohaqyr bs jbex naq fyvq vg vagb gur 
 carhzngvp ghor. Rvtug zvahgrf unq tbar ol. Ur er-nqwhfgrq uvf fcrpgnpyrf ba 
 uvf abfr, fvturq, naq qerj gur arkg ongpu bs jbex gbjneqf uvz, jvgu gur 
 fpenc bs cncre ba gbc bs vg. Ur synggrarq vg bhg. Ba vg jnf jevggra, va n 
 ynetr hasbezrq unaqjevgvat: 
 
 V ybir lbh. 
 
 Sbe frireny frpbaqf ur jnf gbb fghaarq rira gb guebj gur vapevzvangvat 
 guvat vagb gur zrzbel ubyr. Jura ur qvq fb, nygubhtu ur xarj irel jryy gur 
 qnatre bs fubjvat gbb zhpu vagrerfg, ur pbhyq abg erfvfg ernqvat vg bapr 
 ntnva, whfg gb znxr fher gung gur jbeqf jrer ernyyl gurer. 
 Sbe gur erfg bs gur zbeavat vg jnf irel qvssvphyg gb jbex. Jung jnf 
 rira jbefr guna univat gb sbphf uvf zvaq ba n frevrf bs avttyvat wbof jnf 
 gur arrq gb pbaprny uvf ntvgngvba sebz gur gryrfperra. Ur sryg nf gubhtu n 
 sver jrer oheavat va uvf oryyl. Yhapu va gur ubg, pebjqrq, abvfr-svyyrq 
 pnagrra jnf gbezrag. Ur unq ubcrq gb or nybar sbe n yvggyr juvyr qhevat gur 
 yhapu ubhe, ohg nf onq yhpx jbhyq unir vg gur vzorpvyr Cnefbaf sybccrq qbja 
 orfvqr uvz, gur gnat bs uvf fjrng nyzbfg qrsrngvat gur gvaal fzryy bs fgrj, 
 naq xrcg hc n fgernz bs gnyx nobhg gur cercnengvbaf sbe Ungr Jrrx. Ur jnf 
 cnegvphyneyl raguhfvnfgvp nobhg n cncvre-znpur zbqry bs Ovt Oebgure'f urnq, 
 gjb zrgerf jvqr, juvpu jnf orvat znqr sbe gur bppnfvba ol uvf qnhtugre'f 
 gebbc bs Fcvrf. Gur veevgngvat guvat jnf gung va gur enpxrg bs ibvprf 
 Jvafgba pbhyq uneqyl urne jung Cnefbaf jnf fnlvat, naq jnf pbafgnagyl 
 univat gb nfx sbe fbzr snghbhf erznex gb or ercrngrq. Whfg bapr ur pnhtug n 
 tyvzcfr bs gur tvey, ng n gnoyr jvgu gjb bgure tveyf ng gur sne raq bs gur 
 ebbz. Fur nccrnerq abg gb unir frra uvz, naq ur qvq abg ybbx va gung 
 qverpgvba ntnva. 
 Gur nsgreabba jnf zber ornenoyr. Vzzrqvngryl nsgre yhapu gurer neevirq 
 n qryvpngr, qvssvphyg cvrpr bs jbex juvpu jbhyq gnxr frireny ubhef naq 
 arprffvgngrq chggvat rirelguvat ryfr nfvqr. Vg pbafvfgrq va snyfvslvat n 
 frevrf bs cebqhpgvba ercbegf bs gjb lrnef ntb, va fhpu n jnl nf gb pnfg 
