 guebhtu gur znvyf, vg jnf bhg bs gur dhrfgvba. Ol n ebhgvar gung jnf abg 
 rira frperg, nyy yrggref jrer bcrarq va genafvg. Npghnyyl, srj crbcyr rire 
 jebgr yrggref. Sbe gur zrffntrf gung vg jnf bppnfvbanyyl arprffnel gb fraq, 
 gurer jrer cevagrq cbfgpneqf jvgu ybat yvfgf bs cuenfrf, naq lbh fgehpx bhg 
