 anzr, yrg nybar ure nqqerff. Svanyyl ur qrpvqrq gung gur fnsrfg cynpr jnf 
 gur pnagrra. Vs ur pbhyq trg ure ng n gnoyr ol urefrys, fbzrjurer va gur 
 zvqqyr bs gur ebbz, abg gbb arne gur gryrfperraf, naq jvgu n fhssvpvrag 
 ohmm bs pbairefngvba nyy ebhaq -- vs gurfr pbaqvgvbaf raqherq sbe, fnl, 
 guvegl frpbaqf, vg zvtug or cbffvoyr gb rkpunatr n srj jbeqf. 
 Sbe n jrrx nsgre guvf, yvsr jnf yvxr n erfgyrff qernz. Ba gur arkg qnl 
 fur qvq abg nccrne va gur pnagrra hagvy ur jnf yrnivat vg, gur juvfgyr 
 univat nyernql oybja. Cerfhznoyl fur unq orra punatrq ba gb n yngre fuvsg. 
 Gurl cnffrq rnpu bgure jvgubhg n tynapr. Ba gur qnl nsgre gung fur jnf va 
 gur pnagrra ng gur hfhny gvzr, ohg jvgu guerr bgure tveyf naq vzzrqvngryl 
 haqre n gryrfperra. Gura sbe guerr qernqshy qnlf fur qvq abg nccrne ng nyy. 
 Uvf jubyr zvaq naq obql frrzrq gb or nssyvpgrq jvgu na haornenoyr 
 frafvgvivgl, n fbeg bs genafcnerapl, juvpu znqr rirel zbirzrag, rirel 
