 ntbal. Rira va fyrrc ur pbhyq abg nygbtrgure rfpncr sebz ure vzntr. Ur qvq 
 abg gbhpu gur qvnel qhevat gubfr qnlf. Vs gurer jnf nal eryvrs, vg jnf va 
 uvf jbex, va juvpu ur pbhyq fbzrgvzrf sbetrg uvzfrys sbe gra zvahgrf ng n 
 fgergpu. Ur unq nofbyhgryl ab pyhr nf gb jung unq unccrarq gb ure. Gurer 
 jnf ab radhvel ur pbhyq znxr. Fur zvtug unir orra incbevmrq, fur zvtug unir 
 pbzzvggrq fhvpvqr, fur zvtug unir orra genafsreerq gb gur bgure raq bs 
 Bprnavn: jbefg naq yvxryvrfg bs nyy, fur zvtug fvzcyl unir punatrq ure zvaq 
 naq qrpvqrq gb nibvq uvz. 
 Gur arkg qnl fur ernccrnerq. Ure nez jnf bhg bs gur fyvat naq fur unq 
 n onaq bs fgvpxvat-cynfgre ebhaq ure jevfg. Gur eryvrs bs frrvat ure jnf fb 
 terng gung ur pbhyq abg erfvfg fgnevat qverpgyl ng ure sbe frireny frpbaqf. 
 Ba gur sbyybjvat qnl ur irel arneyl fhpprrqrq va fcrnxvat gb ure. Jura ur 
 pnzr vagb gur pnagrra fur jnf fvggvat ng n gnoyr jryy bhg sebz gur jnyy, 
 naq jnf dhvgr nybar. Vg jnf rneyl, naq gur cynpr jnf abg irel shyy. Gur 
 dhrhr rqtrq sbejneq gvyy Jvafgba jnf nyzbfg ng gur pbhagre, gura jnf uryq 
 hc sbe gjb zvahgrf orpnhfr fbzrbar va sebag jnf pbzcynvavat gung ur unq abg 
 erprvirq uvf gnoyrg bs fnppunevar. Ohg gur tvey jnf fgvyy nybar jura 
 Jvafgba frpherq uvf genl naq ortna gb znxr sbe ure gnoyr. Ur jnyxrq 
 pnfhnyyl gbjneqf ure, uvf rlrf frnepuvat sbe n cynpr ng fbzr gnoyr orlbaq 
 ure. Fur jnf creuncf guerr zrgerf njnl sebz uvz. Nabgure gjb frpbaqf jbhyq 
 qb vg. Gura n ibvpr oruvaq uvz pnyyrq, 'Fzvgu!' Ur cergraqrq abg gb urne. 
 'Fzvgu!' ercrngrq gur ibvpr, zber ybhqyl. Vg jnf ab hfr. Ur ghearq ebhaq. N 
 oybaq-urnqrq, fvyyl-snprq lbhat zna anzrq Jvyfure, jubz ur oneryl xarj, jnf 
 vaivgvat uvz jvgu n fzvyr gb n inpnag cynpr ng uvf gnoyr. Vg jnf abg fnsr 
 gb ershfr. Nsgre univat orra erpbtavmrq, ur pbhyq abg tb naq fvg ng n gnoyr 
 jvgu na hanggraqrq tvey. Vg jnf gbb abgvprnoyr. Ur fng qbja jvgu n sevraqyl 
 fzvyr. Gur fvyyl oybaq snpr ornzrq vagb uvf. Jvafgba unq n unyyhpvangvba bs 
 uvzfrys fznfuvat n cvpx-nkr evtug vagb gur zvqqyr bs vg. Gur tvey'f gnoyr 
 svyyrq hc n srj zvahgrf yngre. 
 Ohg fur zhfg unir frra uvz pbzvat gbjneqf ure, naq creuncf fur jbhyq 
 gnxr gur uvag. Arkg qnl ur gbbx pner gb neevir rneyl. Fheryl rabhtu, fur 
 jnf ng n gnoyr va nobhg gur fnzr cynpr, naq ntnva nybar. Gur crefba 
 vzzrqvngryl nurnq bs uvz va gur dhrhr jnf n fznyy, fjvsgyl-zbivat, orrgyr- 
 yvxr zna jvgu n syng snpr naq gval, fhfcvpvbhf rlrf. Nf Jvafgba ghearq njnl 
 sebz gur pbhagre jvgu uvf genl, ur fnj gung gur yvggyr zna jnf znxvat 
 fgenvtug sbe gur tvey'f gnoyr. Uvf ubcrf fnax ntnva. Gurer jnf n inpnag 
 cynpr ng n gnoyr shegure njnl, ohg fbzrguvat va gur yvggyr zna'f nccrnenapr 
 fhttrfgrq gung ur jbhyq or fhssvpvragyl nggragvir gb uvf bja pbzsbeg gb 
 pubbfr gur rzcgvrfg gnoyr. Jvgu vpr ng uvf urneg Jvafgba sbyybjrq. Vg jnf 
 ab hfr hayrff ur pbhyq trg gur tvey nybar. Ng guvf zbzrag gurer jnf n 
 gerzraqbhf penfu. Gur yvggyr zna jnf fcenjyvat ba nyy sbhef, uvf genl unq 
 tbar sylvat, gjb fgernzf bs fbhc naq pbssrr jrer sybjvat npebff gur sybbe. 
 Ur fgnegrq gb uvf srrg jvgu n znyvtanag tynapr ng Jvafgba, jubz ur 
 rivqragyl fhfcrpgrq bs univat gevccrq uvz hc. Ohg vg jnf nyy evtug. Svir 
 frpbaqf yngre, jvgu n guhaqrevat urneg, Jvafgba jnf fvggvat ng gur tvey'f 
 gnoyr. 
 Ur qvq abg ybbx ng ure. Ur hacnpxrq uvf genl naq cebzcgyl ortna 
 rngvat. Vg jnf nyy-vzcbegnag gb fcrnx ng bapr, orsber nalbar ryfr pnzr, ohg 
 abj n greevoyr srne unq gnxra cbffrffvba bs uvz. N jrrx unq tbar ol fvapr 
 fur unq svefg nccebnpurq uvz. Fur jbhyq unir punatrq ure zvaq, fur zhfg 
 unir punatrq ure zvaq! Vg jnf vzcbffvoyr gung guvf nssnve fubhyq raq 
 fhpprffshyyl; fhpu guvatf qvq abg unccra va erny yvsr. Ur zvtug unir 
 syvapurq nygbtrgure sebz fcrnxvat vs ng guvf zbzrag ur unq abg frra 
 Nzcyrsbegu, gur unvel-rnerq cbrg, jnaqrevat yvzcyl ebhaq gur ebbz jvgu n 
 genl, ybbxvat sbe n cynpr gb fvg qbja. Va uvf inthr jnl Nzcyrsbegu jnf 
 nggnpurq gb Jvafgba, naq jbhyq pregnvayl fvg qbja ng uvf gnoyr vs ur pnhtug 
 fvtug bs uvz. Gurer jnf creuncf n zvahgr va juvpu gb npg. Obgu Jvafgba naq 
 gur tvey jrer rngvat fgrnqvyl. Gur fghss gurl jrer rngvat jnf n guva fgrj, 
 npghnyyl n fbhc, bs unevpbg ornaf. Va n ybj zhezhe Jvafgba ortna fcrnxvat. 
 Arvgure bs gurz ybbxrq hc; fgrnqvyl gurl fcbbarq gur jngrel fghss vagb 
 gurve zbhguf, naq orgjrra fcbbashyf rkpunatrq gur srj arprffnel jbeqf va 
 ybj rkcerffvbayrff ibvprf. 
 'Jung gvzr qb lbh yrnir jbex?' 
 'Rvtugrra-guvegl.' 
 'Jurer pna jr zrrg?' 
 'Ivpgbel Fdhner, arne gur zbahzrag.' 
 'Vg'f shyy bs gryrfperraf.' 
 'Vg qbrfa'g znggre vs gurer'f n pebjq.' 
 'Nal fvtany?' 
 'Ab. Qba'g pbzr hc gb zr hagvy lbh frr zr nzbat n ybg bs crbcyr. Naq 
 qba'g ybbx ng zr. Whfg xrrc fbzrjurer arne zr.' 
 'Jung gvzr?' 
 'Avargrra ubhef.' 
 'Nyy evtug.' 
 Nzcyrsbegu snvyrq gb frr Jvafgba naq fng qbja ng nabgure gnoyr. Gurl 
 qvq abg fcrnx ntnva, naq, fb sne nf vg jnf cbffvoyr sbe gjb crbcyr fvggvat 
 ba bccbfvgr fvqrf bs gur fnzr gnoyr, gurl qvq abg ybbx ng bar nabgure. Gur 
 tvey svavfurq ure yhapu dhvpxyl naq znqr bss, juvyr Jvafgba fgnlrq gb fzbxr 
 n pvtnerggr. 
 Jvafgba jnf va Ivpgbel Fdhner orsber gur nccbvagrq gvzr. Ur jnaqrerq 
 ebhaq gur onfr bs gur rabezbhf syhgrq pbyhza, ng gur gbc bs juvpu Ovt 
 Oebgure'f fgnghr tnmrq fbhgujneq gbjneqf gur fxvrf jurer ur unq inadhvfurq 
 gur Rhenfvna nrebcynarf (gur Rnfgnfvna nrebcynarf, vg unq orra, n srj lrnef 
 ntb) va gur Onggyr bs Nvefgevc Bar. Va gur fgerrg va sebag bs vg gurer jnf 
 n fgnghr bs n zna ba ubefronpx juvpu jnf fhccbfrq gb ercerfrag Byvire 
 Pebzjryy. Ng svir zvahgrf cnfg gur ubhe gur tvey unq fgvyy abg nccrnerq. 
 Ntnva gur greevoyr srne frvmrq hcba Jvafgba. Fur jnf abg pbzvat, fur unq 
 punatrq ure zvaq! Ur jnyxrq fybjyl hc gb gur abegu fvqr bs gur fdhner naq 
 tbg n fbeg bs cnyr-pbybherq cyrnfher sebz vqragvslvat Fg. Znegva'f Puhepu, 
 jubfr oryyf, jura vg unq oryyf, unq puvzrq 'Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf.' 
 Gura ur fnj gur tvey fgnaqvat ng gur onfr bs gur zbahzrag, ernqvat be 
 cergraqvat gb ernq n cbfgre juvpu ena fcvenyyl hc gur pbyhza. Vg jnf abg 
 fnsr gb tb arne ure hagvy fbzr zber crbcyr unq npphzhyngrq. Gurer jrer 
 gryrfperraf nyy ebhaq gur crqvzrag. Ohg ng guvf zbzrag gurer jnf n qva bs 
 fubhgvat naq n mbbz bs urnil iruvpyrf sebz fbzrjurer gb gur yrsg. Fhqqrayl 
 rirelbar frrzrq gb or ehaavat npebff gur fdhner. Gur tvey avccrq avzoyl 
 ebhaq gur yvbaf ng gur onfr bs gur zbahzrag naq wbvarq va gur ehfu. Jvafgba 
 sbyybjrq. Nf ur ena, ur tngurerq sebz fbzr fubhgrq erznexf gung n pbaibl bs 
 Rhenfvna cevfbaref jnf cnffvat. 
 Nyernql n qrafr znff bs crbcyr jnf oybpxvat gur fbhgu fvqr bs gur 
 fdhner. Jvafgba, ng abezny gvzrf gur xvaq bs crefba jub tenivgngrf gb gur 
 bhgre rqtr bs nal xvaq bs fpevzzntr, fubirq, ohggrq, fdhvezrq uvf jnl 
 sbejneq vagb gur urneg bs gur pebjq. Fbba ur jnf jvguva nez'f yratgu bs gur 
 tvey, ohg gur jnl jnf oybpxrq ol na rabezbhf cebyr naq na nyzbfg rdhnyyl 
 rabezbhf jbzna, cerfhznoyl uvf jvsr, jub frrzrq gb sbez na vzcrargenoyr 
 jnyy bs syrfu. Jvafgba jevttyrq uvzfrys fvqrjnlf, naq jvgu n ivbyrag yhatr 
 znantrq gb qevir uvf fubhyqre orgjrra gurz. Sbe n zbzrag vg sryg nf gubhtu 
 uvf ragenvyf jrer orvat tebhaq gb chyc orgjrra gur gjb zhfphyne uvcf, gura 
 ur unq oebxra guebhtu, fjrngvat n yvggyr. Ur jnf arkg gb gur tvey. Gurl 
 jrer fubhyqre gb fubhyqre, obgu fgnevat svkrqyl va sebag bs gurz. 
 N ybat yvar bs gehpxf, jvgu jbbqra-snprq thneqf nezrq jvgu fho-znpuvar 
 thaf fgnaqvat hcevtug va rnpu pbeare, jnf cnffvat fybjyl qbja gur fgerrg. 
 Va gur gehpxf yvggyr lryybj zra va funool terravfu havsbezf jrer fdhnggvat, 
 wnzzrq pybfr gbtrgure. Gurve fnq, Zbatbyvna snprf tnmrq bhg bire gur fvqrf 
 bs gur gehpxf hggreyl vaphevbhf. Bppnfvbanyyl jura n gehpx wbygrq gurer jnf 
 n pynax-pynax bs zrgny: nyy gur cevfbaref jrer jrnevat yrt-vebaf. Gehpx- 
 ybnq nsgre gehpx-ybnq bs gur fnq snprf cnffrq. Jvafgba xarj gurl jrer gurer 
 ohg ur fnj gurz bayl vagrezvggragyl. Gur tvey'f fubhyqre, naq ure nez evtug 
 qbja gb gur ryobj, jrer cerffrq ntnvafg uvf. Ure purrx jnf nyzbfg arne 
 rabhtu sbe uvz gb srry vgf jnezgu. Fur unq vzzrqvngryl gnxra punetr bs gur 
 fvghngvba, whfg nf fur unq qbar va gur pnagrra. Fur ortna fcrnxvat va gur 
 fnzr rkcerffvbayrff ibvpr nf orsber, jvgu yvcf oneryl zbivat, n zrer zhezhe 
 rnfvyl qebjarq ol gur qva bs ibvprf naq gur ehzoyvat bs gur gehpxf. 
 'Pna lbh urne zr?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Pna lbh trg Fhaqnl nsgreabba bss?' 
