 yvgrenyyl arire fnj gurz rkprcg va gur thvfr bs cevfbaref, naq rira nf 
 cevfbaref bar arire tbg zber guna n zbzragnel tyvzcfr bs gurz. Abe qvq bar 
 xabj jung orpnzr bs gurz, ncneg sebz gur srj jub jrer unatrq nf jne- 
 pevzvanyf: gur bguref fvzcyl inavfurq, cerfhznoyl vagb sbeprq-ynobhe pnzcf. 
 Gur ebhaq Zbtby snprf unq tvira jnl gb snprf bs n zber Rhebcrna glcr, 
 qvegl, orneqrq naq rkunhfgrq. Sebz bire fpehool purrxobarf rlrf ybbxrq vagb 
