 dhvrgyl. Cerfragyl gurl unq ernpurq gur rqtr bs gur yvggyr jbbq. Fur 
 fgbccrq uvz. 
 'Qba'g tb bhg vagb gur bcra. Gurer zvtug or fbzrbar jngpuvat. Jr'er 
 nyy evtug vs jr xrrc oruvaq gur obhtuf.' 
 Gurl jrer fgnaqvat va gur funqr bs unmry ohfurf. Gur fhayvtug, 
 svygrevat guebhtu vaahzrenoyr yrnirf, jnf fgvyy ubg ba gurve snprf. Jvafgba 
