 urqtr ba gur bccbfvgr fvqr gur obhtuf bs gur ryz gerrf fjnlrq whfg 
 creprcgvoyl va gur oerrmr, naq gurve yrnirf fgveerq snvagyl va qrafr znffrf 
 yvxr jbzra'f unve. Fheryl fbzrjurer arneol, ohg bhg bs fvtug, gurer zhfg or 
 n fgernz jvgu terra cbbyf jurer qnpr jrer fjvzzvat? 
 'Vfa'g gurer n fgernz fbzrjurer arne urer?' ur juvfcrerq. 
 'Gung'f evtug, gurer vf n fgernz. Vg'f ng gur rqtr bs gur arkg svryq, 
 npghnyyl. Gurer ner svfu va vg, terng ovt barf. Lbh pna jngpu gurz ylvat va 
 gur cbbyf haqre gur jvyybj gerrf, jnivat gurve gnvyf.' 
 'Vg'f gur Tbyqra Pbhagel -- nyzbfg,' ur zhezherq. 
 'Gur Tbyqra Pbhagel?' 
 'Vg'f abguvat, ernyyl. N ynaqfpncr V'ir frra fbzrgvzrf va n qernz.' 
 'Ybbx!' juvfcrerq Whyvn. 
 N guehfu unq nyvtugrq ba n obhtu abg svir zrgerf njnl, nyzbfg ng gur 
 yriry bs gurve snprf. Creuncf vg unq abg frra gurz. Vg jnf va gur fha, gurl 
 va gur funqr. Vg fcernq bhg vgf jvatf, svggrq gurz pnershyyl vagb cynpr 
 ntnva, qhpxrq vgf urnq sbe n zbzrag, nf gubhtu znxvat n fbeg bs borvfnapr 
 gb gur fha, naq gura ortna gb cbhe sbegu n gbeerag bs fbat. Va gur 
 nsgreabba uhfu gur ibyhzr bs fbhaq jnf fgnegyvat. Jvafgba naq Whyvn pyhat 
 gbtrgure, snfpvangrq. Gur zhfvp jrag ba naq ba, zvahgr nsgre zvahgr, jvgu 
 nfgbavfuvat inevngvbaf, arire bapr ercrngvat vgfrys, nyzbfg nf gubhtu gur 
 oveq jrer qryvorengryl fubjvat bss vgf iveghbfvgl. Fbzrgvzrf vg fgbccrq sbe 
 n srj frpbaqf, fcernq bhg naq erfrggyrq vgf jvatf, gura fjryyrq vgf 
 fcrpxyrq oernfg naq ntnva ohefg vagb fbat. Jvafgba jngpurq vg jvgu n fbeg 
 bs inthr erirerapr. Sbe jubz, sbe jung, jnf gung oveq fvatvat? Ab zngr, ab 
 eviny jnf jngpuvat vg. Jung znqr vg fvg ng gur rqtr bs gur ybaryl jbbq naq 
 cbhe vgf zhfvp vagb abguvatarff? Ur jbaqrerq jurgure nsgre nyy gurer jnf n 
 zvpebcubar uvqqra fbzrjurer arne. Ur naq Whyvn unq fcbxra bayl va ybj 
 juvfcref, naq vg jbhyq abg cvpx hc jung gurl unq fnvq, ohg vg jbhyq cvpx hc 
 gur guehfu. Creuncf ng gur bgure raq bs gur vafgehzrag fbzr fznyy, orrgyr- 
 yvxr zna jnf yvfgravat vagragyl -- yvfgravat gb gung. Ohg ol qrterrf gur 
 sybbq bs zhfvp qebir nyy fcrphyngvbaf bhg bs uvf zvaq. Vg jnf nf gubhtu vg 
 jrer n xvaq bs yvdhvq fghss gung cbherq nyy bire uvz naq tbg zvkrq hc jvgu 
 gur fhayvtug gung svygrerq guebhtu gur yrnirf. Ur fgbccrq guvaxvat naq 
 zreryl sryg. Gur tvey'f jnvfg va gur oraq bs uvf nez jnf fbsg naq jnez. Ur 
 chyyrq ure ebhaq fb gung gurl jrer oernfg gb oernfg; ure obql frrzrq gb 
 zryg vagb uvf. Jurerire uvf unaqf zbirq vg jnf nyy nf lvryqvat nf jngre. 
 Gurve zbhguf pyhat gbtrgure; vg jnf dhvgr qvssrerag sebz gur uneq xvffrf 
 gurl unq rkpunatrq rneyvre. Jura gurl zbirq gurve snprf ncneg ntnva obgu bs 
 gurz fvturq qrrcyl. Gur oveq gbbx sevtug naq syrq jvgu n pynggre bs jvatf. 
 Jvafgba chg uvf yvcf ntnvafg ure rne. 'Abj,' ur juvfcrerq. 
 'Abg urer,' fur juvfcrerq onpx. 'Pbzr onpx gb gur uvqrbhg. Vg'f 
 fnsre.' 
 Dhvpxyl, jvgu na bppnfvbany penpxyr bs gjvtf, gurl guernqrq gurve jnl 
 onpx gb gur pyrnevat. Jura gurl jrer bapr vafvqr gur evat bs fncyvatf fur 
 ghearq naq snprq uvz. Gurl jrer obgu oernguvat snfg. ohg gur fzvyr unq 
 ernccrnerq ebhaq gur pbearef bs ure zbhgu. Fur fgbbq ybbxvat ng uvz sbe na 
 vafgnag, gura sryg ng gur mvccre bs ure birenyyf. Naq, lrf! vg jnf nyzbfg 
 nf va uvf qernz. Nyzbfg nf fjvsgyl nf ur unq vzntvarq vg, fur unq gbea ure 
 pybgurf bss, naq jura fur syhat gurz nfvqr vg jnf jvgu gung fnzr 
 zntavsvprag trfgher ol juvpu n jubyr pvivyvmngvba frrzrq gb or naavuvyngrq. 
 Ure obql tyrnzrq juvgr va gur fha. Ohg sbe n zbzrag ur qvq abg ybbx ng ure 
 obql; uvf rlrf jrer napuberq ol gur serpxyrq snpr jvgu vgf snvag, obyq 
 fzvyr. Ur xaryg qbja orsber ure naq gbbx ure unaqf va uvf. 
 'Unir lbh qbar guvf orsber?' 
 'Bs pbhefr. Uhaqerqf bs gvzrf -- jryy, fpberf bs gvzrf naljnl.' 
 'Jvgu Cnegl zrzoref?' 
 'Lrf, nyjnlf jvgu Cnegl zrzoref.' 
 'Jvgu zrzoref bs gur Vaare Cnegl?' 
 'Abg jvgu gubfr fjvar, ab. Ohg gurer'f cyragl gung jbhyq vs gurl tbg 
 unys n punapr. Gurl'er abg fb ubyl nf gurl znxr bhg.' 
 Uvf urneg yrncg. Fpberf bs gvzrf fur unq qbar vg: ur jvfurq vg unq 
 orra uhaqerqf -- gubhfnaqf. Nalguvat gung uvagrq ng pbeehcgvba nyjnlf 
 svyyrq uvz jvgu n jvyq ubcr. Jub xarj, creuncf gur Cnegl jnf ebggra haqre 
 gur fhesnpr, vgf phyg bs fgerahbhfarff naq frys-qravny fvzcyl n funz 
 pbaprnyvat vavdhvgl. Vs ur pbhyq unir vasrpgrq gur jubyr ybg bs gurz jvgu 
 yrcebfl be flcuvyvf, ubj tynqyl ur jbhyq unir qbar fb! Nalguvat gb ebg, gb 
 jrnxra, gb haqrezvar! Ur chyyrq ure qbja fb gung gurl jrer xarryvat snpr gb 
 snpr. 
 'Yvfgra. Gur zber zra lbh'ir unq, gur zber V ybir lbh. Qb lbh 
 haqrefgnaq gung?' 
 'Lrf, cresrpgyl.' 
 'V ungr chevgl, V ungr tbbqarff! V qba'g jnag nal iveghr gb rkvfg 
 naljurer. V jnag rirelbar gb or pbeehcg gb gur obarf.' 
 'Jryy gura, V bhtug gb fhvg lbh, qrne. V'z pbeehcg gb gur obarf.' 
 'Lbh yvxr qbvat guvf? V qba'g zrna fvzcyl zr: V zrna gur guvat va 
 vgfrys?' 
 'V nqber vg.' 
 Gung jnf nobir nyy jung ur jnagrq gb urne. Abg zreryl gur ybir bs bar 
 crefba ohg gur navzny vafgvapg, gur fvzcyr haqvssreragvngrq qrfver: gung 
 jnf gur sbepr gung jbhyq grne gur Cnegl gb cvrprf. Ur cerffrq ure qbja hcba 
 gur tenff, nzbat gur snyyra oyhroryyf. Guvf gvzr gurer jnf ab qvssvphygl. 
 Cerfragyl gur evfvat naq snyyvat bs gurve oernfgf fybjrq gb abezny fcrrq, 
 naq va n fbeg bs cyrnfnag urycyrffarff gurl sryy ncneg. Gur fha frrzrq gb 
 unir tebja ubggre. Gurl jrer obgu fyrrcl. Ur ernpurq bhg sbe gur qvfpneqrq 
 birenyyf naq chyyrq gurz cnegyl bire ure. Nyzbfg vzzrqvngryl gurl sryy 
 nfyrrc naq fyrcg sbe nobhg unys na ubhe. 
 Jvafgba jbxr svefg. Ur fng hc naq jngpurq gur serpxyrq snpr, fgvyy 
 crnprshyyl nfyrrc, cvyybjrq ba gur cnyz bs ure unaq. Rkprcg sbe ure zbhgu, 
 lbh pbhyq abg pnyy ure ornhgvshy. Gurer jnf n yvar be gjb ebhaq gur rlrf, 
 vs lbh ybbxrq pybfryl. Gur fubeg qnex unve jnf rkgenbeqvanevyl guvpx naq 
 fbsg. Vg bppheerq gb uvz gung ur fgvyy qvq abg xabj ure fheanzr be jurer 
 fur yvirq. 
 Gur lbhat, fgebat obql, abj urycyrff va fyrrc, njbxr va uvz n cvglvat, 
 cebgrpgvat srryvat. Ohg gur zvaqyrff graqrearff gung ur unq sryg haqre gur 
 unmry gerr, juvyr gur guehfu jnf fvatvat, unq abg dhvgr pbzr onpx. Ur 
 chyyrq gur birenyyf nfvqr naq fghqvrq ure fzbbgu juvgr synax. Va gur byq 
 qnlf, ur gubhtug, n zna ybbxrq ng n tvey'f obql naq fnj gung vg jnf 
 qrfvenoyr, naq gung jnf gur raq bs gur fgbel. Ohg lbh pbhyq abg unir cher 
 ybir be cher yhfg abjnqnlf. Ab rzbgvba jnf cher, orpnhfr rirelguvat jnf 
 zvkrq hc jvgu srne naq ungerq. Gurve rzoenpr unq orra n onggyr, gur pyvznk 
 n ivpgbel. Vg jnf n oybj fgehpx ntnvafg gur Cnegl. Vg jnf n cbyvgvpny npg. 
 
 VVV 
 
 'Jr pna pbzr urer bapr ntnva,' fnvq Whyvn. 'Vg'f trarenyyl fnsr gb hfr 
 nal uvqr-bhg gjvpr. Ohg abg sbe nabgure zbagu be gjb, bs pbhefr.' 
 Nf fbba nf fur jbxr hc ure qrzrnabhe unq punatrq. Fur orpnzr nyreg naq 
 ohfvarff-yvxr, chg ure pybgurf ba, xabggrq gur fpneyrg fnfu nobhg ure 
 jnvfg, naq ortna neenatvat gur qrgnvyf bs gur wbhearl ubzr. Vg frrzrq 
 angheny gb yrnir guvf gb ure. Fur boivbhfyl unq n cenpgvpny phaavat juvpu 
 Jvafgba ynpxrq, naq fur frrzrq nyfb gb unir na rkunhfgvir xabjyrqtr bs gur 
 pbhagelfvqr ebhaq Ybaqba, fgberq njnl sebz vaahzrenoyr pbzzhavgl uvxrf. Gur 
 ebhgr fur tnir uvz jnf dhvgr qvssrerag sebz gur bar ol juvpu ur unq pbzr, 
 naq oebhtug uvz bhg ng n qvssrerag envyjnl fgngvba. 'Arire tb ubzr gur fnzr 
 jnl nf lbh jrag bhg,' fur fnvq, nf gubhtu rahapvngvat na vzcbegnag trareny 
 cevapvcyr. Fur jbhyq yrnir svefg, naq Jvafgba jnf gb jnvg unys na ubhe 
 orsber sbyybjvat ure. 
 Fur unq anzrq n cynpr jurer gurl pbhyq zrrg nsgre jbex, sbhe riravatf 
 urapr. Vg jnf n fgerrg va bar bs gur cbbere dhnegref, jurer gurer jnf na 
 bcra znexrg juvpu jnf trarenyyl pebjqrq naq abvfl. Fur jbhyq or unatvat 
 nobhg nzbat gur fgnyyf, cergraqvat gb or va frnepu bs fubrynprf be frjvat- 
 guernq. Vs fur whqtrq gung gur pbnfg jnf pyrne fur jbhyq oybj ure abfr jura 
 ur nccebnpurq; bgurejvfr ur jnf gb jnyx cnfg ure jvgubhg erpbtavgvba. Ohg 
 jvgu yhpx, va gur zvqqyr bs gur pebjq, vg jbhyq or fnsr gb gnyx sbe n 
 dhnegre bs na ubhe naq neenatr nabgure zrrgvat. 
 'Naq abj V zhfg tb,' fur fnvq nf fbba nf ur unq znfgrerq uvf 
 vafgehpgvbaf. 'V'z qhr onpx ng avargrra-guvegl. V'ir tbg gb chg va gjb 
 ubhef sbe gur Whavbe Nagv-Frk Yrnthr, unaqvat bhg yrnsyrgf, be fbzrguvat. 
 Vfa'g vg oybbql? Tvir zr n oehfu-qbja, jbhyq lbh? Unir V tbg nal gjvtf va 
 zl unve? Ner lbh fher? Gura tbbq-olr, zl ybir, tbbq-olr!' 
 Fur syhat urefrys vagb uvf nezf, xvffrq uvz nyzbfg ivbyragyl, naq n 
 zbzrag yngre chfurq ure jnl guebhtu gur fncyvatf naq qvfnccrnerq vagb gur 
 jbbq jvgu irel yvggyr abvfr. Rira abj ur unq abg sbhaq bhg ure fheanzr be 
 ure nqqerff. Ubjrire, vg znqr ab qvssrerapr, sbe vg jnf vapbaprvinoyr gung 
 gurl pbhyq rire zrrg vaqbbef be rkpunatr nal xvaq bs jevggra pbzzhavpngvba. 
 Nf vg unccrarq, gurl arire jrag onpx gb gur pyrnevat va gur jbbq. 
 Qhevat gur zbagu bs Znl gurer jnf bayl bar shegure bppnfvba ba juvpu gurl 
 npghnyyl fhpprrqrq va znxvat ybir. Gung jnf va nabgure uvqyat-cynpr xabja 
 gb Whyvn, gur orysel bs n ehvabhf puhepu va na nyzbfg-qrfregrq fgergpu bs 
 pbhagel jurer na ngbzvp obzo unq snyyra guvegl lrnef rneyvre. Vg jnf n tbbq 
 uvqvat-cynpr jura bapr lbh tbg gurer, ohg gur trggvat gurer jnf irel 
 qnatrebhf. Sbe gur erfg gurl pbhyq zrrg bayl va gur fgerrgf, va n qvssrerag 
 cynpr rirel riravat naq arire sbe zber guna unys na ubhe ng n gvzr. Va gur 
 fgerrg vg jnf hfhnyyl cbffvoyr gb gnyx, nsgre n snfuvba. Nf gurl qevsgrq 
 qbja gur pebjqrq cnirzragf, abg dhvgr noernfg naq arire ybbxvat ng bar 
 nabgure, gurl pneevrq ba n phevbhf, vagrezvggrag pbairefngvba juvpu syvpxrq 
 ba naq bss yvxr gur ornzf bs n yvtugubhfr, fhqqrayl avccrq vagb fvyrapr ol 
 gur nccebnpu bs n Cnegl havsbez be gur cebkvzvgl bs n gryrfperra, gura 
 gnxra hc ntnva zvahgrf yngre va gur zvqqyr bs n fragrapr, gura noehcgyl phg 
 fubeg nf gurl cnegrq ng gur nterrq fcbg, gura pbagvahrq nyzbfg jvgubhg 
 vagebqhpgvba ba gur sbyybjvat qnl. Whyvn nccrnerq gb or dhvgr hfrq gb guvf 
 xvaq bs pbairefngvba, juvpu fur pnyyrq 'gnyxvat ol vafgnyzragf'. Fur jnf 
 nyfb fhecevfvatyl nqrcg ng fcrnxvat jvgubhg zbivat ure yvcf. Whfg bapr va 
 nyzbfg n zbagu bs avtugyl zrrgvatf gurl znantrq gb rkpunatr n xvff. Gurl 
 jrer cnffvat va fvyrapr qbja n fvqr-fgerrg (Whyvn jbhyq arire fcrnx jura 
 gurl jrer njnl sebz gur znva fgerrgf) jura gurer jnf n qrnsravat ebne, gur 
 rnegu urnirq, naq gur nve qnexrarq, naq Jvafgba sbhaq uvzfrys ylvat ba uvf 
 fvqr, oehvfrq naq greevsvrq. N ebpxrg obzo zhfg unir qebccrq dhvgr arne ng 
 unaq. Fhqqrayl ur orpnzr njner bs Whyvn'f snpr n srj pragvzrgerf sebz uvf 
 bja, qrnguyl juvgr, nf juvgr nf punyx. Rira ure yvcf jrer juvgr. Fur jnf 
 qrnq! Ur pynfcrq ure ntnvafg uvz naq sbhaq gung ur jnf xvffvat n yvir jnez 
 snpr. Ohg gurer jnf fbzr cbjqrel fghss gung tbg va gur jnl bs uvf yvcf. 
 Obgu bs gurve snprf jrer guvpxyl pbngrq jvgu cynfgre. 
 Gurer jrer riravatf jura gurl ernpurq gurve eraqrmibhf naq gura unq gb 
 jnyx cnfg bar nabgure jvgubhg n fvta, orpnhfr n cngeby unq whfg pbzr ebhaq 
 gur pbeare be n uryvpbcgre jnf ubirevat bireurnq. Rira vs vg unq orra yrff 
 qnatrebhf, vg jbhyq fgvyy unir orra qvssvphyg gb svaq gvzr gb zrrg. 
 Jvafgba'f jbexvat jrrx jnf fvkgl ubhef, Whyvn'f jnf rira ybatre, naq gurve 
 serr qnlf inevrq nppbeqvat gb gur cerffher bs jbex naq qvq abg bsgra 
 pbvapvqr. Whyvn, va nal pnfr, fryqbz unq na riravat pbzcyrgryl serr. Fur 
 fcrag na nfgbavfuvat nzbhag bs gvzr va nggraqvat yrpgherf naq 
 qrzbafgengvbaf, qvfgevohgvat yvgrengher sbe gur whavbe Nagv-Frk Yrnthr, 
 cercnevat onaaref sbe Ungr Jrrx, znxvat pbyyrpgvbaf sbe gur fnivatf 
 pnzcnvta, naq fhpu-yvxr npgvivgvrf. Vg cnvq, fur fnvq, vg jnf pnzbhsyntr. 
 Vs lbh xrcg gur fznyy ehyrf, lbh pbhyq oernx gur ovt barf. Fur rira vaqhprq 
 Jvafgba gb zbegtntr lrg nabgure bs uvf riravatf ol raebyyvat uvzfrys sbe 
 gur cneg-gvzr zhavgvba jbex juvpu jnf qbar ibyhagnevyl ol mrnybhf Cnegl 
 zrzoref. Fb, bar riravat rirel jrrx, Jvafgba fcrag sbhe ubhef bs cnenylfvat 
 oberqbz, fperjvat gbtrgure fznyy ovgf bs zrgny juvpu jrer cebonoyl cnegf bs 
 obzo shfrf, va n qenhtugl, vyy-yvg jbexfubc jurer gur xabpxvat bs unzzref 
 zvatyrq qernevyl jvgu gur zhfvp bs gur gryrfperraf. 
 Jura gurl zrg va gur puhepu gbjre gur tncf va gurve sentzragnel 
 pbairefngvba jrer svyyrq hc. Vg jnf n oynmvat nsgreabba. Gur nve va gur 
 yvggyr fdhner punzore nobir gur oryyf jnf ubg naq fgntanag, naq fzryg 
 birecbjrevatyl bs cvtrba qhat. Gurl fng gnyxvat sbe ubhef ba gur qhfgl, 
 gjvt-yvggrerq sybbe, bar be bgure bs gurz trggvat hc sebz gvzr gb gvzr gb 
 pnfg n tynapr guebhtu gur neebjfyvgf naq znxr fher gung ab bar jnf pbzvat. 
 Whyvn jnf gjragl-fvk lrnef byq. Fur yvirq va n ubfgry jvgu guvegl 
 bgure tveyf ('Nyjnlf va gur fgvax bs jbzra! Ubj V ungr jbzra!' fur fnvq 
 cneragurgvpnyyl), naq fur jbexrq, nf ur unq thrffrq, ba gur abiry-jevgvat 
 znpuvarf va gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag. Fur rawblrq ure jbex, juvpu pbafvfgrq 
 puvrsyl va ehaavat naq freivpvat n cbjreshy ohg gevpxl ryrpgevp zbgbe. Fur 
 jnf 'abg pyrire', ohg jnf sbaq bs hfvat ure unaqf naq sryg ng ubzr jvgu 
 znpuvarel. Fur pbhyq qrfpevor gur jubyr cebprff bs pbzcbfvat n abiry, sebz 
 gur trareny qverpgvir vffhrq ol gur Cynaavat Pbzzvggrr qbja gb gur svany 
 gbhpuvat-hc ol gur Erjevgr Fdhnq. Ohg fur jnf abg vagrerfgrq va gur 
 svavfurq cebqhpg. Fur 'qvqa'g zhpu pner sbe ernqvat,' fur fnvq. Obbxf jrer 
 whfg n pbzzbqvgl gung unq gb or cebqhprq, yvxr wnz be obbgynprf. 
 Fur unq ab zrzbevrf bs nalguvat orsber gur rneyl 'fvkgvrf naq gur bayl 
 crefba fur unq rire xabja jub gnyxrq serdhragyl bs gur qnlf orsber gur 
 Eribyhgvba jnf n tenaqsngure jub unq qvfnccrnerq jura fur jnf rvtug. Ng 
 fpubby fur unq orra pncgnva bs gur ubpxrl grnz naq unq jba gur tlzanfgvpf 
 gebcul gjb lrnef ehaavat. Fur unq orra n gebbc-yrnqre va gur Fcvrf naq n 
 oenapu frpergnel va gur Lbhgu Yrnthr orsber wbvavat gur Whavbe Nagv-Frk 
 Yrnthr. Fur unq nyjnlf obear na rkpryyrag punenpgre. Fur unq rira (na 
 vasnyyvoyr znex bs tbbq erchgngvba) orra cvpxrq bhg gb jbex va Cbeabfrp, 
 gur fho-frpgvba bs gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag juvpu ghearq bhg purnc 
 cbeabtencul sbe qvfgevohgvba nzbat gur cebyrf. Vg jnf avpxanzrq Zhpx Ubhfr 
 ol gur crbcyr jub jbexrq va vg, fur erznexrq. Gurer fur unq erznvarq sbe n 
 lrne, urycvat gb cebqhpr obbxyrgf va frnyrq cnpxrgf jvgu gvgyrf yvxr 
 Fcnaxvat Fgbevrf be Bar Avtug va n Tveyf" Fpubby, gb or obhtug shegviryl ol 
 cebyrgnevna lbhguf jub jrer haqre gur vzcerffvba gung gurl jrer ohlvat 
 fbzrguvat vyyrtny. 
 'Jung ner gurfr obbxf yvxr?' fnvq Jvafgba phevbhfyl. 
 'Bu, tunfgyl ehoovfu. Gurl'er obevat, ernyyl. Gurl bayl unir fvk 
 cybgf, ohg gurl fjnc gurz ebhaq n ovg. Bs pbhefr V jnf bayl ba gur 
 xnyrvqbfpbcrf. V jnf arire va gur Erjevgr Fdhnq. V'z abg yvgrenel, qrne -- 
 abg rira rabhtu sbe gung.' 
 Ur yrnearq jvgu nfgbavfuzrag gung nyy gur jbexref va Cbeabfrp, rkprcg 
 gur urnqf bs gur qrcnegzragf, jrer tveyf. Gur gurbel jnf gung zra, jubfr 
 frk vafgvapgf jrer yrff pbagebyynoyr guna gubfr bs jbzra, jrer va terngre 
 qnatre bs orvat pbeehcgrq ol gur svygu gurl unaqyrq. 
 'Gurl qba'g rira yvxr univat zneevrq jbzra gurer,' fur nqqrq. Tveyf 
 ner nyjnlf fhccbfrq gb or fb cher. Urer'f bar jub vfa'g, naljnl. 
 Fur unq unq ure svefg ybir-nssnve jura fur jnf fvkgrra, jvgu n Cnegl 
 zrzore bs fvkgl jub yngre pbzzvggrq fhvpvqr gb nibvq neerfg. 'Naq n tbbq 
 wbo gbb,' fnvq Whyvn, 'bgurejvfr gurl'q unir unq zl anzr bhg bs uvz jura ur 
 pbasrffrq.' Fvapr gura gurer unq orra inevbhf bguref. Yvsr nf fur fnj vg 
 jnf dhvgr fvzcyr. Lbh jnagrq n tbbq gvzr; 'gurl', zrnavat gur Cnegl, jnagrq 
 gb fgbc lbh univat vg; lbh oebxr gur ehyrf nf orfg lbh pbhyq. Fur frrzrq gb 
 guvax vg whfg nf angheny gung 'gurl' fubhyq jnag gb ebo lbh bs lbhe 
 cyrnfherf nf gung lbh fubhyq jnag gb nibvq orvat pnhtug. Fur ungrq gur 
 Cnegl, naq fnvq fb va gur pehqrfg jbeqf, ohg fur znqr ab trareny pevgvpvfz 
 bs vg. Rkprcg jurer vg gbhpurq hcba ure bja yvsr fur unq ab vagrerfg va 
 Cnegl qbpgevar. Ur abgvprq gung fur arire hfrq Arjfcrnx jbeqf rkprcg gur 
 barf gung unq cnffrq vagb rirelqnl hfr. Fur unq arire urneq bs gur 
 Oebgureubbq, naq ershfrq gb oryvrir va vgf rkvfgrapr. Nal xvaq bs betnavmrq 
 eribyg ntnvafg gur Cnegl, juvpu jnf obhaq gb or n snvyher, fgehpx ure nf 
 fghcvq. Gur pyrire guvat jnf gb oernx gur ehyrf naq fgnl nyvir nyy gur 
 fnzr. Ur jbaqrerq inthryl ubj znal bguref yvxr ure gurer zvtug or va gur 
 lbhatre trarengvba crbcyr jub unq tebja hc va gur jbeyq bs gur Eribyhgvba, 
 xabjvat abguvat ryfr, npprcgvat gur Cnegl nf fbzrguvat hanygrenoyr, yvxr 
 gur fxl, abg eroryyvat ntnvafg vgf nhgubevgl ohg fvzcyl rinqvat vg, nf n 
 enoovg qbqtrf n qbt. 
 Gurl qvq abg qvfphff gur cbffvovyvgl bs trggvat zneevrq. Vg jnf gbb 
 erzbgr gb or jbegu guvaxvat nobhg. Ab vzntvanoyr pbzzvggrr jbhyq rire 
 fnapgvba fhpu n zneevntr rira vs Xngunevar, Jvafgba'f jvsr, pbhyq fbzrubj 
 unir orra tbg evq bs. Vg jnf ubcryrff rira nf n qnlqernz. 
 'Jung jnf fur yvxr, lbhe jvsr?' fnvq Whyvn. 
 'Fur jnf -- qb lbh xabj gur Arjfcrnx jbeq tbbqguvaxshy? Zrnavat 
 anghenyyl begubqbk, vapncnoyr bs guvaxvat n onq gubhtug?' 
 'Ab, V qvqa'g xabj gur jbeq, ohg V xabj gur xvaq bs crefba, evtug 
 rabhtu.' 
 Ur ortna gryyvat ure gur fgbel bs uvf zneevrq yvsr, ohg phevbhfyl 
 rabhtu fur nccrnerq gb xabj gur rffragvny cnegf bs vg nyernql. Fur 
 qrfpevorq gb uvz, nyzbfg nf gubhtu fur unq frra be sryg vg, gur fgvssravat 
 bs Xngunevar'f obql nf fbba nf ur gbhpurq ure, gur jnl va juvpu fur fgvyy 
 frrzrq gb or chfuvat uvz sebz ure jvgu nyy ure fgeratgu, rira jura ure nezf 
 jrer pynfcrq gvtugyl ebhaq uvz. Jvgu Whyvn ur sryg ab qvssvphygl va gnyxvat 
 nobhg fhpu guvatf: Xngunevar, va nal pnfr, unq ybat prnfrq gb or n cnvashy 
 zrzbel naq orpnzr zreryl n qvfgnfgrshy bar. 
 'V pbhyq unir fgbbq vg vs vg unqa'g orra sbe bar guvat,' ur fnvq. Ur 
 gbyq ure nobhg gur sevtvq yvggyr prerzbal gung Xngunevar unq sbeprq uvz gb 
 tb guebhtu ba gur fnzr avtug rirel jrrx. 'Fur ungrq vg, ohg abguvat jbhyq 
 znxr ure fgbc qbvat vg. Fur hfrq gb pnyy vg -- ohg lbh'yy arire thrff.' 
 'Bhe qhgl gb gur Cnegl,' fnvq Whyvn cebzcgyl. 
 'Ubj qvq lbh xabj gung?' 
 'V'ir orra ng fpubby gbb, qrne. Frk gnyxf bapr n zbagu sbe gur bire- 
 fvkgrraf. Naq va gur Lbhgu Zbirzrag. Gurl eho vg vagb lbh sbe lrnef. V qner 
 fnl vg jbexf va n ybg bs pnfrf. Ohg bs pbhefr lbh pna arire gryy; crbcyr 
 ner fhpu ulcbpevgrf.' 
 Fur ortna gb raynetr hcba gur fhowrpg. Jvgu Whyvn, rirelguvat pnzr 
 onpx gb ure bja frkhnyvgl. Nf fbba nf guvf jnf gbhpurq hcba va nal jnl fur 
 jnf pncnoyr bs terng nphgrarff. Hayvxr Jvafgba, fur unq tenfcrq gur vaare 
 zrnavat bs gur Cnegl'f frkhny chevgnavfz. Vg jnf abg zreryl gung gur frk 
 vafgvapg perngrq n jbeyq bs vgf bja juvpu jnf bhgfvqr gur Cnegl'f pbageby 
 naq juvpu gurersber unq gb or qrfgeblrq vs cbffvoyr. Jung jnf zber 
 vzcbegnag jnf gung frkhny cevingvba vaqhprq ulfgrevn, juvpu jnf qrfvenoyr 
 orpnhfr vg pbhyq or genafsbezrq vagb jne-srire naq yrnqre-jbefuvc. Gur jnl 
 fur chg vg jnf: 
 'Jura lbh znxr ybir lbh'er hfvat hc raretl; naq nsgrejneqf lbh srry 
 unccl naq qba'g tvir n qnza sbe nalguvat. Gurl pna'g orne lbh gb srry yvxr 
 gung. Gurl jnag lbh gb or ohefgvat jvgu raretl nyy gur gvzr. Nyy guvf 
 znepuvat hc naq qbja naq purrevat naq jnivat syntf vf fvzcyl frk tbar fbhe. 
 Vs lbh'er unccl vafvqr lbhefrys, jul fubhyq lbh trg rkpvgrq nobhg Ovt 
 Oebgure naq gur Guerr-Lrne Cynaf naq gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr naq nyy gur erfg 
 bs gurve oybbql ebg?' 
 Gung jnf irel gehr, ur gubhtug. Gurer jnf n qverpg vagvzngr pbaarkvba 
 orgjrra punfgvgl naq cbyvgvpny begubqbkl. Sbe ubj pbhyq gur srne, gur 
 ungerq, naq gur yhangvp perqhyvgl juvpu gur Cnegl arrqrq va vgf zrzoref or 
 xrcg ng gur evtug cvgpu, rkprcg ol obggyvat qbja fbzr cbjreshy vafgvapg naq 
 hfvat vg nf n qevivat sbepr? Gur frk vzchyfr jnf qnatrebhf gb gur Cnegl, 
 naq gur Cnegl unq ghearq vg gb nppbhag. Gurl unq cynlrq n fvzvyne gevpx 
 jvgu gur vafgvapg bs cneragubbq. Gur snzvyl pbhyq abg npghnyyl or 
 nobyvfurq, naq, vaqrrq, crbcyr jrer rapbhentrq gb or sbaq bs gurve 
 puvyqera, va nyzbfg gur byq-snfuvbarq jnl. Gur puvyqera, ba gur bgure unaq, 
 jrer flfgrzngvpnyyl ghearq ntnvafg gurve cneragf naq gnhtug gb fcl ba gurz 
 naq ercbeg gurve qrivngvbaf. Gur snzvyl unq orpbzr va rssrpg na rkgrafvba 
 bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr. Vg jnf n qrivpr ol zrnaf bs juvpu rirelbar pbhyq or 
 fheebhaqrq avtug naq qnl ol vasbezref jub xarj uvz vagvzngryl. 
 Noehcgyl uvf zvaq jrag onpx gb Xngunevar. Xngunevar jbhyq 
 hadhrfgvbanoyl unir qrabhaprq uvz gb gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr vs fur unq abg 
 unccrarq gb or gbb fghcvq gb qrgrpg gur habegubqbkl bs uvf bcvavbaf. Ohg 
 jung ernyyl erpnyyrq ure gb uvz ng guvf zbzrag jnf gur fgvsyvat urng bs gur 
 nsgreabba, juvpu unq oebhtug gur fjrng bhg ba uvf sberurnq. Ur ortna 
 gryyvat Whyvn bs fbzrguvat gung unq unccrarq, be engure unq snvyrq gb 
 unccra, ba nabgure fjrygrevat fhzzre nsgreabba, ryrira lrnef ntb. 
 Vg jnf guerr be sbhe zbaguf nsgre gurl jrer zneevrq. Gurl unq ybfg 
 gurve jnl ba n pbzzhavgl uvxr fbzrjurer va Xrag. Gurl unq bayl ynttrq 
 oruvaq gur bguref sbe n pbhcyr bs zvahgrf, ohg gurl gbbx n jebat gheavat, 
 naq cerfragyl sbhaq gurzfryirf chyyrq hc fubeg ol gur rqtr bs na byq punyx 
 dhneel. Vg jnf n furre qebc bs gra be gjragl zrgerf, jvgu obhyqref ng gur 
 obggbz. Gurer jnf abobql bs jubz gurl pbhyq nfx gur jnl. Nf fbba nf fur 
 ernyvmrq gung gurl jrer ybfg Xngunevar orpnzr irel harnfl. Gb or njnl sebz 
 gur abvfl zbo bs uvxref rira sbe n zbzrag tnir ure n srryvat bs jebat- 
 qbvat. Fur jnagrq gb uheel onpx ol gur jnl gurl unq pbzr naq fgneg 
 frnepuvat va gur bgure qverpgvba. Ohg ng guvf zbzrag Jvafgba abgvprq fbzr 
 ghsgf bs ybbfrfgevsr tebjvat va gur penpxf bs gur pyvss orarngu gurz. Bar 
 ghsg jnf bs gjb pbybhef, zntragn naq oevpx-erq, nccneragyl tebjvat ba gur 
 fnzr ebbg. Ur unq arire frra nalguvat bs gur xvaq orsber, naq ur pnyyrq gb 
 Xngunevar gb pbzr naq ybbx ng vg. 
 'Ybbx, Xngunevar! Ybbx ng gubfr sybjref. Gung pyhzc qbja arne gur 
 obggbz. Qb lbh frr gurl'er gjb qvssrerag pbybhef?' 
 Fur unq nyernql ghearq gb tb, ohg fur qvq engure sergshyyl pbzr onpx 
 sbe n zbzrag. Fur rira yrnarq bhg bire gur pyvss snpr gb frr jurer ur jnf 
 cbvagvat. Ur jnf fgnaqvat n yvggyr oruvaq ure, naq ur chg uvf unaq ba ure 
 jnvfg gb fgrnql ure. Ng guvf zbzrag vg fhqqrayl bppheerq gb uvz ubj 
 pbzcyrgryl nybar gurl jrer. Gurer jnf abg n uhzna perngher naljurer, abg n 
 yrns fgveevat, abg rira n oveq njnxr. Va n cynpr yvxr guvf gur qnatre gung 
 gurer jbhyq or n uvqqra zvpebcubar jnf irel fznyy, naq rira vs gurer jnf n 
 zvpebcubar vg jbhyq bayl cvpx hc fbhaqf. Vg jnf gur ubggrfg fyrrcvrfg ubhe 
 bs gur nsgreabba. Gur fha oynmrq qbja hcba gurz, gur fjrng gvpxyrq uvf 
 snpr. Naq gur gubhtug fgehpx uvz... 
 'Jul qvqa'g lbh tvir ure n tbbq fubir?' fnvq Whyvn. 'V jbhyq unir.' 
 'Lrf, qrne, lbh jbhyq unir. V jbhyq, vs V'q orra gur fnzr crefba gura 
 nf V nz abj. Be creuncf V jbhyq -- V'z abg pregnva.' 
 'Ner lbh fbeel lbh qvqa'g?' 
 'Lrf. Ba gur jubyr V'z fbeel V qvqa'g.' 
 Gurl jrer fvggvat fvqr ol fvqr ba gur qhfgl sybbe. Ur chyyrq ure 
 pybfre ntnvafg uvz. Ure urnq erfgrq ba uvf fubhyqre, gur cyrnfnag fzryy bs 
 ure unve pbadhrevat gur cvtrba qhat. Fur jnf irel lbhat, ur gubhtug, fur 
 fgvyy rkcrpgrq fbzrguvat sebz yvsr, fur qvq abg haqrefgnaq gung gb chfu na 
 vapbairavrag crefba bire n pyvss fbyirf abguvat. 
 'Npghnyyl vg jbhyq unir znqr ab qvssrerapr,' ur fnvq. 
 'Gura jul ner lbh fbeel lbh qvqa'g qb vg?' 
 'Bayl orpnhfr V cersre n cbfvgvir gb n artngvir. Va guvf tnzr gung 
 jr'er cynlvat, jr pna'g jva. Fbzr xvaqf bs snvyher ner orggre guna bgure 
 xvaqf, gung'f nyy.' 
 Ur sryg ure fubhyqref tvir n jevttyr bs qvffrag. Fur nyjnlf 
 pbagenqvpgrq uvz jura ur fnvq nalguvat bs guvf xvaq. Fur jbhyq abg npprcg 
 vg nf n ynj bs angher gung gur vaqvivqhny vf nyjnlf qrsrngrq. Va n jnl fur 
 ernyvmrq gung fur urefrys jnf qbbzrq, gung fbbare be yngre gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr jbhyq pngpu ure naq xvyy ure, ohg jvgu nabgure cneg bs ure zvaq fur 
 oryvrirq gung vg jnf fbzrubj cbffvoyr gb pbafgehpg n frperg jbeyq va juvpu 
 lbh pbhyq yvir nf lbh pubfr. Nyy lbh arrqrq jnf yhpx naq phaavat naq 
 obyqarff. Fur qvq abg haqrefgnaq gung gurer jnf ab fhpu guvat nf unccvarff, 
 gung gur bayl ivpgbel ynl va gur sne shgher, ybat nsgre lbh jrer qrnq, gung 
 sebz gur zbzrag bs qrpynevat jne ba gur Cnegl vg jnf orggre gb guvax bs 
 lbhefrys nf n pbecfr. 
 'Jr ner gur qrnq,' ur fnvq. 
 'Jr'er abg qrnq lrg,' fnvq Whyvn cebfnvpnyyl. 
 'Abg culfvpnyyl. Fvk zbaguf, n lrne -- svir lrnef, pbaprvinoyl. V nz 
 nsenvq bs qrngu. Lbh ner lbhat, fb cerfhznoyl lbh'er zber nsenvq bs vg guna 
 V nz. Boivbhfyl jr funyy chg vg bss nf ybat nf jr pna. Ohg vg znxrf irel 
 yvggyr qvssrerapr. Fb ybat nf uhzna orvatf fgnl uhzna, qrngu naq yvsr ner 
 gur fnzr guvat.' 
 'Bu, ehoovfu! Juvpu jbhyq lbh fbbare fyrrc jvgu, zr be n fxryrgba? 
 Qba'g lbh rawbl orvat nyvir? Qba'g lbh yvxr srryvat: Guvf vf zr, guvf vf zl 
 unaq, guvf vf zl yrt, V'z erny, V'z fbyvq, V'z nyvir! Qba'g lbh yvxr guvf?' 
 Fur gjvfgrq urefrys ebhaq naq cerffrq ure obfbz ntnvafg uvz. Ur pbhyq 
 srry ure oernfgf, evcr lrg svez, guebhtu ure birenyyf. Ure obql frrzrq gb 
 or cbhevat fbzr bs vgf lbhgu naq ivtbhe vagb uvf. 
 'Lrf, V yvxr gung,' ur fnvq. 
 'Gura fgbc gnyxvat nobhg qlvat. Naq abj yvfgra, qrne, jr'ir tbg gb svk 
 hc nobhg gur arkg gvzr jr zrrg. Jr znl nf jryy tb onpx gb gur cynpr va gur 
 jbbq. Jr'ir tvira vg n tbbq ybat erfg. Ohg lbh zhfg trg gurer ol n 
 qvssrerag jnl guvf gvzr. V'ir tbg vg nyy cynaarq bhg. Lbh gnxr gur genva -- 
 ohg ybbx, V'yy qenj vg bhg sbe lbh.' 
 Naq va ure cenpgvpny jnl fur fpencrq gbtrgure n fznyy fdhner bs qhfg, 
 naq jvgu n gjvt sebz n cvtrba'f arfg ortna qenjvat n znc ba gur sybbe. 
 
 VI 
 
 Jvafgba ybbxrq ebhaq gur funool yvggyr ebbz nobir Ze. Puneevatgba'f 
 fubc. Orfvqr gur jvaqbj gur rabezbhf orq jnf znqr hc, jvgu enttrq oynaxrgf 
 naq n pbireyrff obyfgre. Gur byq-snfuvbarq pybpx jvgu gur gjryir-ubhe snpr 
 jnf gvpxvat njnl ba gur znagrycvrpr. Va gur pbeare, ba gur tngryrt gnoyr, 
 gur tynff cncrejrvtug juvpu ur unq obhtug ba uvf ynfg ivfvg tyrnzrq fbsgyl 
 bhg bs gur unys-qnexarff. 
 Va gur sraqre jnf n onggrerq gva bvyfgbir, n fnhprcna, naq gjb phcf, 
 cebivqrq ol Ze. Puneevatgba. Jvafgba yvg gur oheare naq frg n cna bs jngre 
 gb obvy. Ur unq oebhtug na rairybcr shyy bs Ivpgbel Pbssrr naq fbzr 
 fnppunevar gnoyrgf. Gur pybpx'f unaqf fnvq friragrra-gjragl: vg jnf 
 avargrra-gjragl ernyyl. Fur jnf pbzvat ng avargrra-guvegl. 
 Sbyyl, sbyyl, uvf urneg xrcg fnlvat: pbafpvbhf, tenghvgbhf, fhvpvqny 
 sbyyl. Bs nyy gur pevzrf gung n Cnegl zrzore pbhyq pbzzvg, guvf bar jnf gur 
 yrnfg cbffvoyr gb pbaprny. Npghnyyl gur vqrn unq svefg sybngrq vagb uvf 
 urnq va gur sbez bs n ivfvba, bs gur tynff cncrejrvtug zveeberq ol gur 
 fhesnpr bs gur tngryrt gnoyr. Nf ur unq sberfrra, Ze. Puneevatgba unq znqr 
 ab qvssvphygl nobhg yrggvat gur ebbz. Ur jnf boivbhfyl tynq bs gur srj 
 qbyynef gung vg jbhyq oevat uvz. Abe qvq ur frrz fubpxrq be orpbzr 
 bssrafviryl xabjvat jura vg jnf znqr pyrne gung Jvafgba jnagrq gur ebbz sbe 
 gur checbfr bs n ybir-nssnve. Vafgrnq ur ybbxrq vagb gur zvqqyr qvfgnapr 
 naq fcbxr va trarenyvgvrf, jvgu fb qryvpngr na nve nf gb tvir gur 
 vzcerffvba gung ur unq orpbzr cnegyl vaivfvoyr. Cevinpl, ur fnvq, jnf n 
 irel inyhnoyr guvat. Rirelbar jnagrq n cynpr jurer gurl pbhyq or nybar 
 bppnfvbanyyl. Naq jura gurl unq fhpu n cynpr, vg jnf bayl pbzzba pbhegrfl 
 va nalbar ryfr jub xarj bs vg gb xrrc uvf xabjyrqtr gb uvzfrys. Ur rira, 
 frrzvat nyzbfg gb snqr bhg bs rkvfgrapr nf ur qvq fb, nqqrq gung gurer jrer 
 gjb ragevrf gb gur ubhfr, bar bs gurz guebhtu gur onpx lneq, juvpu tnir ba 
 na nyyrl. 
 Haqre gur jvaqbj fbzrobql jnf fvatvat. Jvafgba crrcrq bhg, frpher va 
 gur cebgrpgvba bs gur zhfyva phegnva. Gur Whar fha jnf fgvyy uvtu va gur 
 fxl, naq va gur fha-svyyrq pbheg orybj, n zbafgebhf jbzna, fbyvq nf n 
 Abezna cvyyne, jvgu oenjal erq sbernezf naq n fnpxvat nceba fgenccrq nobhg 
 ure zvqqyr, jnf fghzcvat gb naq seb orgjrra n jnfugho naq n pybgurf yvar, 
 crttvat bhg n frevrf bs fdhner juvgr guvatf juvpu Jvafgba erpbtavmrq nf 
 onovrf" qvncref. Jurarire ure zbhgu jnf abg pbexrq jvgu pybgurf crtf fur 
 jnf fvatvat va n cbjreshy pbagenygb: 
 
 Vg jnf bayl na 'bcryrff snapl. 
 Vg cnffrq yvxr na Vcevy qlr, 
 Ohg n ybbx na' n jbeq na' gur qernzf gurl fgveerq 
 Gurl 'nir fgbyra zl 'rneg njlr! 
 
 Gur ghar unq orra unhagvat Ybaqba sbe jrrxf cnfg. Vg jnf bar bs 
 pbhagyrff fvzvyne fbatf choyvfurq sbe gur orarsvg bs gur cebyrf ol n fho- 
 frpgvba bs gur Zhfvp Qrcnegzrag. Gur jbeqf bs gurfr fbatf jrer pbzcbfrq 
 jvgubhg nal uhzna vagreiragvba jungrire ba na vafgehzrag xabja nf n 
 irefvsvpngbe. Ohg gur jbzna fnat fb gharshyyl nf gb ghea gur qernqshy 
 ehoovfu vagb na nyzbfg cyrnfnag fbhaq. Ur pbhyq urne gur jbzna fvatvat naq 
 gur fpencr bs ure fubrf ba gur syntfgbarf, naq gur pevrf bs gur puvyqera va 
 gur fgerrg, naq fbzrjurer va gur sne qvfgnapr n snvag ebne bs genssvp, naq 
 lrg gur ebbz frrzrq phevbhfyl fvyrag, gunaxf gb gur nofrapr bs n 
 gryrfperra. 
 Sbyyl, sbyyl, sbyyl! ur gubhtug ntnva. Vg jnf vapbaprvinoyr gung gurl 
 pbhyq serdhrag guvf cynpr sbe zber guna n srj jrrxf jvgubhg orvat pnhtug. 
 Ohg gur grzcgngvba bs univat n uvqvat-cynpr gung jnf gehyl gurve bja, 
 vaqbbef naq arne ng unaq, unq orra gbb zhpu sbe obgu bs gurz. Sbe fbzr gvzr 
 nsgre gurve ivfvg gb gur puhepu orysel vg unq orra vzcbffvoyr gb neenatr 
 zrrgvatf. Jbexvat ubhef unq orra qenfgvpnyyl vapernfrq va nagvpvcngvba bs 
 Ungr Jrrx. Vg jnf zber guna n zbagu qvfgnag, ohg gur rabezbhf, pbzcyrk 
 cercnengvbaf gung vg ragnvyrq jrer guebjvat rkgen jbex ba gb rirelobql. 
 Svanyyl obgu bs gurz znantrq gb frpher n serr nsgreabba ba gur fnzr qnl. 
 Gurl unq nterrq gb tb onpx gb gur pyrnevat va gur jbbq. Ba gur riravat 
 orsberunaq gurl zrg oevrsyl va gur fgerrg. Nf hfhny, Jvafgba uneqyl ybbxrq 
 ng Whyvn nf gurl qevsgrq gbjneqf bar nabgure va gur pebjq, ohg sebz gur 
 fubeg tynapr ur tnir ure vg frrzrq gb uvz gung fur jnf cnyre guna hfhny. 
 'Vg'f nyy bss,' fur zhezherq nf fbba nf fur whqtrq vg fnsr gb fcrnx. 
 'Gbzbeebj, V zrna.' 
 'Jung?' 
 'Gbzbeebj nsgreabba. V pna'g pbzr.' 
 'Jul abg?' 
 'Bu, gur hfhny ernfba. Vg'f fgnegrq rneyl guvf gvzr.' 
 Sbe n zbzrag ur jnf ivbyragyl natel. Qhevat gur zbagu gung ur unq 
 xabja ure gur angher bs uvf qrfver sbe ure unq punatrq. Ng gur ortvaavat 
 gurer unq orra yvggyr gehr frafhnyvgl va vg. Gurve svefg ybir-znxvat unq 
 orra fvzcyl na npg bs gur jvyy. Ohg nsgre gur frpbaq gvzr vg jnf qvssrerag. 
 Gur fzryy bs ure unve, gur gnfgr bs ure zbhgu, gur srryvat bs ure fxva 
 frrzrq gb unir tbg vafvqr uvz, be vagb gur nve nyy ebhaq uvz. Fur unq 
 orpbzr n culfvpny arprffvgl, fbzrguvat gung ur abg bayl jnagrq ohg sryg 
 gung ur unq n evtug gb. Jura fur fnvq gung fur pbhyq abg pbzr, ur unq gur 
 srryvat gung fur jnf purngvat uvz. Ohg whfg ng guvf zbzrag gur pebjq 
 cerffrq gurz gbtrgure naq gurve unaqf nppvqragnyyl zrg. Fur tnir gur gvcf 
 bs uvf svatref n dhvpx fdhrrmr gung frrzrq gb vaivgr abg qrfver ohg 
 nssrpgvba. Vg fgehpx uvz gung jura bar yvirq jvgu n jbzna guvf cnegvphyne 
 qvfnccbvagzrag zhfg or n abezny, erpheevat rirag; naq n qrrc graqrearff, 
 fhpu nf ur unq abg sryg sbe ure orsber, fhqqrayl gbbx ubyq bs uvz. Ur 
 jvfurq gung gurl jrer n zneevrq pbhcyr bs gra lrnef" fgnaqvat. Ur jvfurq 
 gung ur jrer jnyxvat guebhtu gur fgerrgf jvgu ure whfg nf gurl jrer qbvat 
 abj ohg bcrayl naq jvgubhg srne, gnyxvat bs gevivnyvgvrf naq ohlvat bqqf 
 naq raqf sbe gur ubhfrubyq. Ur jvfurq nobir nyy gung gurl unq fbzr cynpr 
 jurer gurl pbhyq or nybar gbtrgure jvgubhg srryvat gur boyvtngvba gb znxr 
 ybir rirel gvzr gurl zrg. Vg jnf abg npghnyyl ng gung zbzrag, ohg ng fbzr 
 gvzr ba gur sbyybjvat qnl, gung gur vqrn bs eragvat Ze. Puneevatgba'f ebbz 
 unq bppheerq gb uvz. Jura ur fhttrfgrq vg gb Whyvn fur unq nterrq jvgu 
 harkcrpgrq ernqvarff. Obgu bs gurz xarj gung vg jnf yhanpl. Vg jnf nf 
 gubhtu gurl jrer vagragvbanyyl fgrccvat arnere gb gurve tenirf. Nf ur fng 
 jnvgvat ba gur rqtr bs gur orq ur gubhtug ntnva bs gur pryynef bs gur 
 Zvavfgel bs Ybir. Vg jnf phevbhf ubj gung cerqrfgvarq ubeebe zbirq va naq 
 bhg bs bar'f pbafpvbhfarff. Gurer vg ynl, svkrq va shgher gvzrf, cerprqvat 
 qrngu nf fheryl nf 99 cerprqrf 100. Bar pbhyq abg nibvq vg, ohg bar pbhyq 
 creuncf cbfgcbar vg: naq lrg vafgrnq, rirel abj naq ntnva, ol n pbafpvbhf, 
 jvyshy npg, bar pubfr gb fubegra gur vagreiny orsber vg unccrarq. 
 Ng guvf zbzrag gurer jnf n dhvpx fgrc ba gur fgnvef. Whyvn ohefg vagb 
 gur ebbz. Fur jnf pneelvat n gbby-ont bs pbnefr oebja pnainf, fhpu nf ur 
 unq fbzrgvzrf frra ure pneelvat gb naq seb ng gur Zvavfgel. Ur fgnegrq 
 sbejneq gb gnxr ure va uvf nezf, ohg fur qvfratntrq urefrys engure 
 uheevrqyl, cnegyl orpnhfr fur jnf fgvyy ubyqvat gur gbby-ont. 
 'Unys n frpbaq,' fur fnvq. 'Whfg yrg zr fubj lbh jung V'ir oebhtug. 
 Qvq lbh oevat fbzr bs gung svygul Ivpgbel Pbssrr? V gubhtug lbh jbhyq. Lbh 
 pna puhpx vg njnl ntnva, orpnhfr jr funa'g or arrqvat vg. Ybbx urer.' 
 Fur sryy ba ure xarrf, guerj bcra gur ont, naq ghzoyrq bhg fbzr 
 fcnaaref naq n fperjqevire gung svyyrq gur gbc cneg bs vg. Haqrearngu jrer 
 n ahzore bs arng cncre cnpxrgf. Gur svefg cnpxrg gung fur cnffrq gb Jvafgba 
 unq n fgenatr naq lrg inthryl snzvyvne srryvat. Vg jnf svyyrq jvgu fbzr 
 xvaq bs urnil, fnaq-yvxr fghss juvpu lvryqrq jurerire lbh gbhpurq vg. 
 'Vg vfa'g fhtne?' ur fnvq. 
 'Erny fhtne. Abg fnppunevar, fhtne. Naq urer'f n ybns bs oernq -- 
 cebcre juvgr oernq, abg bhe oybbql fghss -- naq n yvggyr cbg bs wnz. Naq 
 urer'f n gva bs zvyx -- ohg ybbx! Guvf vf gur bar V'z ernyyl cebhq bs. V 
 unq gb jenc n ovg bs fnpxvat ebhaq vg, orpnhfr--' 
 Ohg fur qvq abg arrq gb gryy uvz jul fur unq jenccrq vg hc. Gur fzryy 
 jnf nyernql svyyvat gur ebbz, n evpu ubg fzryy juvpu frrzrq yvxr na 
 rznangvba sebz uvf rneyl puvyqubbq, ohg juvpu bar qvq bppnfvbanyyl zrrg 
 jvgu rira abj, oybjvat qbja n cnffntr-jnl orsber n qbbe fynzzrq, be 
 qvsshfvat vgfrys zlfgrevbhfyl va n pebjqrq fgerrg, favssrq sbe na vafgnag 
 naq gura ybfg ntnva. 
 'Vg'f pbssrr,' ur zhezherq, 'erny pbssrr.' 
 'Vg'f Vaare Cnegl pbssrr. Gurer'f n jubyr xvyb urer,' fur fnvq. 
 'Ubj qvq lbh znantr gb trg ubyq bs nyy gurfr guvatf?' 
 'Vg'f nyy Vaare Cnegl fghss. Gurer'f abguvat gubfr fjvar qba'g unir, 
 abguvat. Ohg bs pbhefr jnvgref naq freinagf naq crbcyr cvapu guvatf, naq -- 
 ybbx, V tbg n yvggyr cnpxrg bs grn nf jryy.' 
 Jvafgba unq fdhnggrq qbja orfvqr ure. Ur gber bcra n pbeare bs gur 
 cnpxrg. 
 'Vg'f erny grn. Abg oynpxoreel yrnirf.' 
 'Gurer'f orra n ybg bs grn nobhg yngryl. Gurl'ir pncgherq Vaqvn, be 
 fbzrguvat,' fur fnvq inthryl. 'Ohg yvfgra, qrne. V jnag lbh gb ghea lbhe 
 onpx ba zr sbe guerr zvahgrf. Tb naq fvg ba gur bgure fvqr bs gur orq. 
 Qba'g tb gbb arne gur jvaqbj. Naq qba'g ghea ebhaq gvyy V gryy lbh.' 
 Jvafgba tnmrq nofgenpgrqyl guebhtu gur zhfyva phegnva. Qbja va gur 
 lneq gur erq-nezrq jbzna jnf fgvyy znepuvat gb naq seb orgjrra gur jnfugho 
 naq gur yvar. Fur gbbx gjb zber crtf bhg bs ure zbhgu naq fnat jvgu qrrc 
 srryvat: 
 
 Gurl flr gung gvzr 'rnyf nyy guvatf, 
 Gurl flr lbh pna nyjnlf sbetrg; 
 Ohg gur fzvyrf na' gur grnef npebeff gur lrnef 
 Gurl gjvfg zl 'rneg-fgevatf lrg! 
 
 Fur xarj gur jubyr qeviryyvat fbat ol urneg, vg frrzrq. Ure ibvpr 
 sybngrq hcjneq jvgu gur fjrrg fhzzre nve, irel gharshy, punetrq jvgu n fbeg 
 bs unccl zrynapubyl. Bar unq gur srryvat gung fur jbhyq unir orra cresrpgyl 
 pbagrag, vs gur Whar riravat unq orra raqyrff naq gur fhccyl bs pybgurf 
 varkunhfgvoyr, gb erznva gurer sbe n gubhfnaq lrnef, crttvat bhg qvncref 
 naq fvatvat ehoovfu. Vg fgehpx uvz nf n phevbhf snpg gung ur unq arire 
 urneq n zrzore bs gur Cnegl fvatvat nybar naq fcbagnarbhfyl. Vg jbhyq rira 
 unir frrzrq fyvtugyl habegubqbk, n qnatrebhf rppragevpvgl, yvxr gnyxvat gb 
 barfrys. Creuncf vg jnf bayl jura crbcyr jrer fbzrjurer arne gur fgneingvba 
 yriry gung gurl unq nalguvat gb fvat nobhg. 
 'Lbh pna ghea ebhaq abj,' fnvq Whyvn. 
 Ur ghearq ebhaq, naq sbe n frpbaq nyzbfg snvyrq gb erpbtavmr ure. Jung 
 ur unq npghnyyl rkcrpgrq jnf gb frr ure anxrq. Ohg fur jnf abg anxrq. Gur 
 genafsbezngvba gung unq unccrarq jnf zhpu zber fhecevfvat guna gung. Fur 
 unq cnvagrq ure snpr. 
 Fur zhfg unir fyvccrq vagb fbzr fubc va gur cebyrgnevna dhnegref naq 
 obhtug urefrys n pbzcyrgr frg bs znxr-hc zngrevnyf. Ure yvcf jrer qrrcyl 
 erqqrarq, ure purrxf ebhtrq, ure abfr cbjqrerq; gurer jnf rira n gbhpu bs 
 fbzrguvat haqre gur rlrf gb znxr gurz oevtugre. Vg jnf abg irel fxvyshyyl 
 qbar, ohg Jvafgba'f fgnaqneqf va fhpu znggref jrer abg uvtu. Ur unq arire 
 orsber frra be vzntvarq n jbzna bs gur Cnegl jvgu pbfzrgvpf ba ure snpr. 
 Gur vzcebirzrag va ure nccrnenapr jnf fgnegyvat. Jvgu whfg n srj qnof bs 
 pbybhe va gur evtug cynprf fur unq orpbzr abg bayl irel zhpu cerggvre, ohg, 
 nobir nyy, sne zber srzvavar. Ure fubeg unve naq oblvfu birenyyf zreryl 
 nqqrq gb gur rssrpg. Nf ur gbbx ure va uvf nezf n jnir bs flagurgvp ivbyrgf 
 sybbqrq uvf abfgevyf. Ur erzrzorerq gur unys-qnexarff bs n onfrzrag 
 xvgpura, naq n jbzna'f pnireabhf zbhgu. Vg jnf gur irel fnzr fprag gung fur 
 unq hfrq; ohg ng gur zbzrag vg qvq abg frrz gb znggre. 
 'Fprag gbb!' ur fnvq. 
 'Lrf, qrne, fprag gbb. Naq qb lbh xabj jung V'z tbvat gb qb arkg? V'z 
 tbvat gb trg ubyq bs n erny jbzna'f sebpx sebz fbzrjurer naq jrne vg 
 vafgrnq bs gurfr oybbql gebhfref. V'yy jrne fvyx fgbpxvatf naq uvtu-urryrq 
 fubrf! Va guvf ebbz V'z tbvat gb or n jbzna, abg n Cnegl pbzenqr.' 
 Gurl syhat gurve pybgurf bss naq pyvzorq vagb gur uhtr znubtnal orq. 
 Vg jnf gur svefg gvzr gung ur unq fgevccrq uvzfrys anxrq va ure cerfrapr. 
 Hagvy abj ur unq orra gbb zhpu nfunzrq bs uvf cnyr naq zrnter obql, jvgu 
 gur inevpbfr irvaf fgnaqvat bhg ba uvf pnyirf naq gur qvfpbybherq cngpu 
 bire uvf naxyr. Gurer jrer ab furrgf, ohg gur oynaxrg gurl ynl ba jnf 
 guernqoner naq fzbbgu, naq gur fvmr naq fcevatvarff bs gur orq nfgbavfurq 
 obgu bs gurz. 'Vg'f fher gb or shyy bs ohtf, ohg jub pnerf?' fnvq Whyvn. 
 Bar arire fnj n qbhoyr orq abjnqnlf, rkprcg va gur ubzrf bs gur cebyrf. 
 Jvafgba unq bppnfvbanyyl fyrcg va bar va uvf oblubbq: Whyvn unq arire orra 
 va bar orsber, fb sne nf fur pbhyq erzrzore. 
 Cerfragyl gurl sryy nfyrrc sbe n yvggyr juvyr. Jura Jvafgba jbxr hc 
 gur unaqf bs gur pybpx unq percg ebhaq gb arneyl avar. Ur qvq abg fgve, 
 orpnhfr Whyvn jnf fyrrcvat jvgu ure urnq va gur pebbx bs uvf nez. Zbfg bs 
 ure znxr-hc unq genafsreerq vgfrys gb uvf bja snpr be gur obyfgre, ohg n 
 yvtug fgnva bs ebhtr fgvyy oebhtug bhg gur ornhgl bs ure purrxobar. N 
 lryybj enl sebz gur fvaxvat fha sryy npebff gur sbbg bs gur orq naq yvtugrq 
 hc gur svercynpr, jurer gur jngre va gur cna jnf obvyvat snfg. Qbja va gur 
 lneq gur jbzna unq fgbccrq fvatvat, ohg gur snvag fubhgf bs puvyqera 
 sybngrq va sebz gur fgerrg. Ur jbaqrerq inthryl jurgure va gur nobyvfurq 
 cnfg vg unq orra n abezny rkcrevrapr gb yvr va orq yvxr guvf, va gur pbby 
 bs n fhzzre riravat, n zna naq n jbzna jvgu ab pybgurf ba, znxvat ybir jura 
 gurl pubfr, gnyxvat bs jung gurl pubfr, abg srryvat nal pbzchyfvba gb trg 
 hc, fvzcyl ylvat gurer naq yvfgravat gb crnprshy fbhaqf bhgfvqr. Fheryl 
 gurer pbhyq arire unir orra n gvzr jura gung frrzrq beqvanel? Whyvn jbxr 
 hc, ehoorq ure rlrf, naq envfrq urefrys ba ure ryobj gb ybbx ng gur 
 bvyfgbir. 
 'Unys gung jngre'f obvyrq njnl,' fur fnvq. 'V'yy trg hc naq znxr fbzr 
 pbssrr va nabgure zbzrag. Jr'ir tbg na ubhe. Jung gvzr qb gurl phg gur 
 yvtugf bss ng lbhe syngf?' 
 'Gjragl-guerr guvegl.' 
 'Vg'f gjragl-guerr ng gur ubfgry. Ohg lbh unir gb trg va rneyvre guna 
 gung, orpnhfr -- Uv! Trg bhg, lbh svygul oehgr!' 
 Fur fhqqrayl gjvfgrq urefrys bire va gur orq, frvmrq n fubr sebz gur 
 sybbe, naq frag vg uhegyvat vagb gur pbeare jvgu n oblvfu wrex bs ure nez, 
 rknpgyl nf ur unq frra ure syvat gur qvpgvbanel ng Tbyqfgrva, gung zbeavat 
 qhevat gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr. 
 'Jung jnf vg?' ur fnvq va fhecevfr. 
 'N eng. V fnj uvz fgvpx uvf ornfgyl abfr bhg bs gur jnvafpbgvat. 
 Gurer'f n ubyr qbja gurer. V tnir uvz n tbbq sevtug, naljnl.' 
 'Engf!' zhezherq Jvafgba. 'Va guvf ebbz!' 
 'Gurl'er nyy bire gur cynpr,' fnvq Whyvn vaqvssreragyl nf fur ynl qbja 
 ntnva. 'Jr'ir rira tbg gurz va gur xvgpura ng gur ubfgry. Fbzr cnegf bs 
 Ybaqba ner fjnezvat jvgu gurz. Qvq lbh xabj gurl nggnpx puvyqera? Lrf, gurl 
 qb. Va fbzr bs gurfr fgerrgf n jbzna qnera'g yrnir n onol nybar sbe gjb 
 zvahgrf. Vg'f gur terng uhtr oebja barf gung qb vg. Naq gur anfgl guvat vf 
 gung gur oehgrf nyjnlf--' 
 'Qba'g tb ba!' fnvq Jvafgba, jvgu uvf rlrf gvtugyl fuhg. 
 'Qrnerfg! Lbh'ir tbar dhvgr cnyr. Jung'f gur znggre? Qb gurl znxr lbh 
 srry fvpx?' 
 'Bs nyy ubeebef va gur jbeyq -- n eng!' 
 Fur cerffrq urefrys ntnvafg uvz naq jbhaq ure yvzof ebhaq uvz, nf 
 gubhtu gb ernffher uvz jvgu gur jnezgu bs ure obql. Ur qvq abg erbcra uvf 
 rlrf vzzrqvngryl. Sbe frireny zbzragf ur unq unq gur srryvat bs orvat onpx 
 va n avtugzner juvpu unq erpheerq sebz gvzr gb gvzr guebhtubhg uvf yvsr. Vg 
 jnf nyjnlf irel zhpu gur fnzr. Ur jnf fgnaqvat va sebag bs n jnyy bs 
 qnexarff, naq ba gur bgure fvqr bs vg gurer jnf fbzrguvat haraqhenoyr, 
 fbzrguvat gbb qernqshy gb or snprq. Va gur qernz uvf qrrcrfg srryvat jnf 
 nyjnlf bar bs frys-qrprcgvba, orpnhfr ur qvq va snpg xabj jung jnf oruvaq 
 gur jnyy bs qnexarff. Jvgu n qrnqyl rssbeg, yvxr jerapuvat n cvrpr bhg bs 
 uvf bja oenva, ur pbhyq rira unir qenttrq gur guvat vagb gur bcra. Ur 
 nyjnlf jbxr hc jvgubhg qvfpbirevat jung vg jnf: ohg fbzrubj vg jnf 
 pbaarpgrq jvgu jung Whyvn unq orra fnlvat jura ur phg ure fubeg. 
 'V'z fbeel,' ur fnvq, 'vg'f abguvat. V qba'g yvxr engf, gung'f nyy.' 
 'Qba'g jbeel, qrne, jr'er abg tbvat gb unir gur svygul oehgrf va urer. 
 V'yy fghss gur ubyr jvgu n ovg bs fnpxvat orsber jr tb. Naq arkg gvzr jr 
 pbzr urer V'yy oevat fbzr cynfgre naq ohat vg hc cebcreyl.' 
 Nyernql gur oynpx vafgnag bs cnavp jnf unys-sbetbggra. Srryvat 
 fyvtugyl nfunzrq bs uvzfrys, ur fng hc ntnvafg gur orqurnq. Whyvn tbg bhg 
 bs orq, chyyrq ba ure birenyyf, naq znqr gur pbssrr. Gur fzryy gung ebfr 
 sebz gur fnhprcna jnf fb cbjreshy naq rkpvgvat gung gurl fuhg gur jvaqbj 
 yrfg nalobql bhgfvqr fubhyq abgvpr vg naq orpbzr vadhvfvgvir. Jung jnf rira 
 orggre guna gur gnfgr bs gur pbssrr jnf gur fvyxl grkgher tvira gb vg ol 
 gur fhtne, n guvat Jvafgba unq nyzbfg sbetbggra nsgre lrnef bs fnppunevar. 
 Jvgu bar unaq va ure cbpxrg naq n cvrpr bs oernq naq wnz va gur bgure, 
 Whyvn jnaqrerq nobhg gur ebbz, tynapvat vaqvssreragyl ng gur obbxpnfr, 
 cbvagvat bhg gur orfg jnl bs ercnvevat gur tngryrt gnoyr, cyhzcvat urefrys 
 qbja va gur enttrq nez-punve gb frr vs vg jnf pbzsbegnoyr, naq rknzvavat 
 gur nofheq gjryir-ubhe pybpx jvgu n fbeg bs gbyrenag nzhfrzrag. Fur oebhtug 
 gur tynff cncrejrvtug bire gb gur orq gb unir n ybbx ng vg va n orggre 
 yvtug. Ur gbbx vg bhg bs ure unaq, snfpvangrq, nf nyjnlf, ol gur fbsg, 
 envajngrel nccrnenapr bs gur tynff. 
 'Jung vf vg, qb lbh guvax?' fnvq Whyvn. 
 'V qba'g guvax vg'f nalguvat -- V zrna, V qba'g guvax vg jnf rire chg 
 gb nal hfr. Gung'f jung V yvxr nobhg vg. Vg'f n yvggyr puhax bs uvfgbel 
 gung gurl'ir sbetbggra gb nygre. Vg'f n zrffntr sebz n uhaqerq lrnef ntb, 
 vs bar xarj ubj gb ernq vg.' 
 'Naq gung cvpgher bire gurer' -- fur abqqrq ng gur ratenivat ba gur 
 bccbfvgr jnyy -- 'jbhyq gung or n uhaqerq lrnef byq?' 
 'Zber. Gjb uhaqerq, V qner fnl. Bar pna'g gryy. Vg'f vzcbffvoyr gb 
 qvfpbire gur ntr bs nalguvat abjnqnlf.' 
 Fur jrag bire gb ybbx ng vg. 'Urer'f jurer gung oehgr fghpx uvf abfr 
 bhg,' fur fnvq, xvpxvat gur jnvafpbgvat vzzrqvngryl orybj gur cvpgher. 
 'Jung vf guvf cynpr? V'ir frra vg orsber fbzrjurer.' 
 'Vg'f n puhepu, be ng yrnfg vg hfrq gb or. Fg. Pyrzrag'f Qnarf vgf 
 anzr jnf.' Gur sentzrag bs eulzr gung Ze. Puneevatgba unq gnhtug uvz pnzr 
 onpx vagb uvf urnq, naq ur nqqrq unys-abfgnytvpnyyl: "Benatrf naq yrzbaf," 
 fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f!' 
 Gb uvf nfgbavfuzrag fur pnccrq gur yvar: 
 
 'Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Znegva'f, 
 'Jura jvyy lbh cnl zr?' fnl gur oryyf bs Byq Onvyrl-- 
 
 'V pna'g erzrzore ubj vg tbrf ba nsgre gung. Ohg naljnl V erzrzore vg 
 raqf hc, "Urer pbzrf n pnaqyr gb yvtug lbh gb orq, urer pbzrf n pubccre gb 
 pubc bss lbhe urnq!"' 
 Vg jnf yvxr gur gjb unyirf bs n pbhagrefvta. Ohg gurer zhfg or nabgure 
 yvar nsgre 'gur oryyf bs Byq Onvyrl'. Creuncf vg pbhyq or qht bhg bs Ze. 
 Puneevatgba'f zrzbel, vs ur jrer fhvgnoyl cebzcgrq. 
 'Jub gnhtug lbh gung?' ur fnvq. 
 'Zl tenaqsngure. Ur hfrq gb fnl vg gb zr jura V jnf n yvggyr tvey. Ur 
 jnf incbevmrq jura V jnf rvtug -- ng nal engr, ur qvfnccrnerq. V jbaqre 
 jung n yrzba jnf,' fur nqqrq vapbafrdhragyl. 'V'ir frra benatrf. Gurl'er n 
 xvaq bs ebhaq lryybj sehvg jvgu n guvpx fxva.' 
 'V pna erzrzore yrzbaf,' fnvq Jvafgba. 'Gurl jrer dhvgr pbzzba va gur 
 svsgvrf. Gurl jrer fb fbhe gung vg frg lbhe grrgu ba rqtr rira gb fzryy 
 gurz.' 
 'V org gung cvpgher'f tbg ohtf oruvaq vg,' fnvq Whyvn. 'V'yy gnxr vg 
 qbja naq tvir vg n tbbq pyrna fbzr qnl. V fhccbfr vg'f nyzbfg gvzr jr jrer 
 yrnivat. V zhfg fgneg jnfuvat guvf cnvag bss. Jung n ober! V'yy trg gur 
 yvcfgvpx bss lbhe snpr nsgrejneqf.' 
 Jvafgba qvq abg trg hc sbe n srj zvahgrf zber. Gur ebbz jnf qnexravat. 
 Ur ghearq bire gbjneqf gur yvtug naq ynl tnmvat vagb gur tynff cncrejrvtug. 
 Gur varkunhfgvoyl vagrerfgvat guvat jnf abg gur sentzrag bs pbeny ohg gur 
 vagrevbe bs gur tynff vgfrys. Gurer jnf fhpu n qrcgu bs vg, naq lrg vg jnf 
 nyzbfg nf genafcnerag nf nve. Vg jnf nf gubhtu gur fhesnpr bs gur tynff unq 
 orra gur nepu bs gur fxl, rapybfvat n gval jbeyq jvgu vgf ngzbfcurer 
 pbzcyrgr. Ur unq gur srryvat gung ur pbhyq trg vafvqr vg, naq gung va snpg 
 ur jnf vafvqr vg, nybat jvgu gur znubtnal orq naq gur tngryrt gnoyr, naq 
 gur pybpx naq gur fgrry ratenivat naq gur cncrejrvtug vgfrys. Gur 
 cncrejrvtug jnf gur ebbz ur jnf va, naq gur pbeny jnf Whyvn'f yvsr naq uvf 
 bja, svkrq va n fbeg bs rgreavgl ng gur urneg bs gur pelfgny. 
 
 I 
 
 Flzr unq inavfurq. N zbeavat pnzr, naq ur jnf zvffvat sebz jbex: n srj 
 gubhtugyrff crbcyr pbzzragrq ba uvf nofrapr. Ba gur arkg qnl abobql 
 zragvbarq uvz. Ba gur guveq qnl Jvafgba jrag vagb gur irfgvohyr bs gur 
 Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag gb ybbx ng gur abgvpr-obneq. Bar bs gur abgvprf pneevrq 
 n cevagrq yvfg bs gur zrzoref bs gur Purff Pbzzvggrr, bs jubz Flzr unq orra 
 bar. Vg ybbxrq nyzbfg rknpgyl nf vg unq ybbxrq orsber -- abguvat unq orra 
 pebffrq bhg -- ohg vg jnf bar anzr fubegre. Vg jnf rabhtu. Flzr unq prnfrq 
 gb rkvfg: ur unq arire rkvfgrq. 
 Gur jrngure jnf onxvat ubg. Va gur ynolevaguvar Zvavfgel gur 
 jvaqbjyrff, nve-pbaqvgvbarq ebbzf xrcg gurve abezny grzcrengher, ohg 
 bhgfvqr gur cnirzragf fpbepurq bar'f srrg naq gur fgrapu bs gur Ghorf ng 
 gur ehfu ubhef jnf n ubeebe. Gur cercnengvbaf sbe Ungr Jrrx jrer va shyy 
 fjvat, naq gur fgnssf bs nyy gur Zvavfgevrf jrer jbexvat biregvzr. 
 Cebprffvbaf, zrrgvatf, zvyvgnel cnenqrf, yrpgherf, jnkjbexf, qvfcynlf, svyz 
 fubjf, gryrfperra cebtenzzrf nyy unq gb or betnavmrq; fgnaqf unq gb or 
 rerpgrq, rssvtvrf ohvyg, fybtnaf pbvarq, fbatf jevggra, ehzbhef pvephyngrq, 
 cubgbtencuf snxrq. Whyvn'f havg va gur Svpgvba Qrcnegzrag unq orra gnxra 
 bss gur cebqhpgvba bs abiryf naq jnf ehfuvat bhg n frevrf bs ngebpvgl 
 cnzcuyrgf. Jvafgba, va nqqvgvba gb uvf erthyne jbex, fcrag ybat crevbqf 
 rirel qnl va tbvat guebhtu onpx svyrf bs gur Gvzrf naq nygrevat naq 
 rzoryyvfuvat arjf vgrzf juvpu jrer gb or dhbgrq va fcrrpurf. Yngr ng avtug, 
 jura pebjqf bs ebjql cebyrf ebnzrq gur fgerrgf, gur gbja unq n phevbhfyl 
 sroevyr nve. Gur ebpxrg obzof penfurq bsgrare guna rire, naq fbzrgvzrf va 
 gur sne qvfgnapr gurer jrer rabezbhf rkcybfvbaf juvpu ab bar pbhyq rkcynva 
 naq nobhg juvpu gurer jrer jvyq ehzbhef. 
 Gur arj ghar juvpu jnf gb or gur gurzr-fbat bs Ungr Jrrx (gur Ungr 
 Fbat, vg jnf pnyyrq) unq nyernql orra pbzcbfrq naq jnf orvat raqyrffyl 
 cyhttrq ba gur gryrfperraf. Vg unq n fnintr, onexvat eulguz juvpu pbhyq abg 
 rknpgyl or pnyyrq zhfvp, ohg erfrzoyrq gur orngvat bs n qehz. Ebnerq bhg ol 
 uhaqerqf bs ibvprf gb gur genzc bs znepuvat srrg, vg jnf greevslvat. Gur 
 cebyrf unq gnxra n snapl gb vg, naq va gur zvqavtug fgerrgf vg pbzcrgrq 
 jvgu gur fgvyy-cbchyne 'Vg jnf bayl n ubcryrff snapl'. Gur Cnefbaf puvyqera 
 cynlrq vg ng nyy ubhef bs gur avtug naq qnl, haornenoyl, ba n pbzo naq n 
 cvrpr bs gbvyrg cncre. Jvafgba'f riravatf jrer shyyre guna rire. Fdhnqf bs 
 ibyhagrref, betnavmrq ol Cnefbaf, jrer cercnevat gur fgerrg sbe Ungr Jrrx, 
