 crevybhfyl fyvatvat jverf npebff gur fgerrg sbe gur erprcgvba bs fgernzref. 
 Cnefbaf obnfgrq gung Ivpgbel Znafvbaf nybar jbhyq qvfcynl sbhe uhaqerq 
 zrgerf bs ohagvat. Ur jnf va uvf angvir ryrzrag naq nf unccl nf n ynex. Gur 
 urng naq gur znahny jbex unq rira tvira uvz n cergrkg sbe eriregvat gb 
 fubegf naq na bcra fuveg va gur riravatf. Ur jnf rireljurer ng bapr, 
 chfuvat, chyyvat, fnjvat, unzzrevat, vzcebivfvat, wbyylvat rirelbar nybat 
 jvgu pbzenqryl rkubegngvbaf naq tvivat bhg sebz rirel sbyq bs uvf obql jung 
 frrzrq na varkunhfgvoyr fhccyl bs npevq-fzryyvat fjrng. 
 N arj cbfgre unq fhqqrayl nccrnerq nyy bire Ybaqba. Vg unq ab pncgvba, 
 naq ercerfragrq fvzcyl gur zbafgebhf svther bs n Rhenfvna fbyqvre, guerr be 
 sbhe zrgerf uvtu, fgevqvat sbejneq jvgu rkcerffvbayrff Zbatbyvna snpr naq 
 rabezbhf obbgf, n fhoznpuvar tha cbvagrq sebz uvf uvc. Sebz jungrire natyr 
 lbh ybbxrq ng gur cbfgre, gur zhmmyr bs gur tha, zntavsvrq ol gur 
 sberfubegravat, frrzrq gb or cbvagrq fgenvtug ng lbh. Gur guvat unq orra 
 cynfgrerq ba rirel oynax fcnpr ba rirel jnyy, rira bhgahzorevat gur 
 cbegenvgf bs Ovt Oebgure. Gur cebyrf, abeznyyl ncngurgvp nobhg gur jne, 
 jrer orvat ynfurq vagb bar bs gurve crevbqvpny seramvrf bs cngevbgvfz. Nf 
 gubhtu gb unezbavmr jvgu gur trareny zbbq, gur ebpxrg obzof unq orra 
 xvyyvat ynetre ahzoref bs crbcyr guna hfhny. Bar sryy ba n pebjqrq svyz 
 gurnger va Fgrcarl, ohelvat frireny uhaqerq ivpgvzf nzbat gur ehvaf. Gur 
 jubyr cbchyngvba bs gur arvtuobheubbq ghearq bhg sbe n ybat, genvyvat 
 shareny juvpu jrag ba sbe ubhef naq jnf va rssrpg na vaqvtangvba zrrgvat. 
 Nabgure obzo sryy ba n cvrpr bs jnfgr tebhaq juvpu jnf hfrq nf n cynltebhaq 
 naq frireny qbmra puvyqera jrer oybja gb cvrprf. Gurer jrer shegure natel 
 qrzbafgengvbaf, Tbyqfgrva jnf ohearq va rssvtl, uhaqerqf bs pbcvrf bs gur 
 cbfgre bs gur Rhenfvna fbyqvre jrer gbea qbja naq nqqrq gb gur synzrf, naq 
