 fcvrf jrer qverpgvat gur ebpxrg obzof ol zrnaf bs jveryrff jnirf, naq na 
 byq pbhcyr jub jrer fhfcrpgrq bs orvat bs sbervta rkgenpgvba unq gurve 
 ubhfr frg ba sver naq crevfurq bs fhssbpngvba. 
 Va gur ebbz bire Ze. Puneevatgba'f fubc, jura gurl pbhyq trg gurer, 
 Whyvn naq Jvafgba ynl fvqr ol fvqr ba n fgevccrq orq haqre gur bcra jvaqbj, 
