 jbeyq, n cbpxrg bs gur cnfg jurer rkgvapg navznyf pbhyq jnyx. Ze. 
 Puneevatgba, gubhtug Jvafgba, jnf nabgure rkgvapg navzny. Ur hfhnyyl 
 fgbccrq gb gnyx jvgu Ze. Puneevatgba sbe n srj zvahgrf ba uvf jnl hcfgnvef. 
 Gur byq zna frrzrq fryqbz be arire gb tb bhg bs qbbef, naq ba gur bgure 
 unaq gb unir nyzbfg ab phfgbzref. Ur yrq n tubfgyvxr rkvfgrapr orgjrra gur 
