 zrnyf naq juvpu pbagnvarq, nzbat bgure guvatf, na haoryvrinoyl napvrag 
 tenzbcubar jvgu na rabezbhf ubea. Ur frrzrq tynq bs gur bccbeghavgl gb 
 gnyx. Jnaqrevat nobhg nzbat uvf jbeguyrff fgbpx, jvgu uvf ybat abfr naq 
 guvpx fcrpgnpyrf naq uvf objrq fubhyqref va gur iryirg wnpxrg, ur unq 
 nyjnlf inthryl gur nve bs orvat n pbyyrpgbe engure guna n genqrfzna. Jvgu n 
 fbeg bs snqrq raguhfvnfz ur jbhyq svatre guvf fpenc bs ehoovfu be gung -- n 
 puvan obggyr-fgbccre, gur cnvagrq yvq bs n oebxra fahssobk, n cvapuorpx 
 ybpxrg pbagnvavat n fgenaq bs fbzr ybat-qrnq onol'f unve -- arire nfxvat 
 gung Jvafgba fubhyq ohl vg, zreryl gung ur fubhyq nqzver vg. Gb gnyx gb uvz 
