 qenttrq bhg sebz gur pbearef bs uvf zrzbel fbzr zber sentzragf bs sbetbggra 
 eulzrf. Gurer jnf bar nobhg sbhe naq gjragl oynpxoveqf, naq nabgure nobhg n 
 pbj jvgu n pehzcyrq ubea, naq nabgure nobhg gur qrngu bs cbbe Pbpx Ebova. 
 'Vg whfg bppheerq gb zr lbh zvtug or vagrerfgrq,' ur jbhyq fnl jvgu n 
 qrcerpngvat yvggyr ynhtu jurarire ur cebqhprq n arj sentzrag. Ohg ur pbhyq 
 arire erpnyy zber guna n srj yvarf bs nal bar eulzr. 
 Obgu bs gurz xarj -- va n jnl, vg jnf arire bhg bs gurve zvaqf gung 
 jung jnf abj unccravat pbhyq abg ynfg ybat. Gurer jrer gvzrf jura gur snpg 
