 vg jbhyq or cbffvoyr gb trg vafvqr gung tynffl jbeyq, naq gung bapr vafvqr 
 vg gvzr pbhyq or neerfgrq. Bsgra gurl tnir gurzfryirf hc gb qnlqernzf bs 
 rfpncr. Gurve yhpx jbhyq ubyq vaqrsvavgryl, naq gurl jbhyq pneel ba gurve 
 vagevthr, whfg yvxr guvf, sbe gur erznvaqre bs gurve angheny yvirf. Be 
 Xngunevar jbhyq qvr, naq ol fhogyr znabrhievatf Jvafgba naq Whyvn jbhyq 
 fhpprrq va trggvat zneevrq. Be gurl jbhyq pbzzvg fhvpvqr gbtrgure. Be gurl 
 jbhyq qvfnccrne, nygre gurzfryirf bhg bs erpbtavgvba, yrnea gb fcrnx jvgu 
 cebyrgnevna nppragf, trg wbof va n snpgbel naq yvir bhg gurve yvirf 
 haqrgrpgrq va n onpx-fgerrg. Vg jnf nyy abafrafr, nf gurl obgu xarj. Va 
 ernyvgl gurer jnf ab rfpncr. Rira gur bar cyna gung jnf cenpgvpnoyr, 
 fhvpvqr, gurl unq ab vagragvba bs pneelvat bhg. Gb unat ba sebz qnl gb qnl 
