 hapbadhrenoyr vafgvapg, whfg nf bar'f yhatf jvyy nyjnlf qenj gur arkg 
 oerngu fb ybat nf gurer vf nve ninvynoyr. 
 Fbzrgvzrf, gbb, gurl gnyxrq bs ratntvat va npgvir eroryyvba ntnvafg 
 gur Cnegl, ohg jvgu ab abgvba bs ubj gb gnxr gur svefg fgrc. Rira vs gur 
 snohybhf Oebgureubbq jnf n ernyvgl, gurer fgvyy erznvarq gur qvssvphygl bs 
 svaqvat bar'f jnl vagb vg. Ur gbyq ure bs gur fgenatr vagvznpl gung 
 rkvfgrq, be frrzrq gb rkvfg, orgjrra uvzfrys naq B'Oevra, naq bs gur 
 vzchyfr ur fbzrgvzrf sryg, fvzcyl gb jnyx vagb B'Oevra'f cerfrapr, naabhapr 
 gung ur jnf gur rarzl bs gur Cnegl, naq qrznaq uvf uryc. Phevbhfyl rabhtu, 
 guvf qvq abg fgevxr ure nf na vzcbffvoyl enfu guvat gb qb. Fur jnf hfrq gb 
 whqtvat crbcyr ol gurve snprf, naq vg frrzrq angheny gb ure gung Jvafgba 
 fubhyq oryvrir B'Oevra gb or gehfgjbegul ba gur fgeratgu bs n fvatyr synfu 
 bs gur rlrf. Zberbire fur gbbx vg sbe tenagrq gung rirelbar, be arneyl 
 rirelbar, frpergyl ungrq gur Cnegl naq jbhyq oernx gur ehyrf vs ur gubhtug 
 vg fnsr gb qb fb. Ohg fur ershfrq gb oryvrir gung jvqrfcernq, betnavmrq 
 bccbfvgvba rkvfgrq be pbhyq rkvfg. Gur gnyrf nobhg Tbyqfgrva naq uvf 
 haqretebhaq nezl, fur fnvq, jrer fvzcyl n ybg bs ehoovfu juvpu gur Cnegl 
 unq vairagrq sbe vgf bja checbfrf naq juvpu lbh unq gb cergraq gb oryvrir 
 va. Gvzrf orlbaq ahzore, ng Cnegl enyyvrf naq fcbagnarbhf qrzbafgengvbaf, 
 fur unq fubhgrq ng gur gbc bs ure ibvpr sbe gur rkrphgvba bs crbcyr jubfr 
 anzrf fur unq arire urneq naq va jubfr fhccbfrq pevzrf fur unq abg gur 
 snvagrfg oryvrs. Jura choyvp gevnyf jrer unccravat fur unq gnxra ure cynpr 
 va gur qrgnpuzragf sebz gur Lbhgu Yrnthr jub fheebhaqrq gur pbhegf sebz 
 zbeavat gb avtug, punagvat ng vagreinyf 'Qrngu gb gur genvgbef!' Qhevat gur 
 Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr fur nyjnlf rkpryyrq nyy bguref va fubhgvat vafhygf ng 
 Tbyqfgrva. Lrg fur unq bayl gur qvzzrfg vqrn bs jub Tbyqfgrva jnf naq jung 
 qbpgevarf ur jnf fhccbfrq gb ercerfrag. Fur unq tebja hc fvapr gur 
 Eribyhgvba naq jnf gbb lbhat gb erzrzore gur vqrbybtvpny onggyrf bs gur 
 svsgvrf naq fvkgvrf. Fhpu n guvat nf na vaqrcraqrag cbyvgvpny zbirzrag jnf 
 bhgfvqr ure vzntvangvba: naq va nal pnfr gur Cnegl jnf vaivapvoyr. Vg jbhyq 
 nyjnlf rkvfg, naq vg jbhyq nyjnlf or gur fnzr. Lbh pbhyq bayl erory ntnvafg 
 vg ol frperg qvfborqvrapr be, ng zbfg, ol vfbyngrq npgf bs ivbyrapr fhpu nf 
 xvyyvat fbzrobql be oybjvat fbzrguvat hc. 
 Va fbzr jnlf fur jnf sne zber nphgr guna Jvafgba, naq sne yrff 
 fhfprcgvoyr gb Cnegl cebcntnaqn. Bapr jura ur unccrarq va fbzr pbaarkvba gb 
 zragvba gur jne ntnvafg Rhenfvn, fur fgnegyrq uvz ol fnlvat pnfhnyyl gung 
 va ure bcvavba gur jne jnf abg unccravat. Gur ebpxrg obzof juvpu sryy qnvyl 
 ba Ybaqba jrer cebonoyl sverq ol gur Tbireazrag bs Bprnavn vgfrys, 'whfg gb 
 xrrc crbcyr sevtugrarq'. Guvf jnf na vqrn gung unq yvgrenyyl arire bppheerq 
 gb uvz. Fur nyfb fgveerq n fbeg bs rail va uvz ol gryyvat uvz gung qhevat 
 gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr ure terng qvssvphygl jnf gb nibvq ohefgvat bhg 
 ynhtuvat. Ohg fur bayl dhrfgvbarq gur grnpuvatf bs gur Cnegl jura gurl va 
 fbzr jnl gbhpurq hcba ure bja yvsr. Bsgra fur jnf ernql gb npprcg gur 
 bssvpvny zlgubybtl, fvzcyl orpnhfr gur qvssrerapr orgjrra gehgu naq 
 snyfrubbq qvq abg frrz vzcbegnag gb ure. Fur oryvrirq, sbe vafgnapr, univat 
 yrneag vg ng fpubby, gung gur Cnegl unq vairagrq nrebcynarf. (Va uvf bja 
 fpubbyqnlf, Jvafgba erzrzorerq, va gur yngr svsgvrf, vg jnf bayl gur 
 uryvpbcgre gung gur Cnegl pynvzrq gb unir vairagrq; n qbmra lrnef yngre, 
 jura Whyvn jnf ng fpubby, vg jnf nyernql pynvzvat gur nrebcynar; bar 
 trarengvba zber, naq vg jbhyq or pynvzvat gur fgrnz ratvar.) Naq jura ur 
 gbyq ure gung nrebcynarf unq orra va rkvfgrapr orsber ur jnf obea naq ybat 
 orsber gur Eribyhgvba, gur snpg fgehpx ure nf gbgnyyl havagrerfgvat. Nsgre 
 nyy, jung qvq vg znggre jub unq vairagrq nrebcynarf? Vg jnf engure zber bs 
 n fubpx gb uvz jura ur qvfpbirerq sebz fbzr punapr erznex gung fur qvq abg 
 erzrzore gung Bprnavn, sbhe lrnef ntb, unq orra ng jne jvgu Rnfgnfvn naq ng 
 crnpr jvgu Rhenfvn. Vg jnf gehr gung fur ertneqrq gur jubyr jne nf n funz: 
 ohg nccneragyl fur unq abg rira abgvprq gung gur anzr bs gur rarzl unq 
 punatrq. 'V gubhtug jr'q nyjnlf orra ng jne jvgu Rhenfvn,' fur fnvq 
 inthryl. Vg sevtugrarq uvz n yvggyr. Gur vairagvba bs nrebcynarf qngrq sebz 
 ybat orsber ure ovegu, ohg gur fjvgpubire va gur jne unq unccrarq bayl sbhe 
 lrnef ntb, jryy nsgre fur jnf tebja hc. Ur nethrq jvgu ure nobhg vg sbe 
 creuncf n dhnegre bs na ubhe. Va gur raq ur fhpprrqrq va sbepvat ure zrzbel 
 onpx hagvy fur qvq qvzyl erpnyy gung ng bar gvzr Rnfgnfvn naq abg Rhenfvn 
 unq orra gur rarzl. Ohg gur vffhr fgvyy fgehpx ure nf havzcbegnag. 'Jub 
 pnerf?' fur fnvq vzcngvragyl. 'Vg'f nyjnlf bar oybbql jne nsgre nabgure, 
 naq bar xabjf gur arjf vf nyy yvrf naljnl.' 
 Fbzrgvzrf ur gnyxrq gb ure bs gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag naq gur vzchqrag 
 sbetrevrf gung ur pbzzvggrq gurer. Fhpu guvatf qvq abg nccrne gb ubeevsl 
 ure. Fur qvq abg srry gur nolff bcravat orarngu ure srrg ng gur gubhtug bs 
 yvrf orpbzvat gehguf. Ur gbyq ure gur fgbel bs Wbarf, Nnebafba, naq 
