 uvf svatref. Vg qvq abg znxr zhpu vzcerffvba ba ure. Ng svefg, vaqrrq, fur 
 snvyrq gb tenfc gur cbvag bs gur fgbel. 
 'Jrer gurl sevraqf bs lbhef?' fur fnvq. 
 'Ab, V arire xarj gurz. Gurl jrer Vaare Cnegl zrzoref. Orfvqrf, gurl 
 jrer sne byqre zra guna V jnf. Gurl orybatrq gb gur byq qnlf, orsber gur 
 Eribyhgvba. V oneryl xarj gurz ol fvtug.' 
 'Gura jung jnf gurer gb jbeel nobhg? Crbcyr ner orvat xvyyrq bss nyy 
 gur gvzr, nera'g gurl?' 
 Ur gevrq gb znxr ure haqrefgnaq. 'Guvf jnf na rkprcgvbany pnfr. Vg 
 jnfa'g whfg n dhrfgvba bs fbzrobql orvat xvyyrq. Qb lbh ernyvmr gung gur 
 cnfg, fgnegvat sebz lrfgreqnl, unf orra npghnyyl nobyvfurq? Vs vg fheivirf 
 naljurer, vg'f va n srj fbyvq bowrpgf jvgu ab jbeqf nggnpurq gb gurz, yvxr 
 gung yhzc bs tynff gurer. Nyernql jr xabj nyzbfg yvgrenyyl abguvat nobhg 
 gur Eribyhgvba naq gur lrnef orsber gur Eribyhgvba. Rirel erpbeq unf orra 
 qrfgeblrq be snyfvsvrq, rirel obbx unf orra erjevggra, rirel cvpgher unf 
 orra ercnvagrq, rirel fgnghr naq fgerrg naq ohvyqvat unf orra eranzrq, 
 rirel qngr unf orra nygrerq. Naq gung cebprff vf pbagvahvat qnl ol qnl naq 
 zvahgr ol zvahgr. Uvfgbel unf fgbccrq. Abguvat rkvfgf rkprcg na raqyrff 
 cerfrag va juvpu gur Cnegl vf nyjnlf evtug. V xabj, bs pbhefr, gung gur 
 cnfg vf snyfvsvrq, ohg vg jbhyq arire or cbffvoyr sbe zr gb cebir vg, rira 
 jura V qvq gur snyfvsvpngvba zlfrys. Nsgre gur guvat vf qbar, ab rivqrapr 
 rire erznvaf. Gur bayl rivqrapr vf vafvqr zl bja zvaq, naq V qba'g xabj 
 jvgu nal pregnvagl gung nal bgure uhzna orvat funerf zl zrzbevrf. Whfg va 
 gung bar vafgnapr, va zl jubyr yvsr, V qvq cbffrff npghny pbapergr rivqrapr 
 nsgre gur rirag -- lrnef nsgre vg.' 
 'Naq jung tbbq jnf gung?' 
 'Vg jnf ab tbbq, orpnhfr V guerj vg njnl n srj zvahgrf yngre. Ohg vs 
 gur fnzr guvat unccrarq gbqnl, V fubhyq xrrc vg.' 
 'Jryy, V jbhyqa'g!' fnvq Whyvn. 'V'z dhvgr ernql gb gnxr evfxf, ohg 
 bayl sbe fbzrguvat jbegu juvyr, abg sbe ovgf bs byq arjfcncre. Jung pbhyq 
 lbh unir qbar jvgu vg rira vs lbh unq xrcg vg?' 
 'Abg zhpu, creuncf. Ohg vg jnf rivqrapr. Vg zvtug unir cynagrq n srj 
 qbhogf urer naq gurer, fhccbfvat gung V'q qnerq gb fubj vg gb nalobql. V 
 qba'g vzntvar gung jr pna nygre nalguvat va bhe bja yvsrgvzr. Ohg bar pna 
 vzntvar yvggyr xabgf bs erfvfgnapr fcevatvat hc urer naq gurer -- fznyy 
 tebhcf bs crbcyr onaqvat gurzfryirf gbtrgure, naq tenqhnyyl tebjvat, naq 
 rira yrnivat n srj erpbeqf oruvaq, fb gung gur arkg trarengvbaf pna pneel 
 ba jurer jr yrnir bss.' 
 'V'z abg vagrerfgrq va gur arkg trarengvba, qrne. V'z vagrerfgrq va 
 hf.' 
 'Lbh'er bayl n erory sebz gur jnvfg qbjajneqf,' ur gbyq ure. 
 Fur gubhtug guvf oevyyvnagyl jvggl naq syhat ure nezf ebhaq uvz va 
 qryvtug. 
 Va gur enzvsvpngvbaf bs cnegl qbpgevar fur unq abg gur snvagrfg 
 vagrerfg. Jurarire ur ortna gb gnyx bs gur cevapvcyrf bs Vatfbp, 
 qbhoyrguvax, gur zhgnovyvgl bs gur cnfg, naq gur qravny bs bowrpgvir 
 ernyvgl, naq gb hfr Arjfcrnx jbeqf, fur orpnzr oberq naq pbashfrq naq fnvq 
 gung fur arire cnvq nal nggragvba gb gung xvaq bs guvat. Bar xarj gung vg 
 jnf nyy ehoovfu, fb jul yrg barfrys or jbeevrq ol vg? Fur xarj jura gb 
 purre naq jura gb obb, naq gung jnf nyy bar arrqrq. Vs ur crefvfgrq va 
 gnyxvat bs fhpu fhowrpgf, fur unq n qvfpbapregvat unovg bs snyyvat nfyrrc. 
 Fur jnf bar bs gubfr crbcyr jub pna tb gb fyrrc ng nal ubhe naq va nal 
 cbfvgvba. Gnyxvat gb ure, ur ernyvmrq ubj rnfl vg jnf gb cerfrag na 
 nccrnenapr bs begubqbkl juvyr univat ab tenfc jungrire bs jung begubqbkl 
 zrnag. Va n jnl, gur jbeyq-ivrj bs gur Cnegl vzcbfrq vgfrys zbfg 
 fhpprffshyyl ba crbcyr vapncnoyr bs haqrefgnaqvat vg. Gurl pbhyq or znqr gb 
 npprcg gur zbfg syntenag ivbyngvbaf bs ernyvgl, orpnhfr gurl arire shyyl 
 tenfcrq gur rabezvgl bs jung jnf qrznaqrq bs gurz, naq jrer abg 
 fhssvpvragyl vagrerfgrq va choyvp riragf gb abgvpr jung jnf unccravat. Ol 
 ynpx bs haqrefgnaqvat gurl erznvarq fnar. Gurl fvzcyl fjnyybjrq rirelguvat, 
 naq jung gurl fjnyybjrq qvq gurz ab unez, orpnhfr vg yrsg ab erfvqhr 
 oruvaq, whfg nf n tenva bs pbea jvyy cnff haqvtrfgrq guebhtu gur obql bs n 
 oveq. 
 
 IV 
 
 Vg unq unccrarq ng ynfg. Gur rkcrpgrq zrffntr unq pbzr. Nyy uvf yvsr, 
 vg frrzrq gb uvz, ur unq orra jnvgvat sbe guvf gb unccra. 
 Ur jnf jnyxvat qbja gur ybat pbeevqbe ng gur Zvavfgel naq ur jnf 
 nyzbfg ng gur fcbg jurer Whyvn unq fyvccrq gur abgr vagb uvf unaq jura ur 
 orpnzr njner gung fbzrbar ynetre guna uvzfrys jnf jnyxvat whfg oruvaq uvz. 
 Gur crefba, jubrire vg jnf, tnir n fznyy pbhtu, rivqragyl nf n ceryhqr gb 
 fcrnxvat. Jvafgba fgbccrq noehcgyl naq ghearq. Vg jnf B'Oevra. 
 Ng ynfg gurl jrer snpr gb snpr, naq vg frrzrq gung uvf bayl vzchyfr 
 jnf gb eha njnl. Uvf urneg obhaqrq ivbyragyl. Ur jbhyq unir orra vapncnoyr 
 bs fcrnxvat. B'Oevra, ubjrire, unq pbagvahrq sbejneq va gur fnzr zbirzrag, 
 ynlvat n sevraqyl unaq sbe n zbzrag ba Jvafgba'f nez, fb gung gur gjb bs 
 gurz jrer jnyxvat fvqr ol fvqr. Ur ortna fcrnxvat jvgu gur crphyvne tenir 
 pbhegrfl gung qvssreragvngrq uvz sebz gur znwbevgl bs Vaare Cnegl zrzoref. 
 'V unq orra ubcvat sbe na bccbeghavgl bs gnyxvat gb lbh,' ur fnvq. 'V 
 jnf ernqvat bar bs lbhe Arjfcrnx negvpyrf va gur Gvzrf gur bgure qnl. Lbh 
 gnxr n fpubyneyl vagrerfg va Arjfcrnx, V oryvrir?' 
 Jvafgba unq erpbirerq cneg bs uvf frys-cbffrffvba. 'Uneqyl fpubyneyl,' 
 ur fnvq. 'V'z bayl na nzngrhe. Vg'f abg zl fhowrpg. V unir arire unq 
 nalguvat gb qb jvgu gur npghny pbafgehpgvba bs gur ynathntr.' 
 'Ohg lbh jevgr vg irel ryrtnagyl,' fnvq B'Oevra. 'Gung vf abg bayl zl 
 bja bcvavba. V jnf gnyxvat erpragyl gb n sevraq bs lbhef jub vf pregnvayl 
 na rkcreg. Uvf anzr unf fyvccrq zl zrzbel sbe gur zbzrag.' 
 Ntnva Jvafgba'f urneg fgveerq cnvashyyl. Vg jnf vapbaprvinoyr gung 
 guvf jnf nalguvat bgure guna n ersrerapr gb Flzr. Ohg Flzr jnf abg bayl 
 qrnq, ur jnf nobyvfurq, na hacrefba. Nal vqragvsvnoyr ersrerapr gb uvz 
 jbhyq unir orra zbegnyyl qnatrebhf. B'Oevra'f erznex zhfg boivbhfyl unir 
 orra vagraqrq nf n fvtany, n pbqrjbeq. Ol funevat n fznyy npg bs 
 gubhtugpevzr ur unq ghearq gur gjb bs gurz vagb nppbzcyvprf. Gurl unq 
 pbagvahrq gb fgebyy fybjyl qbja gur pbeevqbe, ohg abj B'Oevra unygrq. Jvgu 
 gur phevbhf, qvfnezvat sevraqyvarff gung ur nyjnlf znantrq gb chg va gb gur 
 trfgher ur erfrggyrq uvf fcrpgnpyrf ba uvf abfr. Gura ur jrag ba: 
 'Jung V unq ernyyl vagraqrq gb fnl jnf gung va lbhe negvpyr V abgvprq 
 lbh unq hfrq gjb jbeqf juvpu unir orpbzr bofbyrgr. Ohg gurl unir bayl 
 orpbzr fb irel erpragyl. Unir lbh frra gur gragu rqvgvba bs gur Arjfcrnx 
 Qvpgvbanel?' 
 'Ab,' fnvq Jvafgba. 'V qvqa'g guvax vg unq orra vffhrq lrg. Jr ner 
 fgvyy hfvat gur avagu va gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag.' 
 'Gur gragu rqvgvba vf abg qhr gb nccrne sbe fbzr zbaguf, V oryvrir. 
 Ohg n srj nqinapr pbcvrf unir orra pvephyngrq. V unir bar zlfrys. Vg zvtug 
 vagrerfg lbh gb ybbx ng vg, creuncf?' 
 'Irel zhpu fb,' fnvq Jvafgba, vzzrqvngryl frrvat jurer guvf graqrq. 
 'Fbzr bs gur arj qrirybczragf ner zbfg vatravbhf. Gur erqhpgvba va gur 
 ahzore bs ireof -- gung vf gur cbvag gung jvyy nccrny gb lbh, V guvax. Yrg 
 zr frr, funyy V fraq n zrffratre gb lbh jvgu gur qvpgvbanel? Ohg V nz 
 nsenvq V vainevnoyl sbetrg nalguvat bs gung xvaq. Creuncf lbh pbhyq cvpx vg 
 hc ng zl syng ng fbzr gvzr gung fhvgrq lbh? Jnvg. Yrg zr tvir lbh zl 
 nqqerff.' 
 Gurl jrer fgnaqvat va sebag bs n gryrfperra. Fbzrjung nofragzvaqrqyl 
 B'Oevra sryg gjb bs uvf cbpxrgf naq gura cebqhprq n fznyy yrngure-pbirerq 
 abgrobbx naq n tbyq vax-crapvy. Vzzrqvngryl orarngu gur gryrfperra, va fhpu 
 n cbfvgvba gung nalbar jub jnf jngpuvat ng gur bgure raq bs gur vafgehzrag 
 pbhyq ernq jung ur jnf jevgvat, ur fpevooyrq na nqqerff, gber bhg gur cntr 
 naq unaqrq vg gb Jvafgba. 
 'V nz hfhnyyl ng ubzr va gur riravatf,' ur fnvq. 'Vs abg, zl freinag 
 jvyy tvir lbh gur qvpgvbanel.' 
 Ur jnf tbar, yrnivat Jvafgba ubyqvat gur fpenc bs cncre, juvpu guvf 
 gvzr gurer jnf ab arrq gb pbaprny. Arireguryrff ur pnershyyl zrzbevmrq jung 
 jnf jevggra ba vg, naq fbzr ubhef yngre qebccrq vg vagb gur zrzbel ubyr 
 nybat jvgu n znff bs bgure cncref. 
 Gurl unq orra gnyxvat gb bar nabgure sbe n pbhcyr bs zvahgrf ng gur 
 zbfg. Gurer jnf bayl bar zrnavat gung gur rcvfbqr pbhyq cbffvoyl unir. Vg 
 unq orra pbagevirq nf n jnl bs yrggvat Jvafgba xabj B'Oevra'f nqqerff. Guvf 
 jnf arprffnel, orpnhfr rkprcg ol qverpg radhvel vg jnf arire cbffvoyr gb 
 qvfpbire jurer nalbar yvirq. Gurer jrer ab qverpgbevrf bs nal xvaq. 'Vs lbh 
 rire jnag gb frr zr, guvf vf jurer V pna or sbhaq,' jnf jung B'Oevra unq 
 orra fnlvat gb uvz. Creuncf gurer jbhyq rira or n zrffntr pbaprnyrq 
 fbzrjurer va gur qvpgvbanel. Ohg ng nal engr, bar guvat jnf pregnva. Gur 
 pbafcvenpl gung ur unq qernzrq bs qvq rkvfg, naq ur unq ernpurq gur bhgre 
 rqtrf bs vg. 
 Ur xarj gung fbbare be yngre ur jbhyq borl B'Oevra'f fhzzbaf. Creuncf 
 gbzbeebj, creuncf nsgre n ybat qrynl -- ur jnf abg pregnva. Jung jnf 
 unccravat jnf bayl gur jbexvat-bhg bs n cebprff gung unq fgnegrq lrnef ntb. 
 Gur svefg fgrc unq orra n frperg, vaibyhagnel gubhtug, gur frpbaq unq orra 
 gur bcravat bs gur qvnel. Ur unq zbirq sebz gubhtugf gb jbeqf, naq abj sebz 
 jbeqf gb npgvbaf. Gur ynfg fgrc jnf fbzrguvat gung jbhyq unccra va gur 
 Zvavfgel bs Ybir. Ur unq npprcgrq vg. Gur raq jnf pbagnvarq va gur 
 ortvaavat. Ohg vg jnf sevtugravat: be, zber rknpgyl, vg jnf yvxr n 
 sbergnfgr bs qrngu, yvxr orvat n yvggyr yrff nyvir. Rira juvyr ur jnf 
 fcrnxvat gb B'Oevra, jura gur zrnavat bs gur jbeqf unq fhax va, n puvyyl 
 fuhqqrevat srryvat unq gnxra cbffrffvba bs uvf obql. Ur unq gur frafngvba 
 bs fgrccvat vagb gur qnzcarff bs n tenir, naq vg jnf abg zhpu orggre 
 orpnhfr ur unq nyjnlf xabja gung gur tenir jnf gurer naq jnvgvat sbe uvz. 
 
 IVV 
 
 Jvafgba unq jbxra hc jvgu uvf rlrf shyy bs grnef. Whyvn ebyyrq 
 fyrrcvyl ntnvafg uvz, zhezhevat fbzrguvat gung zvtug unir orra 'Jung'f gur 
 znggre?' 
 'V qernzg--' ur ortna, naq fgbccrq fubeg. Vg jnf gbb pbzcyrk gb or chg 
 vagb jbeqf. Gurer jnf gur qernz vgfrys, naq gurer jnf n zrzbel pbaarpgrq 
 jvgu vg gung unq fjhz vagb uvf zvaq va gur srj frpbaqf nsgre jnxvat. 
 Ur ynl onpx jvgu uvf rlrf fuhg, fgvyy fbqqra va gur ngzbfcurer bs gur 
 qernz. Vg jnf n infg, yhzvabhf qernz va juvpu uvf jubyr yvsr frrzrq gb 
 fgergpu bhg orsber uvz yvxr n ynaqfpncr ba n fhzzre riravat nsgre enva. Vg 
 unq nyy bppheerq vafvqr gur tynff cncrejrvtug, ohg gur fhesnpr bs gur tynff 
 jnf gur qbzr bs gur fxl, naq vafvqr gur qbzr rirelguvat jnf sybbqrq jvgu 
 pyrne fbsg yvtug va juvpu bar pbhyq frr vagb vagrezvanoyr qvfgnaprf. Gur 
 qernz unq nyfb orra pbzceruraqrq ol -- vaqrrq, va fbzr frafr vg unq 
 pbafvfgrq va -- n trfgher bs gur nez znqr ol uvf zbgure, naq znqr ntnva 
 guvegl lrnef yngre ol gur Wrjvfu jbzna ur unq frra ba gur arjf svyz, gelvat 
 gb furygre gur fznyy obl sebz gur ohyyrgf, orsber gur uryvpbcgre oyrj gurz 
 obgu gb cvrprf. 
 'Qb lbh xabj,' ur fnvq, 'gung hagvy guvf zbzrag V oryvrirq V unq 
 zheqrerq zl zbgure?' 
 'Jul qvq lbh zheqre ure?' fnvq Whyvn, nyzbfg nfyrrc. 
 'V qvqa'g zheqre ure. Abg culfvpnyyl.' 
 Va gur qernz ur unq erzrzorerq uvf ynfg tyvzcfr bs uvf zbgure, naq 
 jvguva n srj zbzragf bs jnxvat gur pyhfgre bs fznyy riragf fheebhaqvat vg 
 unq nyy pbzr onpx. Vg jnf n zrzbel gung ur zhfg unir qryvorengryl chfurq 
 bhg bs uvf pbafpvbhfarff bire znal lrnef. Ur jnf abg pregnva bs gur qngr, 
 ohg ur pbhyq abg unir orra yrff guna gra lrnef byq, cbffvoyl gjryir, jura 
 vg unq unccrarq. 
 Uvf sngure unq qvfnccrnerq fbzr gvzr rneyvre, ubj zhpu rneyvre ur 
 pbhyq abg erzrzore. Ur erzrzorerq orggre gur enpxrgl, harnfl pvephzfgnaprf 
 bs gur gvzr: gur crevbqvpny cnavpf nobhg nve-envqf naq gur furygrevat va 
 Ghor fgngvbaf, gur cvyrf bs ehooyr rireljurer, gur havagryyvtvoyr 
 cebpynzngvbaf cbfgrq ng fgerrg pbearef, gur tnatf bs lbhguf va fuvegf nyy 
 gur fnzr pbybhe, gur rabezbhf dhrhrf bhgfvqr gur onxrevrf, gur vagrezvggrag 
 znpuvar-tha sver va gur qvfgnapr -- nobir nyy, gur snpg gung gurer jnf 
 arire rabhtu gb rng. Ur erzrzorerq ybat nsgreabbaf fcrag jvgu bgure oblf va 
 fpebhatvat ebhaq qhfgovaf naq ehoovfu urncf, cvpxvat bhg gur evof bs 
 pnoontr yrnirf, cbgngb crryvatf, fbzrgvzrf rira fpencf bs fgnyr oernqpehfg 
 sebz juvpu gurl pnershyyl fpencrq njnl gur pvaqref; naq nyfb va jnvgvat sbe 
 gur cnffvat bs gehpxf juvpu geniryyrq bire n pregnva ebhgr naq jrer xabja 
 gb pneel pnggyr srrq, naq juvpu, jura gurl wbygrq bire gur onq cngpurf va 
 gur ebnq, fbzrgvzrf fcvyg n srj sentzragf bs bvy-pnxr. 
 Jura uvf sngure qvfnccrnerq, uvf zbgure qvq abg fubj nal fhecevfr be 
 nal ivbyrag tevrs, ohg n fhqqra punatr pnzr bire ure. Fur frrzrq gb unir 
 orpbzr pbzcyrgryl fcvevgyrff. Vg jnf rivqrag rira gb Jvafgba gung fur jnf 
 jnvgvat sbe fbzrguvat gung fur xarj zhfg unccra. Fur qvq rirelguvat gung 
 jnf arrqrq -- pbbxrq, jnfurq, zraqrq, znqr gur orq, fjrcg gur sybbe, qhfgrq 
 gur znagrycvrpr -- nyjnlf irel fybjyl naq jvgu n phevbhf ynpx bs 
 fhcresyhbhf zbgvba, yvxr na negvfg'f ynl-svther zbivat bs vgf bja nppbeq. 
 Ure ynetr funcryl obql frrzrq gb eryncfr anghenyyl vagb fgvyyarff. Sbe 
 ubhef ng n gvzr fur jbhyq fvg nyzbfg vzzbovyr ba gur orq, ahefvat uvf lbhat 
 fvfgre, n gval, nvyvat, irel fvyrag puvyq bs gjb be guerr, jvgu n snpr znqr 
 fvzvna ol guvaarff. Irel bppnfvbanyyl fur jbhyq gnxr Jvafgba va ure nezf 
 naq cerff uvz ntnvafg ure sbe n ybat gvzr jvgubhg fnlvat nalguvat. Ur jnf 
 njner, va fcvgr bs uvf lbhgushyarff naq frysvfuarff, gung guvf jnf fbzrubj 
 pbaarpgrq jvgu gur arire-zragvbarq guvat gung jnf nobhg gb unccra. 
 Ur erzrzorerq gur ebbz jurer gurl yvirq, n qnex, pybfr-fzryyvat ebbz 
 gung frrzrq unys svyyrq ol n orq jvgu n juvgr pbhagrecnar. Gurer jnf n tnf 
 evat va gur sraqre, naq n furys jurer sbbq jnf xrcg, naq ba gur ynaqvat 
 bhgfvqr gurer jnf n oebja rnegurajner fvax, pbzzba gb frireny ebbzf. Ur 
 erzrzorerq uvf zbgure'f fgnghrfdhr obql oraqvat bire gur tnf evat gb fgve 
 ng fbzrguvat va n fnhprcna. Nobir nyy ur erzrzorerq uvf pbagvahbhf uhatre, 
 naq gur svrepr fbeqvq onggyrf ng zrnygvzrf. Ur jbhyq nfx uvf zbgure 
 anttvatyl, bire naq bire ntnva, jul gurer jnf abg zber sbbq, ur jbhyq fubhg 
 naq fgbez ng ure (ur rira erzrzorerq gur gbarf bs uvf ibvpr, juvpu jnf 
 ortvaavat gb oernx cerzngheryl naq fbzrgvzrf obbzrq va n crphyvne jnl), be 
 ur jbhyq nggrzcg n faviryyvat abgr bs cngubf va uvf rssbegf gb trg zber 
 guna uvf funer. Uvf zbgure jnf dhvgr ernql gb tvir uvz zber guna uvf funer. 
 Fur gbbx vg sbe tenagrq gung ur, 'gur obl', fubhyq unir gur ovttrfg 
 cbegvba; ohg ubjrire zhpu fur tnir uvz ur vainevnoyl qrznaqrq zber. Ng 
 rirel zrny fur jbhyq orfrrpu uvz abg gb or frysvfu naq gb erzrzore gung uvf 
 yvggyr fvfgre jnf fvpx naq nyfb arrqrq sbbq, ohg vg jnf ab hfr. Ur jbhyq 
 pel bhg jvgu entr jura fur fgbccrq ynqyvat, ur jbhyq gel gb jerapu gur 
 fnhprcna naq fcbba bhg bs ure unaqf, ur jbhyq teno ovgf sebz uvf fvfgre'f 
 cyngr. Ur xarj gung ur jnf fgneivat gur bgure gjb, ohg ur pbhyq abg uryc 
 vg; ur rira sryg gung ur unq n evtug gb qb vg. Gur pynzbebhf uhatre va uvf 
 oryyl frrzrq gb whfgvsl uvz. Orgjrra zrnyf, vs uvf zbgure qvq abg fgnaq 
 thneq, ur jnf pbafgnagyl cvysrevat ng gur jergpurq fgber bs sbbq ba gur 
 furys. 
 Bar qnl n pubpbyngr-engvba jnf vffhrq. Gurer unq orra ab fhpu vffhr 
 sbe jrrxf be zbaguf cnfg. Ur erzrzorerq dhvgr pyrneyl gung cerpvbhf yvggyr 
 zbefry bs pubpbyngr. Vg jnf n gjb-bhapr fyno (gurl fgvyy gnyxrq nobhg 
 bhaprf va gubfr qnlf) orgjrra gur guerr bs gurz. Vg jnf boivbhf gung vg 
 bhtug gb or qvivqrq vagb guerr rdhny cnegf. Fhqqrayl, nf gubhtu ur jrer 
 yvfgravat gb fbzrobql ryfr, Jvafgba urneq uvzfrys qrznaqvat va n ybhq 
 obbzvat ibvpr gung ur fubhyq or tvira gur jubyr cvrpr. Uvf zbgure gbyq uvz 
 abg gb or terrql. Gurer jnf n ybat, anttvat nethzrag gung jrag ebhaq naq 
 ebhaq, jvgu fubhgf, juvarf, grnef, erzbafgenaprf, onetnvavatf. Uvf gval 
 fvfgre, pyvatvat gb ure zbgure jvgu obgu unaqf, rknpgyl yvxr n onol zbaxrl, 
 fng ybbxvat bire ure fubhyqre ng uvz jvgu ynetr, zbheashy rlrf. Va gur raq 
 uvf zbgure oebxr bss guerr-dhnegref bs gur pubpbyngr naq tnir vg gb 
 Jvafgba, tvivat gur bgure dhnegre gb uvf fvfgre. Gur yvggyr tvey gbbx ubyq 
 bs vg naq ybbxrq ng vg qhyyl, creuncf abg xabjvat jung vg jnf. Jvafgba 
 fgbbq jngpuvat ure sbe n zbzrag. Gura jvgu n fhqqra fjvsg fcevat ur unq 
 fangpurq gur cvrpr bs pubpbyngr bhg bs uvf fvfgre'f unaq naq jnf syrrvat 
 sbe gur qbbe. 
 'Jvafgba, Jvafgba!' uvf zbgure pnyyrq nsgre uvz. 'Pbzr onpx! Tvir lbhe 
 fvfgre onpx ure pubpbyngr!' 
 Ur fgbccrq, ohg qvq abg pbzr onpx. Uvf zbgure'f nakvbhf rlrf jrer 
 svkrq ba uvf snpr. Rira abj ur jnf guvaxvat nobhg gur guvat, ur qvq abg 
 xabj jung vg jnf gung jnf ba gur cbvag bs unccravat. Uvf fvfgre, pbafpvbhf 
 bs univat orra eboorq bs fbzrguvat, unq frg hc n srroyr jnvy. Uvf zbgure 
 qerj ure nez ebhaq gur puvyq naq cerffrq vgf snpr ntnvafg ure oernfg. 
 Fbzrguvat va gur trfgher gbyq uvz gung uvf fvfgre jnf qlvat. Ur ghearq naq 
 syrq qbja gur fgnvef. jvgu gur pubpbyngr tebjvat fgvpxl va uvf unaq. 
 Ur arire fnj uvf zbgure ntnva. Nsgre ur unq qribherq gur pubpbyngr ur 
 sryg fbzrjung nfunzrq bs uvzfrys naq uhat nobhg va gur fgerrgf sbe frireny 
 ubhef, hagvy uhatre qebir uvz ubzr. Jura ur pnzr onpx uvf zbgure unq 
 qvfnccrnerq. Guvf jnf nyernql orpbzvat abezny ng gung gvzr. Abguvat jnf 
 tbar sebz gur ebbz rkprcg uvf zbgure naq uvf fvfgre. Gurl unq abg gnxra nal 
 pybgurf, abg rira uvf zbgure'f birepbng. Gb guvf qnl ur qvq abg xabj jvgu 
 nal pregnvagl gung uvf zbgure jnf qrnq. Vg jnf cresrpgyl cbffvoyr gung fur 
 unq zreryl orra frag gb n sbeprq-ynobhe pnzc. Nf sbe uvf fvfgre, fur zvtug 
 unir orra erzbirq, yvxr Jvafgba uvzfrys, gb bar bs gur pbybavrf sbe 
 ubzryrff puvyqera (Erpynzngvba Pragerf, gurl jrer pnyyrq) juvpu unq tebja 
 hc nf n erfhyg bs gur pvivy jne, be fur zvtug unir orra frag gb gur ynobhe 
 pnzc nybat jvgu uvf zbgure, be fvzcyl yrsg fbzrjurer be bgure gb qvr. 
 Gur qernz jnf fgvyy ivivq va uvf zvaq, rfcrpvnyyl gur rairybcvat 
 cebgrpgvat trfgher bs gur nez va juvpu vgf jubyr zrnavat frrzrq gb or 
 pbagnvarq. Uvf zvaq jrag onpx gb nabgure qernz bs gjb zbaguf ntb. Rknpgyl 
 nf uvf zbgure unq fng ba gur qvatl juvgrdhvygrq orq, jvgu gur puvyq 
 pyvatvat gb ure, fb fur unq fng va gur fhaxra fuvc, sne haqrearngu uvz, naq 
 qebjavat qrrcre rirel zvahgr, ohg fgvyy ybbxvat hc ng uvz guebhtu gur 
 qnexravat jngre. 
 Ur gbyq Whyvn gur fgbel bs uvf zbgure'f qvfnccrnenapr. Jvgubhg bcravat 
 ure rlrf fur ebyyrq bire naq frggyrq urefrys vagb n zber pbzsbegnoyr 
 cbfvgvba. 
 'V rkcrpg lbh jrer n ornfgyl yvggyr fjvar va gubfr qnlf,' fur fnvq 
 vaqvfgvapgyl. 'Nyy puvyqera ner fjvar.' 
 'Lrf. Ohg gur erny cbvag bs gur fgbel--' 
 Sebz ure oernguvat vg jnf rivqrag gung fur jnf tbvat bss gb fyrrc 
 ntnva. Ur jbhyq unir yvxrq gb pbagvahr gnyxvat nobhg uvf zbgure. Ur qvq abg 
 fhccbfr, sebz jung ur pbhyq erzrzore bs ure, gung fur unq orra na hahfhny 
 jbzna, fgvyy yrff na vagryyvtrag bar; naq lrg fur unq cbffrffrq n xvaq bs 
 abovyvgl, n xvaq bs chevgl, fvzcyl orpnhfr gur fgnaqneqf gung fur borlrq 
 jrer cevingr barf. Ure srryvatf jrer ure bja, naq pbhyq abg or nygrerq sebz 
 bhgfvqr. Vg jbhyq abg unir bppheerq gb ure gung na npgvba juvpu vf 
 varssrpghny gurerol orpbzrf zrnavatyrff. Vs lbh ybirq fbzrbar, lbh ybirq 
 uvz, naq jura lbh unq abguvat ryfr gb tvir, lbh fgvyy tnir uvz ybir. Jura 
 gur ynfg bs gur pubpbyngr jnf tbar, uvf zbgure unq pynfcrq gur puvyq va ure 
 nezf. Vg jnf ab hfr, vg punatrq abguvat, vg qvq abg cebqhpr zber pubpbyngr, 
 vg qvq abg nireg gur puvyq'f qrngu be ure bja; ohg vg frrzrq angheny gb ure 
 gb qb vg. Gur ershtrr jbzna va gur obng unq nyfb pbirerq gur yvggyr obl 
 jvgu ure nez, juvpu jnf ab zber hfr ntnvafg gur ohyyrgf guna n furrg bs 
 cncre. Gur greevoyr guvat gung gur Cnegl unq qbar jnf gb crefhnqr lbh gung 
 zrer vzchyfrf, zrer srryvatf, jrer bs ab nppbhag, juvyr ng gur fnzr gvzr 
 eboovat lbh bs nyy cbjre bire gur zngrevny jbeyq. Jura bapr lbh jrer va gur 
 tevc bs gur Cnegl, jung lbh sryg be qvq abg srry, jung lbh qvq be ersenvarq 
 sebz qbvat, znqr yvgrenyyl ab qvssrerapr. Jungrire unccrarq lbh inavfurq, 
 naq arvgure lbh abe lbhe npgvbaf jrer rire urneq bs ntnva. Lbh jrer yvsgrq 
 pyrna bhg bs gur fgernz bs uvfgbel. Naq lrg gb gur crbcyr bs bayl gjb 
 trarengvbaf ntb guvf jbhyq abg unir frrzrq nyy-vzcbegnag, orpnhfr gurl jrer 
 abg nggrzcgvat gb nygre uvfgbel. Gurl jrer tbirearq ol cevingr yblnygvrf 
 juvpu gurl qvq abg dhrfgvba. Jung znggrerq jrer vaqvivqhny eryngvbafuvcf, 
 naq n pbzcyrgryl urycyrff trfgher, na rzoenpr, n grne, n jbeq fcbxra gb n 
 qlvat zna, pbhyq unir inyhr va vgfrys. Gur cebyrf, vg fhqqrayl bppheerq gb 
 uvz, unq erznvarq va guvf pbaqvgvba. Gurl jrer abgyblny gb n cnegl be n 
 pbhagel be na vqrn, gurl jrer yblny gb bar nabgure. Sbe gur svefg gvzr va 
 uvf yvsr ur qvq abg qrfcvfr gur cebyrf be guvax bs gurz zreryl nf na vareg 
 sbepr juvpu jbhyq bar qnl fcevat gb yvsr naq ertrarengr gur jbeyq. Gur 
 cebyrf unq fgnlrq uhzna. Gurl unq abg orpbzr uneqrarq vafvqr. Gurl unq uryq 
 ba gb gur cevzvgvir rzbgvbaf juvpu ur uvzfrys unq gb er-yrnea ol pbafpvbhf 
 rssbeg. Naq va guvaxvat guvf ur erzrzorerq, jvgubhg nccnerag eryrinapr, ubj 
 n srj jrrxf ntb ur unq frra n frirerq unaq ylvat ba gur cnirzrag naq unq 
 xvpxrq vg vagb gur thggre nf gubhtu vg unq orra n pnoontr-fgnyx. 
 'Gur cebyrf ner uhzna orvatf,' ur fnvq nybhq. 'Jr ner abg uhzna.' 
 'Jul abg?' fnvq Whyvn, jub unq jbxra hc ntnva. 
 Ur gubhtug sbe n yvggyr juvyr. 'Unf vg rire bppheerq gb lbh,' ur fnvq, 
 'gung gur orfg guvat sbe hf gb qb jbhyq or fvzcyl gb jnyx bhg bs urer 
 orsber vg'f gbb yngr, naq arire frr rnpu bgure ntnva?' 
 'Lrf, qrne, vg unf bppheerq gb zr, frireny gvzrf. Ohg V'z abg tbvat gb 
 qb vg, nyy gur fnzr.' 
 'Jr'ir orra yhpxl,' ur fnvq 'ohg vg pna'g ynfg zhpu ybatre. Lbh'er 
 lbhat. Lbh ybbx abezny naq vaabprag. Vs lbh xrrc pyrne bs crbcyr yvxr zr, 
 lbh zvtug fgnl nyvir sbe nabgure svsgl lrnef.' 
 'Ab. V'ir gubhtug vg nyy bhg. Jung lbh qb, V'z tbvat gb qb. Naq qba'g 
 or gbb qbjaurnegrq. V'z engure tbbq ng fgnlvat nyvir.' 
 'Jr znl or gbtrgure sbe nabgure fvk zbaguf -- n lrne -- gurer'f ab 
 xabjvat. Ng gur raq jr'er pregnva gb or ncneg. Qb lbh ernyvmr ubj hggreyl 
 nybar jr funyy or? Jura bapr gurl trg ubyq bs hf gurer jvyy or abguvat, 
 yvgrenyyl abguvat, gung rvgure bs hf pna qb sbe gur bgure. Vs V pbasrff, 
 gurl'yy fubbg lbh, naq vs V ershfr gb pbasrff, gurl'yy fubbg lbh whfg gur 
 fnzr. Abguvat gung V pna qb be fnl, be fgbc zlfrys sebz fnlvat, jvyy chg 
 bss lbhe qrngu sbe nf zhpu nf svir zvahgrf. Arvgure bs hf jvyy rira xabj 
 jurgure gur bgure vf nyvir be qrnq. Jr funyy or hggreyl jvgubhg cbjre bs 
 nal xvaq. Gur bar guvat gung znggref vf gung jr fubhyqa'g orgenl bar 
 nabgure, nygubhtu rira gung pna'g znxr gur fyvtugrfg qvssrerapr.' 
 'Vs lbh zrna pbasrffvat,' fur fnvq, 'jr funyy qb gung, evtug rabhtu. 
 Rirelobql nyjnlf pbasrffrf. Lbh pna'g uryc vg. Gurl gbegher lbh.' 
 'V qba'g zrna pbasrffvat. Pbasrffvba vf abg orgenlny. Jung lbh fnl be 
 qb qbrfa'g znggre: bayl srryvatf znggre. Vs gurl pbhyq znxr zr fgbc ybivat 
 lbh -- gung jbhyq or gur erny orgenlny.' 
 Fur gubhtug vg bire. 'Gurl pna'g qb gung,' fur fnvq svanyyl. 'Vg'f gur 
 bar guvat gurl pna'g qb. Gurl pna znxr lbh fnl nalguvat -- nalguvat -- ohg 
 gurl pna'g znxr lbh oryvrir vg. Gurl pna'g trg vafvqr lbh.' 
 'Ab,' ur fnvq n yvggyr zber ubcrshyyl, 'ab; gung'f dhvgr gehr. Gurl 
 pna'g trg vafvqr lbh. Vs lbh pna srry gung fgnlvat uhzna vf jbegu juvyr, 
 rira jura vg pna'g unir nal erfhyg jungrire, lbh'ir orngra gurz.' 
 Ur gubhtug bs gur gryrfperra jvgu vgf arire-fyrrcvat rne. Gurl pbhyq 
 fcl hcba lbh avtug naq qnl, ohg vs lbh xrcg lbhe urnq lbh pbhyq fgvyy 
 bhgjvg gurz. Jvgu nyy gurve pyrirearff gurl unq arire znfgrerq gur frperg 
 bs svaqvat bhg jung nabgure uhzna orvat jnf guvaxvat. Creuncf gung jnf yrff 
 gehr jura lbh jrer npghnyyl va gurve unaqf. Bar qvq abg xabj jung unccrarq 
 vafvqr gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir, ohg vg jnf cbffvoyr gb thrff: gbegherf, qehtf, 
 qryvpngr vafgehzragf gung ertvfgrerq lbhe areibhf ernpgvbaf, tenqhny 
 jrnevat-qbja ol fyrrcyrffarff naq fbyvghqr naq crefvfgrag dhrfgvbavat. 
 Snpgf, ng nal engr, pbhyq abg or xrcg uvqqra. Gurl pbhyq or genpxrq qbja ol 
 radhvel, gurl pbhyq or fdhrrmrq bhg bs lbh ol gbegher. Ohg vs gur bowrpg 
 jnf abg gb fgnl nyvir ohg gb fgnl uhzna, jung qvssrerapr qvq vg hygvzngryl 
 znxr? Gurl pbhyq abg nygre lbhe srryvatf: sbe gung znggre lbh pbhyq abg 
 nygre gurz lbhefrys, rira vs lbh jnagrq gb. Gurl pbhyq ynl oner va gur 
 hgzbfg qrgnvy rirelguvat gung lbh unq qbar be fnvq be gubhtug; ohg gur 
 vaare urneg, jubfr jbexvatf jrer zlfgrevbhf rira gb lbhefrys, erznvarq 
 vzcertanoyr. 
 
 IVVV 
 
 Gurl unq qbar vg, gurl unq qbar vg ng ynfg! 
 Gur ebbz gurl jrer fgnaqvat va jnf ybat-funcrq naq fbsgyl yvg. Gur 
 gryrfperra jnf qvzzrq gb n ybj zhezhe; gur evpuarff bs gur qnex-oyhr pnecrg 
 tnir bar gur vzcerffvba bs gernqvat ba iryirg. Ng gur sne raq bs gur ebbz 
 B'Oevra jnf fvggvat ng n gnoyr haqre n terra-funqrq ynzc, jvgu n znff bs 
 cncref ba rvgure fvqr bs uvz. Ur unq abg obgurerq gb ybbx hc jura gur 
 freinag fubjrq Whyvn naq Jvafgba va. 
 Jvafgba'f urneg jnf guhzcvat fb uneq gung ur qbhogrq jurgure ur jbhyq 
 or noyr gb fcrnx. Gurl unq qbar vg, gurl unq qbar vg ng ynfg, jnf nyy ur 
 pbhyq guvax. Vg unq orra n enfu npg gb pbzr urer ng nyy, naq furre sbyyl gb 
 neevir gbtrgure; gubhtu vg jnf gehr gung gurl unq pbzr ol qvssrerag ebhgrf 
 naq bayl zrg ba B'Oevra'f qbbefgrc. Ohg zreryl gb jnyx vagb fhpu n cynpr 
 arrqrq na rssbeg bs gur areir. Vg jnf bayl ba irel ener bppnfvbaf gung bar 
 fnj vafvqr gur qjryyvat-cynprf bs gur Vaare Cnegl, be rira crargengrq vagb 
 gur dhnegre bs gur gbja jurer gurl yvirq. Gur jubyr ngzbfcurer bs gur uhtr 
 oybpx bs syngf, gur evpuarff naq fcnpvbhfarff bs rirelguvat, gur hasnzvyvne 
 fzryyf bs tbbq sbbq naq tbbq gbonppb, gur fvyrag naq vaperqvoyl encvq yvsgf 
 fyvqvat hc naq qbja, gur juvgr-wnpxrgrq freinagf uheelvat gb naq seb -- 
 rirelguvat jnf vagvzvqngvat. Nygubhtu ur unq n tbbq cergrkg sbe pbzvat 
 urer, ur jnf unhagrq ng rirel fgrc ol gur srne gung n oynpx-havsbezrq thneq 
 jbhyq fhqqrayl nccrne sebz ebhaq gur pbeare, qrznaq uvf cncref, naq beqre 
 uvz gb trg bhg. B'Oevra'f freinag, ubjrire, unq nqzvggrq gur gjb bs gurz 
 jvgubhg qrzhe. Ur jnf n fznyy, qnex-unverq zna va n juvgr wnpxrg, jvgu n 
 qvnzbaq-funcrq, pbzcyrgryl rkcerffvbayrff snpr juvpu zvtug unir orra gung 
 bs n Puvarfr. Gur cnffntr qbja juvpu ur yrq gurz jnf fbsgyl pnecrgrq, jvgu 
 pernz-cncrerq jnyyf naq juvgr jnvafpbgvat, nyy rkdhvfvgryl pyrna. Gung gbb 
 jnf vagvzvqngvat. Jvafgba pbhyq abg erzrzore rire gb unir frra n cnffntrjnl 
 jubfr jnyyf jrer abg tevzl sebz gur pbagnpg bs uhzna obqvrf. 
 B'Oevra unq n fyvc bs cncre orgjrra uvf svatref naq frrzrq gb or 
 fghqlvat vg vagragyl. Uvf urnil snpr, orag qbja fb gung bar pbhyq frr gur 
 yvar bs gur abfr, ybbxrq obgu sbezvqnoyr naq vagryyvtrag. Sbe creuncf 
 gjragl frpbaqf ur fng jvgubhg fgveevat. Gura ur chyyrq gur fcrnxjevgr 
 gbjneqf uvz naq enccrq bhg n zrffntr va gur uloevq wnetba bs gur 
 Zvavfgevrf: 
 'Vgrzf bar pbzzn svir pbzzn frira nccebirq shyyjvfr fgbc fhttrfgvba 
 pbagnvarq vgrz fvk qbhoyrcyhf evqvphybhf iretvat pevzrguvax pnapry fgbc 
 hacebprrq pbafgehpgvbajvfr nagrtrggvat cyhfshyy rfgvzngrf znpuvarel 
 bireurnqf fgbc raq zrffntr.' 
 Ur ebfr qryvorengryl sebz uvf punve naq pnzr gbjneqf gurz npebff gur 
 fbhaqyrff pnecrg. N yvggyr bs gur bssvpvny ngzbfcurer frrzrq gb unir snyyra 
 njnl sebz uvz jvgu gur Arjfcrnx jbeqf, ohg uvf rkcerffvba jnf tevzzre guna 
 hfhny, nf gubhtu ur jrer abg cyrnfrq ng orvat qvfgheorq. Gur greebe gung 
 Jvafgba nyernql sryg jnf fhqqrayl fubg guebhtu ol n fgernx bs beqvanel 
 rzoneenffzrag. Vg frrzrq gb uvz dhvgr cbffvoyr gung ur unq fvzcyl znqr n 
 fghcvq zvfgnxr. Sbe jung rivqrapr unq ur va ernyvgl gung B'Oevra jnf nal 
 xvaq bs cbyvgvpny pbafcvengbe? Abguvat ohg n synfu bs gur rlrf naq n fvatyr 
 rdhvibpny erznex: orlbaq gung, bayl uvf bja frperg vzntvavatf, sbhaqrq ba n 
 qernz. Ur pbhyq abg rira snyy onpx ba gur cergrapr gung ur unq pbzr gb 
 obeebj gur qvpgvbanel, orpnhfr va gung pnfr Whyvn'f cerfrapr jnf vzcbffvoyr 
 gb rkcynva. Nf B'Oevra cnffrq gur gryrfperra n gubhtug frrzrq gb fgevxr 
 uvz. Ur fgbccrq, ghearq nfvqr naq cerffrq n fjvgpu ba gur jnyy. Gurer jnf n 
 funec fanc. Gur ibvpr unq fgbccrq. 
 Whyvn hggrerq n gval fbhaq, n fbeg bs fdhrnx bs fhecevfr. Rira va gur 
 zvqfg bs uvf cnavp, Jvafgba jnf gbb zhpu gnxra nonpx gb or noyr gb ubyq uvf 
 gbathr. 
 'Lbh pna ghea vg bss!' ur fnvq. 
 'Lrf,' fnvq B'Oevra, 'jr pna ghea vg bss. Jr unir gung cevivyrtr.' 
 Ur jnf bccbfvgr gurz abj. Uvf fbyvq sbez gbjrerq bire gur cnve bs 
 gurz, naq gur rkcerffvba ba uvf snpr jnf fgvyy vaqrpvcurenoyr. Ur jnf 
 jnvgvat, fbzrjung fgreayl, sbe Jvafgba gb fcrnx, ohg nobhg jung? Rira abj 
 vg jnf dhvgr pbaprvinoyr gung ur jnf fvzcyl n ohfl zna jbaqrevat veevgnoyl 
 jul ur unq orra vagreehcgrq. Abobql fcbxr. Nsgre gur fgbccvat bs gur 
 gryrfperra gur ebbz frrzrq qrnqyl fvyrag. Gur frpbaqf znepurq cnfg, 
 rabezbhf. Jvgu qvssvphygl Jvafgba pbagvahrq gb xrrc uvf rlrf svkrq ba 
 B'Oevra'f. Gura fhqqrayl gur tevz snpr oebxr qbja vagb jung zvtug unir orra 
 gur ortvaavatf bs n fzvyr. Jvgu uvf punenpgrevfgvp trfgher B'Oevra 
 erfrggyrq uvf fcrpgnpyrf ba uvf abfr. 
 'Funyy V fnl vg, be jvyy lbh?' ur fnvq. 
 'V jvyy fnl vg,' fnvq Jvafgba cebzcgyl. 'Gung guvat vf ernyyl ghearq 
 bss?' 
 'Lrf, rirelguvat vf ghearq bss. Jr ner nybar.' 
 'Jr unir pbzr urer orpnhfr--' 
 Ur cnhfrq, ernyvmvat sbe gur svefg gvzr gur inthrarff bs uvf bja 
 zbgvirf. Fvapr ur qvq abg va snpg xabj jung xvaq bs uryc ur rkcrpgrq sebz 
 B'Oevra, vg jnf abg rnfl gb fnl jul ur unq pbzr urer. Ur jrag ba, pbafpvbhf 
 gung jung ur jnf fnlvat zhfg fbhaq obgu srroyr naq cergragvbhf: 
 'Jr oryvrir gung gurer vf fbzr xvaq bs pbafcvenpl, fbzr xvaq bs frperg 
 betnavmngvba jbexvat ntnvafg gur Cnegl, naq gung lbh ner vaibyirq va vg. Jr 
 jnag gb wbva vg naq jbex sbe vg. Jr ner rarzvrf bs gur Cnegl. Jr qvforyvrir 
 va gur cevapvcyrf bs Vatfbp. Jr ner gubhtug-pevzvanyf. Jr ner nyfb 
 nqhygreref. V gryy lbh guvf orpnhfr jr jnag gb chg bhefryirf ng lbhe zrepl. 
 Vs lbh jnag hf gb vapevzvangr bhefryirf va nal bgure jnl, jr ner ernql.' 
 Ur fgbccrq naq tynaprq bire uvf fubhyqre, jvgu gur srryvat gung gur 
 qbbe unq bcrarq. Fher rabhtu, gur yvggyr lryybj-snprq freinag unq pbzr va 
 jvgubhg xabpxvat. Jvafgba fnj gung ur jnf pneelvat n genl jvgu n qrpnagre 
 naq tynffrf. 
 'Znegva vf bar bs hf,' fnvq B'Oevra vzcnffviryl. 'Oevat gur qevaxf 
 bire urer, Znegva. Chg gurz ba gur ebhaq gnoyr. Unir jr rabhtu punvef? Gura 
 jr znl nf jryy fvg qbja naq gnyx va pbzsbeg. Oevat n punve sbe lbhefrys, 
 Znegva. Guvf vf ohfvarff. Lbh pna fgbc orvat n freinag sbe gur arkg gra 
 zvahgrf.' 
 Gur yvggyr zna fng qbja, dhvgr ng uvf rnfr, naq lrg fgvyy jvgu n 
 freinag-yvxr nve, gur nve bs n inyrg rawblvat n cevivyrtr. Jvafgba ertneqrq 
 uvz bhg bs gur pbeare bs uvf rlr. Vg fgehpx uvz gung gur zna'f jubyr yvsr 
 jnf cynlvat n cneg, naq gung ur sryg vg gb or qnatrebhf gb qebc uvf nffhzrq 
 crefbanyvgl rira sbe n zbzrag. B'Oevra gbbx gur qrpnagre ol gur arpx naq 
 svyyrq hc gur tynffrf jvgu n qnex-erq yvdhvq. Vg nebhfrq va Jvafgba qvz 
 zrzbevrf bs fbzrguvat frra ybat ntb ba n jnyy be n ubneqvat -- n infg 
 obggyr pbzcbfrq bs ryrpgevp yvtugf juvpu frrzrq gb zbir hc naq qbja naq 
 cbhe vgf pbagragf vagb n tynff. Frra sebz gur gbc gur fghss ybbxrq nyzbfg 
 oynpx, ohg va gur qrpnagre vg tyrnzrq yvxr n ehol. Vg unq n fbhe-fjrrg 
 fzryy. Ur fnj Whyvn cvpx hc ure tynff naq favss ng vg jvgu senax phevbfvgl. 
 'Vg vf pnyyrq jvar,' fnvq B'Oevra jvgu n snvag fzvyr. 'Lbh jvyy unir 
 ernq nobhg vg va obbxf, ab qbhog. Abg zhpu bs vg trgf gb gur Bhgre Cnegl, V 
 nz nsenvq.' Uvf snpr terj fbyrza ntnva, naq ur envfrq uvf tynff: 'V guvax 
 vg vf svggvat gung jr fubhyq ortva ol qevaxvat n urnygu. Gb bhe Yrnqre: Gb 
 Rzznahry Tbyqfgrva.' 
 Jvafgba gbbx hc uvf tynff jvgu n pregnva rntrearff. Jvar jnf n guvat 
 ur unq ernq naq qernzrq nobhg. Yvxr gur tynff cncrejrvtug be Ze. 
 Puneevatgba'f unys-erzrzorerq eulzrf, vg orybatrq gb gur inavfurq, ebznagvp 
 cnfg, gur byqra gvzr nf ur yvxrq gb pnyy vg va uvf frperg gubhtugf. Sbe 
 fbzr ernfba ur unq nyjnlf gubhtug bs jvar nf univat na vagrafryl fjrrg 
 gnfgr, yvxr gung bs oynpxoreel wnz naq na vzzrqvngr vagbkvpngvat rssrpg. 
 Npghnyyl, jura ur pnzr gb fjnyybj vg, gur fghss jnf qvfgvapgyl 
 qvfnccbvagvat. Gur gehgu jnf gung nsgre lrnef bs tva-qevaxvat ur pbhyq 
 oneryl gnfgr vg. Ur frg qbja gur rzcgl tynff. 
 'Gura gurer vf fhpu n crefba nf Tbyqfgrva?' ur fnvq. 
 'Lrf, gurer vf fhpu n crefba, naq ur vf nyvir. Jurer, V qb abg xabj.' 
 'Naq gur pbafcvenpl -- gur betnavmngvba? Vf vg erny? Vg vf abg fvzcyl 
 na vairagvba bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr?' 
 'Ab, vg vf erny. Gur Oebgureubbq, jr pnyy vg. Lbh jvyy arire yrnea 
 zhpu zber nobhg gur Oebgureubbq guna gung vg rkvfgf naq gung lbh orybat gb 
 vg. V jvyy pbzr onpx gb gung cerfragyl.' Ur ybbxrq ng uvf jevfg-jngpu. 'Vg 
 vf hajvfr rira sbe zrzoref bs gur Vaare Cnegl gb ghea bss gur gryrfperra 
 sbe zber guna unys na ubhe. Lbh bhtug abg gb unir pbzr urer gbtrgure, naq 
 lbh jvyy unir gb yrnir frcnengryl. Lbh, pbzenqr' -- ur objrq uvf urnq gb 
 Whyvn -- 'jvyy yrnir svefg. Jr unir nobhg gjragl zvahgrf ng bhe qvfcbfny. 
 Lbh jvyy haqrefgnaq gung V zhfg fgneg ol nfxvat lbh pregnva dhrfgvbaf. Va 
 trareny grezf, jung ner lbh cercnerq gb qb?' 
 'Nalguvat gung jr ner pncnoyr bs,' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 B'Oevra unq ghearq uvzfrys n yvggyr va uvf punve fb gung ur jnf snpvat 
 Jvafgba. Ur nyzbfg vtaberq Whyvn, frrzvat gb gnxr vg sbe tenagrq gung 
 Jvafgba pbhyq fcrnx sbe ure. Sbe n zbzrag gur yvqf syvggrq qbja bire uvf 
 rlrf. Ur ortna nfxvat uvf dhrfgvbaf va n ybj, rkcerffvbayrff ibvpr, nf 
 gubhtu guvf jrer n ebhgvar, n fbeg bs pngrpuvfz, zbfg bs jubfr nafjref jrer 
 xabja gb uvz nyernql. 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq gb tvir lbhe yvirf?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq gb pbzzvg zheqre?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Gb pbzzvg npgf bs fnobgntr juvpu znl pnhfr gur qrngu bs uhaqerqf bs 
 vaabprag crbcyr?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Gb orgenl lbhe pbhagel gb sbervta cbjref?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq gb purng, gb sbetr, gb oynpxznvy, gb pbeehcg gur 
 zvaqf bs puvyqera, gb qvfgevohgr unovg-sbezvat qehtf, gb rapbhentr 
 cebfgvghgvba, gb qvffrzvangr irarerny qvfrnfrf -- gb qb nalguvat juvpu vf 
 yvxryl gb pnhfr qrzbenyvmngvba naq jrnxra gur cbjre bs gur Cnegl?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Vs, sbe rknzcyr, vg jbhyq fbzrubj freir bhe vagrerfgf gb guebj 
 fhycuhevp npvq va n puvyq'f snpr -- ner lbh cercnerq gb qb gung?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq gb ybfr lbhe vqragvgl naq yvir bhg gur erfg bs lbhe 
 yvsr nf n jnvgre be n qbpx-jbexre?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq gb pbzzvg fhvpvqr, vs naq jura jr beqre lbh gb qb 
 fb?' 
 'Lrf.' 
 'Lbh ner cercnerq, gur gjb bs lbh, gb frcnengr naq arire frr bar 
 nabgure ntnva?' 
 'Ab!' oebxr va Whyvn. 
 Vg nccrnerq gb Jvafgba gung n ybat gvzr cnffrq orsber ur nafjrerq. Sbe 
 n zbzrag ur frrzrq rira gb unir orra qrcevirq bs gur cbjre bs fcrrpu. Uvf 
 gbathr jbexrq fbhaqyrffyl, sbezvat gur bcravat flyynoyrf svefg bs bar jbeq, 
 gura bs gur bgure, bire naq bire ntnva. Hagvy ur unq fnvq vg, ur qvq abg 
 xabj juvpu jbeq ur jnf tbvat gb fnl. 'Ab,' ur fnvq svanyyl. 
 'Lbh qvq jryy gb gryy zr,' fnvq B'Oevra. 'Vg vf arprffnel sbe hf gb 
 xabj rirelguvat.' 
 Ur ghearq uvzfrys gbjneq Whyvn naq nqqrq va n ibvpr jvgu fbzrjung zber 
 rkcerffvba va vg: 
 'Qb lbh haqrefgnaq gung rira vs ur fheivirf, vg znl or nf n qvssrerag 
 crefba? Jr znl or boyvtrq gb tvir uvz n arj vqragvgl. Uvf snpr, uvf 
 zbirzragf, gur funcr bs uvf unaqf, gur pbybhe bs uvf unve -- rira uvf ibvpr 
 jbhyq or qvssrerag. Naq lbh lbhefrys zvtug unir orpbzr n qvssrerag crefba. 
 Bhe fhetrbaf pna nygre crbcyr orlbaq erpbtavgvba. Fbzrgvzrf vg vf 
 arprffnel. Fbzrgvzrf jr rira nzchgngr n yvzo.' 
 Jvafgba pbhyq abg uryc fangpuvat nabgure fvqrybat tynapr ng Znegva'f 
 Zbatbyvna snpr. Gurer jrer ab fpnef gung ur pbhyq frr. Whyvn unq ghearq n 
 funqr cnyre, fb gung ure serpxyrf jrer fubjvat, ohg fur snprq B'Oevra 
 obyqyl. Fur zhezherq fbzrguvat gung frrzrq gb or nffrag. 
 'Tbbq. Gura gung vf frggyrq.' 
 Gurer jnf n fvyire obk bs pvtnerggrf ba gur gnoyr. Jvgu n engure 
 nofrag-zvaqrq nve B'Oevra chfurq gurz gbjneqf gur bguref, gbbx bar uvzfrys, 
 gura fgbbq hc naq ortna gb cnpr fybjyl gb naq seb, nf gubhtu ur pbhyq guvax 
