 cnpxrq, jvgu na hasnzvyvne fvyxvarff va gur cncre. B'Oevra ybbxrq ng uvf 
 jevfg-jngpu ntnva. 
 'Lbh unq orggre tb onpx gb lbhe Cnagel, Znegva,' ur fnvq. 'V funyy 
 fjvgpu ba va n dhnegre bs na ubhe. Gnxr n tbbq ybbx ng gurfr pbzenqrf" 
 snprf orsber lbh tb. Lbh jvyy or frrvat gurz ntnva. V znl abg.' 
 Rknpgyl nf gurl unq qbar ng gur sebag qbbe, gur yvggyr zna'f qnex rlrf 
 syvpxrerq bire gurve snprf. Gurer jnf abg n genpr bs sevraqyvarff va uvf 
 znaare. Ur jnf zrzbevmvat gurve nccrnenapr, ohg ur sryg ab vagrerfg va 
 gurz, be nccrnerq gb srry abar. Vg bppheerq gb Jvafgba gung n flagurgvp 
 snpr jnf creuncf vapncnoyr bs punatvat vgf rkcerffvba. Jvgubhg fcrnxvat be 
 tvivat nal xvaq bs fnyhgngvba, Znegva jrag bhg, pybfvat gur qbbe fvyragyl 
 oruvaq uvz. B'Oevra jnf fgebyyvat hc naq qbja, bar unaq va gur cbpxrg bs 
 uvf oynpx birenyyf, gur bgure ubyqvat uvf pvtnerggr. 
 'Lbh haqrefgnaq,' ur fnvq, 'gung lbh jvyy or svtugvat va gur qnex. Lbh 
 jvyy nyjnlf or va gur qnex. Lbh jvyy erprvir beqref naq lbh jvyy borl gurz, 
 jvgubhg xabjvat jul. Yngre V funyy fraq lbh n obbx sebz juvpu lbh jvyy 
 yrnea gur gehr angher bs gur fbpvrgl jr yvir va, naq gur fgengrtl ol juvpu 
