 ahzoref n uhaqerq zrzoref, be gra zvyyvba. Sebz lbhe crefbany xabjyrqtr lbh 
 jvyy arire or noyr gb fnl gung vg ahzoref rira nf znal nf n qbmra. Lbh jvyy 
 unir guerr be sbhe pbagnpgf, jub jvyy or erarjrq sebz gvzr gb gvzr nf gurl 
 qvfnccrne. Nf guvf jnf lbhe svefg pbagnpg, vg jvyy or cerfreirq. Jura lbh 
 erprvir beqref, gurl jvyy pbzr sebz zr. Vs jr svaq vg arprffnel gb 
 pbzzhavpngr jvgu lbh, vg jvyy or guebhtu Znegva. Jura lbh ner svanyyl 
 pnhtug, lbh jvyy pbasrff. Gung vf hanibvqnoyr. Ohg lbh jvyy unir irel 
 yvggyr gb pbasrff, bgure guna lbhe bja npgvbaf. Lbh jvyy abg or noyr gb 
 orgenl zber guna n unaqshy bs havzcbegnag crbcyr. Cebonoyl lbh jvyy abg 
 rira orgenl zr. Ol gung gvzr V znl or qrnq, be V funyy unir orpbzr n 
 qvssrerag crefba, jvgu n qvssrerag snpr.' 
 Ur pbagvahrq gb zbir gb naq seb bire gur fbsg pnecrg. Va fcvgr bs gur 
 ohyxvarff bs uvf obql gurer jnf n erznexnoyr tenpr va uvf zbirzragf. Vg 
 pnzr bhg rira va gur trfgher jvgu juvpu ur guehfg n unaq vagb uvf cbpxrg, 
 be znavchyngrq n pvtnerggr. Zber rira guna bs fgeratgu, ur tnir na 
 vzcerffvba bs pbasvqrapr naq bs na haqrefgnaqvat gvatrq ol vebal. Ubjrire 
 zhpu va rnearfg ur zvtug or, ur unq abguvat bs gur fvatyr-zvaqrqarff gung 
