 vzcerffrq. Fur unq yrg ure pvtnerggr tb bhg naq jnf yvfgravat vagragyl. 
 B'Oevra jrag ba: 
 'Lbh jvyy unir urneq ehzbhef bs gur rkvfgrapr bs gur Oebgureubbq. Ab 
 qbhog lbh unir sbezrq lbhe bja cvpgher bs vg. Lbh unir vzntvarq, cebonoyl, 
 n uhtr haqrejbeyq bs pbafcvengbef, zrrgvat frpergyl va pryynef, fpevooyvat 
