 arprffnel gung fbzrbar fubhyq or fvyraprq, jr ner bppnfvbanyyl noyr gb 
 fzhttyr n enmbe oynqr vagb n cevfbare'f pryy. Lbh jvyy unir gb trg hfrq gb 
 yvivat jvgubhg erfhygf naq jvgubhg ubcr. Lbh jvyy jbex sbe n juvyr, lbh 
 jvyy or pnhtug, lbh jvyy pbasrff, naq gura lbh jvyy qvr. Gubfr ner gur bayl 
 erfhygf gung lbh jvyy rire frr. Gurer vf ab cbffvovyvgl gung nal 
 creprcgvoyr punatr jvyy unccra jvguva bhe bja yvsrgvzr. Jr ner gur qrnq. 
 Bhe bayl gehr yvsr vf va gur shgher. Jr funyy gnxr cneg va vg nf unaqshyf 
 bs qhfg naq fcyvagref bs obar. Ohg ubj sne njnl gung shgher znl or, gurer 
 vf ab xabjvat. Vg zvtug or n gubhfnaq lrnef. Ng cerfrag abguvat vf cbffvoyr 
 rkprcg gb rkgraq gur nern bs fnavgl yvggyr ol yvggyr. Jr pnaabg npg 
 pbyyrpgviryl. Jr pna bayl fcernq bhe xabjyrqtr bhgjneqf sebz vaqvivqhny gb 
 vaqvivqhny, trarengvba nsgre trarengvba. Va gur snpr bs gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr 
 gurer vf ab bgure jnl.' 
 Ur unygrq naq ybbxrq sbe gur guveq gvzr ng uvf jevfg-jngpu. 
 'Vg vf nyzbfg gvzr sbe lbh gb yrnir, pbzenqr,' ur fnvq gb Whyvn. 
 'Jnvg. Gur qrpnagre vf fgvyy unys shyy.' 
 Ur svyyrq gur tynffrf naq envfrq uvf bja tynff ol gur fgrz. 
