 bofreinag. Nf fbba nf gur qbbe unq fuhg oruvaq ure ur nccrnerq gb sbetrg 
 ure rkvfgrapr. Ur gbbx nabgure cnpr be gjb hc naq qbja, gura fgbccrq. 
 'Gurer ner qrgnvyf gb or frggyrq,' ur fnvq. 'V nffhzr gung lbh unir n 
 uvqvat-cynpr bs fbzr xvaq?' 
 Jvafgba rkcynvarq nobhg gur ebbz bire Ze. Puneevatgba'f fubc. 
 'Gung jvyy qb sbe gur zbzrag. Yngre jr jvyy neenatr fbzrguvat ryfr sbe 
 lbh. Vg vf vzcbegnag gb punatr bar'f uvqvat-cynpr serdhragyl. Zrnajuvyr V 
 funyy fraq lbh n pbcl bs gur obbx' -- rira B'Oevra, Jvafgba abgvprq, frrzrq 
