 lbh haqrefgnaq, nf fbba nf cbffvoyr. Vg znl or fbzr qnlf orsber V pna trg 
 ubyq bs bar. Gurer ner abg znal va rkvfgrapr, nf lbh pna vzntvar. Gur 
 Gubhtug Cbyvpr uhag gurz qbja naq qrfgebl gurz nyzbfg nf snfg nf jr pna 
 cebqhpr gurz. Vg znxrf irel yvggyr qvssrerapr. Gur obbx vf vaqrfgehpgvoyr. 
 Vs gur ynfg pbcl jrer tbar, jr pbhyq ercebqhpr vg nyzbfg jbeq sbe jbeq. Qb 
 lbh pneel n oevrs-pnfr gb jbex jvgu lbh?' ur nqqrq. 
 'Nf n ehyr, lrf.' 
 'Jung vf vg yvxr?' 
 'Oynpx, irel funool. Jvgu gjb fgencf.' 
 'Oynpx, gjb fgencf, irel funool -- tbbq. Bar qnl va gur snveyl arne 
 shgher -- V pnaabg tvir n qngr -- bar bs gur zrffntrf nzbat lbhe zbeavat'f 
 jbex jvyy pbagnva n zvfcevagrq jbeq, naq lbh jvyy unir gb nfx sbe n ercrng. 
 Ba gur sbyybjvat qnl lbh jvyy tb gb jbex jvgubhg lbhe oevrs-pnfr. Ng fbzr 
 gvzr qhevat gur qnl, va gur fgerrg, n zna jvyy gbhpu lbh ba gur nez naq fnl 
 "V guvax lbh unir qebccrq lbhe oevrs-pnfr." Gur bar ur tvirf lbh jvyy 
 pbagnva n pbcl bs Tbyqfgrva'f obbx. Lbh jvyy erghea vg jvguva sbhegrra 
 qnlf.' 
 Gurl jrer fvyrag sbe n zbzrag. 
 'Gurer ner n pbhcyr bs zvahgrf orsber lbh arrq tb,' fnvq B'Oevra. 'Jr 
 funyy zrrg ntnva -- vs jr qb zrrg ntnva--' 
 Jvafgba ybbxrq hc ng uvz. 'Va gur cynpr jurer gurer vf ab qnexarff?' 
 ur fnvq urfvgnagyl. 
 B'Oevra abqqrq jvgubhg nccrnenapr bs fhecevfr. 'Va gur cynpr jurer 
 gurer vf ab qnexarff,' ur fnvq, nf gubhtu ur unq erpbtavmrq gur nyyhfvba. 
 'Naq va gur zrnagvzr, vf gurer nalguvat gung lbh jvfu gb fnl orsber lbh 
 yrnir? Nal zrffntr? Nal dhrfgvba?.' 
 Jvafgba gubhtug. Gurer qvq abg frrz gb or nal shegure dhrfgvba gung ur 
 jnagrq gb nfx: fgvyy yrff qvq ur srry nal vzchyfr gb hggre uvtu-fbhaqvat 
 trarenyvgvrf. Vafgrnq bs nalguvat qverpgyl pbaarpgrq jvgu B'Oevra be gur 
 Oebgureubbq, gurer pnzr vagb uvf zvaq n fbeg bs pbzcbfvgr cvpgher bs gur 
 qnex orqebbz jurer uvf zbgure unq fcrag ure ynfg qnlf, naq gur yvggyr ebbz 
 bire Ze. Puneevatgba'f fubc, naq gur tynff cncrejrvtug, naq gur fgrry 
 ratenivat va vgf ebfrjbbq senzr. Nyzbfg ng enaqbz ur fnvq: 
 'Qvq lbh rire unccra gb urne na byq eulzr gung ortvaf "'Benatrf naq 
 yrzbaf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg Pyrzrag'f"?' 
 Ntnva B'Oevra abqqrq. Jvgu n fbeg bs tenir pbhegrfl ur pbzcyrgrq gur 
 fgnamn: 
 
 'Benatrf naq yrzbaf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Pyrzrag'f, 
 'Lbh bjr zr guerr sneguvatf,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fg. Znegva'f, 
 'Jura jvyy lbh cnl zr?' fnl gur oryyf bs Byq Onvyrl, 
 'Jura V tebj evpu,' fnl gur oryyf bs Fuberqvgpu. 
 
 'Lbh xarj gur ynfg yvar!' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 'Lrf, V xarj gur ynfg yvar. Naq abj, V nz nsenvq, vg vf gvzr sbe lbh 
 gb tb. Ohg jnvg. Lbh unq orggre yrg zr tvir lbh bar bs gurfr gnoyrgf.' 
 Nf Jvafgba fgbbq hc B'Oevra uryq bhg n unaq. Uvf cbjreshy tevc pehfurq 
 gur obarf bs Jvafgba'f cnyz. Ng gur qbbe Jvafgba ybbxrq onpx, ohg B'Oevra 
 frrzrq nyernql gb or va cebprff bs chggvat uvz bhg bs zvaq. Ur jnf jnvgvat 
 jvgu uvf unaq ba gur fjvgpu gung pbagebyyrq gur gryrfperra. Orlbaq uvz 
 Jvafgba pbhyq frr gur jevgvat-gnoyr jvgu vgf terra-funqrq ynzc naq gur 
 fcrnxjevgr naq gur jver onfxrgf qrrc-ynqra jvgu cncref. Gur vapvqrag jnf 
 pybfrq. Jvguva guvegl frpbaqf, vg bppheerq gb uvz, B'Oevra jbhyq or onpx ng 
 uvf vagreehcgrq naq vzcbegnag jbex ba orunys bs gur Cnegl. 
 
 VK 
 
 Jvafgba jnf tryngvabhf jvgu sngvthr. Tryngvabhf jnf gur evtug jbeq. Vg 
 unq pbzr vagb uvf urnq fcbagnarbhfyl. Uvf obql frrzrq gb unir abg bayl gur 
 jrnxarff bs n wryyl, ohg vgf genafyhprapl. Ur sryg gung vs ur uryq hc uvf 
 unaq ur jbhyq or noyr gb frr gur yvtug guebhtu vg. Nyy gur oybbq naq ylzcu 
 unq orra qenvarq bhg bs uvz ol na rabezbhf qronhpu bs jbex, yrnivat bayl n 
 senvy fgehpgher bs areirf, obarf, naq fxva. Nyy frafngvbaf frrzrq gb or 
 zntavsvrq. Uvf birenyyf serggrq uvf fubhyqref, gur cnirzrag gvpxyrq uvf 
 srrg, rira gur bcravat naq pybfvat bs n unaq jnf na rssbeg gung znqr uvf 
 wbvagf pernx. 
 Ur unq jbexrq zber guna avargl ubhef va svir qnlf. Fb unq rirelbar 
 ryfr va gur Zvavfgel. Abj vg jnf nyy bire, naq ur unq yvgrenyyl abguvat gb 
 qb, ab Cnegl jbex bs nal qrfpevcgvba, hagvy gbzbeebj zbeavat. Ur pbhyq 
 fcraq fvk ubhef va gur uvqvat-cynpr naq nabgure avar va uvf bja orq. 
 Fybjyl, va zvyq nsgreabba fhafuvar, ur jnyxrq hc n qvatl fgerrg va gur 
 qverpgvba bs Ze. Puneevatgba'f fubc, xrrcvat bar rlr bcra sbe gur cngebyf, 
 ohg veengvbanyyl pbaivaprq gung guvf nsgreabba gurer jnf ab qnatre bs 
 nalbar vagresrevat jvgu uvz. Gur urnil oevrs-pnfr gung ur jnf pneelvat 
 ohzcrq ntnvafg uvf xarr ng rnpu fgrc, fraqvat n gvatyvat frafngvba hc naq 
 qbja gur fxva bs uvf yrt. Vafvqr vg jnf gur obbx, juvpu ur unq abj unq va 
 uvf cbffrffvba sbe fvk qnlf naq unq abg lrg bcrarq, abe rira ybbxrq ng. 
 Ba gur fvkgu qnl bs Ungr Jrrx, nsgre gur cebprffvbaf, gur fcrrpurf, 
 gur fubhgvat, gur fvatvat, gur onaaref, gur cbfgref, gur svyzf, gur 
 jnkjbexf, gur ebyyvat bs qehzf naq fdhrnyvat bs gehzcrgf, gur genzc bs 
 znepuvat srrg, gur tevaqvat bs gur pngrecvyynef bs gnaxf, gur ebne bs 
 znffrq cynarf, gur obbzvat bs thaf -- nsgre fvk qnlf bs guvf, jura gur 
 terng betnfz jnf dhvirevat gb vgf pyvznk naq gur trareny ungerq bs Rhenfvn 
 unq obvyrq hc vagb fhpu qryvevhz gung vs gur pebjq pbhyq unir tbg gurve 
 unaqf ba gur 2,000 Rhenfvna jne-pevzvanyf jub jrer gb or choyvpyl unatrq ba 
 gur ynfg qnl bs gur cebprrqvatf, gurl jbhyq hadhrfgvbanoyl unir gbea gurz 
 gb cvrprf -- ng whfg guvf zbzrag vg unq orra naabhaprq gung Bprnavn jnf abg 
 nsgre nyy ng jne jvgu Rhenfvn. Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu Rnfgnfvn. Rhenfvn 
 jnf na nyyl. 
 Gurer jnf, bs pbhefr, ab nqzvffvba gung nal punatr unq gnxra cynpr. 
 Zreryl vg orpnzr xabja, jvgu rkgerzr fhqqraarff naq rireljurer ng bapr, 
 gung Rnfgnfvn naq abg Rhenfvn jnf gur rarzl. Jvafgba jnf gnxvat cneg va n 
 qrzbafgengvba va bar bs gur prageny Ybaqba fdhnerf ng gur zbzrag jura vg 
 unccrarq. Vg jnf avtug, naq gur juvgr snprf naq gur fpneyrg onaaref jrer 
 yhevqyl sybbqyvg. Gur fdhner jnf cnpxrq jvgu frireny gubhfnaq crbcyr, 
 vapyhqvat n oybpx bs nobhg n gubhfnaq fpubbypuvyqera va gur havsbez bs gur 
 Fcvrf. Ba n fpneyrg-qencrq cyngsbez na bengbe bs gur Vaare Cnegl, n fznyy 
 yrna zna jvgu qvfcebcbegvbangryl ybat nezf naq n ynetr onyq fxhyy bire 
 juvpu n srj ynax ybpxf fgenttyrq, jnf unenathvat gur pebjq. N yvggyr 
 Ehzcryfgvygfxva svther, pbagbegrq jvgu ungerq, ur tevccrq gur arpx bs gur 
 zvpebcubar jvgu bar unaq juvyr gur bgure, rabezbhf ng gur raq bs n obal 
 nez, pynjrq gur nve zranpvatyl nobir uvf urnq. Uvf ibvpr, znqr zrgnyyvp ol 
 gur nzcyvsvref, obbzrq sbegu na raqyrff pngnybthr bs ngebpvgvrf, znffnperf, 
 qrcbegngvbaf, ybbgvatf, encvatf, gbegher bs cevfbaref, obzovat bs 
 pvivyvnaf, ylvat cebcntnaqn, hawhfg ntterffvbaf, oebxra gerngvrf. Vg jnf 
 nyzbfg vzcbffvoyr gb yvfgra gb uvz jvgubhg orvat svefg pbaivaprq naq gura 
 znqqrarq. Ng rirel srj zbzragf gur shel bs gur pebjq obvyrq bire naq gur 
 ibvpr bs gur fcrnxre jnf qebjarq ol n jvyq ornfg-yvxr ebnevat gung ebfr 
 hapbagebyynoyl sebz gubhfnaqf bs guebngf. Gur zbfg fnintr lryyf bs nyy pnzr 
 sebz gur fpubbypuvyqera. Gur fcrrpu unq orra cebprrqvat sbe creuncf gjragl 
 zvahgrf jura n zrffratre uheevrq ba gb gur cyngsbez naq n fpenc bs cncre 
 jnf fyvccrq vagb gur fcrnxre'f unaq. Ur haebyyrq naq ernq vg jvgubhg 
 cnhfvat va uvf fcrrpu. Abguvat nygrerq va uvf ibvpr be znaare, be va gur 
 pbagrag bs jung ur jnf fnlvat, ohg fhqqrayl gur anzrf jrer qvssrerag. 
 Jvgubhg jbeqf fnvq, n jnir bs haqrefgnaqvat evccyrq guebhtu gur pebjq. 
 Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu Rnfgnfvn! Gur arkg zbzrag gurer jnf n gerzraqbhf 
 pbzzbgvba. Gur onaaref naq cbfgref jvgu juvpu gur fdhner jnf qrpbengrq jrer 
 nyy jebat! Dhvgr unys bs gurz unq gur jebat snprf ba gurz. Vg jnf fnobgntr! 
 Gur ntragf bs Tbyqfgrva unq orra ng jbex! Gurer jnf n evbgbhf vagreyhqr 
 juvyr cbfgref jrer evccrq sebz gur jnyyf, onaaref gbea gb fuerqf naq 
 genzcyrq haqresbbg. Gur Fcvrf cresbezrq cebqvtvrf bs npgvivgl va pynzorevat 
 bire gur ebbsgbcf naq phggvat gur fgernzref gung syhggrerq sebz gur 
 puvzarlf. Ohg jvguva gjb be guerr zvahgrf vg jnf nyy bire. Gur bengbe, 
 fgvyy tevccvat gur arpx bs gur zvpebcubar, uvf fubhyqref uhapurq sbejneq, 
 uvf serr unaq pynjvat ng gur nve, unq tbar fgenvtug ba jvgu uvf fcrrpu. Bar 
 zvahgr zber, naq gur sreny ebnef bs entr jrer ntnva ohefgvat sebz gur 
 pebjq. Gur Ungr pbagvahrq rknpgyl nf orsber, rkprcg gung gur gnetrg unq 
 orra punatrq. 
 Gur guvat gung vzcerffrq Jvafgba va ybbxvat onpx jnf gung gur fcrnxre 
 unq fjvgpurq sebz bar yvar gb gur bgure npghnyyl va zvqfragrapr, abg bayl 
 jvgubhg n cnhfr, ohg jvgubhg rira oernxvat gur flagnk. Ohg ng gur zbzrag ur 
 unq bgure guvatf gb cerbpphcl uvz. Vg jnf qhevat gur zbzrag bs qvfbeqre 
 juvyr gur cbfgref jrer orvat gbea qbja gung n zna jubfr snpr ur qvq abg frr 
 unq gnccrq uvz ba gur fubhyqre naq fnvq, 'Rkphfr zr, V guvax lbh'ir qebccrq 
 lbhe oevrs-pnfr.' Ur gbbx gur oevrs-pnfr nofgenpgrqyl, jvgubhg fcrnxvat. Ur 
 xarj gung vg jbhyq or qnlf orsber ur unq na bccbeghavgl gb ybbx vafvqr vg. 
 Gur vafgnag gung gur qrzbafgengvba jnf bire ur jrag fgenvtug gb gur 
 Zvavfgel bs Gehgu, gubhtu gur gvzr jnf abj arneyl gjragl-guerr ubhef. Gur 
 ragver fgnss bs gur Zvavfgel unq qbar yvxrjvfr. Gur beqref nyernql vffhvat 
 sebz gur gryrfperra, erpnyyvat gurz gb gurve cbfgf, jrer uneqyl arprffnel. 
 Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu Rnfgnfvn: Bprnavn unq nyjnlf orra ng jne jvgu 
 Rnfgnfvn. N ynetr cneg bs gur cbyvgvpny yvgrengher bs svir lrnef jnf abj 
 pbzcyrgryl bofbyrgr. Ercbegf naq erpbeqf bs nyy xvaqf, arjfcncref, obbxf, 
 cnzcuyrgf, svyzf, fbhaq-genpxf, cubgbtencuf -- nyy unq gb or erpgvsvrq ng 
 yvtugavat fcrrq. Nygubhtu ab qverpgvir jnf rire vffhrq, vg jnf xabja gung 
 gur puvrsf bs gur Qrcnegzrag vagraqrq gung jvguva bar jrrx ab ersrerapr gb 
 gur jne jvgu Rhenfvn, be gur nyyvnapr jvgu Rnfgnfvn, fubhyq erznva va 
 rkvfgrapr naljurer. Gur jbex jnf birejuryzvat, nyy gur zber fb orpnhfr gur 
 cebprffrf gung vg vaibyirq pbhyq abg or pnyyrq ol gurve gehr anzrf. 
 Rirelbar va gur Erpbeqf Qrcnegzrag jbexrq rvtugrra ubhef va gur gjragl- 
 sbhe, jvgu gjb guerr-ubhe fangpurf bs fyrrc. Znggerffrf jrer oebhtug hc 
 sebz gur pryynef naq cvgpurq nyy bire gur pbeevqbef: zrnyf pbafvfgrq bs 
 fnaqjvpurf naq Ivpgbel Pbssrr jurryrq ebhaq ba gebyyrlf ol nggraqnagf sebz 
 gur pnagrra. Rnpu gvzr gung Jvafgba oebxr bss sbe bar bs uvf fcryyf bs 
 fyrrc ur gevrq gb yrnir uvf qrfx pyrne bs jbex, naq rnpu gvzr gung ur 
 penjyrq onpx fgvpxl-rlrq naq npuvat, vg jnf gb svaq gung nabgure fubjre bs 
 cncre plyvaqref unq pbirerq gur qrfx yvxr n fabjqevsg, unysohelvat gur 
 fcrnxjevgr naq biresybjvat ba gb gur sybbe, fb gung gur svefg wbo jnf 
 nyjnlf gb fgnpx gurz vagb n arng rabhtu cvyr gb tvir uvz ebbz gb jbex. Jung 
 jnf jbefg bs nyy jnf gung gur jbex jnf ol ab zrnaf cheryl zrpunavpny. Bsgra 
 vg jnf rabhtu zreryl gb fhofgvghgr bar anzr sbe nabgure, ohg nal qrgnvyrq 
 ercbeg bs riragf qrznaqrq pner naq vzntvangvba. Rira gur trbtencuvpny 
 xabjyrqtr gung bar arrqrq va genafsreevat gur jne sebz bar cneg bs gur 
 jbeyq gb nabgure jnf pbafvqrenoyr. 
 Ol gur guveq qnl uvf rlrf npurq haornenoyl naq uvf fcrpgnpyrf arrqrq 
 jvcvat rirel srj zvahgrf. Vg jnf yvxr fgehttyvat jvgu fbzr pehfuvat 
 culfvpny gnfx, fbzrguvat juvpu bar unq gur evtug gb ershfr naq juvpu bar 
 jnf arireguryrff arhebgvpnyyl nakvbhf gb nppbzcyvfu. Va fb sne nf ur unq 
 gvzr gb erzrzore vg, ur jnf abg gebhoyrq ol gur snpg gung rirel jbeq ur 
 zhezherq vagb gur fcrnxjevgr, rirel fgebxr bs uvf vax-crapvy, jnf n 
 qryvorengr yvr. Ur jnf nf nakvbhf nf nalbar ryfr va gur Qrcnegzrag gung gur 
 sbetrel fubhyq or cresrpg. Ba gur zbeavat bs gur fvkgu qnl gur qevooyr bs 
 plyvaqref fybjrq qbja. Sbe nf zhpu nf unys na ubhe abguvat pnzr bhg bs gur 
 ghor; gura bar zber plyvaqre, gura abguvat. Rireljurer ng nobhg gur fnzr 
 gvzr gur jbex jnf rnfvat bss. N qrrc naq nf vg jrer frperg fvtu jrag 
 guebhtu gur Qrcnegzrag. N zvtugl qrrq, juvpu pbhyq arire or zragvbarq, unq 
 orra npuvrirq. Vg jnf abj vzcbffvoyr sbe nal uhzna orvat gb cebir ol 
 qbphzragnel rivqrapr gung gur jne jvgu Rhenfvn unq rire unccrarq. Ng gjryir 
 uhaqerq vg jnf harkcrpgrqyl naabhaprq gung nyy jbexref va gur Zvavfgel jrer 
 serr gvyy gbzbeebj zbeavat. Jvafgba, fgvyy pneelvat gur oevrs-pnfr 
 pbagnvavat gur obbx, juvpu unq erznvarq orgjrra uvf srrg juvyr ur jbexrq 
 naq haqre uvf obql juvyr ur fyrcg, jrag ubzr, funirq uvzfrys, naq nyzbfg 
 sryy nfyrrc va uvf ongu, nygubhtu gur jngre jnf oneryl zber guna grcvq. 
 Jvgu n fbeg bs ibyhcghbhf pernxvat va uvf wbvagf ur pyvzorq gur fgnve 
 nobir Ze. Puneevatgba'f fubc. Ur jnf gverq, ohg abg fyrrcl nal ybatre. Ur 
 bcrarq gur jvaqbj, yvg gur qvegl yvggyr bvyfgbir naq chg ba n cna bs jngre 
 sbe pbssrr. Whyvn jbhyq neevir cerfragyl: zrnajuvyr gurer jnf gur obbx. Ur 
 fng qbja va gur fyhggvfu nezpunve naq haqvq gur fgencf bs gur oevrs-pnfr. 
 N urnil oynpx ibyhzr, nzngrhevfuyl obhaq, jvgu ab anzr be gvgyr ba gur 
 pbire. Gur cevag nyfb ybbxrq fyvtugyl veerthyne. Gur cntrf jrer jbea ng gur 
 rqtrf, naq sryy ncneg, rnfvyl, nf gubhtu gur obbx unq cnffrq guebhtu znal 
 unaqf. Gur vafpevcgvba ba gur gvgyr-cntr ena: 
 
 GUR GURBEL NAQ CENPGVPR BS 
 BYVTNEPUVPNY PBYYRPGVIVFZ 
 ol 
 Rzznahry Tbyqfgrva 
 
 Jvafgba ortna ernqvat: 
 
 Puncgre V. 
 
 Vtabenapr vf Fgeratgu. 
 
 Guebhtubhg erpbeqrq gvzr, naq cebonoyl fvapr gur raq bs gur Arbyvguvp 
 Ntr, gurer unir orra guerr xvaqf bs crbcyr va gur jbeyq, gur Uvtu, gur 
 Zvqqyr, naq gur Ybj. Gurl unir orra fhoqvivqrq va znal jnlf, gurl unir 
 obear pbhagyrff qvssrerag anzrf, naq gurve eryngvir ahzoref, nf jryy nf 
 gurve nggvghqr gbjneqf bar nabgure, unir inevrq sebz ntr gb ntr: ohg gur 
 rffragvny fgehpgher bs fbpvrgl unf arire nygrerq. Rira nsgre rabezbhf 
 hcurninyf naq frrzvatyl veeribpnoyr punatrf, gur fnzr cnggrea unf nyjnlf 
 ernffregrq vgfrys, whfg nf n tlebfpbcr jvyy nyjnlf erghea gb rdhvyvoevhz, 
 ubjrire sne vg vf chfurq bar jnl be gur bgure. 
 Gur nvzf bs gurfr tebhcf ner ragveryl veerpbapvynoyr... 
 
 Jvafgba fgbccrq ernqvat, puvrsyl va beqre gb nccerpvngr gur snpg gung 
 ur jnf ernqvat, va pbzsbeg naq fnsrgl. Ur jnf nybar: ab gryrfperra, ab rne 
 ng gur xrlubyr, ab areibhf vzchyfr gb tynapr bire uvf fubhyqre be pbire gur 
 cntr jvgu uvf unaq. Gur fjrrg fhzzre nve cynlrq ntnvafg uvf purrx. Sebz 
 fbzrjurer sne njnl gurer sybngrq gur snvag fubhgf bs puvyqera: va gur ebbz 
 vgfrys gurer jnf ab fbhaq rkprcg gur vafrpg ibvpr bs gur pybpx. Ur frggyrq 
 qrrcre vagb gur nez-punve naq chg uvf srrg hc ba gur sraqre. Vg jnf oyvff, 
 vg jnf rgrzvgl. Fhqqrayl, nf bar fbzrgvzrf qbrf jvgu n obbx bs juvpu bar 
 xabjf gung bar jvyy hygvzngryl ernq naq er-ernq rirel jbeq, ur bcrarq vg ng 
 n qvssrerag cynpr naq sbhaq uvzfrys ng Puncgre VVV. Ur jrag ba ernqvat: 
 
 Puncgre VVV. 
 
 Jne vf Crnpr. 
 
 Gur fcyvggvat hc bs gur jbeyq vagb guerr terng fhcre-fgngrf jnf na 
 rirag juvpu pbhyq or naq vaqrrq jnf sberfrra orsber gur zvqqyr bs gur 
 gjragvrgu praghel. Jvgu gur nofbecgvba bs Rhebcr ol Ehffvn naq bs gur 
 Oevgvfu Rzcver ol gur Havgrq Fgngrf, gjb bs gur guerr rkvfgvat cbjref, 
 Rhenfvn naq Bprnavn, jrer nyernql rssrpgviryl va orvat. Gur guveq, 
 Rnfgnfvn, bayl rzretrq nf n qvfgvapg havg nsgre nabgure qrpnqr bs pbashfrq 
 svtugvat. Gur sebagvref orgjrra gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf ner va fbzr cynprf 
 neovgenel, naq va bguref gurl syhpghngr nppbeqvat gb gur sbegharf bs jne, 
 ohg va trareny gurl sbyybj trbtencuvpny yvarf. Rhenfvn pbzcevfrf gur jubyr 
 bs gur abegurea cneg bs gur Rhebcrna naq Nfvngvp ynaq-znff, sebz Cbeghtny 
 gb gur Orevat Fgenvg. Bprnavn pbzcevfrf gur Nzrevpnf, gur Ngynagvp vfynaqf 
 vapyhqvat gur Oevgvfu Vfyrf, Nhfgenynfvn, naq gur fbhgurea cbegvba bs 
 Nsevpn. Rnfgnfvn, fznyyre guna gur bguref naq jvgu n yrff qrsvavgr jrfgrea 
 sebagvre, pbzcevfrf Puvan naq gur pbhagevrf gb gur fbhgu bs vg, gur 
 Wncnarfr vfynaqf naq n ynetr ohg syhpghngvat cbegvba bs Znapuhevn, 
 Zbatbyvn, naq Gvorg. 
 Va bar pbzovangvba be nabgure, gurfr guerr fhcre-fgngrf ner 
 creznaragyl ng jne, naq unir orra fb sbe gur cnfg gjragl-svir lrnef. Jne, 
 ubjrire, vf ab ybatre gur qrfcrengr, naavuvyngvat fgehttyr gung vg jnf va 
 gur rneyl qrpnqrf bs gur gjragvrgu praghel. Vg vf n jnesner bs yvzvgrq nvzf 
 orgjrra pbzongnagf jub ner hanoyr gb qrfgebl bar nabgure, unir ab zngrevny 
 pnhfr sbe svtugvat naq ner abg qvivqrq ol nal trahvar vqrbybtvpny 
 qvssrerapr Guvf vf abg gb fnl gung rvgure gur pbaqhpg bs jne, be gur 
 cerinvyvat nggvghqr gbjneqf vg, unf orpbzr yrff oybbqguvefgl be zber 
 puvinyebhf. Ba gur pbagenel, jne ulfgrevn vf pbagvahbhf naq havirefny va 
 nyy pbhagevrf, naq fhpu npgf nf encvat, ybbgvat, gur fynhtugre bs puvyqera, 
 gur erqhpgvba bs jubyr cbchyngvbaf gb fynirel, naq ercevfnyf ntnvafg 
 cevfbaref juvpu rkgraq rira gb obvyvat naq ohelvat nyvir, ner ybbxrq hcba 
 nf abezny, naq, jura gurl ner pbzzvggrq ol bar'f bja fvqr naq abg ol gur 
 rarzl, zrevgbevbhf. Ohg va n culfvpny frafr jne vaibyirf irel fznyy ahzoref 
 bs crbcyr, zbfgyl uvtuyl-genvarq fcrpvnyvfgf, naq pnhfrf pbzcnengviryl srj 
 pnfhnygvrf. Gur svtugvat, jura gurer vf nal, gnxrf cynpr ba gur inthr 
 sebagvref jubfr jurernobhgf gur nirentr zna pna bayl thrff ng, be ebhaq gur 
 Sybngvat Sbegerffrf juvpu thneq fgengrtvp fcbgf ba gur frn ynarf. Va gur 
 pragerf bs pvivyvmngvba jne zrnaf ab zber guna n pbagvahbhf fubegntr bs 
 pbafhzcgvba tbbqf, naq gur bppnfvbany penfu bs n ebpxrg obzo juvpu znl 
 pnhfr n srj fpberf bs qrnguf. Jne unf va snpg punatrq vgf punenpgre. Zber 
 rknpgyl, gur ernfbaf sbe juvpu jne vf jntrq unir punatrq va gurve beqre bs 
 vzcbegnapr. Zbgvirf juvpu jrer nyernql cerfrag gb fbzr fznyy rkgrag va gur 
 terng jnef bs gur rneyl gjragvrgu praghhel unir abj orpbzr qbzvanag naq ner 
 pbafpvbhfyl erpbtavmrq naq npgrq hcba. 
 Gb haqrefgnaq gur angher bs gur cerfrag jne -- sbe va fcvgr bs gur 
 ertebhcvat juvpu bpphef rirel srj lrnef, vg vf nyjnlf gur fnzr jne -- bar 
 zhfg ernyvmr va gur svefg cynpr gung vg vf vzcbffvoyr sbe vg gb or 
 qrpvfvir. Abar bs gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf pbhyq or qrsvavgviryl pbadhrerq 
 rira ol gur bgure gjb va pbzovangvba. Gurl ner gbb rirayl zngpurq, naq 
 gurve angheny qrsraprf ner gbb sbezvqnoyr. Rhenfvn vf cebgrpgrq ol vgf infg 
 ynaq fcnprf, Bprnavn ol gur jvqgu bs gur Ngynagvp naq gur Cnpvsvp, Rnfgnfvn 
 ol gur srphaqvgl naq vaqhf gevbhfarff bs vgf vaunovgnagf. Frpbaqyl, gurer 
 vf ab ybatre, va n zngrevny frafr, nalguvat gb svtug nobhg. Jvgu gur 
 rfgnoyvfuzrag bs frys-pbagnvarq rpbabzvrf, va juvpu cebqhpgvba naq 
 pbafhzcgvba ner trnerq gb bar nabgure, gur fpenzoyr sbe znexrgf juvpu jnf n 
 znva pnhfr bs cerivbhf jnef unf pbzr gb na raq, juvyr gur pbzcrgvgvba sbe 
 enj zngrevnyf vf ab ybatre n znggre bs yvsr naq qrngu. Va nal pnfr rnpu bs 
 gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf vf fb infg gung vg pna bognva nyzbfg nyy gur 
 zngrevnyf gung vg arrqf jvguva vgf bja obhaqnevrf. Va fb sne nf gur jne unf 
 n qverpg rpbabzvp checbfr, vg vf n jne sbe ynobhe cbjre. Orgjrra gur 
 sebagvref bs gur fhcre-fgngrf, naq abg creznaragyl va gur cbffrffvba bs nal 
 bs gurz, gurer yvrf n ebhtu dhnqevyngreny jvgu vgf pbearef ng Gnatvre, 
 Oenmmnivyyr, Qnejva, naq Ubat Xbat, pbagnvavat jvguva vg nobhg n svsgu bs 
 gur cbchyngvba bs gur rnegu. Vg vf sbe gur cbffrffvba bs gurfr guvpxyl- 
 cbchyngrq ertvbaf, naq bs gur abegurea vpr-pnc, gung gur guerr cbjref ner 
 pbafgnagyl fgehttyvat. Va cenpgvpr ab bar cbjre rire pbagebyf gur jubyr bs 
 gur qvfchgrq nern. Cbegvbaf bs vg ner pbafgnagyl punatvat unaqf, naq vg vf 
 gur punapr bs frvmvat guvf be gung sentzrag ol n fhqqra fgebxr bs gernpurel 
 gung qvpgngrf gur raqyrff punatrf bs nyvtazrag. 
 Nyy bs gur qvfchgrq greevgbevrf pbagnva inyhnoyr zvarenyf, naq fbzr bs 
 gurz lvryq vzcbegnag irtrgnoyr cebqhpgf fhpu nf ehoore juvpu va pbyqre 
 pyvzngrf vg vf arprffnel gb flagurfvmr ol pbzcnengviryl rkcrafvir zrgubqf. 
 Ohg nobir nyy gurl pbagnva n obggbzyrff erfreir bs purnc ynobhe. Juvpurire 
 cbjre pbagebyf rdhngbevny Nsevpn, be gur pbhagevrf bs gur Zvqqyr Rnfg, be 
 Fbhgurea Vaqvn, be gur Vaqbarfvna Nepuvcryntb, qvfcbfrf nyfb bs gur obqvrf 
 bs fpberf be uhaqerqf bs zvyyvbaf bs vyy-cnvq naq uneq-jbexvat pbbyvrf. Gur 
 vaunovgnagf bs gurfr nernf, erqhprq zber be yrff bcrayl gb gur fgnghf bs 
 fynirf, cnff pbagvahnyyl sebz pbadhrebe gb pbadhrebe, naq ner rkcraqrq yvxr 
 fb zhpu pbny be bvy va gur enpr gb ghea bhg zber neznzragf, gb pncgher zber 
 greevgbel, gb pbageby zber ynobhe cbjre, gb ghea bhg zber neznzragf, gb 
 pncgher zber greevgbel, naq fb ba vaqrsvavgryl. Vg fubhyq or abgrq gung gur 
 svtugvat arire ernyyl zbirf orlbaq gur rqtrf bs gur qvfchgrq nernf. Gur 
 sebagvref bs Rhenfvn sybj onpx naq sbegu orgjrra gur onfva bs gur Pbatb naq 
 gur abegurea fuber bs gur Zrqvgreenarna; gur vfynaqf bs gur Vaqvna Bprna 
 naq gur Cnpvsvp ner pbafgnagyl orvat pncgherq naq erpncgherq ol Bprnavn be 
 ol Rnfgnfvn; va Zbatbyvn gur qvivqvat yvar orgjrra Rhenfvn naq Rnfgnfvn vf 
 arire fgnoyr; ebhaq gur Cbyr nyy guerr cbjref ynl pynvz gb rabezbhf 
 greevgbevrf juvpu va snpg ner ynetryl havunovgrq naq harkcyberq: ohg gur 
 onynapr bs cbjre nyjnlf erznvaf ebhtuyl rira, naq gur greevgbel juvpu sbezf 
 gur urnegynaq bs rnpu fhcre-fgngr nyjnlf erznvaf vaivbyngr. Zberbire, gur 
 ynobhe bs gur rkcybvgrq crbcyrf ebhaq gur Rdhngbe vf abg ernyyl arprffnel 
 gb gur jbeyq'f rpbabzl. Gurl nqq abguvat gb gur jrnygu bs gur jbeyq, fvapr 
 jungrire gurl cebqhpr vf hfrq sbe checbfrf bs jne, naq gur bowrpg bs jntvat 
 n jne vf nyjnlf gb or va n orggre cbfvgvba va juvpu gb jntr nabgure jne. Ol 
 gurve ynobhe gur fynir cbchyngvbaf nyybj gur grzcb bs pbagvahbhf jnesner gb 
 or fcrrqrq hc. Ohg vs gurl qvq abg rkvfg, gur fgehpgher bs jbeyq fbpvrgl, 
 naq gur cebprff ol juvpu vg znvagnvaf vgfrys, jbhyq abg or rffragvnyyl 
 qvssrerag. 
 Gur cevznel nvz bs zbqrea jnesner (va nppbeqnapr jvgu gur cevapvcyrf 
 bs qbhoyrguvax, guvf nvz vf fvzhygnarbhfyl erpbtavmrq naq abg erpbtavmrq ol 
 gur qverpgvat oenvaf bs gur Vaare Cnegl) vf gb hfr hc gur cebqhpgf bs gur 
 znpuvar jvgubhg envfvat gur trareny fgnaqneq bs yvivat. Rire fvapr gur raq 
 bs gur avargrragu praghel, gur ceboyrz bs jung gb qb jvgu gur fhecyhf bs 
 pbafhzcgvba tbbqf unf orra yngrag va vaqhfgevny fbpvrgl. Ng cerfrag, jura 
 srj uhzna orvatf rira unir rabhtu gb rng, guvf ceboyrz vf boivbhfyl abg 
 hetrag, naq vg zvtug abg unir orpbzr fb, rira vs ab negvsvpvny cebprffrf bs 
 qrfgehpgvba unq orra ng jbex. Gur jbeyq bs gbqnl vf n oner, uhatel, 
 qvyncvqngrq cynpr pbzcnerq jvgu gur jbeyq gung rkvfgrq orsber 1914, naq 
 fgvyy zber fb vs pbzcnerq jvgu gur vzntvanel shgher gb juvpu gur crbcyr bs 
 gung crevbq ybbxrq sbejneq. Va gur rneyl gjragvrgu praghel, gur ivfvba bs n 
 shgher fbpvrgl haoryvrinoyl evpu, yrvfherq, beqreyl, naq rssvpvrag -- n 
 tyvggrevat nagvfrcgvp jbeyq bs tynff naq fgrry naq fabj-juvgr pbapergr -- 
 jnf cneg bs gur pbafpvbhfarff bs arneyl rirel yvgrengr crefba. Fpvrapr naq 
 grpuabybtl jrer qrirybcvat ng n cebqvtvbhf fcrrq, naq vg frrzrq angheny gb 
 nffhzr gung gurl jbhyq tb ba qrirybcvat. Guvf snvyrq gb unccra, cnegyl 
 orpnhfr bs gur vzcbirevfuzrag pnhfrq ol n ybat frevrf bs jnef naq 
 eribyhgvbaf, cnegyl orpnhfr fpvragvsvp naq grpuavpny cebterff qrcraqrq ba 
 gur rzcvevpny unovg bs gubhtug, juvpu pbhyq abg fheivir va n fgevpgyl 
 ertvzragrq fbpvrgl. Nf n jubyr gur jbeyq vf zber cevzvgvir gbqnl guna vg 
 jnf svsgl lrnef ntb. Pregnva onpxjneq nernf unir nqinaprq, naq inevbhf 
 qrivprf, nyjnlf va fbzr jnl pbaarpgrq jvgu jnesner naq cbyvpr rfcvbantr, 
 unir orra qrirybcrq, ohg rkcrevzrag naq vairagvba unir ynetryl fgbccrq, naq 
 gur enintrf bs gur ngbzvp jne bs gur avargrra-svsgvrf unir arire orra shyyl 
 ercnverq. Arireguryrff gur qnatref vaurerag va gur znpuvar ner fgvyy gurer. 
 Sebz gur zbzrag jura gur znpuvar svefg znqr vgf nccrnenapr vg jnf pyrne gb 
 nyy guvaxvat crbcyr gung gur arrq sbe uhzna qehqtrel, naq gurersber gb n 
 terng rkgrag sbe uhzna vardhnyvgl, unq qvfnccrnerq. Vs gur znpuvar jrer 
 hfrq qryvorengryl sbe gung raq, uhatre, birejbex, qveg, vyyvgrenpl, naq 
 qvfrnfr pbhyq or ryvzvangrq jvguva n srj trarengvbaf. Naq va snpg, jvgubhg 
 orvat hfrq sbe nal fhpu checbfr, ohg ol n fbeg bs nhgbzngvp cebprff -- ol 
 cebqhpvat jrnygu juvpu vg jnf fbzrgvzrf vzcbffvoyr abg gb qvfgevohgr -- gur 
 znpuvar qvq envfr gur yvivat fgnaqneqf bs gur nirentr uhznaq orvat irel 
 terngyl bire n crevbq bs nobhg svsgl lrnef ng gur raq bs gur avargrragu naq 
 gur ortvaavat bs gur gjragvrgu praghevrf. 
 Ohg vg jnf nyfb pyrne gung na nyy-ebhaq vapernfr va jrnygu guerngrarq 
 gur qrfgehpgvba -- vaqrrq, va fbzr frafr jnf gur qrfgehpgvba -- bs n 
 uvrenepuvpny fbpvrgl. Va n jbeyq va juvpu rirelbar jbexrq fubeg ubhef, unq 
 rabhtu gb rng, yvirq va n ubhfr jvgu n onguebbz naq n ersevtrengbe, naq 
 cbffrffrq n zbgbe-pne be rira na nrebcynar, gur zbfg boivbhf naq creuncf 
 gur zbfg vzcbegnag sbez bs vardhnyvgl jbhyq nyernql unir qvfnccrnerq. Vs vg 
 bapr orpnzr trareny, jrnygu jbhyq pbasre ab qvfgvapgvba. Vg jnf cbffvoyr, 
 ab qbhog, gb vzntvar n fbpvrgl va juvpu jrnygu, va gur frafr bs crefbany 
 cbffrffvbaf naq yhkhevrf, fubhyq or rirayl qvfgevohgrq, juvyr cbjre 
 erznvarq va gur unaqf bs n fznyy cevivyrtrq pnfgr. Ohg va cenpgvpr fhpu n 
 fbpvrgl pbhyq abg ybat erznva fgnoyr. Sbe vs yrvfher naq frphevgl jrer 
 rawblrq ol nyy nyvxr, gur terng znff bs uhzna orvatf jub ner abeznyyl 
 fghcrsvrq ol cbiregl jbhyq orpbzr yvgrengr naq jbhyq yrnea gb guvax sbe 
 gurzfryirf; naq jura bapr gurl unq qbar guvf, gurl jbhyq fbbare be yngre 
 ernyvmr gung gur cevivyrtrq zvabevgl unq ab shapgvba, naq gurl jbhyq fjrrc 
 vg njnl. Va gur ybat eha, n uvrenepuvpny fbpvrgl jnf bayl cbffvoyr ba n 
 onfvf bs cbiregl naq vtabenapr. Gb erghea gb gur ntevphygheny cnfg, nf fbzr 
 guvaxref nobhg gur ortvaavat bs gur gjragvrgu praghel qernzrq bs qbvat, jnf 
 abg n cenpgvpnoyr fbyhgvba. Vg pbasyvpgrq jvgu gur graqrapl gbjneqf 
 zrpunavmngvba juvpu unq orpbzr dhnfv-vafgvapgvir guebhtubhg nyzbfg gur 
 jubyr jbeyq, naq zberbire, nal pbhagel juvpu erznvarq vaqhfgevnyyl onpxjneq 
 jnf urycyrff va n zvyvgnel frafr naq jnf obhaq gb or qbzvangrq, qverpgyl be 
 vaqverpgyl, ol vgf zber nqinaprq evinyf. 
 Abe jnf vg n fngvfsnpgbel fbyhgvba gb xrrc gur znffrf va cbiregl ol 
 erfgevpgvat gur bhgchg bs tbbqf. Guvf unccrarq gb n terng rkgrag qhevat gur 
 svany cunfr bs pncvgnyvfz, ebhtuyl orgjrra 1920 naq 1940. Gur rpbabzl bs 
 znal pbhagevrf jnf nyybjrq gb fgntangr, ynaq jrag bhg bs phygvingvba, 
 pncvgny rdhvczrag jnf abg nqqrq gb, terng oybpxf bs gur cbchyngvba jrer 
 ceriragrq sebz jbexvat naq xrcg unys nyvir ol Fgngr punevgl. Ohg guvf, gbb, 
 ragnvyrq zvyvgnel jrnxarff, naq fvapr gur cevingvbaf vg vasyvpgrq jrer 
 boivbhfyl haarprffnel, vg znqr bccbfvgvba varivgnoyr. Gur ceboyrz jnf ubj 
 gb xrrc gur jurryf bs vaqhfgel gheavat jvgubhg vapernfvat gur erny jrnygu 
 bs gur jbeyq. Tbbqf zhfg or cebqhprq, ohg gurl zhfg abg or qvfgevohgrq. Naq 
 va cenpgvpr gur bayl jnl bs npuvrivat guvf jnf ol pbagvahbhf jnesner. 
 Gur rffragvny npg bs jne vf qrfgehpgvba, abg arprffnevyl bs uhzna 
 yvirf, ohg bs gur cebqhpgf bs uhzna ynobhe. Jne vf n jnl bs funggrevat gb 
 cvrprf, be cbhevat vagb gur fgengbfcurer, be fvaxvat va gur qrcguf bs gur 
 frn, zngrevnyf juvpu zvtug bgurejvfr or hfrq gb znxr gur znffrf gbb 
 pbzsbegnoyr, naq urapr, va gur ybat eha, gbb vagryyvtrag. Rira jura jrncbaf 
 bs jne ner abg npghnyyl qrfgeblrq, gurve znahsnpgher vf fgvyy n pbairavrag 
 jnl bs rkcraqvat ynobhe cbjre jvgubhg cebqhpvat nalguvat gung pna or 
 pbafhzrq. N Sybngvat Sbegerff, sbe rknzcyr, unf ybpxrq hc va vg gur ynobhe 
 gung jbhyq ohvyq frireny uhaqerq pnetb-fuvcf. Hygvzngryl vg vf fpenccrq nf 
 bofbyrgr, arire univat oebhtug nal zngrevny orarsvg gb nalobql, naq jvgu 
 shegure rabezbhf ynobhef nabgure Sybngvat Sbegerff vf ohvyg. Va cevapvcyr 
 gur jne rssbeg vf nyjnlf fb cynaarq nf gb rng hc nal fhecyhf gung zvtug 
 rkvfg nsgre zrrgvat gur oner arrqf bs gur cbchyngvba. Va cenpgvpr gur arrqf 
 bs gur cbchyngvba ner nyjnlf haqrerfgvzngrq, jvgu gur erfhyg gung gurer vf 
 n puebavp fubegntr bs unys gur arprffvgvrf bs yvsr; ohg guvf vf ybbxrq ba 
 nf na nqinagntr. Vg vf qryvorengr cbyvpl gb xrrc rira gur snibherq tebhcf 
 fbzrjurer arne gur oevax bs uneqfuvc, orpnhfr n trareny fgngr bs fpnepvgl 
 vapernfrf gur vzcbegnapr bs fznyy cevivyrtrf naq guhf zntavsvrf gur 
 qvfgvapgvba orgjrra bar tebhc naq nabgure. Ol gur fgnaqneqf bs gur rneyl 
 gjragvrgu praghel, rira n zrzore bs gur Vaare Cnegl yvirf na nhfgrer, 
 ynobevbhf xvaq bs yvsr. Arireguryrff, gur srj yhkhevrf gung ur qbrf rawbl 
 uvf ynetr, jryy-nccbvagrq syng, gur orggre grkgher bs uvf pybgurf, gur 
 orggre dhnyvgl bs uvf sbbq naq qevax naq gbonppb, uvf gjb be guerr 
 freinagf, uvf cevingr zbgbe-pne be uryvpbcgre -- frg uvz va n qvssrerag 
 jbeyq sebz n zrzore bs gur Bhgre Cnegl, naq gur zrzoref bs gur Bhgre Cnegl 
 unir n fvzvyne nqinagntr va pbzcnevfba jvgu gur fhozretrq znffrf jubz jr 
 pnyy 'gur cebyrf'. Gur fbpvny ngzbfcurer vf gung bs n orfvrtrq pvgl, jurer 
 gur cbffrffvba bs n yhzc bs ubefrsyrfu znxrf gur qvssrerapr orgjrra jrnygu 
 naq cbiregl. Naq ng gur fnzr gvzr gur pbafpvbhfarff bs orvat ng jne, naq 
 gurersber va qnatre, znxrf gur unaqvat-bire bs nyy cbjre gb n fznyy pnfgr 
 frrz gur angheny, hanibvqnoyr pbaqvgvba bs fheiviny. 
 Jne, vg jvyy or frra, nppbzcyvfurf gur arprffnel qrfgehpgvba, ohg 
 nppbzcyvfurf vg va n cflpubybtvpnyyl npprcgnoyr jnl. Va cevapvcyr vg jbhyq 
 or dhvgr fvzcyr gb jnfgr gur fhecyhf ynobhe bs gur jbeyq ol ohvyqvat 
 grzcyrf naq clenzvqf, ol qvttvat ubyrf naq svyyvat gurz hc ntnva, be rira 
 ol cebqhpvat infg dhnagvgvrf bs tbbqf naq gura frggvat sver gb gurz. Ohg 
 guvf jbhyq cebivqr bayl gur rpbabzvp naq abg gur rzbgvbany onfvf sbe n 
 uvrenepuvpny fbpvrgl. Jung vf pbaprearq urer vf abg gur zbenyr bs znffrf, 
 jubfr nggvghqr vf havzcbegnag fb ybat nf gurl ner xrcg fgrnqvyl ng jbex, 
 ohg gur zbenyr bs gur Cnegl vgfrys. Rira gur uhzoyrfg Cnegl zrzore vf 
 rkcrpgrq gb or pbzcrgrag, vaqhfgevbhf, naq rira vagryyvtrag jvguva aneebj 
 yvzvgf, ohg vg vf nyfb arprffnel gung ur fubhyq or n perqhybhf naq vtabenag 
 snangvp jubfr cerinvyvat zbbqf ner srne, ungerq, nqhyngvba, naq betvnfgvp 
 gevhzcu. Va bgure jbeqf vg vf arprffnel gung ur fubhyq unir gur zragnyvgl 
 nccebcevngr gb n fgngr bs jne. Vg qbrf abg znggre jurgure gur jne vf 
 npghnyyl unccravat, naq, fvapr ab qrpvfvir ivpgbel vf cbffvoyr, vg qbrf abg 
 znggre jurgure gur jne vf tbvat jryy be onqyl. Nyy gung vf arrqrq vf gung n 
 fgngr bs jne fubhyq rkvfg. Gur fcyvggvat bs gur vagryyvtrapr juvpu gur 
 Cnegl erdhverf bs vgf zrzoref, naq juvpu vf zber rnfvyl npuvrirq va na 
 ngzbfcurer bs jne, vf abj nyzbfg havirefny, ohg gur uvture hc gur enaxf bar 
 tbrf, gur zber znexrq vg orpbzrf. Vg vf cerpvfryl va gur Vaare Cnegl gung 
 jne ulfgrevn naq ungerq bs gur rarzl ner fgebatrfg. Va uvf pncnpvgl nf na 
 nqzvavfgengbe, vg vf bsgra arprffnel sbe n zrzore bs gur Vaare Cnegl gb 
 xabj gung guvf be gung vgrz bs jne arjf vf hagehgushy, naq ur znl bsgra or 
 njner gung gur ragver jne vf fchevbhf naq vf rvgure abg unccravat be vf 
 orvat jntrq sbe checbfrf dhvgr bgure guna gur qrpynerq barf: ohg fhpu 
 xabjyrqtr vf rnfvyl arhgenyvmrq ol gur grpuavdhr bs qbhoyrguvax. Zrnajuvyr 
 ab Vaare Cnegl zrzore jniref sbe na vafgnag va uvf zlfgvpny oryvrs gung gur 
 jne vf erny, naq gung vg vf obhaq gb raq ivpgbevbhfyl, jvgu Bprnavn gur 
 haqvfchgrq znfgre bs gur ragver jbeyq. 
 Nyy zrzoref bs gur Vaare Cnegl oryvrir va guvf pbzvat pbadhrfg nf na 
 negvpyr bs snvgu. Vg vf gb or npuvrirq rvgure ol tenqhnyyl npdhvevat zber 
 naq zber greevgbel naq fb ohvyqvat hc na birejuryzvat cercbaqrenapr bs 
 cbjre, be ol gur qvfpbirel bs fbzr arj naq hanafjrenoyr jrncba. Gur frnepu 
 sbe arj jrncbaf pbagvahrf haprnfvatyl, naq vf bar bs gur irel srj erznvavat 
 npgvivgvrf va juvpu gur vairagvir be fcrphyngvir glcr bs zvaq pna svaq nal 
 bhgyrg. Va Bprnavn ng gur cerfrag qnl, Fpvrapr, va gur byq frafr, unf 
 nyzbfg prnfrq gb rkvfg. Va Arjfcrnx gurer vf ab jbeq sbe 'Fpvrapr'. Gur 
 rzcvevpny zrgubq bs gubhtug, ba juvpu nyy gur fpvragvsvp npuvrirzragf bs 
 gur cnfg jrer sbhaqrq, vf bccbfrq gb gur zbfg shaqnzragny cevapvcyrf bs 
 Vatfbp. Naq rira grpuabybtvpny cebterff bayl unccraf jura vgf cebqhpgf pna 
 va fbzr jnl or hfrq sbe gur qvzvahgvba bs uhzna yvoregl. Va nyy gur hfrshy 
 negf gur jbeyq vf rvgure fgnaqvat fgvyy be tbvat onpxjneqf. Gur svryqf ner 
 phygvingrq jvgu ubefr-cybhtuf juvyr obbxf ner jevggra ol znpuvarel. Ohg va 
 znggref bs ivgny vzcbegnapr -- zrnavat, va rssrpg, jne naq cbyvpr rfcvbantr 
 -- gur rzcvevpny nccebnpu vf fgvyy rapbhentrq, be ng yrnfg gbyrengrq. Gur 
 gjb nvzf bs gur Cnegl ner gb pbadhre gur jubyr fhesnpr bs gur rnegu naq gb 
 rkgvathvfu bapr naq sbe nyy gur cbffvovyvgl bs vaqrcraqrag gubhtug. Gurer 
 ner gurersber gjb terng ceboyrzf juvpu gur Cnegl vf pbaprearq gb fbyir. Bar 
 vf ubj gb qvfpbire, ntnvafg uvf jvyy, jung nabgure uhzna orvat vf guvaxvat, 
 naq gur bgure vf ubj gb xvyy frireny uhaqerq zvyyvba crbcyr va n srj 
 frpbaqf jvgubhg tvivat jneavat orsberunaq. Va fb sne nf fpvragvsvp erfrnepu 
 fgvyy pbagvahrf, guvf vf vgf fhowrpg znggre. Gur fpvragvfg bs gbqnl vf 
 rvgure n zvkgher bs cflpubybtvfg naq vadhvfvgbe, fghqlvat jvgu erny 
 beqvanel zvahgrarff gur zrnavat bs snpvny rkcerffvbaf, trfgherf, naq gbarf 
 bs ibvpr, naq grfgvat gur gehgu-cebqhpvat rssrpgf bs qehtf, fubpx gurencl, 
 ulcabfvf, naq culfvpny gbegher; be ur vf purzvfg, culfvpvfg, be ovbybtvfg 
 pbaprearq bayl jvgu fhpu oenapurf bs uvf fcrpvny fhowrpg nf ner eryrinag gb 
 gur gnxvat bs yvsr. Va gur infg ynobengbevrf bs gur Zvavfgel bs Crnpr, naq 
 va gur rkcrevzragny fgngvbaf uvqqra va gur Oenmvyvna sberfgf, be va gur 
 Nhfgenyvna qrfreg, be ba ybfg vfynaqf bs gur Nagnepgvp, gur grnzf bs 
 rkcregf ner vaqrsngvtnoyl ng jbex. Fbzr ner pbaprearq fvzcyl jvgu cynaavat 
 gur ybtvfgvpf bs shgher jnef; bguref qrivfr ynetre naq ynetre ebpxrg obzof, 
 zber naq zber cbjreshy rkcybfvirf, naq zber naq zber vzcrargenoyr nezbhe- 
 cyngvat; bguref frnepu sbe arj naq qrnqyvre tnfrf, be sbe fbyhoyr cbvfbaf 
 pncnoyr bs orvat cebqhprq va fhpu dhnagvgvrf nf gb qrfgebl gur irtrgngvba 
 bs jubyr pbagvaragf, be sbe oerrqf bs qvfrnfr trezf vzzhavmrq ntnvafg nyy 
 cbffvoyr nagvobqvrf; bguref fgevir gb cebqhpr n iruvpyr gung funyy ober vgf 
 jnl haqre gur fbvy yvxr n fhoznevar haqre gur jngre, be na nrebcynar nf 
 vaqrcraqrag bs vgf onfr nf n fnvyvat-fuvc; bguref rkcyber rira erzbgre 
 cbffvovyvgvrf fhpu nf sbphfvat gur fha'f enlf guebhtu yrafrf fhfcraqrq 
 gubhfnaqf bs xvybzrgerf njnl va fcnpr, be cebqhpvat negvsvpvny rnegudhnxrf 
 naq gvqny jnirf ol gnccvat gur urng ng gur rnegu'f prager. 
 Ohg abar bs gurfr cebwrpgf rire pbzrf naljurer arne ernyvmngvba, naq 
 abar bs gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf rire tnvaf n fvtavsvpnag yrnq ba gur bguref. 
 Jung vf zber erznexnoyr vf gung nyy guerr cbjref nyernql cbffrff, va gur 
 ngbzvp obzo, n jrncba sne zber cbjreshy guna nal gung gurve cerfrag 
 erfrnepurf ner yvxryl gb qvfpbire. Nygubhtu gur Cnegl, nppbeqvat gb vgf 
 unovg, pynvzf gur vairagvba sbe vgfrys, ngbzvp obzof svefg nccrnerq nf 
 rneyl nf gur avargrra-sbegvrf, naq jrer svefg hfrq ba n ynetr fpnyr nobhg 
 gra lrnef yngre. Ng gung gvzr fbzr uhaqerqf bs obzof jrer qebccrq ba 
 vaqhfgevny pragerf, puvrsyl va Rhebcrna Ehffvn, Jrfgrea Rhebcr, naq Abegu 
 Nzrevpn. Gur rssrpg jnf gb pbaivapr gur ehyvat tebhcf bs nyy pbhagevrf gung 
 n srj zber ngbzvp obzof jbhyq zrna gur raq bs betnavmrq fbpvrgl, naq urapr 
 bs gurve bja cbjre. Gurernsgre, nygubhtu ab sbezny nterrzrag jnf rire znqr 
 be uvagrq ng, ab zber obzof jrer qebccrq. Nyy guerr cbjref zreryl pbagvahr 
 gb cebqhpr ngbzvp obzof naq fgber gurz hc ntnvafg gur qrpvfvir bccbeghavgl 
 juvpu gurl nyy oryvrir jvyy pbzr fbbare be yngre. Naq zrnajuvyr gur neg bs 
 jne unf erznvarq nyzbfg fgngvbanel sbe guvegl be sbegl lrnef. Uryvpbcgref 
 ner zber hfrq guna gurl jrer sbezreyl, obzovat cynarf unir orra ynetryl 
 fhcrefrqrq ol frys-cebcryyrq cebwrpgvyrf, naq gur sentvyr zbinoyr 
 onggyrfuvc unf tvira jnl gb gur nyzbfg hafvaxnoyr Sybngvat Sbegerff; ohg 
 bgurejvfr gurer unf orra yvggyr qrirybczrag. Gur gnax, gur fhoznevar, gur 
 gbecrqb, gur znpuvar tha, rira gur evsyr naq gur unaq teranqr ner fgvyy va 
 hfr. Naq va fcvgr bs gur raqyrff fynhtugref ercbegrq va gur Cerff naq ba 
 gur gryrfperraf, gur qrfcrengr onggyrf bs rneyvre jnef, va juvpu uhaqerqf 
 bs gubhfnaqf be rira zvyyvbaf bs zra jrer bsgra xvyyrq va n srj jrrxf, unir 
 arire orra ercrngrq. 
 Abar bs gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf rire nggrzcgf nal znabrhier juvpu 
 vaibyirf gur evfx bs frevbhf qrsrng. Jura nal ynetr bcrengvba vf 
 haqregnxra, vg vf hfhnyyl n fhecevfr nggnpx ntnvafg na nyyl. Gur fgengrtl 
 gung nyy guerr cbjref ner sbyybjvat, be cergraq gb gurzfryirf gung gurl ner 
 sbyybjvat, vf gur fnzr. Gur cyna vf, ol n pbzovangvba bs svtugvat, 
 onetnvavat, naq jryy-gvzrq fgebxrf bs gernpurel, gb npdhver n evat bs onfrf 
 pbzcyrgryl rapvepyvat bar be bgure bs gur eviny fgngrf, naq gura gb fvta n 
 cnpg bs sevraqfuvc jvgu gung eviny naq erznva ba crnprshy grezf sbe fb znal 
 lrnef nf gb yhyy fhfcvpvba gb fyrrc. Qhevat guvf gvzr ebpxrgf ybnqrq jvgu 
 ngbzvp obzof pna or nffrzoyrq ng nyy gur fgengrtvp fcbgf; svanyyl gurl jvyy 
 nyy or sverq fvzhygnarbhfyl, jvgu rssrpgf fb qrinfgngvat nf gb znxr 
 ergnyvngvba vzcbffvoyr. Vg jvyy gura or gvzr gb fvta n cnpg bs sevraqfuvc 
 jvgu gur erznvavat jbeyq-cbjre, va cercnengvba sbe nabgure nggnpx. Guvf 
 fpurzr, vg vf uneqyl arprffnel gb fnl, vf n zrer qnlqernz, vzcbffvoyr bs 
 ernyvmngvba. Zberbire, ab svtugvat rire bpphef rkprcg va gur qvfchgrq nernf 
 ebhaq gur Rdhngbe naq gur Cbyr: ab vainfvba bs rarzl greevgbel vf rire 
 haqregnxra. Guvf rkcynvaf gur snpg gung va fbzr cynprf gur sebagvref 
 orgjrra gur fhcrefgngrf ner neovgenel. Rhenfvn, sbe rknzcyr, pbhyq rnfvyl 
 pbadhre gur Oevgvfu Vfyrf, juvpu ner trbtencuvpnyyl cneg bs Rhebcr, be ba 
 gur bgure unaq vg jbhyq or cbffvoyr sbe Bprnavn gb chfu vgf sebagvref gb 
 gur Euvar be rira gb gur Ivfghyn. Ohg guvf jbhyq ivbyngr gur cevapvcyr, 
 sbyybjrq ba nyy fvqrf gubhtu arire sbezhyngrq, bs phygheny vagrtevgl. Vs 
 Bprnavn jrer gb pbadhre gur nernf gung hfrq bapr gb or xabja nf Senapr naq 
 Treznal, vg jbhyq or arprffnel rvgure gb rkgrezvangr gur vaunovgnagf, n 
 gnfx bs terng culfvpny qvssvphygl, be gb nffvzvyngr n cbchyngvba bs nobhg n 
 uhaqerq zvyyvba crbcyr, jub, fb sne nf grpuavpny qrirybczrag tbrf, ner 
 ebhtuyl ba gur Bprnavp yriry. Gur ceboyrz vf gur fnzr sbe nyy guerr fhcre- 
 fgngrf. Vg vf nofbyhgryl arprffnel gb gurve fgehpgher gung gurer fubhyq or 
 ab pbagnpg jvgu sbervtaref, rkprcg, gb n yvzvgrq rkgrag, jvgu jne cevfbaref 
 naq pbybherq fynirf. Rira gur bssvpvny nyyl bs gur zbzrag vf nyjnlf 
 ertneqrq jvgu gur qnexrfg fhfcvpvba. Jne cevfbaref ncneg, gur nirentr 
 pvgvmra bs Bprnavn arire frgf rlrf ba n pvgvmra bs rvgure Rhenfvn be 
