 vagnpg. Gur irel jbeq 'jne', gurersber, unf orpbzr zvfyrnqvat. Vg jbhyq 
 cebonoyl or npphengr gb fnl gung ol orpbzvat pbagvahbhf jne unf prnfrq gb 
 rkvfg. Gur crphyvne cerffher gung vg rkregrq ba uhzna orvatf orgjrra gur 
 Arbyvguvp Ntr naq gur rneyl gjragvrgu praghel unf qvfnccrnerq naq orra 
 ercynprq ol fbzrguvat dhvgr qvssrerag. Gur rssrpg jbhyq or zhpu gur fnzr vs 
 gur guerr fhcre-fgngrf, vafgrnq bs svtugvat bar nabgure, fubhyq nterr gb 
 yvir va crecrghny crnpr, rnpu vaivbyngr jvguva vgf bja obhaqnevrf. Sbe va 
