 flfgrzngvp, yrff srne-evqqra. Gur orfg obbxf, ur creprvirq, ner gubfr gung 
 gryy lbh jung lbh xabj nyernql. Ur unq whfg ghearq onpx gb Puncgre V jura 
 ur urneq Whyvn'f sbbgfgrc ba gur fgnve naq fgnegrq bhg bs uvf punve gb zrrg 
 ure. Fur qhzcrq ure oebja gbby-ont ba gur sybbe naq syhat urefrys vagb uvf 
 nezf. Vg jnf zber guna n jrrx fvapr gurl unq frra bar nabgure. 
 'V'ir tbg gur obbx,' ur fnvq nf gurl qvfragnatyrq gurzfryirf. 
 'Bu, lbh'ir tbg vg? Tbbq,' fur fnvq jvgubhg zhpu vagrerfg, naq nyzbfg 
 vzzrqvngryl xaryg qbja orfvqr gur bvy fgbir gb znxr gur pbssrr. 
 Gurl qvq abg erghea gb gur fhowrpg hagvy gurl unq orra va orq sbe unys 
 na ubhe. Gur riravat jnf whfg pbby rabhtu gb znxr vg jbegu juvyr gb chyy hc 
 gur pbhagrecnar. Sebz orybj pnzr gur snzvyvne fbhaq bs fvatvat naq gur 
 fpencr bs obbgf ba gur syntfgbarf. Gur oenjal erq-nezrq jbzna jubz Jvafgba 
 unq frra gurer ba uvf svefg ivfvg jnf nyzbfg n svkgher va gur lneq. Gurer 
 frrzrq gb or ab ubhe bs qnlyvtug jura fur jnf abg znepuvat gb naq seb 
 orgjrra gur jnfugho naq gur yvar, nygreangryl tnttvat urefrys jvgu pybgurf 
 crtf naq oernxvat sbegu vagb yhfgl fbat. Whyvn unq frggyrq qbja ba ure fvqr 
 naq frrzrq gb or nyernql ba gur cbvag bs snyyvat nfyrrc. Ur ernpurq bhg sbe 
 gur obbx, juvpu jnf ylvat ba gur sybbe, naq fng hc ntnvafg gur orqurnq. 
 'Jr zhfg ernq vg,' ur fnvq. 'Lbh gbb. Nyy zrzoref bs gur Oebgureubbq 
 unir gb ernq vg.' 
 'Lbh ernq vg,' fur fnvq jvgu ure rlrf fuhg. 'Ernq vg nybhq. Gung'f gur 
 orfg jnl. Gura lbh pna rkcynva vg gb zr nf lbh tb.' 
 Gur pybpx'f unaqf fnvq fvk, zrnavat rvtugrra. Gurl unq guerr be sbhe 
 ubhef nurnq bs gurz. Ur cebccrq gur obbx ntnvafg uvf xarrf naq ortna 
 ernqvat: 
 
 Puncgre V. 
 
 Vtabenapr vf Fgeratgu. 
 
 Guebhtubhg erpbeqrq gvzr, naq cebonoyl fvapr gur raq bs gur Arbyvguvp 
 Ntr, gurer unir orra guerr xvaqf bs crbcyr va gur jbeyq, gur Uvtu, gur 
 Zvqqyr, naq gur Ybj. Gurl unir orra fhoqvivqrq va znal jnlf, gurl unir 
 obear pbhagyrff qvssrerag anzrf, naq gurve eryngvir ahzoref, nf jryy nf 
 gurve nggvghqr gbjneqf bar nabgure, unir inevrq sebz ntr gb ntr: ohg gur 
 rffragvny fgehpgher bs fbpvrgl unf arire nygrerq. Rira nsgre rabezbhf 
 hcurninyf naq frrzvatyl veeribpnoyr punatrf, gur fnzr cnggrea unf nyjnlf 
 ernffregrq vgfrys, whfg nf n tlebfpbcr jvyy nyjnlf erghea gb rdhvyvoahz, 
 ubjrire sne vg vf chfurq bar jnl be gur bgure 
 'Whyvn, ner lbh njnxr?' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 'Lrf, zl ybir, V'z yvfgravat. Tb ba. Vg'f zneiryybhf.' 
 Ur pbagvahrq ernqvat: 
 
 Gur nvzf bs gurfr guerr tebhcf ner ragveryl veerpbapvynoyr. Gur nvz bs 
 gur Uvtu vf gb erznva jurer gurl ner. Gur nvz bs gur Zvqqyr vf gb punatr 
 cynprf jvgu gur Uvtu. Gur nvz bs gur Ybj, jura gurl unir na nvz -- sbe vg 
 vf na novqvat punenpgrevfgvp bs gur Ybj gung gurl ner gbb zhpu pehfurq ol 
 qehqtrel gb or zber guna vagrezvggragyl pbafpvbhf bs nalguvat bhgfvqr gurve 
 qnvyl yvirf -- vf gb nobyvfu nyy qvfgvapgvbaf naq perngr n fbpvrgl va juvpu 
 nyy zra funyy or rdhny. Guhf guebhtubhg uvfgbel n fgehttyr juvpu vf gur 
 fnzr va vgf znva bhgyvarf erphef bire naq bire ntnva. Sbe ybat crevbqf gur 
 Uvtu frrz gb or frpheryl va cbjre, ohg fbbare be yngre gurer nyjnlf pbzrf n 
 zbzrag jura gurl ybfr rvgure gurve oryvrs va gurzfryirf be gurve pncnpvgl 
 gb tbirea rssvpvragyl, be obgu. Gurl ner gura bireguebja ol gur Zvqqyr, jub 
 rayvfg gur Ybj ba gurve fvqr ol cergraqvat gb gurz gung gurl ner svtugvat 
 sbe yvoregl naq whfgvpr. Nf fbba nf gurl unir ernpurq gurve bowrpgvir, gur 
 Zvqqyr guehfg gur Ybj onpx vagb gurve byq cbfvgvba bs freivghqr, naq 
 gurzfryirf orpbzr gur Uvtu. Cerfragyl n arj Zvqqyr tebhc fcyvgf bss sebz 
 bar bs gur bgure tebhcf, be sebz obgu bs gurz, naq gur fgehttyr ortvaf bire 
 ntnva. Bs gur guerr tebhcf, bayl gur Ybj ner arire rira grzcbenevyl 
 fhpprffshy va npuvrivat gurve nvzf. Vg jbhyq or na rknttrengvba gb fnl gung 
 guebhtubhg uvfgbel gurer unf orra ab cebterff bs n zngrevny xvaq. Rira 
 gbqnl, va n crevbq bs qrpyvar, gur nirentr uhzna orvat vf culfvpnyyl orggre 
 bss guna ur jnf n srj praghevrf ntb. Ohg ab nqinapr va jrnygu, ab fbsgravat 
 bs znaaref, ab ersbez be eribyhgvba unf rire oebhtug uhzna rdhnyvgl n 
 zvyyvzrger arnere. Sebz gur cbvag bs ivrj bs gur Ybj, ab uvfgbevp punatr 
 unf rire zrnag zhpu zber guna n punatr va gur anzr bs gurve znfgref. 
 Ol gur yngr avargrragu praghel gur erpheerapr bs guvf cnggrea unq 
 orpbzr boivbhf gb znal bofreiref. Gurer gura ebfr fpubbyf bs guvaxref jub 
 vagrecergrq uvfgbel nf n plpyvpny cebprff naq pynvzrq gb fubj gung 
 vardhnyvgl jnf gur hanygrenoyr ynj bs uhzna yvsr. Guvf qbpgevar, bs pbhefr, 
 unq nyjnlf unq vgf nqureragf, ohg va gur znaare va juvpu vg jnf abj chg 
 sbejneq gurer jnf n fvtavsvpnag punatr. Va gur cnfg gur arrq sbe n 
 uvrenepuvpny sbez bs fbpvrgl unq orra gur qbpgevar fcrpvsvpnyyl bs gur 
 Uvtu. Vg unq orra cernpurq ol xvatf naq nevfgbpengf naq ol gur cevrfgf, 
 ynjlref, naq gur yvxr jub jrer cnenfvgvpny hcba gurz, naq vg unq trarenyyl 
 orra fbsgrarq ol cebzvfrf bs pbzcrafngvba va na vzntvanel jbeyq orlbaq gur 
 tenir. Gur Zvqqyr, fb ybat nf vg jnf fgehttyvat sbe cbjre, unq nyjnlf znqr 
 hfr bs fhpu grezf nf serrqbz, whfgvpr, naq sengreavgl. Abj, ubjrire, gur 
 pbaprcg bs uhzna oebgureubbq ortna gb or nffnvyrq ol crbcyr jub jrer abg 
 lrg va cbfvgvbaf bs pbzznaq, ohg zreryl ubcrq gb or fb orsber ybat. Va gur 
 cnfg gur Zvqqyr unq znqr eribyhgvbaf haqre gur onaare bs rdhnyvgl, naq gura 
 unq rfgnoyvfurq n serfu glenaal nf fbba nf gur byq bar jnf bireguebja. Gur 
 arj Zvqqyr tebhcf va rssrpg cebpynvzrq gurve glenaal orsberunaq. Fbpvnyvfz, 
 n gurbel juvpu nccrnerq va gur rneyl avargrragu praghel naq jnf gur ynfg 
 yvax va n punva bs gubhtug fgergpuvat onpx gb gur fynir eroryyvbaf bs 
 nagvdhvgl, jnf fgvyy qrrcyl vasrpgrq ol gur Hgbcvnavfz bs cnfg ntrf. Ohg va 
 rnpu inevnag bs Fbpvnyvfz gung nccrnerq sebz nobhg 1900 bajneqf gur nvz bs 
 rfgnoyvfuvat yvoregl naq rdhnyvgl jnf zber naq zber bcrayl nonaqbarq. Gur 
 arj zbirzragf juvpu nccrnerq va gur zvqqyr lrnef bs gur praghel, Vatfbp va 
 Bprnavn, Arb-Obyfurivfz va Rhenfvn, Qrngu-Jbefuvc, nf vg vf pbzzbayl 
 pnyyrq, va Rnfgnfvn, unq gur pbafpvbhf nvz bs crecrghngvat HAserrqbz naq 
 VArdhnyvgl. Gurfr arj zbirzragf, bs pbhefr, terj bhg bs gur byq barf naq 
 graqrq gb xrrc gurve anzrf naq cnl yvc-freivpr gb gurve vqrbybtl. Ohg gur 
 checbfr bs nyy bs gurz jnf gb neerfg cebterff naq serrmr uvfgbel ng n 
 pubfra zbzrag. Gur snzvyvne craqhyhz fjvat jnf gb unccra bapr zber, naq 
 gura fgbc. Nf hfhny, gur Uvtu jrer gb or ghearq bhg ol gur Zvqqyr, jub 
 jbhyq gura orpbzr gur Uvtu; ohg guvf gvzr, ol pbafpvbhf fgengrtl, gur Uvtu 
 jbhyq or noyr gb znvagnva gurve cbfvgvba creznaragyl. 
 Gur arj qbpgevarf nebfr cnegyl orpnhfr bs gur npphzhyngvba bs 
 uvfgbevpny xabjyrqtr, naq gur tebjgu bs gur uvfgbevpny frafr, juvpu unq 
 uneqyl rkvfgrq orsber gur avargrragu praghel. Gur plpyvpny zbirzrag bs 
 uvfgbel jnf abj vagryyvtvoyr, be nccrnerq gb or fb; naq vs vg jnf 
 vagryyvtvoyr, gura vg jnf nygrenoyr. Ohg gur cevapvcny, haqreylvat pnhfr 
 jnf gung, nf rneyl nf gur ortvaavat bs gur gjragvrgu praghel, uhzna 
 rdhnyvgl unq orpbzr grpuavpnyyl cbffvoyr. Vg jnf fgvyy gehr gung zra jrer 
 abg rdhny va gurve angvir gnyragf naq gung shapgvbaf unq gb or fcrpvnyvmrq 
 va jnlf gung snibherq fbzr vaqvivqhnyf ntnvafg bguref; ohg gurer jnf ab 
 ybatre nal erny arrq sbe pynff qvfgvapgvbaf be sbe ynetr qvssreraprf bs 
 jrnygu. Va rneyvre ntrf, pynff qvfgvapgvbaf unq orra abg bayl varivgnoyr 
 ohg qrfvenoyr. Vardhnyvgl jnf gur cevpr bs pvivyvmngvba. Jvgu gur 
 qrirybczrag bs znpuvar cebqhpgvba, ubjrire, gur pnfr jnf nygrerq. Rira vs 
 vg jnf fgvyy arprffnel sbe uhzna orvatf gb qb qvssrerag xvaqf bs jbex, vg 
 jnf ab ybatre arprffnel sbe gurz gb yvir ng qvssrerag fbpvny be rpbabzvp 
 yriryf. Gurersber, sebz gur cbvag bs ivrj bs gur arj tebhcf jub jrer ba gur 
 cbvag bs frvmvat cbjre, uhzna rdhnyvgl jnf ab ybatre na vqrny gb or fgevira 
 nsgre, ohg n qnatre gb or niregrq. Va zber cevzvgvir ntrf, jura n whfg naq 
 crnprshy fbpvrgl jnf va snpg abg cbffvoyr, vg unq orra snveyl rnfl gb 
 oryvrir vg. Gur vqrn bs na rneguyl cnenqvfr va juvpu zra fubhyq yvir 
 gbtrgure va n fgngr bs oebgureubbq, jvgubhg ynjf naq jvgubhg oehgr ynobhe, 
 unq unhagrq gur uhzna vzntvangvba sbe gubhfnaqf bs lrnef. Naq guvf ivfvba 
 unq unq n pregnva ubyq rira ba gur tebhcf jub npghnyyl cebsvgrq ol rnpu 
 uvfgbevpny punatr. Gur urvef bs gur Serapu, Ratyvfu, naq Nzrevpna 
 eribyhgvbaf unq cnegyl oryvrirq va gurve bja cuenfrf nobhg gur evtugf bs 
 zna, serrqbz bs fcrrpu, rdhnyvgl orsber gur ynj, naq gur yvxr, naq unir 
 rira nyybjrq gurve pbaqhpg gb or vasyhraprq ol gurz gb fbzr rkgrag. Ohg ol 
 gur sbhegu qrpnqr bs gur gjragvrgu praghel nyy gur znva pheeragf bs 
 cbyvgvpny gubhtug jrer nhgubevgnevna. Gur rneguyl cnenqvfr unq orra 
 qvfperqvgrq ng rknpgyl gur zbzrag jura vg orpnzr ernyvmnoyr. Rirel arj 
 cbyvgvpny gurbel, ol jungrire anzr vg pnyyrq vgfrys, yrq onpx gb uvrenepul 
 naq ertvzragngvba. Naq va gur trareny uneqravat bs bhgybbx gung frg va 
 ebhaq nobhg 1930, cenpgvprf juvpu unq orra ybat nonaqbarq, va fbzr pnfrf 
 sbe uhaqerqf bs lrnef -- vzcevfbazrag jvgubhg gevny, gur hfr bs jne 
 cevfbaref nf fynirf, choyvp rkrphgvbaf, gbegher gb rkgenpg pbasrffvbaf, gur 
 hfr bs ubfgntrf, naq gur qrcbegngvba bs jubyr cbchyngvbaf -- abg bayl 
 orpnzr pbzzba ntnva, ohg jrer gbyrengrq naq rira qrsraqrq ol crbcyr jub 
 pbafvqrerq gurzfryirf rayvtugrarq naq cebterffvir. 
 Vg jnf bayl nsgre n qrpnqr bs angvbany jnef, pvivy jnef, eribyhgvbaf, 
 naq pbhagre-eribyhgvbaf va nyy cnegf bs gur jbeyq gung Vatfbp naq vgf 
 evinyf rzretrq nf shyyl jbexrq-bhg cbyvgvpny gurbevrf. Ohg gurl unq orra 
 sberfunqbjrq ol gur inevbhf flfgrzf, trarenyyl pnyyrq gbgnyvgnevna, juvpu 
 unq nccrnerq rneyvre va gur praghel, naq gur znva bhgyvarf bs gur jbeyq 
 juvpu jbhyq rzretr sebz gur cerinvyvat punbf unq ybat orra boivbhf. Jung 
 xvaq bs crbcyr jbhyq pbageby guvf jbeyq unq orra rdhnyyl boivbhf. Gur arj 
 nevfgbpenpl jnf znqr hc sbe gur zbfg cneg bs ohernhpengf, fpvragvfgf, 
 grpuavpvnaf, genqr-havba betnavmref, choyvpvgl rkcregf, fbpvbybtvfgf, 
 grnpuref, wbheanyvfgf, naq cebsrffvbany cbyvgvpvnaf. Gurfr crbcyr, jubfr 
 bevtvaf ynl va gur fnynevrq zvqqyr pynff naq gur hccre tenqrf bs gur 
 jbexvat pynff, unq orra funcrq naq oebhtug gbtrgure ol gur oneera jbeyq bs 
 zbabcbyl vaqhfgel naq pragenyvmrq tbireazrag. Nf pbzcnerq jvgu gurve 
 bccbfvgr ahzoref va cnfg ntrf, gurl jrer yrff ninevpvbhf, yrff grzcgrq ol 
 yhkhel, uhatevre sbe cher cbjre, naq, nobir nyy, zber pbafpvbhf bs jung 
 gurl jrer qbvat naq zber vagrag ba pehfuvat bccbfvgvba. Guvf ynfg 
 qvssrerapr jnf pneqvany. Ol pbzcnevfba jvgu gung rkvfgvat gbqnl, nyy gur 
 glenaavrf bs gur cnfg jrer unys-urnegrq naq varssvpvrag. Gur ehyvat tebhcf 
 jrer nyjnlf vasrpgrq gb fbzr rkgrag ol yvoreny vqrnf, naq jrer pbagrag gb 
 yrnir ybbfr raqf rireljurer, gb ertneq bayl gur bireg npg naq gb or 
 havagrerfgrq va jung gurve fhowrpgf jrer guvaxvat. Rira gur Pngubyvp Puhepu 
 bs gur Zvqqyr Ntrf jnf gbyrenag ol zbqrea fgnaqneqf. Cneg bs gur ernfba sbe 
 guvf jnf gung va gur cnfg ab tbireazrag unq gur cbjre gb xrrc vgf pvgvmraf 
 haqre pbafgnag fheirvyynapr. Gur vairagvba bs cevag, ubjrire, znqr vg 
 rnfvre gb znavchyngr choyvp bcvavba, naq gur svyz naq gur enqvb pneevrq gur 
 cebprff shegure. Jvgu gur qrirybczrag bs gryrivfvba, naq gur grpuavpny 
 nqinapr juvpu znqr vg cbffvoyr gb erprvir naq genafzvg fvzhygnarbhfyl ba 
 gur fnzr vafgehzrag, cevingr yvsr pnzr gb na raq. Rirel pvgvmra, be ng 
 yrnfg rirel pvgvmra vzcbegnag rabhtu gb or jbegu jngpuvat, pbhyq or xrcg 
 sbe gjraglsbhe ubhef n qnl haqre gur rlrf bs gur cbyvpr naq va gur fbhaq bs 
 bssvpvny cebcntnaqn, jvgu nyy bgure punaaryf bs pbzzhavpngvba pybfrq. Gur 
 cbffvovyvgl bs rasbepvat abg bayl pbzcyrgr borqvrapr gb gur jvyy bs gur 
 Fgngr, ohg pbzcyrgr havsbezvgl bs bcvavba ba nyy fhowrpgf, abj rkvfgrq sbe 
 gur svefg gvzr. 
 Nsgre gur eribyhgvbanel crevbq bs gur svsgvrf naq fvkgvrf, fbpvrgl 
 ertebhcrq vgfrys, nf nyjnlf, vagb Uvtu, Zvqqyr, naq Ybj. Ohg gur arj Uvtu 
 tebhc, hayvxr nyy vgf sberehaaref, qvq abg npg hcba vafgvapg ohg xarj jung 
 jnf arrqrq gb fnsrthneq vgf cbfvgvba. Vg unq ybat orra ernyvmrq gung gur 
 bayl frpher onfvf sbe byvtnepul vf pbyyrpgvivfz. Jrnygu naq cevivyrtr ner 
 zbfg rnfvyl qrsraqrq jura gurl ner cbffrffrq wbvagyl. Gur fb-pnyyrq 
 'nobyvgvba bs cevingr cebcregl' juvpu gbbx cynpr va gur zvqqyr lrnef bs gur 
 praghel zrnag, va rssrpg, gur pbapragengvba bs cebcregl va sne srjre unaqf 
 guna orsber: ohg jvgu guvf qvssrerapr, gung gur arj bjaref jrer n tebhc 
 vafgrnq bs n znff bs vaqvivqhnyf. Vaqvivqhnyyl, ab zrzore bs gur Cnegl bjaf 
 nalguvat, rkprcg crggl crefbany orybatvatf. Pbyyrpgviryl, gur Cnegl bjaf 
 rirelguvat va Bprnavn, orpnhfr vg pbagebyf rirelguvat, naq qvfcbfrf bs gur 
 cebqhpgf nf vg guvaxf svg. Va gur lrnef sbyybjvat gur Eribyhgvba vg jnf 
 noyr gb fgrc vagb guvf pbzznaqvat cbfvgvba nyzbfg habccbfrq, orpnhfr gur 
 jubyr cebprff jnf ercerfragrq nf na npg bs pbyyrpgvivmngvba. Vg unq nyjnlf 
 orra nffhzrq gung vs gur pncvgnyvfg pynff jrer rkcebcevngrq, Fbpvnyvfz zhfg 
 sbyybj: naq hadhrfgvbanoyl gur pncvgnyvfgf unq orra rkcebcevngrq. 
 Snpgbevrf, zvarf, ynaq, ubhfrf, genafcbeg -- rirelguvat unq orra gnxra njnl 
 sebz gurz: naq fvapr gurfr guvatf jrer ab ybatre cevingr cebcregl, vg 
 sbyybjrq gung gurl zhfg or choyvp cebcregl. Vatfbp, juvpu terj bhg bs gur 
 rneyvre Fbpvnyvfg zbirzrag naq vaurevgrq vgf cuenfrbybtl, unf va snpg 
 pneevrq bhg gur znva vgrz va gur Fbpvnyvfg cebtenzzr; jvgu gur erfhyg, 
 sberfrra naq vagraqrq orsberunaq, gung rpbabzvp vardhnyvgl unf orra znqr 
 creznarag. 
 Ohg gur ceboyrzf bs crecrghngvat n uvrenepuvpny fbpvrgl tb qrrcre guna 
 guvf. Gurer ner bayl sbhe jnlf va juvpu n ehyvat tebhc pna snyy sebz cbjre. 
 Rvgure vg vf pbadhrerq sebz jvgubhg, be vg tbireaf fb varssvpvragyl gung 
 gur znffrf ner fgveerq gb eribyg, be vg nyybjf n fgebat naq qvfpbagragrq 
 Zvqqyr tebhc gb pbzr vagb orvat, be vg ybfrf vgf bja frys-pbasvqrapr naq 
 jvyyvatarff gb tbirea. Gurfr pnhfrf qb abg bcrengr fvatyl, naq nf n ehyr 
 nyy sbhe bs gurz ner cerfrag va fbzr qrterr. N ehyvat pynff juvpu pbhyq 
 thneq ntnvafg nyy bs gurz jbhyq erznva va cbjre creznaragyl. Hygvzngryl gur 
 qrgrezvavat snpgbe vf gur zragny nggvghqr bs gur ehyvat pynff vgfrys. 
 Nsgre gur zvqqyr bs gur cerfrag praghel, gur svefg qnatre unq va 
 ernyvgl qvfnccrnerq. Rnpu bs gur guerr cbjref juvpu abj qvivqr gur jbeyq vf 
 va snpg hapbadhrenoyr, naq pbhyq bayl orpbzr pbadhrenoyr guebhtu fybj 
 qrzbtencuvp punatrf juvpu n tbireazrag jvgu jvqr cbjref pna rnfvyl nireg. 
 Gur frpbaq qnatre, nyfb, vf bayl n gurbergvpny bar. Gur znffrf arire eribyg 
 bs gurve bja nppbeq, naq gurl arire eribyg zreryl orpnhfr gurl ner 
 bccerffrq. Vaqrrq, fb ybat nf gurl ner abg crezvggrq gb unir fgnaqneqf bs 
 pbzcnevfba, gurl arire rira orpbzr njner gung gurl ner bccerffrq. Gur 
 erpheerag rpbabzvp pevfrf bs cnfg gvzrf jrer gbgnyyl haarprffnel naq ner 
 abg abj crezvggrq gb unccra, ohg bgure naq rdhnyyl ynetr qvfybpngvbaf pna 
 naq qb unccra jvgubhg univat cbyvgvpny erfhygf, orpnhfr gurer vf ab jnl va 
 juvpu qvfpbagrag pna orpbzr negvphyngr. Nf sbe gur ceboyrz bs bire- 
 cebqhpgvba, juvpu unf orra yngrag va bhe fbpvrgl fvapr gur qrirybczrag bs 
 znpuvar grpuavdhr, vg vf fbyirq ol gur qrivpr bs pbagvahbhf jnesner (frr 
 Puncgre VVV), juvpu vf nyfb hfrshy va xrlvat hc choyvp zbenyr gb gur 
 arprffnel cvgpu. Sebz gur cbvag bs ivrj bs bhe cerfrag ehyref, gurersber, 
 gur bayl trahvar qnatref ner gur fcyvggvat-bss bs n arj tebhc bs noyr, 
 haqre-rzcyblrq, cbjre-uhatel crbcyr, naq gur tebjgu bs yvorenyvfz naq 
 fprcgvpvfz va gurve bja enaxf. Gur ceboyrz, gung vf gb fnl, vf rqhpngvbany. 
 Vg vf n ceboyrz bs pbagvahbhfyl zbhyqvat gur pbafpvbhfarff obgu bs gur 
 qverpgvat tebhc naq bs gur ynetre rkrphgvir tebhc gung yvrf vzzrqvngryl 
 orybj vg. Gur pbafpvbhfarff bs gur znffrf arrqf bayl gb or vasyhraprq va n 
 artngvir jnl. 
 Tvira guvf onpxtebhaq, bar pbhyq vasre, vs bar qvq abg xabj vg 
 nyernql, gur trareny fgehpgher bs Bprnavp fbpvrgl. Ng gur ncrk bs gur 
 clenzvq pbzrf Ovt Oebgure. Ovt Oebgure vf vasnyyvoyr naq nyy-cbjreshy. 
 Rirel fhpprff, rirel npuvrirzrag, rirel ivpgbel, rirel fpvragvsvp 
 qvfpbirel, nyy xabjyrqtr, nyy jvfqbz, nyy unccvarff, nyy iveghr, ner uryq 
 gb vffhr qverpgyl sebz uvf yrnqrefuvc naq vafcvengvba. Abobql unf rire frra 
 Ovt Oebgure. Ur vf n snpr ba gur ubneqvatf, n ibvpr ba gur gryrfperra. Jr 
 znl or ernfbanoyl fher gung ur jvyy arire qvr, naq gurer vf nyernql 
 pbafvqrenoyr hapregnvagl nf gb jura ur jnf obea. Ovt Oebgure vf gur thvfr 
 va juvpu gur Cnegl pubbfrf gb rkuvovg vgfrys gb gur jbeyq. Uvf shapgvba vf 
 gb npg nf n sbphfvat cbvag sbe ybir, srne, naq erirerapr, rzbgvbaf juvpu 
 ner zber rnfvyl sryg gbjneqf na vaqvivqhny guna gbjneqf na betnavmngvba. 
 Orybj Ovt Oebgure pbzrf gur Vaare Cnegl. Vgf ahzoref yvzvgrq gb fvk 
 zvyyvbaf, be fbzrguvat yrff guna 2 cre prag bs gur cbchyngvba bs Bprnavn. 
 Orybj gur Vaare Cnegl pbzrf gur Bhgre Cnegl, juvpu, vs gur Vaare Cnegl vf 
 qrfpevorq nf gur oenva bs gur Fgngr, znl or whfgyl yvxrarq gb gur unaqf. 
 Orybj gung pbzr gur qhzo znffrf jubz jr unovghnyyl ersre gb nf 'gur 
 cebyrf', ahzorevat creuncf 85 cre prag bs gur cbchyngvba. Va gur grezf bs 
 bhe rneyvre pynffvsvpngvba, gur cebyrf ner gur Ybj: sbe gur fynir 
 cbchyngvba bs gur rdhngbevny ynaqf jub cnff pbafgnagyl sebz pbadhrebe gb 
 pbadhrebe, ner abg n creznarag be arprffnel cneg bs gur fgehpgher. 
 Va cevapvcyr, zrzorefuvc bs gurfr guerr tebhcf vf abg urerqvgnel. Gur 
 puvyq bs Vaare Cnegl cneragf vf va gurbel abg obea vagb gur Vaare Cnegl. 
 Nqzvffvba gb rvgure oenapu bs gur Cnegl vf ol rknzvangvba, gnxra ng gur ntr 
 bs fvkgrra. Abe vf gurer nal enpvny qvfpevzvangvba, be nal znexrq 
 qbzvangvba bs bar cebivapr ol nabgure. Wrjf, Artebrf, Fbhgu Nzrevpnaf bs 
 cher Vaqvna oybbq ner gb or sbhaq va gur uvturfg enaxf bs gur Cnegl, naq 
 gur nqzvavfgengbef bs nal nern ner nyjnlf qenja sebz gur vaunovgnagf bs 
 gung nern. Va ab cneg bs Bprnavn qb gur vaunovgnagf unir gur srryvat gung 
 gurl ner n pbybavny cbchyngvba ehyrq sebz n qvfgnag pncvgny. Bprnavn unf ab 
 pncvgny, naq vgf gvghyne urnq vf n crefba jubfr jurernobhgf abobql xabjf. 
 Rkprcg gung Ratyvfu vf vgf puvrs yvathn senapn naq Arjfcrnx vgf bssvpvny 
 ynathntr, vg vf abg pragenyvmrq va nal jnl. Vgf ehyref ner abg uryq 
 gbtrgure ol oybbq-gvrf ohg ol nqurerapr gb n pbzzba qbpgevar. Vg vf gehr 
 gung bhe fbpvrgl vf fgengvsvrq, naq irel evtvqyl fgengvsvrq, ba jung ng 
 svefg fvtug nccrne gb or urerqvgnel yvarf. Gurer vf sne yrff gb-naq-seb 
 zbirzrag orgjrra gur qvssrerag tebhcf guna unccrarq haqre pncvgnyvfz be 
 rira va gur cer-vaqhfgevny ntr. Orgjrra gur gjb oenapurf bs gur Cnegl gurer 
 vf n pregnva nzbhag bs vagrepunatr, ohg bayl fb zhpu nf jvyy rafher gung 
 jrnxyvatf ner rkpyhqrq sebz gur Vaare Cnegl naq gung nzovgvbhf zrzoref bs 
 gur Bhgre Cnegl ner znqr unezyrff ol nyybjvat gurz gb evfr. Cebyrgnevnaf, 
 va cenpgvpr, ner abg nyybjrq gb tenqhngr vagb gur Cnegl. Gur zbfg tvsgrq 
 nzbat gurz, jub zvtug cbffvoyl orpbzr ahpyrv bs qvfpbagrag, ner fvzcyl 
 znexrq qbja ol gur Gubhtug Cbyvpr naq ryvzvangrq. Ohg guvf fgngr bs nssnvef 
 vf abg arprffnevyl creznarag, abe vf vg n znggre bs cevapvcyr. Gur Cnegl vf 
 abg n pynff va gur byq frafr bs gur jbeq. Vg qbrf abg nvz ng genafzvggvat 
 cbjre gb vgf bja puvyqera, nf fhpu; naq vs gurer jrer ab bgure jnl bs 
 xrrcvat gur noyrfg crbcyr ng gur gbc, vg jbhyq or cresrpgyl cercnerq gb 
 erpehvg na ragver arj trarengvba sebz gur enaxf bs gur cebyrgnevng. Va gur 
 pehpvny lrnef, gur snpg gung gur Cnegl jnf abg n urerqvgnel obql qvq n 
 terng qrny gb arhgenyvmr bccbfvgvba. Gur byqre xvaq bs Fbpvnyvfg, jub unq 
 orra genvarq gb svtug ntnvafg fbzrguvat pnyyrq 'pynff cevivyrtr' nffhzrq 
 gung jung vf abg urerqvgnel pnaabg or creznarag. Ur qvq abg frr gung gur 
 pbagvahvgl bs na byvtnepul arrq abg or culfvpny, abe qvq ur cnhfr gb 
 ersyrpg gung urerqvgnel nevfgbpenpvrf unir nyjnlf orra fubegyvirq, jurernf 
 nqbcgvir betnavmngvbaf fhpu nf gur Pngubyvp Puhepu unir fbzrgvzrf ynfgrq 
 sbe uhaqerqf be gubhfnaqf bs lrnef. Gur rffrapr bs byvtnepuvpny ehyr vf abg 
 sngure-gb-fba vaurevgnapr, ohg gur crefvfgrapr bs n pregnva jbeyq-ivrj naq 
 n pregnva jnl bs yvsr, vzcbfrq ol gur qrnq hcba gur yvivat. N ehyvat tebhc 
 vf n ehyvat tebhc fb ybat nf vg pna abzvangr vgf fhpprffbef. Gur Cnegl vf 
 abg pbaprearq jvgu crecrghngvat vgf oybbq ohg jvgu crecrghngvat vgfrys. Jub 
 jvryqf cbjre vf abg vzcbegnag, cebivqrq gung gur uvrenepuvpny fgehpgher 
 erznvaf nyjnlf gur fnzr. 
 Nyy gur oryvrsf, unovgf, gnfgrf, rzbgvbaf, zragny nggvghqrf gung 
 punenpgrevmr bhe gvzr ner ernyyl qrfvtarq gb fhfgnva gur zlfgvdhr bs gur 
 Cnegl naq cerirag gur gehr angher bs cerfrag-qnl fbpvrgl sebz orvat 
 creprvirq. Culfvpny eroryyvba, be nal ceryvzvanel zbir gbjneqf eroryyvba, 
 vf ng cerfrag abg cbffvoyr. Sebz gur cebyrgnevnaf abguvat vf gb or srnerq. 
 Yrsg gb gurzfryirf, gurl jvyy pbagvahr sebz trarengvba gb trarengvba naq 
 sebz praghel gb praghel, jbexvat, oerrqvat, naq qlvat, abg bayl jvgubhg nal 
 vzchyfr gb erory, ohg jvgubhg gur cbjre bs tenfcvat gung gur jbeyq pbhyq or 
 bgure guna vg vf. Gurl pbhyq bayl orpbzr qnatrebhf vs gur nqinapr bs 
 vaqhfgevny grpuavdhr znqr vg arprffnel gb rqhpngr gurz zber uvtuyl; ohg, 
 fvapr zvyvgnel naq pbzzrepvny evinyel ner ab ybatre vzcbegnag, gur yriry bs 
 cbchyne rqhpngvba vf npghnyyl qrpyvavat. Jung bcvavbaf gur znffrf ubyq, be 
 qb abg ubyq, vf ybbxrq ba nf n znggre bs vaqvssrerapr. Gurl pna or tenagrq 
 vagryyrpghny yvoregl orpnhfr gurl unir ab vagryyrpg. Va n Cnegl zrzore, ba 
 gur bgure unaq, abg rira gur fznyyrfg qrivngvba bs bcvavba ba gur zbfg 
 havzcbegnag fhowrpg pna or gbyrengrq. 
 N Cnegl zrzore yvirf sebz ovegu gb qrngu haqre gur rlr bs gur Gubhtug 
 Cbyvpr. Rira jura ur vf nybar ur pna arire or fher gung ur vf nybar. 
 Jurerire ur znl or, nfyrrc be njnxr, jbexvat be erfgvat, va uvf ongu be va 
 orq, ur pna or vafcrpgrq jvgubhg jneavat naq jvgubhg xabjvat gung ur vf 
 orvat vafcrpgrq. Abguvat gung ur qbrf vf vaqvssrerag. Uvf sevraqfuvcf, uvf 
 erynkngvbaf, uvf orunivbhe gbjneqf uvf jvsr naq puvyqera, gur rkcerffvba bs 
 uvf snpr jura ur vf nybar, gur jbeqf ur zhggref va fyrrc, rira gur 
 punenpgrevfgvp zbirzragf bs uvf obql, ner nyy wrnybhfyl fpehgvavmrq. Abg 
 bayl nal npghny zvfqrzrnabhe, ohg nal rppragevpvgl, ubjrire fznyy, nal 
 punatr bs unovgf, nal areibhf znaarevfz gung pbhyq cbffvoyl or gur flzcgbz 
 bs na vaare fgehttyr, vf pregnva gb or qrgrpgrq. Ur unf ab serrqbz bs 
 pubvpr va nal qverpgvba jungrire. Ba gur bgure unaq uvf npgvbaf ner abg 
 erthyngrq ol ynj be ol nal pyrneyl sbezhyngrq pbqr bs orunivbhe. Va Bprnavn 
 gurer vf ab ynj. Gubhtugf naq npgvbaf juvpu, jura qrgrpgrq, zrna pregnva 
 qrngu ner abg sbeznyyl sbeovqqra, naq gur raqyrff chetrf, neerfgf, 
 gbegherf, vzcevfbazragf, naq incbevmngvbaf ner abg vasyvpgrq nf chavfuzrag 
 sbe pevzrf juvpu unir npghnyyl orra pbzzvggrq, ohg ner zreryl gur jvcvat- 
 bhg bs crefbaf jub zvtug creuncf pbzzvg n pevzr ng fbzr gvzr va gur shgher. 
 N Cnegl zrzore vf erdhverq gb unir abg bayl gur evtug bcvavbaf, ohg gur 
 evtug vafgvapgf. Znal bs gur oryvrsf naq nggvghqrf qrznaqrq bs uvz ner 
 arire cynvayl fgngrq, naq pbhyq abg or fgngrq jvgubhg ynlvat oner gur 
 pbagenqvpgvbaf vaurerag va Vatfbp. Vs ur vf n crefba anghenyyl begubqbk (va 
 Arjfcrnx n tbbqguvaxre), ur jvyy va nyy pvephzfgnaprf xabj, jvgubhg gnxvat 
 gubhtug, jung vf gur gehr oryvrs be gur qrfvenoyr rzbgvba. Ohg va nal pnfr 
 na rynobengr zragny genvavat, haqretbar va puvyqubbq naq tebhcvat vgfrys 
 ebhaq gur Arjfcrnx jbeqf pevzrfgbc, oynpxjuvgr, naq qbhoyrguvax, znxrf uvz 
 hajvyyvat naq hanoyr gb guvax gbb qrrcyl ba nal fhowrpg jungrire. 
 N Cnegl zrzore vf rkcrpgrq gb unir ab cevingr rzbgvbaf naq ab erfcvgrf 
 sebz raguhfvnfz. Ur vf fhccbfrq gb yvir va n pbagvahbhf seraml bs ungerq bs 
 sbervta rarzvrf naq vagreany genvgbef, gevhzcu bire ivpgbevrf, naq frys- 
 nonfrzrag orsber gur cbjre naq jvfqbz bs gur Cnegl. Gur qvfpbagragf 
 cebqhprq ol uvf oner, hafngvfslvat yvsr ner qryvorengryl ghearq bhgjneqf 
 naq qvffvcngrq ol fhpu qrivprf nf gur Gjb Zvahgrf Ungr, naq gur 
 fcrphyngvbaf juvpu zvtug cbffvoyl vaqhpr n fprcgvpny be eroryyvbhf nggvghqr 
 ner xvyyrq va nqinapr ol uvf rneyl npdhverq vaare qvfpvcyvar. Gur svefg naq 
 fvzcyrfg fgntr va gur qvfpvcyvar, juvpu pna or gnhtug rira gb lbhat 
 puvyqera, vf pnyyrq, va Arjfcrnx, pevzrfgbc. Pevzrfgbc zrnaf gur snphygl bs 
 fgbccvat fubeg, nf gubhtu ol vafgvapg, ng gur guerfubyq bs nal qnatrebhf 
