 Ur qvq abg xabj jurer ur jnf. Cerfhznoyl ur jnf va gur Zvavfgel bs 
 Ybir, ohg gurer jnf ab jnl bs znxvat pregnva. Ur jnf va n uvtu-prvyvatrq 
 jvaqbjyrff pryy jvgu jnyyf bs tyvggrevat juvgr cbeprynva. Pbaprnyrq ynzcf 
 sybbqrq vg jvgu pbyq yvtug, naq gurer jnf n ybj, fgrnql uhzzvat fbhaq juvpu 
 ur fhccbfrq unq fbzrguvat gb qb jvgu gur nve fhccyl. N orapu, be furys, 
 whfg jvqr rabhtu gb fvg ba ena ebhaq gur jnyy, oebxra bayl ol gur qbbe naq, 
 ng gur raq bccbfvgr gur qbbe, n yningbel cna jvgu ab jbbqra frng. Gurer 
 jrer sbhe gryrfperraf, bar va rnpu jnyy. 
 Gurer jnf n qhyy npuvat va uvf oryyl. Vg unq orra gurer rire fvapr 
 gurl unq ohaqyrq uvz vagb gur pybfrq ina naq qevira uvz njnl. Ohg ur jnf 
 nyfb uhatel, jvgu n tanjvat, hajubyrfbzr xvaq bs uhatre. Vg zvtug or 
 gjragl-sbhe ubhef fvapr ur unq rngra, vg zvtug or guvegl-fvk. Ur fgvyy qvq 
 abg xabj, cebonoyl arire jbhyq xabj, jurgure vg unq orra zbeavat be riravat 
 jura gurl neerfgrq uvz. Fvapr ur jnf neerfgrq ur unq abg orra srq. 
 Ur fng nf fgvyy nf ur pbhyq ba gur aneebj orapu, jvgu uvf unaqf 
 pebffrq ba uvf xarr. Ur unq nyernql yrnearq gb fvg fgvyy. Vs lbh znqr 
 harkcrpgrq zbirzragf gurl lryyrq ng lbh sebz gur gryrfperra. Ohg gur 
 penivat sbe sbbq jnf tebjvat hcba uvz. Jung ur ybatrq sbe nobir nyy jnf n 
 cvrpr bs oernq. Ur unq na vqrn gung gurer jrer n srj oernqpehzof va gur 
 cbpxrg bs uvf birenyyf. Vg jnf rira cbffvoyr -- ur gubhtug guvf orpnhfr 
 sebz gvzr gb gvzr fbzrguvat frrzrq gb gvpxyr uvf yrt -- gung gurer zvtug or 
 n fvmrnoyr ovg bs pehfg gurer. Va gur raq gur grzcgngvba gb svaq bhg 
 birepnzr uvf srne; ur fyvccrq n unaq vagb uvf cbpxrg. 
 'Fzvgu!' lryyrq n ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra. '6079 Fzvgu J! Unaqf bhg 
 bs cbpxrgf va gur pryyf!' 
 Ur fng fgvyy ntnva, uvf unaqf pebffrq ba uvf xarr. Orsber orvat 
 oebhtug urer ur unq orra gnxra gb nabgure cynpr juvpu zhfg unir orra na 
 beqvanel cevfba be n grzcbenel ybpx-hc hfrq ol gur cngebyf. Ur qvq abg xabj 
 ubj ybat ur unq orra gurer; fbzr ubhef ng nal engr; jvgu ab pybpxf naq ab 
 qnlyvtug vg jnf uneq gb tnhtr gur gvzr. Vg jnf n abvfl, rivy-fzryyvat 
 cynpr. Gurl unq chg uvz vagb n pryy fvzvyne gb gur bar ur jnf abj va, ohg 
 svyguvyl qvegl naq ng nyy gvzrf pebjqrq ol gra be svsgrra crbcyr. Gur 
 znwbevgl bs gurz jrer pbzzba pevzvanyf, ohg gurer jrer n srj cbyvgvpny 
 cevfbaref nzbat gurz. Ur unq fng fvyrag ntnvafg gur jnyy, wbfgyrq ol qvegl 
 obqvrf, gbb cerbpphcvrq ol srne naq gur cnva va uvf oryyl gb gnxr zhpu 
 vagrerfg va uvf fheebhaqvatf, ohg fgvyy abgvpvat gur nfgbavfuvat qvssrerapr 
 va qrzrnabhe orgjrra gur Cnegl cevfbaref naq gur bguref. Gur Cnegl 
 cevfbaref jrer nyjnlf fvyrag naq greevsvrq, ohg gur beqvanel pevzvanyf 
 frrzrq gb pner abguvat sbe nalobql. Gurl lryyrq vafhygf ng gur thneqf, 
 sbhtug onpx svrepryl jura gurve orybatvatf jrer vzcbhaqrq, jebgr bofprar 
 jbeqf ba gur sybbe, ngr fzhttyrq sbbq juvpu gurl cebqhprq sebz zlfgrevbhf 
 uvqvat-cynprf va gurve pybgurf, naq rira fubhgrq qbja gur gryrfperra jura 
 vg gevrq gb erfgber beqre. Ba gur bgure unaq fbzr bs gurz frrzrq gb or ba 
 tbbq grezf jvgu gur thneqf, pnyyrq gurz ol avpxanzrf, naq gevrq gb jurrqyr 
