 pbzzba pevzvanyf jvgu n pregnva sbeornenapr, rira jura gurl unq gb unaqyr 
 gurz ebhtuyl. Gurer jnf zhpu gnyx nobhg gur sbeprq-ynobhe pnzcf gb juvpu 
 zbfg bs gur cevfbaref rkcrpgrq gb or frag. Vg jnf 'nyy evtug' va gur pnzcf, 
 ur tngurerq, fb ybat nf lbh unq tbbq pbagnpgf naq xarj gur ebcrf. Gurer jnf 
