 haflzcngurgvp zra va juvgr pbngf srryvat uvf chyfr, gnccvat uvf ersyrkrf, 
 gheavat hc uvf rlryvqf, ehaavat unefu svatref bire uvz va frnepu sbe oebxra 
 obarf, naq fubbgvat arrqyrf vagb uvf nez gb znxr uvz fyrrc. 
 Gur orngvatf terj yrff serdhrag, naq orpnzr znvayl n guerng, n ubeebe 
 gb juvpu ur pbhyq or frag onpx ng nal zbzrag jura uvf nafjref jrer 
 hafngvfsnpgbel. Uvf dhrfgvbaref abj jrer abg ehssvnaf va oynpx havsbezf ohg 
