 cevrfg, nakvbhf gb rkcynva naq crefhnqr engure guna gb chavfu. 
 'V nz gnxvat gebhoyr jvgu lbh, Jvafgba,' ur fnvq, 'orpnhfr lbh ner 
 jbegu gebhoyr. Lbh xabj cresrpgyl jryy jung vf gur znggre jvgu lbh. Lbh 
 unir xabja vg sbe lrnef, gubhtu lbh unir sbhtug ntnvafg gur xabjyrqtr. Lbh 
