 qryhfvba vaqrrq. Lbh oryvrirq gung guerr zra, guerr bar-gvzr Cnegl zrzoref 
 anzrq Wbarf, Nnebafba, naq Ehguresbeq zra jub jrer rkrphgrq sbe gernpurel 
 naq fnobgntr nsgre znxvat gur shyyrfg cbffvoyr pbasrffvba -- jrer abg 
 thvygl bs gur pevzrf gurl jrer punetrq jvgu. Lbh oryvrirq gung lbh unq frra 
 hazvfgnxnoyr qbphzragnel rivqrapr cebivat gung gurve pbasrffvbaf jrer 
 snyfr. Gurer jnf n pregnva cubgbtencu nobhg juvpu lbh unq n unyyhpvangvba. 
 Lbh oryvrirq gung lbh unq npghnyyl uryq vg va lbhe unaqf. Vg jnf n 
 cubgbtencu fbzrguvat yvxr guvf.' 
 Na boybat fyvc bs arjfcncre unq nccrnerq orgjrra B'Oevra'f svatref. 
 Sbe creuncf svir frpbaqf vg jnf jvguva gur natyr bs Jvafgba'f ivfvba. Vg 
