 jvyy chg vg zber cerpvfryl. Qbrf gur cnfg rkvfg pbapergryl, va fcnpr? Vf 
 gurer fbzrjurer be bgure n cynpr, n jbeyq bs fbyvq bowrpgf, jurer gur cnfg 
 vf fgvyy unccravat?' 
 'Ab.' 
 'Gura jurer qbrf gur cnfg rkvfg, vs ng nyy?' 
 'Va erpbeqf. Vg vf jevggra qbja.' 
 'Va erpbeqf. Naq--?' 
 'Va gur zvaq. Va uhzna zrzbevrf.' 
 'Va zrzbel. Irel jryy, gura. Jr, gur Cnegl, pbageby nyy erpbeqf, naq 
 jr pbageby nyy zrzbevrf. Gura jr pbageby gur cnfg, qb jr abg?' 
