 ybbxvat guebhtu gur rlrf bs gur Cnegl. Gung vf gur snpg gung lbh unir tbg 
 gb eryrnea, Jvafgba. Vg arrqf na npg bs frys-qrfgehpgvba, na rssbeg bs gur 
 jvyy. Lbh zhfg uhzoyr lbhefrys orsber lbh pna orpbzr fnar.' 
 Ur cnhfrq sbe n srj zbzragf, nf gubhtu gb nyybj jung ur unq orra 
 fnlvat gb fvax va. 
 'Qb lbh erzrzore,' ur jrag ba, 'jevgvat va lbhe qvnel, "Serrqbz vf gur 
 serrqbz gb fnl gung gjb cyhf gjb znxr sbhe"?' 
 'Lrf,' fnvq Jvafgba. 
 B'Oevra uryq hc uvf yrsg unaq, vgf onpx gbjneqf Jvafgba, jvgu gur 
 guhzo uvqqra naq gur sbhe svatref rkgraqrq. 
 'Ubj znal svatref nz V ubyqvat hc, Jvafgba?' 
 'Sbhe.' 
 'Naq vs gur cnegl fnlf gung vg vf abg sbhe ohg svir -- gura ubj znal?' 
 'Sbhe.' 
 Gur jbeq raqrq va n tnfc bs cnva. Gur arrqyr bs gur qvny unq fubg hc 
 gb svsgl-svir. Gur fjrng unq fcehat bhg nyy bire Jvafgba'f obql. Gur nve 
