 rkgraqrq. Ur qerj onpx gur yrire. Guvf gvzr gur cnva jnf bayl fyvtugyl 
 rnfrq. 
 'Ubj znal svatref, Jvafgba?' 
 'Sbhe.' 
 Gur arrqyr jrag hc gb fvkgl. 
 'Ubj znal svatref, Jvafgba?' 
 'Sbhe! Sbhe! Jung ryfr pna V fnl? Sbhe!' 
 Gur arrqyr zhfg unir evfra ntnva, ohg ur qvq abg ybbx ng vg. Gur 
 urnil, fgrea snpr naq gur sbhe svatref svyyrq uvf ivfvba. Gur svatref fgbbq 
 hc orsber uvf rlrf yvxr cvyynef, rabezbhf, oyheel, naq frrzvat gb ivoengr, 
 ohg hazvfgnxnoyl sbhe. 
 'Ubj znal svatref, Jvafgba?' 
 'Sbhe! Fgbc vg, fgbc vg! Ubj pna lbh tb ba? Sbhe! Sbhe!' 
