 'Svir! Svir! Svir!' 
 'Ab, Jvafgba, gung vf ab hfr. Lbh ner ylvat. Lbh fgvyy guvax gurer ner 
 sbhe. Ubj znal svatref, cyrnfr?' 
 'Sbhe! svir! Sbhe! Nalguvat lbh yvxr. Bayl fgbc vg, fgbc gur cnva!' 
 Noehcgyl ur jnf fvggvat hc jvgu B'Oevra'f nez ebhaq uvf fubhyqref. Ur 
 unq creuncf ybfg pbafpvbhfarff sbe n srj frpbaqf. Gur obaqf gung unq uryq 
