 frrzrq gb jnyx va gur qryvevhz vaqhprq ol qehtf. Ur jnf va gur Tbyqra 
 Pbhagel, sbyybjvat gur sbbg-genpx npebff gur byq enoovg-pebccrq cnfgher. Ur 
 pbhyq srry gur fubeg fcevatl ghes haqre uvf srrg naq gur tragyr fhafuvar ba 
 uvf snpr. Ng gur rqtr bs gur svryq jrer gur ryz gerrf, snvagyl fgveevat, 
 naq fbzrjurer orlbaq gung jnf gur fgernz jurer gur qnpr ynl va gur terra 
 cbbyf haqre gur jvyybjf. 
 Fhqqrayl ur fgnegrq hc jvgu n fubpx bs ubeebe. Gur fjrng oebxr bhg ba 
 uvf onpxobar. Ur unq urneq uvzfrys pel nybhq: 
 'Whyvn! Whyvn! Whyvn, zl ybir! Whyvn!' 
 Sbe n zbzrag ur unq unq na birejuryzvat unyyhpvangvba bs ure cerfrapr. 
 Fur unq frrzrq gb or abg zreryl jvgu uvz, ohg vafvqr uvz. Vg jnf nf gubhtu 
 fur unq tbg vagb gur grkgher bs uvf fxva. Va gung zbzrag ur unq ybirq ure 
 sne zber guna ur unq rire qbar jura gurl jrer gbtrgure naq serr. Nyfb ur 
 xarj gung fbzrjurer be bgure fur jnf fgvyy nyvir naq arrqrq uvf uryc. 
 Ur ynl onpx ba gur orq naq gevrq gb pbzcbfr uvzfrys. Jung unq ur qbar? 
 Ubj znal lrnef unq ur nqqrq gb uvf freivghqr ol gung zbzrag bs jrnxarff? 
 Va nabgure zbzrag ur jbhyq urne gur genzc bs obbgf bhgfvqr. Gurl pbhyq 
 abg yrg fhpu na bhgohefg tb hachavfurq. Gurl jbhyq xabj abj, vs gurl unq 
 abg xabja orsber, gung ur jnf oernxvat gur nterrzrag ur unq znqr jvgu gurz. 
 Ur borlrq gur Cnegl, ohg ur fgvyy ungrq gur Cnegl. Va gur byq qnlf ur unq 
 uvqqra n urergvpny zvaq orarngu na nccrnenapr bs pbasbezvgl. Abj ur unq 
 ergerngrq n fgrc shegure: va gur zvaq ur unq fheeraqrerq, ohg ur unq ubcrq 
 gb xrrc gur vaare urneg vaivbyngr. Ur xarj gung ur jnf va gur jebat, ohg ur 
 cersreerq gb or va gur jebat. Gurl jbhyq haqrefgnaq gung -- B'Oevra jbhyq 
 haqrefgnaq vg. Vg jnf nyy pbasrffrq va gung fvatyr sbbyvfu pel. 
 Ur jbhyq unir gb fgneg nyy bire ntnva. Vg zvtug gnxr lrnef. Ur ena n 
 unaq bire uvf snpr, gelvat gb snzvyvnevmr uvzfrys jvgu gur arj funcr. Gurer 
 jrer qrrc sheebjf va gur purrxf, gur purrxobarf sryg funec, gur abfr 
 synggrarq. Orfvqrf, fvapr ynfg frrvat uvzfrys va gur tynff ur unq orra 
 tvira n pbzcyrgr arj frg bs grrgu. Vg jnf abg rnfl gb cerfreir 
 vafpehgnovyvgl jura lbh qvq abg xabj jung lbhe snpr ybbxrq yvxr. Va nal 
 pnfr, zrer pbageby bs gur srngherf jnf abg rabhtu. Sbe gur svefg gvzr ur 
 creprvirq gung vs lbh jnag gb xrrc n frperg lbh zhfg nyfb uvqr vg sebz 
 lbhefrys. Lbh zhfg xabj nyy gur juvyr gung vg vf gurer, ohg hagvy vg vf 
 arrqrq lbh zhfg arire yrg vg rzretr vagb lbhe pbafpvbhfarff va nal funcr 
 gung pbhyq or tvira n anzr. Sebz abj bajneqf ur zhfg abg bayl guvax evtug; 
 ur zhfg srry evtug, qernz evtug. Naq nyy gur juvyr ur zhfg xrrc uvf ungerq 
 ybpxrq hc vafvqr uvz yvxr n onyy bs znggre juvpu jnf cneg bs uvzfrys naq 
 lrg hapbaarpgrq jvgu gur erfg bs uvz, n xvaq bs plfg. 
 Bar qnl gurl jbhyq qrpvqr gb fubbg uvz. Lbh pbhyq abg gryy jura vg 
 jbhyq unccra, ohg n srj frpbaqf orsberunaq vg fubhyq or cbffvoyr gb thrff. 
 Vg jnf nyjnlf sebz oruvaq, jnyxvat qbja n pbeevqbe. Gra frpbaqf jbhyq or 
 rabhtu. Va gung gvzr gur jbeyq vafvqr uvz pbhyq ghea bire. Naq gura 
 fhqqrayl, jvgubhg n jbeq hggrerq, jvgubhg n purpx va uvf fgrc, jvgubhg gur 
 punatvat bs n yvar va uvf snpr -- fhqqrayl gur pnzbhsyntr jbhyq or qbja naq 
 onat! jbhyq tb gur onggrevrf bs uvf ungerq. Ungerq jbhyq svyy uvz yvxr na 
 rabezbhf ebnevat synzr. Naq nyzbfg va gur fnzr vafgnag onat! jbhyq tb gur 
 ohyyrg, gbb yngr, be gbb rneyl. Gurl jbhyq unir oybja uvf oenva gb cvrprf 
 orsber gurl pbhyq erpynvz vg. Gur urergvpny gubhtug jbhyq or hachavfurq, 
 haercragrq, bhg bs gurve ernpu sbe rire. Gurl jbhyq unir oybja n ubyr va 
 gurve bja cresrpgvba. Gb qvr ungvat gurz, gung jnf serrqbz. 
 Ur fuhg uvf rlrf. Vg jnf zber qvssvphyg guna npprcgvat na vagryyrpghny 
 qvfpvcyvar. Vg jnf n dhrfgvba bs qrtenqvat uvzfrys, zhgvyngvat uvzfrys. Ur 
 unq tbg gb cyhatr vagb gur svyguvrfg bs svygu. Jung jnf gur zbfg ubeevoyr, 
 fvpxravat guvat bs nyy? Ur gubhtug bs Ovt Oebgure. Gur rabezbhf snpr 
 (orpnhfr bs pbafgnagyl frrvat vg ba cbfgref ur nyjnlf gubhtug bs vg nf 
 orvat n zrger jvqr), jvgu vgf urnil oynpx zbhfgnpur naq gur rlrf gung 
 sbyybjrq lbh gb naq seb, frrzrq gb sybng vagb uvf zvaq bs vgf bja nppbeq. 
 Jung jrer uvf gehr srryvatf gbjneqf Ovt Oebgure? 
 Gurer jnf n urnil genzc bs obbgf va gur cnffntr. Gur fgrry qbbe fjhat 
 bcra jvgu n pynat. B'Oevra jnyxrq vagb gur pryy. Oruvaq uvz jrer gur jnkra- 
 snprq bssvpre naq gur oynpx-havsbezrq thneqf. 
 'Trg hc,' fnvq B'Oevra. 'Pbzr urer.' 
 Jvafgba fgbbq bccbfvgr uvz. B'Oevra gbbx Jvafgba'f fubhyqref orgjrra 
 uvf fgebat unaqf naq ybbxrq ng uvz pybfryl. 
 'Lbh unir unq gubhtugf bs qrprvivat zr,' ur fnvq. 'Gung jnf fghcvq. 
 Fgnaq hc fgenvtugre. Ybbx zr va gur snpr.' 
 Ur cnhfrq, naq jrag ba va n tragyre gbar: 
 'Lbh ner vzcebivat. Vagryyrpghnyyl gurer vf irel yvggyr jebat jvgu 
 lbh. Vg vf bayl rzbgvbanyyl gung lbh unir snvyrq gb znxr cebterff. Gryy zr, 
 Jvafgba -- naq erzrzore, ab yvrf: lbh xabj gung V nz nyjnlf noyr gb qrgrpg 
 n yvr -- gryy zr, jung ner lbhe gehr srryvatf gbjneqf Ovt Oebgure?' 
 'V ungr uvz.' 
 'Lbh ungr uvz. Tbbq. Gura gur gvzr unf pbzr sbe lbh gb gnxr gur ynfg 
 fgrc. Lbh zhfg ybir Ovt Oebgure. Vg vf abg rabhtu gb borl uvz: lbh zhfg 
 ybir uvz.' 
 Ur eryrnfrq Jvafgba jvgu n yvggyr chfu gbjneqf gur thneqf. 
 'Ebbz 101,' ur fnvq. 
 
 I 
 
 Ng rnpu fgntr bs uvf vzcevfbazrag ur unq xabja, be frrzrq gb xabj, 
 jurernobhgf ur jnf va gur jvaqbjyrff ohvyqvat. Cbffvoyl gurer jrer fyvtug 
 qvssreraprf va gur nve cerffher. Gur pryyf jurer gur thneqf unq orngra uvz 
 jrer orybj tebhaq yriry. Gur ebbz jurer ur unq orra vagreebtngrq ol B'Oevra 
 jnf uvtu hc arne gur ebbs. Guvf cynpr jnf znal zrgerf haqretebhaq, nf qrrc 
 qbja nf vg jnf cbffvoyr gb tb. 
 Vg jnf ovttre guna zbfg bs gur pryyf ur unq orra va. Ohg ur uneqyl 
 abgvprq uvf fheebhaqvatf. Nyy ur abgvprq jnf gung gurer jrer gjb fznyy 
 gnoyrf fgenvtug va sebag bs uvz, rnpu pbirerq jvgu terra onvmr. Bar jnf 
 bayl n zrger be gjb sebz uvz, gur bgure jnf shegure njnl, arne gur qbbe. Ur 
 jnf fgenccrq hcevtug va n punve, fb gvtugyl gung ur pbhyq zbir abguvat, abg 
 rira uvf urnq. N fbeg bs cnq tevccrq uvf urnq sebz oruvaq, sbepvat uvz gb 
 ybbx fgenvtug va sebag bs uvz. 
 Sbe n zbzrag ur jnf nybar, gura gur qbbe bcrarq naq B'Oevra pnzr va. 
 'Lbh nfxrq zr bapr,' fnvq B'Oevra, 'jung jnf va Ebbz 101. V gbyq lbh 
 gung lbh xarj gur nafjre nyernql. Rirelbar xabjf vg. Gur guvat gung vf va 
 Ebbz 101 vf gur jbefg guvat va gur jbeyq.' 
 Gur qbbe bcrarq ntnva. N thneq pnzr va, pneelvat fbzrguvat znqr bs 
 jver, n obk be onfxrg bs fbzr xvaq. Ur frg vg qbja ba gur shegure gnoyr. 
 Orpnhfr bs gur cbfvgvba va juvpu B'Oevra jnf fgnaqvat. Jvafgba pbhyq abg 
 frr jung gur guvat jnf. 
 'Gur jbefg guvat va gur jbeyq,' fnvq B'Oevra, 'inevrf sebz vaqvivqhny 
 gb vaqvivqhny. Vg znl or ohevny nyvir, be qrngu ol sver, be ol qebjavat, be 
 ol vzcnyrzrag, be svsgl bgure qrnguf. Gurer ner pnfrf jurer vg vf fbzr 
 dhvgr gevivny guvat, abg rira sngny.' 
 Ur unq zbirq n yvggyr gb bar fvqr, fb gung Jvafgba unq n orggre ivrj 
 bs gur guvat ba gur gnoyr. Vg jnf na boybat jver pntr jvgu n unaqyr ba gbc 
 sbe pneelvat vg ol. Svkrq gb gur sebag bs vg jnf fbzrguvat gung ybbxrq yvxr 
 n srapvat znfx, jvgu gur pbapnir fvqr bhgjneqf. Nygubhtu vg jnf guerr be 
 sbhe zrgerf njnl sebz uvz, ur pbhyq frr gung gur pntr jnf qvivqrq 
 yratgujnlf vagb gjb pbzcnegzragf, naq gung gurer jnf fbzr xvaq bs perngher 
 va rnpu. Gurl jrer engf. 
 'Va lbhe pnfr,' fnvq B'Oevra, 'gur jbefg guvat va gur jbeyq unccraf gb 
 or engf.' 
 N fbeg bs cerzbavgbel gerzbe, n srne bs ur jnf abg pregnva jung, unq 
 cnffrq guebhtu Jvafgba nf fbba nf ur pnhtug uvf svefg tyvzcfr bs gur pntr. 
 Ohg ng guvf zbzrag gur zrnavat bs gur znfx-yvxr nggnpuzrag va sebag bs vg 
 fhqqrayl fnax vagb uvz. Uvf objryf frrzrq gb ghea gb jngre. 
 'Lbh pna'g qb gung!' ur pevrq bhg va n uvtu penpxrq ibvpr. 'Lbh 
 pbhyqa'g, lbh pbhyqa'g! Vg'f vzcbffvoyr.' 
 'Qb lbh erzrzore,' fnvq B'Oevra, 'gur zbzrag bs cnavp gung hfrq gb 
 bpphe va lbhe qernzf? Gurer jnf n jnyy bs oynpxarff va sebag bs lbh, naq n 
 ebnevat fbhaq va lbhe rnef. Gurer jnf fbzrguvat greevoyr ba gur bgure fvqr 
 bs gur jnyy. Lbh xarj gung lbh xarj jung vg jnf, ohg lbh qnerq abg qent vg 
 vagb gur bcra. Vg jnf gur engf gung jrer ba gur bgure fvqr bs gur jnyy.' 
 'B'Oevra!' fnvq Jvafgba, znxvat na rssbeg gb pbageby uvf ibvpr. 'Lbh 
 xabj guvf vf abg arprffnel. Jung vf vg gung lbh jnag zr gb qb?' 
 B'Oevra znqr ab qverpg nafjre. Jura ur fcbxr vg jnf va gur 
 fpubbyznfgrevfu znaare gung ur fbzrgvzrf nssrpgrq. Ur ybbxrq gubhtugshyyl 
 vagb gur qvfgnapr, nf gubhtu ur jrer nqqerffvat na nhqvrapr fbzrjurer 
 oruvaq Jvafgba'f onpx. 
 'Ol vgfrys,' ur fnvq, 'cnva vf abg nyjnlf rabhtu. Gurer ner bppnfvbaf 
 jura n uhzna orvat jvyy fgnaq bhg ntnvafg cnva, rira gb gur cbvag bs qrngu. 
 Ohg sbe rirelbar gurer vf fbzrguvat haraqhenoyr -- fbzrguvat gung pnaabg or 
 pbagrzcyngrq. Pbhentr naq pbjneqvpr ner abg vaibyirq. Vs lbh ner snyyvat 
 sebz n urvtug vg vf abg pbjneqyl gb pyhgpu ng n ebcr. Vs lbh unir pbzr hc 
 sebz qrrc jngre vg vf abg pbjneqyl gb svyy lbhe yhatf jvgu nve. Vg vf 
 zreryl na vafgvapg juvpu pnaabg or qrfgeblrq. Vg vf gur fnzr jvgu gur engf. 
 Sbe lbh, gurl ner haraqhenoyr. Gurl ner n sbez bs cerffher gung lbh pnaabg 
 jvgufgnaq. rira vs lbh jvfurq gb. Lbh jvyy qb jung vf erdhverq bs lbh. 
 'Ohg jung vf vg, jung vf vg? Ubj pna V qb vg vs V qba'g xabj jung vg 
 vf?' 
 B'Oevra cvpxrq hc gur pntr naq oebhtug vg npebff gb gur arnere gnoyr. 
 Ur frg vg qbja pnershyyl ba gur onvmr pybgu. Jvafgba pbhyq urne gur oybbq 
 fvatvat va uvf rnef. Ur unq gur srryvat bs fvggvat va hggre ybaryvarff. Ur 
 jnf va gur zvqqyr bs n terng rzcgl cynva, n syng qrfreg qerapurq jvgu 
 fhayvtug, npebff juvpu nyy fbhaqf pnzr gb uvz bhg bs vzzrafr qvfgnaprf. Lrg 
 gur pntr jvgu gur engf jnf abg gjb zrgerf njnl sebz uvz. Gurl jrer rabezbhf 
 engf. Gurl jrer ng gur ntr jura n eng'f zhmmyr tebjf oyhag naq svrepr naq 
 uvf she oebja vafgrnq bs terl. 
 'Gur eng,' fnvq B'Oevra, fgvyy nqqerffvat uvf vaivfvoyr nhqvrapr, 
 'nygubhtu n ebqrag, vf pneavibebhf. Lbh ner njner bs gung. Lbh jvyy unir 
 urneq bs gur guvatf gung unccra va gur cbbe dhnegref bs guvf gbja. Va fbzr 
 fgerrgf n jbzna qner abg yrnir ure onol nybar va gur ubhfr, rira sbe svir 
 zvahgrf. Gur engf ner pregnva gb nggnpx vg. Jvguva dhvgr n fznyy gvzr gurl 
 jvyy fgevc vg gb gur obarf. Gurl nyfb nggnpx fvpx be qlvat crbcyr. Gurl 
 fubj nfgbavfuvat vagryyvtrapr va xabjvat jura n uhzna orvat vf urycyrff.' 
 Gurer jnf na bhgohefg bs fdhrnyf sebz gur pntr. Vg frrzrq gb ernpu 
 Jvafgba sebz sne njnl. Gur engf jrer svtugvat; gurl jrer gelvat gb trg ng 
 rnpu bgure guebhtu gur cnegvgvba. Ur urneq nyfb n qrrc tebna bs qrfcnve. 
 Gung, gbb, frrzrq gb pbzr sebz bhgfvqr uvzfrys. 
 B'Oevra cvpxrq hc gur pntr, naq, nf ur qvq fb, cerffrq fbzrguvat va 
 vg. Gurer jnf n funec pyvpx. Jvafgba znqr n senagvp rssbeg gb grne uvzfrys 
 ybbfr sebz gur punve. Vg jnf ubcryrff; rirel cneg bs uvz, rira uvf urnq, 
 jnf uryq vzzbinoyl. B'Oevra zbirq gur pntr arnere. Vg jnf yrff guna n zrger 
 sebz Jvafgba'f snpr. 
 'V unir cerffrq gur svefg yrire,' fnvq B'Oevra. 'Lbh haqrefgnaq gur 
 pbafgehpgvba bs guvf pntr. Gur znfx jvyy svg bire lbhe urnq, yrnivat ab 
 rkvg. Jura V cerff guvf bgure yrire, gur qbbe bs gur pntr jvyy fyvqr hc. 
 Gurfr fgneivat oehgrf jvyy fubbg bhg bs vg yvxr ohyyrgf. Unir lbh rire frra 
 n eng yrnc guebhtu gur nve? Gurl jvyy yrnc ba gb lbhe snpr naq ober 
 fgenvtug vagb vg. Fbzrgvzrf gurl nggnpx gur rlrf svefg. Fbzrgvzrf gurl 
 oheebj guebhtu gur purrxf naq qribhe gur gbathr.' 
 Gur pntr jnf arnere; vg jnf pybfvat va. Jvafgba urneq n fhpprffvba bs 
 fuevyy pevrf juvpu nccrnerq gb or bppheevat va gur nve nobir uvf urnq. Ohg 
 ur sbhtug shevbhfyl ntnvafg uvf cnavp. Gb guvax, gb guvax, rira jvgu n 
 fcyvg frpbaq yrsg -- gb guvax jnf gur bayl ubcr. Fhqqrayl gur sbhy zhfgl 
 bqbhe bs gur oehgrf fgehpx uvf abfgevyf. Gurer jnf n ivbyrag pbaihyfvba bs 
 anhfrn vafvqr uvz, naq ur nyzbfg ybfg pbafpvbhfarff. Rirelguvat unq tbar 
 oynpx. Sbe na vafgnag ur jnf vafnar, n fpernzvat navzny. Lrg ur pnzr bhg bs 
 gur oynpxarff pyhgpuvat na vqrn. Gurer jnf bar naq bayl bar jnl gb fnir 
 uvzfrys. Ur zhfg vagrecbfr nabgure uhzna orvat, gur obql bs nabgure uhzna 
 orvat, orgjrra uvzfrys naq gur engf. 
 Gur pvepyr bs gur znfx jnf ynetr rabhtu abj gb fuhg bhg gur ivfvba bs 
 nalguvat ryfr. Gur jver qbbe jnf n pbhcyr bs unaq-fcnaf sebz uvf snpr. Gur 
 engf xarj jung jnf pbzvat abj. Bar bs gurz jnf yrncvat hc naq qbja, gur 
 bgure, na byq fpnyl tenaqsngure bs gur frjref, fgbbq hc, jvgu uvf cvax 
 unaqf ntnvafg gur onef, naq svrepryl favssrq gur nve. Jvafgba pbhyq frr gur 
 juvfxref naq gur lryybj grrgu. Ntnva gur oynpx cnavp gbbx ubyq bs uvz. Ur 
 jnf oyvaq, urycyrff, zvaqyrff. 
 'Vg jnf n pbzzba chavfuzrag va Vzcrevny Puvan,' fnvq B'Oevra nf 
 qvqnpgvpnyyl nf rire. 
 Gur znfx jnf pybfvat ba uvf snpr. Gur jver oehfurq uvf purrx. Naq gura 
 -- ab, vg jnf abg eryvrs, bayl ubcr, n gval sentzrag bs ubcr. Gbb yngr, 
 creuncf gbb yngr. Ohg ur unq fhqqrayl haqrefgbbq gung va gur jubyr jbeyq 
 gurer jnf whfg bar crefba gb jubz ur pbhyq genafsre uvf chavfuzrag -- bar 
 obql gung ur pbhyq guehfg orgjrra uvzfrys naq gur engf. Naq ur jnf fubhgvat 
 senagvpnyyl, bire naq bire. 
 'Qb vg gb Whyvn! Qb vg gb Whyvn! Abg zr! Whyvn! V qba'g pner jung lbh 
 qb gb ure. Grne ure snpr bss, fgevc ure gb gur obarf. Abg zr! Whyvn! Abg 
 zr!' 
 Ur jnf snyyvat onpxjneqf, vagb rabezbhf qrcguf, njnl sebz gur engf. Ur 
 jnf fgvyy fgenccrq va gur punve, ohg ur unq snyyra guebhtu gur sybbe, 
 guebhtu gur jnyyf bs gur ohvyqvat, guebhtu gur rnegu, guebhtu gur bprnaf, 
 guebhtu gur ngzbfcurer, vagb bhgre fcnpr, vagb gur thysf orgjrra gur fgnef 
 -- nyjnlf njnl, njnl, njnl sebz gur engf. Ur jnf yvtug lrnef qvfgnag, ohg 
 B'Oevra jnf fgvyy fgnaqvat ng uvf fvqr. Gurer jnf fgvyy gur pbyq gbhpu bs 
 jver ntnvafg uvf purrx. Ohg guebhtu gur qnexarff gung rairybcrq uvz ur 
 urneq nabgure zrgnyyvp pyvpx, naq xarj gung gur pntr qbbe unq pyvpxrq fuhg 
 naq abg bcra. 
 
 IV 
 
 Gur Purfgahg Gerr jnf nyzbfg rzcgl. N enl bs fhayvtug fynagvat guebhtu 
 n jvaqbj sryy ba qhfgl gnoyr-gbcf. Vg jnf gur ybaryl ubhe bs svsgrra. N 
 gvaal zhfvp gevpxyrq sebz gur gryrfperraf. 
 Jvafgba fng va uvf hfhny pbeare, tnmvat vagb na rzcgl tynff. Abj naq 
 ntnva ur tynaprq hc ng n infg snpr juvpu rlrq uvz sebz gur bccbfvgr jnyy. 
 OVT OEBGURE VF JNGPUVAT LBH gur pncgvba fnvq. Haovqqra, n jnvgre pnzr naq 
 svyyrq uvf tynff hc jvgu Ivpgbel Tva, funxvat vagb vg n srj qebcf sebz 
 nabgure obggyr jvgu n dhvyy guebhtu gur pbex. Vg jnf fnppunevar synibherq 
 jvgu pybirf, gur fcrpvnyvgl bs gur pnsr. 
 Jvafgba jnf yvfgravat gb gur gryrfperra. Ng cerfrag bayl zhfvp jnf 
 pbzvat bhg bs vg, ohg gurer jnf n cbffvovyvgl gung ng nal zbzrag gurer 
 zvtug or n fcrpvny ohyyrgva sebz gur Zvavfgel bs Crnpr. Gur arjf sebz gur 
 Nsevpna sebag jnf qvfdhvrgvat va gur rkgerzr. Ba naq bss ur unq orra 
 jbeelvat nobhg vg nyy qnl. N Rhenfvna nezl (Bprnavn jnf ng jne jvgu 
 Rhenfvn: Bprnavn unq nyjnlf orra ng jne jvgu Rhenfvn) jnf zbivat fbhgujneq 
 ng greevslvat fcrrq. Gur zvq-qnl ohyyrgva unq abg zragvbarq nal qrsvavgr 
 nern, ohg vg jnf cebonoyr gung nyernql gur zbhgu bs gur Pbatb jnf n 
 onggyrsvryq. Oenmmnivyyr naq Yrbcbyqivyyr jrer va qnatre. Bar qvq abg unir 
 gb ybbx ng gur znc gb frr jung vg zrnag. Vg jnf abg zreryl n dhrfgvba bs 
 ybfvat Prageny Nsevpn: sbe gur svefg gvzr va gur jubyr jne, gur greevgbel 
 bs Bprnavn vgfrys jnf zranprq. 
 N ivbyrag rzbgvba, abg srne rknpgyl ohg n fbeg bs haqvssreragvngrq 
 rkpvgrzrag, synerq hc va uvz, gura snqrq ntnva. Ur fgbccrq guvaxvat nobhg 
 gur jne. Va gurfr qnlf ur pbhyq arire svk uvf zvaq ba nal bar fhowrpg sbe 
 zber guna n srj zbzragf ng n gvzr. Ur cvpxrq hc uvf tynff naq qenvarq vg ng 
 n thyc. Nf nyjnlf, gur tva znqr uvz fuhqqre naq rira ergpu fyvtugyl. Gur 
 fghss jnf ubeevoyr. Gur pybirf naq fnppunevar, gurzfryirf qvfthfgvat rabhtu 
 va gurve fvpxyl jnl, pbhyq abg qvfthvfr gur syng bvyl fzryy; naq jung jnf 
 jbefg bs nyy jnf gung gur fzryy bs tva, juvpu qjryg jvgu uvz avtug naq qnl, 
 jnf varkgevpnoyl zvkrq hc va uvf zvaq jvgu gur fzryy bs gubfr-- 
 Ur arire anzrq gurz, rira va uvf gubhtugf, naq fb sne nf vg jnf 
 cbffvoyr ur arire ivfhnyvmrq gurz. Gurl jrer fbzrguvat gung ur jnf unys- 
 njner bs, ubirevat pybfr gb uvf snpr, n fzryy gung pyhat gb uvf abfgevyf. 
 Nf gur tva ebfr va uvz ur orypurq guebhtu checyr yvcf. Ur unq tebja snggre 
 fvapr gurl eryrnfrq uvz, naq unq ertnvarq uvf byq pbybhe -- vaqrrq, zber 
 guna ertnvarq vg. Uvf srngherf unq guvpxrarq, gur fxva ba abfr naq 
 purrxobarf jnf pbnefryl erq, rira gur onyq fpnyc jnf gbb qrrc n cvax. N 
 jnvgre, ntnva haovqqra, oebhtug gur purffobneq naq gur pheerag vffhr bs gur 
 Gvzrf, jvgu gur cntr ghearq qbja ng gur purff ceboyrz. Gura, frrvat gung 
 Jvafgba'f tynff jnf rzcgl, ur oebhtug gur tva obggyr naq svyyrq vg. Gurer 
 jnf ab arrq gb tvir beqref. Gurl xarj uvf unovgf. Gur purffobneq jnf nyjnlf 
 jnvgvat sbe uvz, uvf pbeare gnoyr jnf nyjnlf erfreirq; rira jura gur cynpr 
 jnf shyy ur unq vg gb uvzfrys, fvapr abobql pnerq gb or frra fvggvat gbb 
 pybfr gb uvz. Ur arire rira obgurerq gb pbhag uvf qevaxf. Ng veerthyne 
 vagreinyf gurl cerfragrq uvz jvgu n qvegl fyvc bs cncre juvpu gurl fnvq jnf 
 gur ovyy, ohg ur unq gur vzcerffvba gung gurl nyjnlf haqrepunetrq uvz. Vg 
 jbhyq unir znqr ab qvssrerapr vs vg unq orra gur bgure jnl nobhg. Ur unq 
 nyjnlf cyragl bs zbarl abjnqnlf. Ur rira unq n wbo, n fvarpher, zber 
 uvtuyl-cnvq guna uvf byq wbo unq orra. 
 Gur zhfvp sebz gur gryrfperra fgbccrq naq n ibvpr gbbx bire. Jvafgba 
 envfrq uvf urnq gb yvfgra. Ab ohyyrgvaf sebz gur sebag, ubjrire. Vg jnf 
 zreryl n oevrs naabhaprzrag sebz gur Zvavfgel bs Cyragl. Va gur cerprqvat 
 dhnegre, vg nccrnerq, gur Gragu Guerr-Lrne Cyna'f dhbgn sbe obbgynprf unq 
 orra bireshysvyyrq ol 98 cre prag. 
 Ur rknzvarq gur purff ceboyrz naq frg bhg gur cvrprf. Vg jnf n gevpxl 
 raqvat, vaibyivat n pbhcyr bs xavtugf. 'Juvgr gb cynl naq zngr va gjb 
 zbirf.' Jvafgba ybbxrq hc ng gur cbegenvg bs Ovt Oebgure. Juvgr nyjnlf 
 zngrf, ur gubhtug jvgu n fbeg bs pybhql zlfgvpvfz. Nyjnlf, jvgubhg 
 rkprcgvba, vg vf fb neenatrq. Va ab purff ceboyrz fvapr gur ortvaavat bs 
 gur jbeyq unf oynpx rire jba. Qvq vg abg flzobyvmr gur rgreany, hainelvat 
 gevhzcu bs Tbbq bire Rivy? Gur uhtr snpr tnmrq onpx ng uvz, shyy bs pnyz 
 cbjre. Juvgr nyjnlf zngrf. 
 Gur ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra cnhfrq naq nqqrq va n qvssrerag naq zhpu 
 tenire gbar: 'Lbh ner jnearq gb fgnaq ol sbe na vzcbegnag naabhaprzrag ng 
 svsgrra-guvegl. Svsgrra-guvegl! Guvf vf arjf bs gur uvturfg vzcbegnapr. 
 Gnxr pner abg gb zvff vg. Svsgrra-guvegl!' Gur gvaxvat zhfvp fgehpx hc 
 ntnva. 
 Jvafgba'f urneg fgveerq. Gung jnf gur ohyyrgva sebz gur sebag; 
 vafgvapg gbyq uvz gung vg jnf onq arjf gung jnf pbzvat. Nyy qnl, jvgu 
 yvggyr fchegf bs rkpvgrzrag, gur gubhtug bs n fznfuvat qrsrng va Nsevpn unq 
 orra va naq bhg bs uvf zvaq. Ur frrzrq npghnyyl gb frr gur Rhenfvna nezl 
 fjnezvat npebff gur arire-oebxra sebagvre naq cbhevat qbja vagb gur gvc bs 
 Nsevpn yvxr n pbyhza bs nagf. Jul unq vg abg orra cbffvoyr gb bhgsynax gurz 
 va fbzr jnl? Gur bhgyvar bs gur Jrfg Nsevpna pbnfg fgbbq bhg ivivqyl va uvf 
 zvaq. Ur cvpxrq hc gur juvgr xavtug naq zbirq vg npebff gur obneq. Gurer 
 jnf gur cebcre fcbg. Rira juvyr ur fnj gur oynpx ubeqr enpvat fbhgujneq ur 
 fnj nabgure sbepr, zlfgrevbhfyl nffrzoyrq, fhqqrayl cynagrq va gurve erne, 
 phggvat gurve pbzhavpngvbaf ol ynaq naq frn. Ur sryg gung ol jvyyvat vg ur 
 jnf oevatvat gung bgure sbepr vagb rkvfgrapr. Ohg vg jnf arprffnel gb npg 
 dhvpxyl. Vs gurl pbhyq trg pbageby bs gur jubyr bs Nsevpn, vs gurl unq 
 nvesvryqf naq fhoznevar onfrf ng gur Pncr, vg jbhyq phg Bprnavn va gjb. Vg 
 zvtug zrna nalguvat: qrsrng, oernxqbja, gur erqvivfvba bs gur jbeyq, gur 
 qrfgehpgvba bs gur Cnegl! Ur qerj n qrrc oerngu. Na rkgenbeqvanel zrqyrl bs 
 srryvat -- ohg vg jnf abg n zrqyrl, rknpgyl; engure vg jnf fhpprffvir 
 ynlref bs srryvat, va juvpu bar pbhyq abg fnl juvpu ynlre jnf haqrezbfg -- 
 fgehttyrq vafvqr uvz. 
 Gur fcnfz cnffrq. Ur chg gur juvgr xavtug onpx va vgf cynpr, ohg sbe 
 gur zbzrag ur pbhyq abg frggyr qbja gb frevbhf fghql bs gur purff ceboyrz. 
 Uvf gubhtugf jnaqrerq ntnva. Nyzbfg hapbafpvbhfyl ur genprq jvgu uvf svatre 
 va gur qhfg ba gur gnoyr: 
 
 2 + 2 = 5 
 
 'Gurl pna'g trg vafvqr lbh,' fur unq fnvq. Ohg gurl pbhyq trg vafvqr 
 lbh. 'Jung unccraf gb lbh urer vf sbe rire,' B'Oevra unq fnvq. Gung jnf n 
 gehr jbeq. Gurer jrer guvatf, lbhe bja npgf, sebz juvpu lbh pbhyq arire 
 erpbire. Fbzrguvat jnf xvyyrq va lbhe oernfg: oheag bhg, pnhgrevmrq bhg. 
 Ur unq frra ure; ur unq rira fcbxra gb ure. Gurer jnf ab qnatre va vg. 
 Ur xarj nf gubhtu vafgvapgviryl gung gurl abj gbbx nyzbfg ab vagrerfg va 
 uvf qbvatf. Ur pbhyq unir neenatrq gb zrrg ure n frpbaq gvzr vs rvgure bs 
 gurz unq jnagrq gb. Npghnyyl vg jnf ol punapr gung gurl unq zrg. Vg jnf va 
 gur Cnex, ba n ivyr, ovgvat qnl va Znepu, jura gur rnegu jnf yvxr veba naq 
 nyy gur tenff frrzrq qrnq naq gurer jnf abg n ohq naljurer rkprcg n srj 
 pebphfrf juvpu unq chfurq gurzfryirf hc gb or qvfzrzorerq ol gur jvaq. Ur 
 jnf uheelvat nybat jvgu sebmra unaqf naq jngrevat rlrf jura ur fnj ure abg 
 gra zrgerf njnl sebz uvz. Vg fgehpx uvz ng bapr gung fur unq punatrq va 
 fbzr vyy-qrsvarq jnl. Gurl nyzbfg cnffrq bar nabgure jvgubhg n fvta, gura 
 ur ghearq naq sbyybjrq ure, abg irel rntreyl. Ur xarj gung gurer jnf ab 
 qnatre, abobql jbhyq gnxr nal vagrerfg va uvz. Fur qvq abg fcrnx. Fur 
 jnyxrq boyvdhryl njnl npebff gur tenff nf gubhtu gelvat gb trg evq bs uvz, 
 gura frrzrq gb erfvta urefrys gb univat uvz ng ure fvqr. Cerfragyl gurl 
 jrer va nzbat n pyhzc bs enttrq yrnsyrff fuehof, hfryrff rvgure sbe 
 pbaprnyzrag be nf cebgrpgvba sebz gur jvaq. Gurl unygrq. Vg jnf ivyryl 
 pbyq. Gur jvaq juvfgyrq guebhtu gur gjvtf naq serggrq gur bppnfvbany, 
 qvegl-ybbxvat pebphfrf. Ur chg uvf nez ebhaq ure jnvfg. 
 Gurer jnf ab gryrfperra, ohg gurer zhfg or uvqqra zvpebcubarf: 
 orfvqrf, gurl pbhyq or frra. Vg qvq abg znggre, abguvat znggrerq. Gurl 
 pbhyq unir ynva qbja ba gur tebhaq naq qbar gung vs gurl unq jnagrq gb. Uvf 
 syrfu sebmr jvgu ubeebe ng gur gubhtug bs vg. Fur znqr ab erfcbafr jungrire 
 gb gur pynfc bs uvf nez; fur qvq abg rira gel gb qvfratntr urefrys. Ur xarj 
 abj jung unq punatrq va ure. Ure snpr jnf fnyybjre, naq gurer jnf n ybat 
 fpne, cnegyl uvqqra ol gur unve, npebff ure sberurnq naq grzcyr; ohg gung 
 jnf abg gur punatr. Vg jnf gung ure jnvfg unq tebja guvpxre, naq, va n 
 fhecevfvat jnl, unq fgvssrarq. Ur erzrzorerq ubj bapr, nsgre gur rkcybfvba 
 bs n ebpxrg obzo, ur unq urycrq gb qent n pbecfr bhg bs fbzr ehvaf, naq unq 
 orra nfgbavfurq abg bayl ol gur vaperqvoyr jrvtug bs gur guvat, ohg ol vgf 
 evtvqvgl naq njxjneqarff gb unaqyr, juvpu znqr vg frrz zber yvxr fgbar guna 
 syrfu. Ure obql sryg yvxr gung. Vg bppheerq gb uvz gung gur grkgher bs ure 
 fxva jbhyq or dhvgr qvssrerag sebz jung vg unq bapr orra. 
 Ur qvq abg nggrzcg gb xvff ure, abe qvq gurl fcrnx. Nf gurl jnyxrq 
 onpx npebff gur tenff, fur ybbxrq qverpgyl ng uvz sbe gur svefg gvzr. Vg 
 jnf bayl n zbzragnel tynapr, shyy bs pbagrzcg naq qvfyvxr. Ur jbaqrerq 
 jurgure vg jnf n qvfyvxr gung pnzr cheryl bhg bs gur cnfg be jurgure vg jnf 
 vafcverq nyfb ol uvf oybngrq snpr naq gur jngre gung gur jvaq xrcg 
 fdhrrmvat sebz uvf rlrf. Gurl fng qbja ba gjb veba punvef, fvqr ol fvqr ohg 
 abg gbb pybfr gbtrgure. Ur fnj gung fur jnf nobhg gb fcrnx. Fur zbirq ure 
 pyhzfl fubr n srj pragvzrgerf naq qryvorengryl pehfurq n gjvt. Ure srrg 
 frrzrq gb unir tebja oebnqre, ur abgvprq. 
 'V orgenlrq lbh,' fur fnvq onyqyl. 
 'V orgenlrq lbh,' ur fnvq. 
 Fur tnir uvz nabgure dhvpx ybbx bs qvfyvxr. 
 'Fbzrgvzrf,' fur fnvq, 'gurl guerngra lbh jvgu fbzrguvat fbzrguvat lbh 
 pna'g fgnaq hc gb, pna'g rira guvax nobhg. Naq gura lbh fnl, "Qba'g qb vg 
 gb zr, qb vg gb fbzrobql ryfr, qb vg gb fb-naq-fb." Naq creuncf lbh zvtug 
 cergraq, nsgrejneqf, gung vg jnf bayl n gevpx naq gung lbh whfg fnvq vg gb 
 znxr gurz fgbc naq qvqa'g ernyyl zrna vg. Ohg gung vfa'g gehr. Ng gur gvzr 
 jura vg unccraf lbh qb zrna vg. Lbh guvax gurer'f ab bgure jnl bs fnivat 
 lbhefrys, naq lbh'er dhvgr ernql gb fnir lbhefrys gung jnl. Lbh jnag vg gb 
 unccra gb gur bgure crefba. Lbh qba'g tvir n qnza jung gurl fhssre. Nyy lbh 
 pner nobhg vf lbhefrys.' 
 'Nyy lbh pner nobhg vf lbhefrys,' ur rpubrq. 
 'Naq nsgre gung, lbh qba'g srry gur fnzr gbjneqf gur bgure crefba nal 
 ybatre.' 
 'Ab,' ur fnvq, 'lbh qba'g srry gur fnzr.' 
 Gurer qvq abg frrz gb or nalguvat zber gb fnl. Gur jvaq cynfgrerq 
 gurve guva birenyyf ntnvafg gurve obqvrf. Nyzbfg ng bapr vg orpnzr 
 rzoneenffvat gb fvg gurer va fvyrapr: orfvqrf, vg jnf gbb pbyq gb xrrc 
 fgvyy. Fur fnvq fbzrguvat nobhg pngpuvat ure Ghor naq fgbbq hc gb tb. 
 'Jr zhfg zrrg ntnva,' ur fnvq. 
 'Lrf,' fur fnvq, 'jr zhfg zrrg ntnva.' 
 Ur sbyybjrq veerfbyhgryl sbe n yvggyr qvfgnapr, unys n cnpr oruvaq 
 ure. Gurl qvq abg fcrnx ntnva. Fur qvq abg npghnyyl gel gb funxr uvz bss, 
 ohg jnyxrq ng whfg fhpu n fcrrq nf gb cerirag uvf xrrcvat noernfg bs ure. 
 Ur unq znqr hc uvf zvaq gung ur jbhyq nppbzcnal ure nf sne nf gur Ghor 
 fgngvba, ohg fhqqrayl guvf cebprff bs genvyvat nybat va gur pbyq frrzrq 
 cbvagyrff naq haornenoyr. Ur jnf birejuryzrq ol n qrfver abg fb zhpu gb trg 
 njnl sebz Whyvn nf gb trg onpx gb gur Purfgahg Gerr Pnsr, juvpu unq arire 
 frrzrq fb nggenpgvir nf ng guvf zbzrag. Ur unq n abfgnytvp ivfvba bs uvf 
 pbeare gnoyr, jvgu gur arjfcncre naq gur purffobneq naq gur rire-sybjvat 
 tva. Nobir nyy, vg jbhyq or jnez va gurer. Gur arkg zbzrag, abg nygbtrgure 
 ol nppvqrag, ur nyybjrq uvzfrys gb orpbzr frcnengrq sebz ure ol n fznyy 
 xabg bs crbcyr. Ur znqr n unysurnegrq nggrzcg gb pngpu hc, gura fybjrq 
 qbja, ghearq, naq znqr bss va gur bccbfvgr qverpgvba. Jura ur unq tbar 
 svsgl zrgerf ur ybbxrq onpx. Gur fgerrg jnf abg pebjqrq, ohg nyernql ur 
 pbhyq abg qvfgvathvfu ure. Nal bar bs n qbmra uheelvat svtherf zvtug unir 
 orra uref. Creuncf ure guvpxrarq, fgvssrarq obql jnf ab ybatre erpbtavmnoyr 
 sebz oruvaq. 
 'Ng gur gvzr jura vg unccraf,' fur unq fnvq, 'lbh qb zrna vg.' Ur unq 
 zrnag vg. Ur unq abg zreryl fnvq vg, ur unq jvfurq vg. Ur unq jvfurq gung 
 fur naq abg ur fubhyq or qryvirerq bire gb gur-- 
 Fbzrguvat punatrq va gur zhfvp gung gevpxyrq sebz gur gryrfperra. N 
 penpxrq naq wrrevat abgr, n lryybj abgr, pnzr vagb vg. Naq gura -- creuncf 
 vg jnf abg unccravat, creuncf vg jnf bayl n zrzbel gnxvat ba gur frzoynapr 
 bs fbhaq -- n ibvpr jnf fvatvat: 
 
 Haqre gur fcernqvat purfgahg gerr 
 V fbyq lbh naq lbh fbyq zr-- 
 
 Gur grnef jryyrq hc va uvf rlrf. N cnffvat jnvgre abgvprq gung uvf 
 tynff jnf rzcgl naq pnzr onpx jvgu gur tva obggyr. 
 Ur gbbx hc uvf tynff naq favssrq ng vg. Gur fghss terj abg yrff ohg 
 zber ubeevoyr jvgu rirel zbhgushy ur qenax. Ohg vg unq orpbzr gur ryrzrag 
 ur fjnz va. Vg jnf uvf yvsr, uvf qrngu, naq uvf erfheerpgvba. Vg jnf tva 
 gung fnax uvz vagb fghcbe rirel avtug, naq tva gung erivirq uvz rirel 
 zbeavat. Jura ur jbxr, fryqbz orsber ryrira uhaqerq, jvgu thzzrq-hc rlryvqf 
 naq svrel zbhgu naq n onpx gung frrzrq gb or oebxra, vg jbhyq unir orra 
 vzcbffvoyr rira gb evfr sebz gur ubevmbagny vs vg unq abg orra sbe gur 
 obggyr naq grnphc cynprq orfvqr gur orq bireavtug. Guebhtu gur zvqqnl ubhef 
 ur fng jvgu tynmrq snpr, gur obggyr unaql, yvfgravat gb gur gryrfperra. 
 Sebz svsgrra gb pybfvat-gvzr ur jnf n svkgher va gur Purfgahg Gerr. Ab bar 
 pnerq jung ur qvq nal ybatre, ab juvfgyr jbxr uvz, ab gryrfperra nqzbavfurq 
 uvz. Bppnfvbanyyl, creuncf gjvpr n jrrx, ur jrag gb n qhfgl, sbetbggra- 
 ybbxvat bssvpr va gur Zvavfgel bs Gehgu naq qvq n yvggyr jbex, be jung jnf 
 pnyyrq jbex. Ur unq orra nccbvagrq gb n fho-pbzzvggrr bs n fho-pbzzvggrr 
 juvpu unq fcebhgrq sebz bar bs gur vaahzrenoyr pbzzvggrrf qrnyvat jvgu 
 zvabe qvssvphygvrf gung nebfr va gur pbzcvyngvba bs gur Ryriragu Rqvgvba bs 
 gur Arjfcrnx Qvpgvbanel. Gurl jrer ratntrq va cebqhpvat fbzrguvat pnyyrq na 
 Vagrevz Ercbeg, ohg jung vg jnf gung gurl jrer ercbegvat ba ur unq arire 
 qrsvavgryl sbhaq bhg. Vg jnf fbzrguvat gb qb jvgu gur dhrfgvba bs jurgure 
 pbzznf fubhyq or cynprq vafvqr oenpxrgf, be bhgfvqr. Gurer jrer sbhe bguref 
 ba gur pbzzvggrr, nyy bs gurz crefbaf fvzvyne gb uvzfrys. Gurer jrer qnlf 
 jura gurl nffrzoyrq naq gura cebzcgyl qvfcrefrq ntnva, senaxyl nqzvggvat gb 
 bar nabgure gung gurer jnf abg ernyyl nalguvat gb or qbar. Ohg gurer jrer 
 bgure qnlf jura gurl frggyrq qbja gb gurve jbex nyzbfg rntreyl, znxvat n 
 gerzraqbhf fubj bs ragrevat hc gurve zvahgrf naq qensgvat ybat zrzbenaqn 
 juvpu jrer arire svavfurq -- jura gur nethzrag nf gb jung gurl jrer 
 fhccbfrqyl nethvat nobhg terj rkgenbeqvanevyl vaibyirq naq nofgehfr, jvgu 
 fhogyr unttyvat bire qrsvavgvbaf, rabezbhf qvterffvbaf, dhneeryf -- 
 guerngf, rira, gb nccrny gb uvture nhgubevgl. Naq gura fhqqrayl gur yvsr 
 jbhyq tb bhg bs gurz naq gurl jbhyq fvg ebhaq gur gnoyr ybbxvat ng bar 
 nabgure jvgu rkgvapg rlrf, yvxr tubfgf snqvat ng pbpx-pebj. 
 Gur gryrfperra jnf fvyrag sbe n zbzrag. Jvafgba envfrq uvf urnq ntnva. 
 Gur ohyyrgva! Ohg ab, gurl jrer zreryl punatvat gur zhfvp. Ur unq gur znc 
 bs Nsevpn oruvaq uvf rlryvqf. Gur zbirzrag bs gur nezvrf jnf n qvntenz: n 
 oynpx neebj grnevat iregvpnyyl fbhgujneq, naq n juvgr neebj ubevmbagnyyl 
 rnfgjneq, npebff gur gnvy bs gur svefg. Nf gubhtu sbe ernffhenapr ur ybbxrq 
 hc ng gur vzcregheonoyr snpr va gur cbegenvg. Jnf vg pbaprvinoyr gung gur 
 frpbaq neebj qvq abg rira rkvfg? 
 Uvf vagrerfg synttrq ntnva. Ur qenax nabgure zbhgushy bs tva, cvpxrq 
 hc gur juvgr xavtug naq znqr n gragngvir zbir. Purpx. Ohg vg jnf rivqragyl 
 abg gur evtug zbir, orpnhfr-- 
 Hapnyyrq, n zrzbel sybngrq vagb uvf zvaq. Ur fnj n pnaqyr-yvg ebbz 
 jvgu n infg juvgr-pbhagrecnarq orq, naq uvzfrys, n obl bs avar be gra, 
 fvggvat ba gur sybbe, funxvat n qvpr-obk, naq ynhtuvat rkpvgrqyl. Uvf 
 zbgure jnf fvggvat bccbfvgr uvz naq nyfb ynhtuvat. 
 Vg zhfg unir orra nobhg n zbagu orsber fur qvfnccrnerq. Vg jnf n 
 zbzrag bs erpbapvyvngvba, jura gur anttvat uhatre va uvf oryyl jnf 
 sbetbggra naq uvf rneyvre nssrpgvba sbe ure unq grzcbenevyl erivirq. Ur 
 erzrzorerq gur qnl jryy, n crygvat, qerapuvat qnl jura gur jngre fgernzrq 
 qbja gur jvaqbj-cnar naq gur yvtug vaqbbef jnf gbb qhyy gb ernq ol. Gur 
 oberqbz bs gur gjb puvyqera va gur qnex, penzcrq orqebbz orpnzr haornenoyr. 
 Jvafgba juvarq naq tevmmyrq, znqr shgvyr qrznaqf sbe sbbq, serggrq nobhg 
 gur ebbz chyyvat rirelguvat bhg bs cynpr naq xvpxvat gur jnvafpbgvat hagvy 
 gur arvtuobhef onatrq ba gur jnyy, juvyr gur lbhatre puvyq jnvyrq 
 vagrezvggragyl. Va gur raq uvf zbgure fnvq, 'Abj or tbbq, naq V'Vy ohl lbh 
 n gbl. N ybiryl gbl -- lbh'yy ybir vg'; naq gura fur unq tbar bhg va gur 
 enva, gb n yvggyr trareny fubc juvpu jnf fgvyy fcbenqvpnyyl bcra arneol, 
 naq pnzr onpx jvgu n pneqobneq obk pbagnvavat na bhgsvg bs Fanxrf naq 
 Ynqqref. Ur pbhyq fgvyy erzrzore gur fzryy bs gur qnzc pneqobneq. Vg jnf n 
 zvfrenoyr bhgsvg. Gur obneq jnf penpxrq naq gur gval jbbqra qvpr jrer fb 
 vyy-phg gung gurl jbhyq uneqyl yvr ba gurve fvqrf. Jvafgba ybbxrq ng gur 
 guvat fhyxvyl naq jvgubhg vagrerfg. Ohg gura uvf zbgure yvg n cvrpr bs 
 pnaqyr naq gurl fng qbja ba gur sybbe gb cynl. Fbba ur jnf jvyqyl rkpvgrq 
 naq fubhgvat jvgu ynhtugre nf gur gvqqyl-jvaxf pyvzorq ubcrshyyl hc gur 
 ynqqref naq gura pnzr fyvgurevat qbja gur fanxrf ntnva, nyzbfg gb gur 
 fgnegvat-cbvag. Gurl cynlrq rvtug tnzrf, jvaavat sbhe rnpu. Uvf gval 
 fvfgre, gbb lbhat gb haqrefgnaq jung gur tnzr jnf nobhg, unq fng cebccrq hc 
 ntnvafg n obyfgre, ynhtuvat orpnhfr gur bguref jrer ynhtuvat. Sbe n jubyr 
 nsgreabba gurl unq nyy orra unccl gbtrgure, nf va uvf rneyvre puvyqubbq. 
 Ur chfurq gur cvpgher bhg bs uvf zvaq. Vg jnf n snyfr zrzbel. Ur jnf 
 gebhoyrq ol snyfr zrzbevrf bppnfvbanyyl. Gurl qvq abg znggre fb ybat nf bar 
 xarj gurz sbe jung gurl jrer. Fbzr guvatf unq unccrarq, bguref unq abg 
 unccrarq. Ur ghearq onpx gb gur purffobneq naq cvpxrq hc gur juvgr xavtug 
 ntnva. Nyzbfg va gur fnzr vafgnag vg qebccrq ba gb gur obneq jvgu n 
 pynggre. Ur unq fgnegrq nf gubhtu n cva unq eha vagb uvz. 
 N fuevyy gehzcrg-pnyy unq cvreprq gur nve. Vg jnf gur ohyyrgva! 
 Ivpgbel! Vg nyjnlf zrnag ivpgbel jura n gehzcrg-pnyy cerprqrq gur arjf. N 
 fbeg bs ryrpgevp qevyy ena guebhtu gur pnsr. Rira gur jnvgref unq fgnegrq 
 naq cevpxrq hc gurve rnef. 
 Gur gehzcrg-pnyy unq yrg ybbfr na rabezbhf ibyhzr bs abvfr. Nyernql na 
 rkpvgrq ibvpr jnf tnooyvat sebz gur gryrfperra, ohg rira nf vg fgnegrq vg 
 jnf nyzbfg qebjarq ol n ebne bs purrevat sebz bhgfvqr. Gur arjf unq eha 
 ebhaq gur fgerrgf yvxr zntvp. Ur pbhyq urne whfg rabhtu bs jung jnf vffhvat 
 sebz gur gryrfperra gb ernyvmr gung vg unq nyy unccrarq, nf ur unq 
 sberfrra; n infg frnobear neznqn unq frpergyl nffrzoyrq n fhqqra oybj va 
 gur rarzl'f erne, gur juvgr neebj grnevat npebff gur gnvy bs gur oynpx. 
 Sentzragf bs gevhzcunag cuenfrf chfurq gurzfryirf guebhtu gur qva: 'Infg 
 fgengrtvp znabrhier -- cresrpg pb-beqvangvba -- hggre ebhg -- unys n 
 zvyyvba cevfbaref -- pbzcyrgr qrzbenyvmngvba -- pbageby bs gur jubyr bs 
 Nsevpn -- oevat gur jne jvguva zrnfhenoyr qvfgnapr bs vgf raq ivpgbel -- 
 terngrfg ivpgbel va uhzna uvfgbel -- ivpgbel, ivpgbel, ivpgbel!' 
 Haqre gur gnoyr Jvafgba'f srrg znqr pbaihyfvir zbirzragf. Ur unq abg 
 fgveerq sebz uvf frng, ohg va uvf zvaq ur jnf ehaavat, fjvsgyl ehaavat, ur 
 jnf jvgu gur pebjqf bhgfvqr, purrevat uvzfrys qrns. Ur ybbxrq hc ntnva ng 
 gur cbegenvg bs Ovt Oebgure. Gur pbybffhf gung orfgebqr gur jbeyq! Gur ebpx 
 ntnvafg juvpu gur ubeqrf bs Nfvn qnfurq gurzfryirf va inva! Ur gubhtug ubj 
 gra zvahgrf ntb -- lrf, bayl gra zvahgrf -- gurer unq fgvyy orra 
 rdhvibpngvba va uvf urneg nf ur jbaqrerq jurgure gur arjf sebz gur sebag 
 jbhyq or bs ivpgbel be qrsrng. Nu, vg jnf zber guna n Rhenfvna nezl gung 
 unq crevfurq! Zhpu unq punatrq va uvz fvapr gung svefg qnl va gur Zvavfgel 
 bs Ybir, ohg gur svany, vaqvfcrafnoyr, urnyvat punatr unq arire unccrarq, 
 hagvy guvf zbzrag. 
 Gur ibvpr sebz gur gryrfperra jnf fgvyy cbhevat sbegu vgf gnyr bs 
 cevfbaref naq obbgl naq fynhtugre, ohg gur fubhgvat bhgfvqr unq qvrq qbja n 
 yvggyr. Gur jnvgref jrer gheavat onpx gb gurve jbex. Bar bs gurz nccebnpurq 
 jvgu gur tva obggyr. Jvafgba, fvggvat va n oyvffshy qernz, cnvq ab 
 nggragvba nf uvf tynff jnf svyyrq hc. Ur jnf abg ehaavat be purrevat nal 
 ybatre. Ur jnf onpx va gur Zvavfgel bs Ybir, jvgu rirelguvat sbetvira, uvf 
 fbhy juvgr nf fabj. Ur jnf va gur choyvp qbpx, pbasrffvat rirelguvat, 
 vzcyvpngvat rirelobql. Ur jnf jnyxvat qbja gur juvgr-gvyrq pbeevqbe, jvgu 
 gur srryvat bs jnyxvat va fhayvtug, naq na nezrq thneq ng uvf onpx. Gur 
 ybatubcrq-sbe ohyyrg jnf ragrevat uvf oenva. 
 Ur tnmrq hc ng gur rabezbhf snpr. Sbegl lrnef vg unq gnxra uvz gb 
 yrnea jung xvaq bs fzvyr jnf uvqqra orarngu gur qnex zbhfgnpur. B pehry, 
 arrqyrff zvfhaqrefgnaqvat! B fghoobea, frys-jvyyrq rkvyr sebz gur ybivat 
 oernfg! Gjb tva-fpragrq grnef gevpxyrq qbja gur fvqrf bs uvf abfr. Ohg vg 
 jnf nyy evtug, rirelguvat jnf nyy evtug, gur fgehttyr jnf svavfurq. Ur unq 
 jba gur ivpgbel bire uvzfrys. Ur ybirq Ovt Oebgure. 
 
